śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ || ||
śrīgaurīśaṃkarābhyāṃ namaḥ || ||
atha dvitīyā rudrasaṃhitā prārabhyate || ||
viśvodbhavasthitilayādiṣu hetumekaṃ gaurīpati viditatattvamanantakīrtim ||
māyāśrayamvigatamāyamacityarūpambodhasvarūpamamalaṃ hi śivannamāmi || 1 ||
vande śivantamprakṛteranādimpraśāntame kampuruṣottamaṃ hi ||
svamāyayā kṛtsnamidaṃ hi sṛṣṭvā nabhovadantarbahirāsthito yaḥ || 2 ||
vandetarasthaṃ nijagūḍharūpaṃ śivaṃ svatastraṣṭumidamvicaṣṭe ||
jaganti nityamparitoṃ amaṃti yatsannidhau cumbakalohavattam || 3 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
jagataḥ pitaraṃ śambhuñjagato mātaraṃ śivām |
tatputrañca gaṇādhīśannatvaitadvarṇayāmahe || 4 ||
ekadā munayassarve naimiṣāraṇyavāsinaḥ ||
papracchurvarayā bhaktyā sūtante śaunakādayaḥ || 5 || ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
vidyeśvarasaṃhitāyāḥ śrutā sā satkathā śubhā ||
sādhyasādhanakhaṃḍākhyā ramyādyā bhaktavatsalā || 6 ||
sūta sūta mahābhāga cirañjīva sukhī bhava ||
yacchāvayāsa nastāta śāṃkaroṃ paramāṃ kathām || 7 ||
pibantastvanmukhāmbhojacyutaṃ jñānāmṛtamvayam |
avitṛptāḥ punaḥ kiṃcitpraṣṭumicchāmahe'nagha || || 8 ||
vyāsaprasādātsarvajño prāpto'si kṛtakṛtyatām ||
nājñātavidyate kiṃcidbhūtaṃ bhavyaṃ bhavacca yat || 9 ||
gurorvyāsasya sadbhaktyā samāsādya kṛpāṃ parām ||
sarvaṃ jñātaviśeṣeṇa sarvaṃ sārthaṃ kṛtaṃ januḥ || 10 ||
idānīṃ kathaya prājña śivarūpamanuttamam ||
divyāni vai caritrāṇi śivayorapya śeṣataḥ || 11 ||
aguṇo guṇatāṃ yāti kathaṃ loke maheśvaraḥ ||
śivatattvaṃ vayaṃ sarve na jānīmo vicārataḥ || 12 ||
sṛṣṭeḥ pūrvaṃ kathaṃ śaṃbhussvarūpeṇāva tiṣṭhate ||
sṛṣṭimadhye sa hi kathaṃ krīḍansaṃvarttate prabhuḥ || 13 ||
tadante ca kathandevassa tiṣṭhati maheśvaraḥ ||
kathamprasannatāṃ yāti śaṃkaro lokaśaṃkaraḥ || 14 ||
sa prasanno maheśānaḥ kiṃ prayacchati satphalam ||
svabhaktebhyaḥ parebhyaśca tatsarvaṃ kathayasva naḥ || 15 ||
sadyaḥ prasanno bhagavānbhavatītyanuśuśru ma ||
bhaktaprayāsaṃ sa mahānna paśyati dayāparaḥ || 16 ||
brahmā viṣṇurmaheśaśca trayo devāśśivāṃgajāḥ ||
maheśastatra pūrṇāśassvayameva śivo'paraḥ || 17 ||
tasyāvirbhāvamākhyāhi caritāni viśeṣataḥ ||
umāvirbhāvamākhyāhi tadvivāha tathā prabho || 18 ||
tadgārhasthyaṃ viśeṣeṇa tathā līlāḥ parā api ||
etatsarvaṃ tadanyacca kathanīyaṃ tvayā'nagha || 19 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
iti pṛṣṭastadā taistu sato harṣasamanvitaḥ ||
smṛtvā śaṃbhupadābhojampratyu vāca munīśvarān || 20 ||
sūta uvāca ||
samyak pṛṣṭaṃ bhavadbhiśva dhanyā yūyaṃ munīśvarāḥ ||
sadāśivakathāyāṃ vo yajjātā naiṣṭhikī matiḥ || 21 ||
sadāśivakathāpraśnaḥ puruṣāṃstrīnpunāti hi ||
vaktāraṃ pṛcchakaṃ śrotṛāhnavīsalilaṃ yathā || 22 ||
śaṃbhorguṇānuvādātko virajyeta pumāndvijāḥ ||
vinā paśunaṃ trividhajanānandakarātsadā || 23 ||
gīyamāno vitṛṣṇaiśca bhavarogauṣadho'pi hi ||
manaḥśrotrābhirāmaśca yatassarvārthadassa vai || 24 ||
