śi0pu0 || 31||
kathayāmi yathābuddhi bhavatpraśnānusārataḥ ||
śivalīlāṃ prayatnena dvijāstāṃ śṛṇutādarāt || 25 ||
bhavadbhiḥ pṛcchayate yadvattattathā nāradena vai ||
pṛṣṭaṃ pitre preritena hariṇā śivarūpiṇā || 26 ||
brahmā śrutvā sutavacaśśivabhaktaḥ prasannadhīḥ ||
jagau śivayaśaḥ prītyā harṣayanmunisattamam || 27 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
sūtoktamiti tadvākyamākarṇya dvijasattamāḥ ||
papracchustatsusaṃvādaṃ kutūhalasamanvitāḥ || 28 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
sūta sūta mahābhāga śaivottama mahāmate ||
śrutvā tava vaco ramyaṃ ceto nassakutūhalam || 29 ||
kaṃdā babhruva sukhakṛdvidhināradayormahān ||
saṃvādo yatra giriśasulīlā bhavamocinī || || 30 ||
vidhināradasaṃvādapūrvakaṃ śāṃkaraṃ yaśaḥ ||
brūhi nastāta tatprītyā tattatpraśnānusārataḥ ||31||
ityākarṇya vacasteṣāṃ munīnāṃ bhāvitātmanām ||
sūtaḥ provāca suprītastatsaṃvādānusārataḥ || 32 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṃḍe sṛṣṭayupākhyāne munipraśnavarṇano nāma prathamo'dhyāyaḥ || 1 || ||
sūta uvāca || ||
ekasminsamaye viprā nārado munisattamaḥ ||
brahmaputro vinītātmā taporthaṃ mana ādadhe || 1 ||
himaśailaguhā kācidekā paramaśobhanā ||
yatsamīpe suranadī sadā vahati vegataḥ || 2 ||
tatrāśramo mahādivyo nānāśobhāsamanvitaḥ ||
taporthaṃ sa yayau tatra nārado divyadarśanaḥ || 3 ||
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā muniśārdūlastepe sa suciraṃ tapaḥ ||
badhvāsanaṃ dṛḍhaṃ maunī prāṇānāyamya śuddhadhīḥ || 4 ||
cakre suni ssamādhiṃ tamahambrahmeti yatra ha ||
vijñānaṃ bhavati brahmasākṣātkārakaraṃ dvijāḥ || 5 ||
itthaṃ tapati tasminvai nārade munisattame ||
cakaṃpe'tha śunāsīro manassaṃtāpavihvalaḥ || 6 ||
manasīti vicityāsau munimeṃ rājyamicchati ||
tadvighnakaraṇārthaṃ hi hariryatnamiyeṣa saḥ || 7 ||
sasmāra sa smaraṃ śakraśce tasā devanāyakaḥ ||
ājagāma drutaṃ kāmassamadhīmahiṣīsutaḥ || 8 ||
athāgataṃ smaraṃ dṛṣṭvā saṃbodhya surarāṭ prabhuḥ ||
uvāca taṃ prapaśyāśu svārthe kuṭi laśemuṣiḥ || 9 || ||
indra uvāca || ||
mitravaryyaṃ mahāvīra sarvadā hitakāraka ||
śṛṇu prītyā vaco me tvaṃ kuru sāhāyyamātmanā || 10 ||
tvadva lānme bahūnāñca tapogava vināśitaḥ ||
madrājya sthiratā mitra tvadanugrahatassadā || 13 ||
himaśailaguhāyāṃ hi munistapati nāradaḥ ||
manasoddiśya viśveśaṃ mahāsaṃyamavān dṛḍhaḥ || 12 ||
yācenna vidhito rājyaṃ sa mameti viśaṃkitaḥ ||
adyaiva gaccha tatra tvaṃ tattapovighnamācara || 13 ||
ityājñapto mahendreṇa sa kāmas samadhupriyaḥ || ||
jagāma tatsthalaṃ garvādupāyaṃ svañcakāra ha || 14 ||
racayāmāsa tatrāśu svakalāssakalā api ||
vasaṃtopi svaprabhāvaṃ cakāra vividhaṃ madāt || 15 ||
na babhruva muneśveto vikṛtaṃ munisattamāḥ ||
bhraṣṭo babhūva tadbhava maheśānugraheṇa ha || 16 ||
śṛṇutādarata statra kāraṇaṃ śaunakādayaḥ ||
īśvarānugraheṇātra na prabhāvaḥ smarasya hi || 17 ||
atraiva śambhunā'kāri sutapaśca smarāriṇā ||
atraiva dagdhastenāśu

--- Page 6 [gcv] ---
oṃ kāmo sunitapopahaḥ || 18 ||
kāmajīvanahetohi ratyā saṃprārthitairasuraiḥ ||
samprārthita uvācedaṃ śaṃkaro lokaśaṃkaraḥ || 19 ||
kaṃcitsamayamāsādya jīviṣyati surāḥ smaraḥ ||
paraṃtviha smaropāyaścaliṣyati na kaścana || 20 ||
iha yāvaddṛśyate bhūrjanaiḥ sthitvā'marāssadā ||
kāmavāṇaprabhāvotra na caliṣyatyasaṃśayam || 21 ||
iti śaṃbhūktitaḥ kāmo mithyātmagatikastadā ||
nārade sa jagāmāśu divamindrasamīpataḥ || 22 ||
ācakhyau sarvavṛ ttāṃtaṃ prabhāvaṃ ca muneḥ smaraḥ ||
tadājñayā yayau sthānaṃ svakīyaṃ sa madhupriyaḥ || 23 ||
vismitobhūtsurādhīśaḥ praśaśaṃsātha nāradam ||
tadvṛttāṃtānabhijño hi mohitaśśivamāyayā || 24 ||
durjñeyā śāṃbhavī māyā sarveṣāṃ prāṇināmiha ||
bhaktaṃ vinārpitātmānaṃ tayā saṃmodyate jagat || 25 ||
nārado'pi ciraṃ tasthau tatreśānugraheṇa ha ||
pūrṇe matvā tapastatsvaṃ virarāma tato muniḥ || 26 ||
kāmājjayaṃ nijaṃ matvā garvito'bhūnmunīśvaraḥ ||
vṛthaiva vigatajñāna śśivamāyāvimohitaḥ || 27 ||
dhanyā dhanyā mahāmāyā śāṃbhavī munisattamāḥ ||
tadgatiṃ na hi paśyaṃti viṣṇubrahmādayopi hi || 28 ||
tayā saṃmo hitotīva nārado munisattamaḥ ||
kailāsaṃ prayayau śīghraṃ svavṛttaṃ gadituṃ madī || 29 ||
rudrannatvābravītsarvaṃ svavṛttaṅgarvavānmuniḥ ||
mattvātmānaṃ mahātmānaṃ svaprabhuñca smarañjayam || 30 ||
tacchrutvā śaṃkaraḥ prāha nāradaṃ bhaktavatsalaḥ ||
svamāyāmohitaṃ hetvanabhijñaṃ bhraṣṭacetasam || 31 || ||
rudra uvāca || ||
he tāta nārada prājña dhanyastvaṃ śṛṇu madvacaḥ ||
vācyamevaṃ na kutrāpi hareraye viśeṣataḥ || 32 ||
pṛcchamāno'pi na brūyāḥ svavṛttaṃ me yaduktavān ||
gopyaṃ gopyaṃ sarvathāhi naiva vācyaṃ kadācana || 33 ||
śāsmyahaṃ tvāṃ viśeṣeṇa mama priyatamo bhavān ||
viṣṇubhakto yatastvaṃ hi tadbhaktotīva me'nugaḥ || || 34 ||
śāsti smetthañca bahuśo rudrassūtikaraḥ prabhuḥ ||
nārado naḥ hitaṃ mene śivamāyāvimohitaḥ || 35 ||
prabalā bhāvinī karmagatijñeyā vica kṣaṇaiḥ ||
na nivāryā janaiḥ kaiśvidapīcchā saiva śāṃkarī || 36 ||
tatassa munivayoṃ hi brahmalokaṃ jagāmaha ||
vidhiṃ natvā'bravītkāmajayaṃ svasya tapo balāt || 37 ||
tadākarṇya vidhissotha smṛtvā śambhupadāmbujam ||
jñātvā savai kāraṇaṃ tanniṣiṣedha sutaṃ tadā || 38 ||
maine hitanna vidhyuktaṃ nārado jñānisattamaḥ ||
śivamāyāmohitaśca rūḍhacittamadāṃkuraḥ || 39 ||
śivecchā yādṛśī loke bhavatyeva hi sā tadā ||
tadadhīnaṃ jagatsarvaṃ vacastaṃtyāṃ sthitaṃ yataḥ || 40 ||
nārado'tha yayaiau śīghraṃ viṣṇulokaṃ vinaṣṭadhīḥ ||
madāṃkuramanā. vṛttaṃ madituṃ svaṃ tadagrataḥ || 41 ||
āgacchaṃtaṃ munindṛṣṭvā nāraṃda viṣṇurādarāt ||
utthitvādye gatā'raṃ taṃ śiśleṣa jñātahetukaḥ || 42 ||
svāsane samupāveśya smṛtvā śivapadāmbujam ||
hariḥ prāha vacastathrthyaṃ nāradaṃ 1 laghukṣipramarandbhutamityamaraḥ |
