kṛtāṃjaliḥ ||
duhiteyaṃ mama mune śrīmatī nāma nāmataḥ || 13 ||
pradānasamayaṃ prāptā varamanveṣatī śubham ||
sā svayaṃmvarasaṃprāptā sarvalakṣaṇalakṣitā || || 14 ||
asyā bhāgyaṃ vada sune savai jātakamādrāta ||
kīdṛśaṃ tanayeyaṃ me varamāpsyati tadvad || 15 ||
ityukto muniśārdūlastāmicchuḥ kāmaviha laḥ ||
samābhāṣya sa rājānaṃ nārado vākyamabravīt || 16 ||
suteyaṃ tava bhūpāla sarvalakṣaṇalakṣitā ||
mahābhāgyavatī dhanyā lakṣmīriva guṇālayā || || 17 ||
sarveśvaro'jito vīro girīśasadṛśo vibhuḥ ||
asyāḥ patirdhruvaṃ bhāvī kāmajitsurasattamaḥ || 18 ||
ityuktvā nṛpamāmaṃtrya yayau yādṛcchi ko muniḥ ||
babhūva kāmavivaśaśśivamāyāvimohitaḥ || 19 ||
citte vicintya sa munirāpnuyāṃ kathamenakām ||
svayamvare nṛpālānāmekaṃ māṃ vṛṇuyātkatha m || 20 ||
saundarya sarvanārīṇāṃ priyaṃ bhavati sarvathā ||
taddṛṣṭcaiva prasannā sā svavaśā nātra saṃśayaḥ || 21 ||
vidhāyetthaṃ viṣṇurūpaṃ grahītuṃ muni sattamaḥ ||
viṣṇulokaṃ jagāmāśu nāradaḥ smaravihvalaḥ || 22 ||
praṇipatya hṛṣīkeśaṃ vākyametaduvāca ha ||
rahasi tvāṃ pravakṣyāmi svavṛttāṃtamaśeṣataḥ || || 23 ||
tathetyukte tathā bhūte śivecchākāryakartari ||
brūhītyuktavati śrīśe munirāha ca keśavam || 24 || ||
nārad uvāca ||
tvadīyo bhūpatiḥ śīlanidhissa vṛṣatatparaḥ ||
tasya kanyā viśālākṣī śrīmatī varavarṇinī || 25 ||
jaganmohinyabhikhyātā trailokyepyatisundarī ||
pariṇetu mahaṃ viṣṇo tāmicchāmyadya mā ciram || 26 ||
svayaṃvaraṃ cakārāsau bhūpatistanayecchayā ||
caturdigbhyassamāyātā rājaputrāssahasraśaḥ || 27 ||
yadi dāsyasi rūpa me tadā tāṃ prāpnuyāṃ dhruvam ||
tvadrūpaṃ sā vinā kaṃṭhe jayamālāṃ na dhāsyati || 28 ||
svarūpaṃ dehi me nātha sevako'haṃ priyastava ||
vṛṇuyānmāṃ yathā sā vai śrīmatī kṣitipātmajā || 29 || ||
sūta uvāca ||
vacaḥ śrutvā muneritthaṃ vihasya madhusudanaḥ ||
śāṃkarīṃ prabhutāṃ budhvā pratyu vāca dayāparaḥ || 30 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
sveṣṭadeśaṃ mune gaccha kariṣyāmi hitaṃ tava ||
bhiṣagvaro yathārttasya yataḥ priyataro'si me || 31 ||
ityuktvā munaye tasmai dadau viṣṇurmukhaṃ hareḥ ||
svarūpamanugṛhyāsya tirodhānaṃ jagāma saḥ || 32 ||
evamukto munirdṛṣṭaḥ svarūpaṃ prāpya vai hareḥ ||
mena kṛtārthamātmānaṃ tadyatnaṃ na bubodha saḥ || 33 ||
atha tatra gataḥ śīghrannārado munisattamaḥ ||
cakre svayamvaraṃ yatra rājaputraissamākulam || 34 ||
svaya mvarasabhā divyā rājaputrasamāvṛtā ||
śuśubhe'tīva viprendrā yathā śakrasabhāparā || 35 ||
tasyāṃ nṛpasabhāyāṃ vai nāradaḥ samupāviśat ||
sthitvā tatra vicitnyeti prītiyuktena cetasā || 36 ||
māṃ variṣyati nānyaṃ sā viṣṇurūpadharandhruvam ||
ānanasya kurūpatvaṃ na veda munisattamaḥ || 37 ||
pūrva rūpaṃ muniṃ sarve dadṛśustatra mānavāḥ ||
tadbhedaṃ bubudhuste na rājaputrādayo dvijāḥ || 38 ||
tatra rudragaṇau dvau tadrakṣaṇārthe samāgatau ||
viprarūpadharau gūḍhau

