tadvedaṃ jagmatuḥ param || 39 ||
mūḍhaṃ matvā muniṃ tau tannikaṭaṃ jagmaturgaṇau |
kurutastattrahāsaṃ vai bhāṣamāṇau parasparam || 40 ||
paśya nārada rūpaṃ hi viṣṇoriva mahottamam |
mukhaṃ tu vānarasyeva vikaṭaṃ ca bhayaṅkaram || 41 ||
icchatyayaṃ nṛpasutāṃ vṛthaiva smaramohitaḥ |
ityuktvā sacchalaṃ vākyasupahāsaṃ pracakratuḥ || 42 ||
na śuśrāva yathārthaṃ tu tadvākyaṃ smaravihvalaḥ |
paryaikṣacchrīmatīṃ tāṃ vai tallipsurmohito muniḥ || 43 ||
etasminnantare bhūpakanyā cāntaḥpurāttu sā |
strībhissamāvṛtā tatrājagāma varavarṇinī || 44 ||
mālāṃ hiraṇmayīṃ ramyāmādāya śubhalakṣaṇā |
tatra svayaṃvare reje sthitā madhye rameva sā || 45 ||
babhrāma sā sabhāṃ sarvāṃ mālāmādāya suvratā |
varamanveṣatī tatra svātmābhīṣṭaṃ nṛpātmajā || 46 ||
vānarāsyaṃ viṣṇutanuṃ munindradvayā cukopa sā |
dṛṣṭiṃ nivārya ca tataḥ prasthitā prītamānasā || 47 ||
na dṛṣṭvā svavaraṃ tatra trastāsīnmanasepsitam |
antassabhāsthitā kasminnarpayāmāsa na srajam || 48 ||
etasminnantare viṣṇurājagāma nṛpākṛtiḥ |
na dṛṣṭaḥ kaiścidvaiparaiḥ kevalaṃ sā dadarśa hi || 49 ||
atha sā taṃ samālokya prasannavadanāmbujā |
arpayāmāsa tatkaṇṭhe tāṃ mālāṃ varavarṇinī || 50 ||
tāmādāya tato viṣṇū rājarūpadharaḥ prabhuḥ |
antardhānamagātsadyassvasthānaṃ prayayau kila || 51 ||
sarve rājakumārāśca nirāśāḥ śrīmatīṃ prati |
munistu vihvalo'tīva babhūva madanāturaḥ || 52 ||
tadā tāvūcatussadyo nāradaṃ smaravihvalam |
viprarūpadharau rudragaṇau jñānaviśāradau || 53 ||
gaṇāvūcatuḥ |
he nārada mune tvaṃ hi vṛthā madanamohitaḥ |
tallipsussvamukhaṃ paśya vānarasyeva garhitam || 54 ||
sūta uvāca |
ityākarṇya tayorvākyaṃ nārado vismito'bhavat |
mukhaṃ dadarśa mukure śivamāyāvimohitaḥ || 55 ||
svamukhaṃ vānarasyeva dṛṣṭvā cukrodha satvaram |
śāpaṃ dadau tayostatra gaṇayormohito muniḥ || 56 ||
yuvāṃ mamopahāsaṃ vai cakraturbrāhmaṇasya hi |
bhavetāṃ rākṣasau vipravīryejau vai tadā kṛtī || 57 ||
śrutvā haragaṇāvitthaṃ svaśāpaṃ jñānisattamau |
na kiñciducyatustau hi munimājñāya mohitam || 58 ||
svasthānaṃ jagmuturvipra udāsīnau śivastutiḥ |
cakraturmanyamānau vai śivecchāṃ sakalāṃ sadā || 59 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṇḍe sṛṣṭyupākhyāne nāradamohavarṇano nāma tṛtīyo'dhyāyaḥ || 3 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ |
sūta sūta mahāprājña varṇitādbhutā kathā |
dhanyā tu śāmbhavī māyā tadadhīnaṃ carācaram || 1 ||
gatayogeśayośśambhossvayamātmecchayā vibhoḥ |
kiṃ cakāra muniḥ kruddho nāradaḥ smaravihvalaḥ || 2 ||
sūta uvāca |
vimohito munindretvā tayośśāpaṃ yathocitam |
jale mukhaṃ nirīkṣyātha svarūpaṃ giriśecchayā || 3 ||
śivecchayā na prabuddhaḥ smṛtvā harikṛtacchalam |
krodhaṃ durviṣahaṃ kṛtvā viṣṇulokaṃ jagāma ha || 4 ||
