adyāpi nirbhayastvaṃ hi saṃgaṃ nāpastarasvinā ||
idānīṃ lapsyase viṣṇo phalaṃ svakṛtakarmaṇaḥ || 13 ||
ittha muktvā hariṃ sotha mubhirmāyāvimohitaḥ ||
śaśāpa krodhanirviṇṇo brahmatejaḥ pradarśayan || 14 ||
