tadrūpeṇa manuṣyastvaṃ bhava tadduḥkhabhugghare ||
yanmukhaṃ kṛtavānmetvaṃ te bhavaṃtu sahāyinaḥ || 16 ||
tvaṃ strīviyogajaṃ duḥkhaṃ labhasva paraduḥkhadaḥ ||
manuṣyagatikaḥ prāyo bhavājñānavimohitaḥ || 17||
iti śavā hariṃ mohānnārado'jñānamohitaḥ ||
viṣṇurjagrāha taṃ śāpaṃ praśaṃsanśāṃbhavīmajām || 18 ||
atha śaṃsurmahālīlo niśvakarṣa vimohinīm ||
svamāyāṃ mohito jñānī nāradopyabhavadyayā || 19 ||
aṃta hiṃtāyāṃ māyāyāṃ pūrvavanmatimānabhūt ||
nārado vismitamanāḥ prāptabodho nirākulaḥ || 20 ||
paścāttāpamavāpyāti nininda svaṃ muhurmuhuḥ ||
praśaśaṃsa tadā māyāṃ śāṃbhavīṃ jñānimohinīm || 21 ||
atha jñāttvā munissarve māyāvibhramamātmanaḥ ||
apatatpādayorviṣṇornārado vaiṣṇavottamaḥ || 22 ||
iryupasthāpitaḥ prāha vacanaṃ naṣṭadurmatiḥ ||
mayā duruktayaḥ proktā mohitena kubuddhinā || 23 ||
dattaśśāpo'pi te nātha vitathaṃ kuru taṃ prabho ||
mahatpāpamakārṣa hi yāsyāmi nirayaṃ dhruvam || 24 ||
kamupāyaṃ hare kuryāṃ dā'sohaṃ te tamādiśa ||
yena pāpakulaṃ naśyennirayo na bhavenmama || 25 ||
ityuktvā sa punarviṣṇoḥ pādayormunisattamaḥ ||
papāta sumatirbhaktyā paścāttāpamupāgataḥ || 26 ||
atha viṣṇustamutthāpya babhāṣe sūnṛta vacaḥ ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
na khedaṃ kuru me bhakta varastvaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 27 ||
śṛṇu tāta pravakṣyāmi suhitaṃ tava niśvayāt ||
