atastvāṃ śaraṇaṃ prāptaḥ kṛpāṃ kuru mamopari || 34||
iti śrutvā vacastasya nāradasyāṃgajasya hi ||
uvāca vacanaṃ tatra brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ || 35 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṃḍe sṛṣṭayupākhyāne nāradapraśnavarṇano nāma pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ || 5 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
bho brahmansādhu pṛṣṭo'haṃ tvayā vibudhasattama ||
lokopakāriṇā nityaṃ lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā || 1 ||
yacchrutvā sarvalokānāṃ sarvapāpakṣayo bhavet ||
tadahaṃ te pravakṣyāmi śivatatvamanāmayam || 2 ||
śivatattvaṃ mayā naiva viṣṇunāpi yathārthataḥ ||
jñātañca paramaṃ rūpamadbhutaṃ ca pareṇa na || 3 ||
mahāpralayakāle ca naṣṭe sthāvarajaṃgame ||
āsīttamomayaṃ sarvamanarkagrahatā rakam || 4 ||
acandramanahorātramananyanilabhūjalam ||
apradhānaṃ viyacchūnyamanyatejovivarjitam || 5 ||
adṛṣṭatvādi rahitaṃ śabdasparśasamu jhitam ||
avyaktagaṃdharūpaṃ ca rasatyaktamadiṅmukham || 6 ||
itthaṃ satyaṃdhatamase sūcībhedye niraṃtare ||
tatsadbrahmeti yacchutvā sadekaṃ pratipadyate || 7 ||
itīdṛśaṃ yadā nāsīdyattatsadasadātmakam ||
yoginoṃtarhitākāśe yatpaśyati niraṃtaram || 8 ||
amanogocaramvācāṃ viṣayanna kadācana ||
anāmarūpa varṇe ca na ca sthūlaṃ na yatkṛśam || 9 ||
ahrasvadīrghamalaghu gurutvaparivarjitam |
na yatropacayaḥ kaścittathā nāpacayo'pi ca || 10 ||
abhidhatte sa cakitaṃ yadastīti śrutiḥ punaḥ ||
satyaṃ jñānamanaṃtaṃ ca parānaṃdamparammahaḥ || 11 ||
aprameyamanādhāramavikāramanākṛti ||
nirguṇaṃ yogigamyañca sarvavyāpyekakārakam || 12 ||
nirvikalpaṃ nirāraṃbhaṃ nirmāyaṃ nirupadravam ||
advitīyamanādyantamavikāśaṃ cidātmakam || 13 ||
yasyetthaṃ saṃvi kalpate saṃjñāsaṃjñoktitaḥ sma vai ||
kiyatā caiva kālena dvitīyecchā'bhavatkila || 14 ||
amūrtena svamūrtiśca tenākalpi svalīlayā ||
sarvaiśvarya guṇopetā sarvajñānamayī śubhā || 15 ||
sarvagā sarvarūpā ca sarvadṛksarvakāriṇī ||
sarvaikavaṃdyā sarvādyā sarvadā sarvasaṃskṛtiḥ || 16 ||
parikalpye ti tāṃ mūrtimaiśvarīṃ śuddharūpiṇīm ||
advitīyamanādyaṃtaṃ sarvābhāsaṃ cidātmakam ||
aṃtardadhe parākhyaṃ yadvā sarvagamavyayam || 17 ||
amūrte yatparā khyaṃ vai tasya mūrtissadāśivaḥ ||
arvācīnāḥ parācīnā īśvaraṃ taṃ jagurbudhāḥ || 18 ||
śaktistadaikalenāpi svairaṃ viharatā tanuḥ ||
svavigrahātsvayaṃ sṛṣṭā svaśarīrānapāyinī || 19 ||
pradhānaṃ prakṛti tāṃ ca māyāṃ guṇavatīṃ parām ||
buddhitattvasya jananīmāhurvikṛtivarjitām || 20 ||
sā śaktira mbikā proktā prakṛtissakaleśvarī ||
tridevajananī nityā mūlakāraṇamityuta || 21 ||
asyā aṣṭau bhujāśvāsanvicitravadanā śubhā ||
ekā candrasahasrasya vadane bhāśva nityaśaḥ || 22 ||
nānābharaṇasaṃyuktā nānāgatisamanvitā ||
nānāyudhadharā devī phulapaṃkajalocanā || 23 ||
aciṃtyate

