asyānandavanaṃ nāma purākāri pinākinā |
kṣetrasyānandahetutvād visṛṣṭamanantaram || 31 ||
athānandavane tasmiñchivayo ramamāṇayoḥ |
icchetyabhūtsuraiśca hi sṛjyaḥ ko'pyaparaḥ kila || 32 ||
yasminnasya mahābhāramārvāṃ svasvairacāriṇau |
nirvāṇadhāraṇaṃ kurvaḥ kevalaṃ kāśiśāyinau || 33 ||
sa eva sarvaṃ kurutāṃ sa eva paripātu ca |
sa eva saṃvṛṇotvante madanugraha tassadā || 34 ||
cetassamudramākuñcya cintākallolalolitam |
satvarajjaṃ tamoṣṭhāṃ rajovidumavāñchitam || 35 ||
yasya prasādāttiṣṭhāvassukhamānandakānane |
parikṣiptamanovṛttau bahirniśvātare sukham || 36 ||
