lasatpracaṇḍadordaṇḍayugalo hyaparājitaḥ || 40 ||
tatassa puruṣaśśambhuṃ praṇamya parameśvaram |
nāmāni kuru me svāminvada karme jagāviti || 41 ||
tacchrutvā vacanaṃ prāha śaṃkaraḥ prahasanprabhuḥ |
puruṣaṃ taṃ maheśāno vācā meghagabhīrayā || 42 ||
śiva uvāca |
viṣṇurvyāpakatvāttvaṃ nāma khyātaṃ bhaviṣyati |
bahūnyanyāni nāmāni bhaktasaukhyakarāṇi ha || 43 ||
