kiṃ yattattvamaho iti || 50 ||
pariśramavatastasya viṣṇoḥ svāṅgebhya eva ca ||
jaladhārā hi saṃyātā vividhāśśivamāyayā || 61 ||
abhivyāptaṃ ca sakalaṃ śūnyaṃ yattanmahāmune ||
brahmarūpaṃ jalamabhūtsparśanātpāpanāśanam || 52 ||
tadā śrāṃtaśca puruṣo viṣṇustasmiñjale svayam ||
suṣvāpa parama prīto bahukālaṃ vimohitaḥ || 53 ||
nārāyaṇeti nāmāpi tasyāsīcchutisaṃmatam ||
nānyatkicittadā hyāsītprākṛtaṃ puruṣaṃ vinā || 54 ||
eta sminnantare kāle tattvānyāsanmahātmanaḥ ||
tatprakāraṃ śṛṇu prājña gadato me mahāmate || 55 ||
prakṛteśca mahānāsīnmahataśca guṇāstrayaḥ ||
ahaṃkāra stato jātastrividho guṇabhedataḥ || 56 ||
tanmātrāśca tato jātāḥ pañca bhūtāni vai tataḥ ||
tadaiva tānīndriyāṇi jñānakarmamayāni ca || 57 ||
tattvā nāmiti saṃkhyānamuktaṃ te ṛṣisattama ||
jaḍātmakañca tatsarvaṃ prakṛteḥ puruṣaṃ vinā ||58||
tattadaikīkṛtaṃ tattvaṃ caturviṃśatisaṃkhyakam ||
śivecchayā gṛhītvā sa śuṣvāpa brahmarūpake ||59||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudra saṃhitāyāṃ sṛṣṭivyākhyāne prathamakhaṃḍe viṣṇūtpattivarṇano nāma ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ ||6|| ||
brahmovāca ||
supte nārāyaṇe deve nābhau paṃkajamuttamam ||
āvirbabhūva sahasā bṛhadvai. śaṃkarecchayā || 1 ||
anaṃtayaṣṭikāyuktaṃ karṇikārasamaprabham ||
anaṃta yojanāyāmamanaṃ tocchrāyasaṃyutam || 2 ||
koṭisūryapratīkāśaṃ suṃdaraṃ tattvasaṃyutam ||
atyadbhutaṃ mahāramyaṃ darśanīyamanuttamam || 3 ||
kṛtvā yatnaṃ pūrvavatsa śaṃkaraḥ parameśvaraḥ ||
dakṣiṇāṃgānnijānmāṃ vai sāmbaśśaṃbhūrajījanat || 4 ||
sa māyāmohitaṃ kṛtvā māṃ maheśo drutaṃ sune ||
tannābhipaṃkajādā virbhāvayāmāsa līlayā || 5 ||
evampadmāttato jajñe putro'haṃ hemagarbhakaḥ ||
caturmukho raktavarṇastripuṃḍrāṃkitamastakaḥ || 6 ||
tanmāyāmohitaścāhaṃ nāvidaṃ kamalaṃ vinā |
svadehajanakaṃ tāta pitaraṃ jñānadurbalaḥ || 7 ||
kohaṃ vā kuta āyātaḥ kiṃ kāryaṃ tu madīyakam ||
kasya putro'hamutpannaḥ kenaiva nirmito'dhunā || 8 ||
iti saṃśayamāpannaṃ buddhima samapadyata ||
kimarthaṃ mohamāyāmi tajjñānaṃ sukaraṃ khalu || 9 ||
eta tkamalapuṣpasya putrārohasthalaṃ hyadhaḥ ||
matkartā ca sa vai tatra bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ || 10 ||
iti buddhiṃ samāsthāya kamalā davarohayam ||
nāle nāle gatastatra varṣāṇāṃ śatakaṃ mune || 11 ||
na labdhaṃ tu mayā tatra karmalasthānamuttamam ||
saṃśayaṃ ca punaḥ prāptaḥ kamale gantumutsukaḥ || 12 ||
ārurohātha kamalaṃ nālamārgeṇa vai mune ||
kumalaṃ kamalasyātha labdhavānna vimohitaḥ || 13 ||
nālamārgeṇa bhramato gataṃ varṣa śataṃ punaḥ ||
kṣaṇamātraṃ tadā tatra tatastiṣṭhanvimohitaḥ || 14 ||
tadā vāṇī samutpannā tapeti paramā śubhā ||
śivecchayā parā vyomno mohavidhvaṃsinī mune || 15 ||
tacchrutvā vyomavacanaṃ dvādaśābdaṃ prayatnataḥ ||
punastaptaṃ tapo ghoraṃ draṣṭuṃ svajanakaṃ tadā || 16 ||
tadā hi bhagavānviṣṇuścaturvāhussulo
