mayyevānugrahaṃ kartuṃ drutamāvibaṃbhūva ha || 17 ||
śaṃkhacakrāyudhakaro gadāpadmadharaḥ paraḥ ||
ghanaśyāmalasarvāgaḥ pītāmbaradharaḥ paraḥ || 18 ||
mukuṭādimahābhūṣaḥ prasannamukhapaṃkajaḥ ||
koṭikaṃdarpa saṃkāśassandṛṣṭo mohitena saḥ || 19 ||
taddṛṣṭvā sundaraṃ rūpaṃ vismayaṃ paramaṃ gataḥ ||
kālābhaṃ kāṃcanābhaṃ ca sarvātmānaṃ caturbhujam || 20 ||
tathābhūtamahaṃ dṛṣṭvā sadasanmayamātmanā ||
