brahmovāca || ||
kastvaṃ vadeti hastena samutthāpya sanātanam ||
tadā hastaprahāreṇa tīvreṇa sudṛḍhena tu || 23 ||
prabuddhayotthāya śayanātsamāsīnaḥ kṣaṇaṃ vaśī ||
dadarśa nidrāvi klinnanīrajāmalalocanaḥ || 24 ||
māmatra saṃsthitaṃ bhāsādhyāsito bhagavānhariḥ ||
āha cotthāya brahmāṇaṃ hasanmāṃ madhuraṃ sakṛt || 25 || ||
viṣṇu ruvāca || ||
svāgataṃ svāgataṃ vatsa pitāmaha mahādyute ||
nirbhayo bhava dāsye'haṃ sarvānkāmānna saṃśayaḥ || 26 ||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā smita pūrvaṃ sura rṣabhaḥ ||
rajasā baddhavairaśca tamavo caṃ janārdanam || || 27 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
bhāṣase vatsa vatseti sarvasaṃhārakāraṇam ||
māmihāti smitaṃ kṛtvā guruśśiṣyamivānagha || 28 ||
kartāraṃ jagatāṃ sākṣātprakṛteśca pravartakam ||
sanātanamajaṃ viṣṇuṃ viriṃci viṣṇusaṃbhavam || 29 ||
viśvātmānaṃ vidhātāraṃ dhātārampaṃkajekṣaṇam ||
kimarthaṃ bhāṣase mohādvaktumarhasi satvaram || 30 ||
vedo māṃ vakti niyamātsvayaṃbhuvamajaṃ vibhum ||
pitāmahaṃ svarājaṃ ca para meṣṭhinamuttamam ||31||
ityākarṇya harirvākyaṃ mama kruddho ramāpatiḥ ||
so'pi māmāha jāne tvāṃ kartāramiti lokataḥ || 32 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
katai dhatu bhavānaṃgādavatīrṇo mamāvyayāt ||
vismṛto'si jagannāthaṃ nārāyaṇamanāmayam || 33 ||
puruṣaṃ paramātmānaṃ puruhūtaṃ puruṣṭutam ||
viṣṇumacyutamī śānaṃ viśvasya prabhavodbhavam || 34 ||
nārāyaṇaṃ mahāvāhuṃ sarvavyāpakamīśvaram ||
mannābhipadmatastvaṃ hi prasūto nātra saṃśayaḥ || 35 ||
tavāparādho nā styatra tvayi māyākṛtaṃ mama ||
śṛṇu satyaṃ caturvaca sarvadeveśvaro hyaham || 36 ||
kartā hartā ca bhartā ca na mayāsti samo vibhuḥ ||
ahameva paraṃ brahma paraṃ tattvaṃ pitāmaha ||37||
ahameva paraṃ jyotiḥ paramātmā tvahaṃ vibhuḥ ||
adya dṛṣṭaṃ śrutaṃ sarvaṃ jagatyasmiñcarācaram ||38||
tattadviddhi caturvakra sarve manmaya mityatha ||
mayā sṛṣṭaṃ purāvyaktaṃ caturviṃśatitattvakam || 39 ||
nityaṃ teṣvaṇavo baddhāspṛṣṭakrodhabhayādayaḥ ||
prabhāvācca bhavānaṅgānyanekānīha līlayā || || 40 ||
sṛṣṭā buddhirmayā tasyāmahaṃkārastridhā tataḥ ||
tanmātraṃ paṃcakaṃ tasmānmano dehendriyāṇi ca || 41 ||
ākāśādīni bhūtāni bhautikāni ca līlayā ||
iti buddhā prajānātha śaraṇaṃ vraja me vidhe || 42 ||
ahaṃ tvāṃ sarvaduḥkhebhyo rakṣiṣyāmi na saṃśayaḥ || ||
brahmovāca || ||
iti śrutvā

--- Page 18 [gcv] ---
vacastasya brahmā krodhasamanvitaḥ ||
ko vā tvamiti saṃbhabruvaṃ māyāvimohitaḥ || 43 ||
kimarthaṃ bhāṣase bhūri bahvanarthakaraṃ vacaḥ ||
neśvarastvaṃ para brahma kaścitkartā bhavettava || 44 ||
māyayā mohitaścāhaṃ yuddhaṃ cakre sudāruṇam ||
hariṇā tenavai sārddhaṃ śaṃkarasya mahāprabhoḥ || 45 ||
evaṃ mama hareśvāsītsaṃgaro romaharṣaṇaḥ ||
pralayārṇavamadhye tu rajasā baddhavairayoḥ || 46 ||
etasminnaṃtare liṃgamabhavaccāvayoḥ puraḥ ||
vivādaśamanārthaṃ hi prabodhārthī tathāvayoḥ || 47 ||
jvālāmālāsahasrāḍhyaṃ kālānalaśatopamam ||
kṣayavṛddhivinirmuktamādimadhyāṃta varjitam || 48 ||
anaupamyamanirdeśyamavyaktaṃ viśvasaṃbhavam ||
tasya jvālāsahasreṇa mohito bhagavānhariḥ || 49 ||
mohitaṃ cāha māmatra kimarthaṃ sparddhase'dhunā ||
āgatastu tṛtīyo'tra tiṣṭhatāṃ yuddhamāvayoḥ || 50 ||
kuta evātra saṃbhūtaḥ parīkṣāvo'gnisaṃbhavam ||
adho gamiṣyāmyanalastaṃbhasyānupamasya ca || 51 ||
parīkṣārthaṃ prajānātha tasya vai vāyuvegataḥ ||
bhavānūrddha prayatnena gaṃtumarhasi satvaram || 52 ||
brahmovāca ||
evaṃ vyāhṛtya viśvātmā svarūpamakarottadā ||
vārāhamahamapyāśu haṃsatvaṃ prāptavānmune || 53 ||
tadā prabhṛti māmāhuīṃ haṃso virāḍiti ||
haṃsahaṃseti yo brūyātsa haṃso'tha bhaviṣyati ||54||
suśveto hyanalaprakhyo viśvataḥ padāsaṃyutaḥ ||
manonilajavo bhūtvā gatorddha corddhataḥ purā || 55 ||
nārāyaṇo'pi viśvātmā suśveto hyabhavattadā ||
daśayojanavistīrṇaṃ śatayojanamāyatam ||56||
meruparvatavarmāṇaṃ gauratī kṣṇodaṃṣṭriṇam ||
kālādityasamābhāsaṃ dīrghaghoṇaṃ mahāsvanam || 57||
hrasvapādaṃ vicitrāṃgaṃ jaitraṃ dṛḍhamanopamam ||
vārāhākāramāsthāya gatavāṃstadadho javāt || 58 ||
evamvarṣasahasraṃ ca caranviṣṇuradhogataḥ ||
tadā prabhṛti lokeṣu śvetavārāhasaṃjñakaḥ || 59 ||
kalpo babhūva devarṣe narāṇāṃ kālasaṃjñakaḥ ||
babhrāma bahudhā viṣṇuḥ prabhaviṣṇuradhogataḥ || 60 ||
nāpaśyadalpamapyasya mūlaṃ liṃgasya sūkaraḥ ||
tāvatkālaṃ gataścorddhamahamapyarisūdanaḥ || 61 ||
satvaraṃ sarvayatnena tasyāntaṃ jñātumicchayā ||
śrānto na dṛṣṭvā tasyāṃtamahaṃ kālādadhogataḥ || 62 ||
tathaiva bhagavānviṣṇuścāṃtaṃ kamalalocanaḥ ||
sarvadevanibhastṛrṇamutthitassa mahāvapuḥ || 63 ||
samāgato mayā sārddhaṃ praṇipatya bhavaṃ muhuḥ ||
māyayā mohitaśśaṃbhostasthau saṃvignamānasaḥ || 64 ||
pṛṣṭhataḥ pārśvataścaiva hyagrataḥ parameśvaram ||
praṇipatya mayā sārddhaṃ sasmāra kimidaṃ tviti || 65 ||
anirdeśyaṃ ca tadrūpamanāma karmavarjitam ||
aliṃgaṃ liṃgatāṃ prāptaṃ dhyānamārgepyagocaram ||66||
svasthaṃ cittaṃ tadā kṛtvā namaskāraparāyaṇau ||
babhūvaturubhāvāvāmahaṃ harirapi dhruvam ||67||
jānīvo na hi te rūpaṃ yo'si yo'si mahāprabho||
namo'stu te maheśāna rūpaṃ darśaya nau tvaran || 68 ||
evaṃ śaracchatānyāsannamaskāraṃ prakurvatoḥ ||
āvayormuniśārdūla madamāsthitayostadā || 69 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṃḍe viṣṇubrahmavivādavarṇano nāma saptamo'dhyāyaḥ || 7 || ||
