evaṃ tayormuniśreṣṭha darśanaṃ kāṃkṣamāṇayoḥ ||
vigarvayośca surayoḥ sadā nau sthitayormune || 1 ||
dayālurabhavacchaṃbhunānāṃ pratipālakaḥ ||
garviṇāṃ garvahartā ca sarveṣāṃ prabhuravyayaḥ || 2 ||
tadā samabhavattatra nādo vai śabdalakṣaṇaḥ ||
omomiti suraśreṣṭhātsuvyaktaḥ plutalakṣaṇaḥ || 3 ||
kimidaṃ tviti saṃcitya mayā tiṣṭhanmahāsvanaḥ ||
viṣṇussarvahurārādhyo nirvairastuṣṭacetasā || 4 ||
liṃgasya dakṣiṇe bhāge tathāpaśyatsanāta nam ||
ādyaṃ varṇamakārākhyamukāraṃcottare tataḥ || 5 ||
makāraṃ madhyataścaiva nādamaṃte'sya comiti ||
sūryamaṃḍalavaddṛṣṭvā varṇamādyaṃ tu dakṣiṇe || 6 ||
uttare pāvakaprakhya mukāramṛṣisattama ||
śītāṃśumaṇḍalaprakhyaṃ makāraṃ tasya madhyataḥ || 7 ||
tasyopari tadā'paśyacchuisphaṭikasuprabham ||
turīyātītama malaṃ niṣkalaṃ nirupadravam || 8 ||
niīṃīṃ kevalaṃ śūnyaṃ bāhyābhyaṃtaravarjitam ||
sa bāhyābhyaṃtare caiva bāhyābhyaṃtarasaṃsthitam || 9 ||
ādima dhyāṃtarahitamānaṃdasyāpi kāraṇam ||
satyamānandamamṛtaṃ paraṃ brahma parāyaṇam || 10 ||
kuta evātra saṃbhūtaḥ parīkṣāvo'gnisaṃbhavam ||
adho gamiṣyāmyanalastaṃbhasyānupamasya ca || 11 ||
vedaśabdobhayāveśaṃ viśvātmānaṃ vyaciṃtayat ||
tadā'bhavadṛṣistatra ṛṣessāratamaṃ smṛtam || 12 ||
tenaiva ṛṣiṇā viṣṇurjñātavānparameśvaram ||
mahādevaṃ paraṃ brahma śabdabrahmatanuṃ param || 13 ||
ciṃtayā rahito rudro vāco yanmanasā saha ||
aprāpya tannivartate vācyastvekākṣareṇa saḥ || 14 ||
ekākṣareṇa tadvākyamṛtaṃ paramakāraṇam ||
satyamānandamamṛtaṃ paraṃ brahma parā tparam || 15 ||
ekākṣarādakārākhyādbhagavānbījakoṇḍajaḥ ||
ekākṣarādukārākhyāddhariḥ paramakāraṇam || 16 ||
ekākṣarānmakārākhyādbha |
gavānnīlalohitaḥ ||
sargakartā svakārākhyo jhukārākhyastu mohakaḥ || 17 ||
makārākhyastu yo nityamanugrahakaro'bhavat ||
makārākhyo vibhurbījī hyakāro bīja ucyate || 18 ||
ukārākhyo hariyoniḥ pradhānapuruṣeśvaraḥ ||
bījī ca vījaṃ tadyonirnādākhyaśca maheśvaraḥ || 19 ||
bījī vibhajya cātmānaṃ svecchayā tu vyavasthitaḥ ||
asya liṃgādabhūdvījamakāro bījinaḥ prabhoḥ || 20 ||
ukārayonau niḥkṣiptamavarddhata samaṃtataḥ ||
sauvarṇamabhava cāṃḍamāvedyaṃ tadalakṣaṇam || 21 ||
anekābdaṃ tathā cāpsu divyamaṃḍa vyavasthitam ||
tato varṣasahasrāṃte dvidhākṛtamajodbhavam || 22 ||
aṃḍa mapsu sthitaṃ sākṣādvyāghāteneśvareṇa tu ||
tathā'sya suśubhaṃ haimaṃ kapālaṃ corddhasaṃsthitam || 23 ||
jajñe sā dyaustadaparaṃ pṛthavī paṃcalakṣaṇā ||
tasmā daṃḍādbhavo jajñe kakārākhyaścaturmukhaḥ || 24 ||
sa sraṣṭā sarvalokānāṃ sa eva trividhaḥ prabhuḥ ||
evamomomiti proktamityāhuryajuṣāṃ varāḥ || 25 ||
yajuṣāṃ vacanaṃ śrutvā ṛcaḥ sāmāni sādaram ||
evameva hare brahmanityāhuśśrāvayostadā || 26 ||
tato vijñāya deveśaṃ yathāvacchaktisaṃbhavaiḥ ||
maṃtra

--- Page 20 [gcv] ---
maheśvaraṃ devaṃ tuṣṭāva sumahodayam || 27 ||
etasminnaṃtare'nyacca rūpamadbhutasundaram ||
dadarśa ca mayā sārddhaṃ bhagavānviśvapālakaḥ || 28 ||
paṃcavakraṃ daśa bhujaṃ gaurakarpūravansune ||
nānākāṃtisamāyuktaṃ nānābhūṣaṇabhūṣitam || 29 ||
mahodāraṃ mahāvīrye mahāpuruṣalakṣaṇam ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā paramaṃ rūpaṃ kṛtārtho' bhūnmayā hariḥ || 30 ||
atha prasanno bhagavānmaheśaḥ parameśvaraḥ ||
divyaṃ śabdamayaṃ rūpamākhyāya prahasaṃsthitaḥ || 31 ||
akārastasya mūrchā hi lalāṭo dīrgha ucyate ||
akāro dakṣiṇaṃ netramīkāro vāmalocanam ||32||
ukāro dakṣiṇaṃ śrotramūkāro vāma ucyate ||
akāro dakṣiṇaṃ tasya kapolaṃ parameṣṭhinaḥ || 33 ||
vāmaṃ kapolamūkāro la la nāsāpuṭe ubhe ||
ekāraśvoṣṭha ūrddhaśva hokārastvadharo vibhoḥ || 34 ||
okāraśca tathaukāro dantapaṅki dvayaṃ kramāt ||
amastu tālunī tasya devadevasya śūlinaḥ || 35 ||
kādipaṃcākṣarāṇyasya pañca hastāśca dakṣiṇeḥ ||
cādipaṃcākṣarāṇyevaṃ paṃca hastāstu vāmataḥ || 36 ||
ṭādipaṃcākṣaraṃ pādāstāṃdi paṃcākṣaraṃ tathā ||
pakāra udaraṃ tasyaṃ phakāraḥ pārśva ucyate || 37 ||
bakāro vāmapārśvastu bhakāraḥ skaṃdha ucyate ||
makāro hṛdayaṃ śaṃbhormahādevasya yoginaḥ || 38 ||
yakārādisakārāntā vibhorvai saptadhātavaḥ ||
"hakāro nābhirūpo hi kṣakāro prāṇa ucyate || 39 ||
evaṃ śabdamayaṃ rūpamaguṇasya guṇātmanaḥ ||
dṛṣṭvā tamumayā sārddhaṃ kṛtārtho'bhūnmayā hariḥ || 40 ||
evaṃ dṛṣṭvā maheśānaṃ śabdabrahma tanuṃ śivam ||
praṇamya ca mayā viṣṇuḥ punaścāpaśyadūrddhataḥ || 41 ||
oṃkāraprabhavaṃ maṃtra kalāpaṃcakasaṃyutam ||
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśaṃ śubhāṣṭatriṃśadakṣaram || || 42 ||
medhākāramabhūdbhūyassarvadharmārthasādhakam ||
gāyatrīprabhavaṃ maṃtraṃ sahitaṃ vaśyakārakam || 43 ||
caturviṃśativarṇāḍhyaṃ catuṣkālamanuttamam ||
atha paṃcasitaṃ maṃtraṃ kalāṣṭakasamāyutam || 44 ||
ābhicārikamatyarthaṃ prāyastriṃśacchubhākṣaram ||
yajurvedasamāyuktaṃ pañcaviṃśacchubhākṣaram || 45 ||
kalāṣṭakasamāyuktaṃ suśvetaṃ śāṃtikaṃ tathā ||
trayodaśakalāyuktaṃ bālādyaissaha lehitam || 46 ||
babhūvurasya cotpattivṛddhisaṃhārakāraṇam ||
varṇā ekā dhikāḥ ṣaṣṭirasya maṃtravarasya tu || 47 ||
punarmṛtyuṃjayaṃ maṃtraṃ pañcākṣaramataḥ param ||
ciṃtāmaṇi tathā maṃtraṃ dakṣiṇāmūrtisaṃjñakam || 48 ||
tatastattvama sītyuktaṃ mahāvākyaṃ harasya ca ||
pañcamaṃtrāṃstathā labdhvā jajāpa bhagavānhariḥ || 49 ||
atha dṛṣṭvā kalāvarṇamṛgyajussāmarūpiṇam ||
īśānamīśamu kuṭaṃ puruṣākhyaṃ purātanam ||50||
aghorahṛdayaṃ hṛdyaṃ sarvaguhyaṃ sadāśivam ||
vāmapādaṃ mahādevaṃ mahābhogīndrabhūṣaṇam || 51 ||
viśvataḥ pādavantaṃ taṃ viśvato kṣikaraṃ śivam ||
brahmaṇo'dhipatiṃ sargasthitisaṃhārakāraṇam || 52 ||
tuṣṭāva vāgbhiriṣṭābhissāmbaṃ varadamīśvaram ||
mayā ca sahito viṣṇurbhagavāṃstuṣṭace tasā ||53||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṃḍe sṛṣṭayupākhyāne śabdabrahmatanuvarṇano nāmāṣṭamo'dhyāyaḥ || 8|| ||
