brahmovāca ||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā punaḥ prāha haro harim ||
praṇipatya sthitaṃ mūrdhnā kṛtāṃjalipuṭaḥ svayam ||26|| ||
śrīmaheśa uvāca ||
pralayasthitisargāṇāṃ kartāhaṃ saguṇo'guṇaḥ ||
parabrahma nirvikārī saccidānaṃdalakṣaṇaḥ || 27 ||
tridhā bhinno hyahaṃ viṣṇo brahmaviṣṇuharākhyayā ||
sargarakṣālayaguṇairniṣkalohaṃ sadā hare || 28 ||
stuto'haṃ yattvayā viṣṇo brahmaṇā me'vatāraṇe ||
prārthanāṃ tāṃ kariṣyāmi satyāṃ yadbhaktava tsalaḥ || 29 ||
madrūpaṃ paramaṃ brahmannīdṛśaṃ bhavadaṃgataḥ ||
prakaṭībhavitā loke nānā rudraḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 30 ||
madaṃśāttasya sāmarthya nyūnaṃ naiva bhavi ṣyati ||
yohaṃ sohaṃ na bhedosti pūjāvidhividhānataḥ || 31 ||
yathā ca jyotiṣassaṃgā jalādeḥ sparśatā na vai !! tathā mamāguṇasyāpi saṃyogādva ndhanaṃ na hi || 32 ||
śivarūpaṃ mamaitañca rudro'pi śivavattadā ||
na tatra parabhedo vai kartavyaśca mahāmune || 33 ||
vastuto hyekarūpaṃ hi dvidhā bhinnaṃ jagatyuta ||
ato na bhedo vijñeyaḥ śive rudre kadācana || 34 ||
suvarṇasya tathaikasya vastutvaṃ naiva gacchati ||
alaṃkṛtikṛte deva nāmabhedo na vastu taḥ || 35 ||
yathaikasyā mṛdo bhedo nānāpātre na vastutaḥ ||
kāraṇasyaiva kārye ca sannidhānaṃ nidarśanam || 36 ||
jñātavyaṃ budhavaryaiśca nirmalajñānibhiḥ surau ||
evaṃ jñātvā bhavadbhyāṃ tu na dṛśyaṃ bhedakāraṇam || 37 ||
vastuvatsarvadṛśyaṃ ca śivarūpaṃmmatammama ||
ahaṃ bhavānajaścaiva rudro yo'yaṃ bhaviṣyati || 38 ||
ekarūpā na bhedastu bhede vai baṃdhanaṃ bhavet ||
tathāpi ca madīyaṃ hi śivarūpaṃ sanātanam || 39 ||
mūlībhūtaṃ sadoktaṃ ca satyajñānamanaṃtakam ||
evaṃ jñātvā sadā dhyeyaṃ manasā caiva tattvataḥ || 40 ||
śrūyatāṃ caiva bho brahmanyagopyaṃ kathyate mayā ||
bhavaṃtau prakṛteryātau nāyaṃ vai prakṛteḥ punaḥ || 41 ||
madājñā jāyate tatra brahmaṇo bhrukuṭeraham ||
guṇeṣvapi yathā proktastāmasaḥ prakṛto haraḥ || 42 ||
vaikārikaśca vijñeyo yo'haṃkāra udāhṛtaḥ ||
nāmato vastuto naiva tāmasaḥ paricakṣyate || 43 ||
etasmātkāraṇādbrahmankaraṇīyamidaṃ tvayā ||
sṛṣṭikartā bhava brahmansṛṣṭeśva pālako hariḥ || 44 ||
madīyaśca tathāṃ'śo yo layakartā bhaviṣyati ||
iyaṃ yā prakṛtirdevī ghumākhyā parameśvarī || 45 ||
tasyāstuśaktirvāgdevī brahmāṇaṃ sā bhajiṣyati ||
anyā śaktiḥ punastatra prakṛteḥ saṃbhaviṣyati || 46 ||
samāśrayiṣyate, viṣṇuṃ lakṣmīrūpeṇa sā tadā ||
punaśca kālī nāmnā sā madaṃśaṃ prāpsyati dhruvam || || 47 ||
jyotīrūpeṇa sā tatra kāryārthe saṃbhaviṣyati ||
evaṃ devyāstathā proktāśśaktayaḥ paramāśśubhāḥ || 48 ||
sṛṣṭisthitilayānāṃ hi kārya tāsāṃ kramādbhuvam ||
etasyāḥ prakṛteraṃśā matpriyāyāssurottam || 49 ||
tvaṃ ca lakṣmīmupāśritya kāryaṃ kartumihārhasi ||
brahmastvaṃḥ ca girāṃ devīṃ prakṛtyaṃśāma vāpya ca || 50 ||
sṛṣṭikāryaṃ hṛdā kartummannirdeśādihārhasi ||
ahaṃ kālīṃ samāśritya matpriyāṃśāṃ parātparām || 51 ||
rudrarūpeṇa pralayaṃ kariṣye

--- Page 23 [gcv] ---
śi0pu0 || 40 ||
• kāryamuttamam ||
caturvarṇamayaṃ lokaṃ tatsarvairāśramairdhruvam || 52 ||
tadanyairvividhaiḥ kāyaiḥ kṛtvā sukhamavāpsyayaḥ ||
jñānavijñānasaṃyukto lokānāṃ hita kārakaḥ || 53 ||
muktido'tra bhavānadya bhava loke madājñayā ||
maddarśane phalaṃ yadvattadeva tava darśane ||54||
iti datto varastedya satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||
mamaiva hṛdaye viṣṇurviṣṇośca hṛdaye hyaham || 55 ||
ubhayoraṃtaraṃ yo vai na jānāti mano mama ||
vāmāṃgajo mama harirdakṣiṇāṃgodbhavo vidhiḥ || 56 ||
mahāpralayadudro viśvātmāhṛdayodbhavaḥ ||
tridhā bhinno hyahaṃ viṣṇo brahmaviṣṇubhavākhyayā || 57 ||
sargarakṣālayakarastriguṇairaja ādibhiḥ ||
guṇabhinna śśivassākṣātprakṛteḥ puruṣātparaḥ || 58 ||
paraṃ brahmādvayo nityo'nantaḥ pūrṇo niraṃjanaḥ ||
aṃtastamo bahissattvatrijagatpālako hariḥ || 59 ||
aṃtassattvasta movāhyastrijagallayakṛddharaḥ || 60 ||
aṃtarbahīrajāścaiva trijagatsṛṣṭikṛdvidhiḥ ||
evaṃ guṇāstrideveṣu guṇabhinnaḥ śivaḥ smṛtaḥ || 61 ||
viṣṇo sṛṣṭikaraṃ prītyā pālayainaṃ pitāmaham ||
saṃpūjyastriṣu lokeṣu bhaviṣyasi madājñayā || 62 ||
tava sevyo vidheśvāpi rudra eva bhaviṣyati ||
śivapūrṇāvatāro hi trijagallayakārakaḥ || 63 ||
pādme bhaviṣyati srutaḥ kalpe tava pitāmahaḥ ||
tadā drakṣyasi māṃ caiva so'pi drakṣyati padmajaḥ || 64 ||
evamuktvā maheśānaḥ kṛpāṃ kṛtvātulāṃ haraḥ ||
punaḥ provāca suprītyā viṣṇuṃ sarveśvaraḥ prabhuḥ || 65 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ prathamakhaṃḍe sṛṣṭayupākhyāne śivatattvavarṇano nāma navamo'dhyāyaḥ || 9 || ||
parameśvara uvāca ||
anyacchṛṇu hare viṣṇo śāsanaṃ mama suvrata ||
sadā sarveṣu lokeṣu mānyaḥ pūjyo bhaviṣyasi || 1 ||
brahmaṇā nirmite loke yadā duḥkhaṃ prajāyate ||
tadā tvaṃ sarvaduḥkhānāṃ nāśāya tatparo bhava || 2 ||
sahāyaṃ te kariṣyāmi sarvakārye ca dussahe ||
tava śatrūnhaniṣyāmi dussādhyānparamotkaṭān || 3 ||
vividhānavatārāṃśca gṛhītvā kīrtimuttamām ||
vistāraya hare loke tāraṇāya paro bhava || 4 ||
guṇarūpo hyahaṃ rudro hyanena vapuṣā sadā ||
kārya kariṣye lokānāṃ tavāśakyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 5 ||
rudradhyeyo bhavāṃścaiva bhavaddheyo harastathā ||
yuvayorantarannaiva tava rudrasya kiṃcana || 6 ||
vastutaśvāpi caikatvaṃ varato'pi tathaiva ca ||
līlayāpi mahā viṣṇo satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 7 ||
rudrabhakto naro yastu tava niṃdāṃ kariṣyati ||
