loke'sminmuktido nṛṇāṃ bhuktiśca viśeṣataḥ ||
dhyeyaḥ pūjyaśca bhaktānāṃ nigrahānugrahau kuru ||10||
ityuktvā māṃ ca dhātāraṃ haste dhṛtvā svayaṃ harim ||
kathayāmāsa duḥkheṣu sahāyo bhava sarvadā || 11 ||
