vedamaṃtrairyathāyogyaṃ nāmabhirvā samaṃtrakaiḥ ||
caturthyātapadairbhaktyā dravyāṇyevāpayettadā || 56 ||
tathābhilaṣitaṃ dravyamarpaye cchaṃkaropāre ||
tataśca vāruṇaṃ snānaṃ karaṇīyaṃ śivāya vai || 57 ||
sugaṃdhaṃ caṃdanaṃ dadyādanyalepāni yatnataḥ ||
sasugaṃdhajalenaiva jaladhārāṃ prakalpayet || 58 ||
vedamaṃtraiḥ ṣaḍaṃgairvā nāmabhī rudrasaṃkhyayā ||
yathāvakāśaṃ tāṃ datvā vastreṇa mārjayettataḥ || 59 ||
paścādācamanaṃ dadyāttato vastraṃ samarpayet ||
tilāścaiva javā vāpi godhūmā mudgamāṣakāḥ || 60 ||
arpaṇīyāḥ śivāyaivaṃ maṃtrairnānāvidhairapi ||
tataḥ puṣpāṇi deyāni paṃcāsyāya mahātmane || 61 ||
prativakraṃ yathādhyānaṃ yathāyogyabhilāṣataḥ ||
kamaleśśatapatraiśca śaṃkhapuṣpaiḥ paraistathā || 62 ||
kuśapuṣpaiśca dhattūrairmaṃdāraidroṇasaṃbhavaiḥ ||
tathā ca tulasīpatrairbilpatrairviśeṣataḥ ||63||
pūjayetparayā bhaktyā śaṃkaraṃ bhaktavatsalam ||
sarvābhāve bilvapatramarpaṇīyaṃ śivāya vai || 64||
vilvapatrārpaṇe naiva sarvapūjā prasidhyati ||
tatassugaṃdhacūrṇaṃ vai vāsitaṃ tailamuttamam || 65 ||
arpaṇīyaṃ ca vividhaṃ śivāya parayā mudā |
tato dhūpaḥ prakartavyo guggulā gurubhirmudā || 66 ||
dīpo deyastatastasmai śaṃkarāya ghṛtaplutaḥ ||
ardhe dadyātpunastasmai maṃtreṇānena bhaktitaḥ || 67 ||
kārayedbhāvato bhaktyā

