kimarthaṃ na karoṣi tvaṃ suruciṃ prītamānasaḥ || 21 ||
sacchrotriyāste'nū cānā dīkṣitāssomayājinaḥ ||
iti rūḍhimiha prāptāstava pūrvapitāmahāḥ || 22 ||
tyaktvā durvṛttasaṃsarga sādhusaṃgarato bhava ||
sadvidyāsu mano dhehi brāhmaṇācāramācara || 23 ||
tātānu rūpo rūpeṇa yaśasā kulaśīlataḥ ||
tato na trapase kinnastyaja durvṛttatāṃ svakām || 24 ||
ūnaviṃśatiko'si tvameṣā ṣoḍaśavārṣikī ||
etāṃ saṃvṛṇu sadvṛttāṃ pitṛbhaktiyuto bhava || 25 ||
śvaśuro'pi hi te mānyassarvatra guṇaśīlataḥ ||
tato na trapase kinnastyaja durvṛttatāṃ suta || 26 ||
mātulāste' tulāḥ putra vidyāśīlakulādibhiḥ ||
tebhyo'pi na bibheṣi tvaṃ śuddho'syubhayavaṃśataḥ || 27 ||
paśyaitānprativeśmasthānbrāhmaṇānāṃ kumārakān ||
gṛhe'pi śiṣyānpaśyaitānpituste vinayocitān || 28 ||
rājāpi śroṣyati yadā tava duśceṣṭitaṃ suta ||
śraddhāṃ vihāya te tāte vṛttilopaṃ kariṣyati || 29 ||
bālaceṣṭitamevaitadvadatyadyāpi te janāḥ ||
anaṃtaraṃ hariṣyati yuktāṃ dīkṣitatāmiha || 30 ||
sarvepyākṣārayiṣyati tava tātaṃ ca māmapi ||
mātuścaritraṃ tanayo dhatte durbhāṣaṇauriti ||31||
pitāpi te na pāpīyāñchutismṛtipathānugaḥ ||
tadaṃprilīnamanaso mama sākṣī maheśvaraḥ || 32 ||
na cartusnātayāpīha mukhaṃ duṣṭasya vīkṣitam ||
aho balīyānsa vidhiryena jāto bhavāniti ||33||
pratikṣaṇaṃ jananyeti śikṣyamāṇoti durmatiḥ ||
na tatyāja ca taddhamai dubaudho vyasanī yataḥ ||34||
mṛgayāmadyapaiśūnyānṛtacauryadurodaraiḥ ||
savāradārairvyasanairebhiḥ ko'tra na khaṃḍitaḥ || 35 ||
yadyanmadhyagṛhe paśyettattannītvā sudurma tiḥ ||
arpayedyūtakārāṇāṃ sakupyaṃ vasanādikam || 36 ||
nyastāṃ ratnamayīṃ gehe karasya piturūrmikām ||
corayitvaikadādāya durodarakare'rpayat || 37 ||
dīkṣitena parijñāto daivādyūtakṛtaḥ kare ||
uvāca dīkṣitastaṃ ca kuto labdhā tvayormikā || 38 ||
pṛṣṭastenātha nirbaṃdhādasakṛttamuvāca saḥ ||
māmākṣipasi viproccaiḥ kiṃ mayā cauryakarmaṇā || 39 ||
labdhā mudrā tvadīyena putreṇaiva samarpitā ||
mama māturhi pūrvedyurjitvā nīto hi śāṭakaḥ||40||
na kevalaṃ mamaivai tadaṃgulīyaṃ samarpitam ||
anyeṣāṃ dyutakartṝṇāṃ bhūri tenārpitaṃ vasu || 4 ||
ratnakupyadukūlāni śṛṃgāraprabhṛtīni ca ||
bhājanāni vicitrāṇi kāṃsyatāmramayā ni ca||42||
namīkṛtya pratidinaṃ badhyate dyūtakāribhiḥ ||
na tena sadṛśaḥ kaśvidākṣiko bhūmimaṃḍale ||43||
adyāvadhi tvayā vipra durodaraśiromaṇiḥ ||
