pāvanaṃ paramaṃ divyaṃ guhyādbahyatamaṃ param || 8 ||
etacchaṃbhuḥ purovāca bhaktavaryāya viṣṇave ||
pṛṣṭhastena mahābhaktyā paropakṛtaye mune || 9 ||
tatassopi mayā pṛṣṭo viṣṇu śśaivavarassudhīḥ ||
prītyā mahyaṃ samācakhyau vistarānmunisattama ||10||
ahaṃ tatkathayiṣyāmi kathāmetāṃ purātanīm ||
śivāśivayaśoyuktāṃ sarvakāmaphala pradām || 11||
purā yadā śivo devo nirguṇo nirvikalpakaḥ ||
arūpaśśaktirahitaścinmātrassadasatparaḥ || 12 ||
abhavatsaguṇassopi dvirūpaśśaktimānpra bhuḥ ||
somo divyākṛtirvipra nirvikārī parātparaḥ || 13 ||
tasya vāmāṃgajo viṣṇurbrahmāhaṃ dakṣiṇāṃgajaḥ ||
rudro hṛdayato jāto'bhavacca munisattama || 14 ||
sṛṣṭikartābhavaṃ brahmā viṣṇuḥ pālanakārakaḥ ||
layakarttā svayaṃ rudraḥ stridhābhūtassadāśivaḥ || 15 ||
tamevāhaṃ samārādhya brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ ||
prajāḥ sasarja sarvāstāssurāsuranarādikāḥ || 16 ||
mṛṣṭvā prajāpatīn dakṣapramukhānsurasattamān ||
amanyaṃ suprasannohaṃ nijaṃ sarvamahonnatam || 17 ||
maricimatriṃ pulahaṃ pulastyāṃgirisau kratum ||
vasiṣṭhaṃ nāradaṃ dakṣaṃ bhṛguṃ ceti mahāprabhūn || 18 ||
brahmāhaṃ mānasānputrāna sarja ca yadā mune ||
tadā manmanaso jātā cārurūpā varāṃganā || 19 ||
nāmnā saṃdhyādivaśāṃtā sāyaṃ saṃdhyā japaṃtikā ||
atīva sundarī subhrūrmunicetovimohinī || 20 ||
na tādṛśī devaloke na matyai na rasātale ||
kālatrayepi vai nārī sampūrṇaguṇaśālinī || 21 ||
dṛṣṭvāhaṃ tāṃ samutthāya ciṃtayanhṛdi gatam ||
dakṣāda yaśca khaṣṭāro marīcyādyāśca matsutāḥ || 22 ||
evaṃ ciṃtayato me hi brahmaṇo munisattama ||
mānasaḥ puruṣo maṃjurāvirbhūto mahādbhutaḥ || 23 ||
kāṃcanī kṛtajātābhaḥ pīnoraskassunāsikaḥ ||
suvṛttorukaṭījaṃgho nīlavelitakeśaraḥ || 24 ||
lagnabhrūyugalo lolaḥ pūrṇacaṃdranibhānanaḥ ||
kapāṭāyatasa kṣo romarājīvarājitaḥ || 25 ||
abhramātaṃgakākāraḥ pīnaḥ nīlamuvāsakaḥ ||
āraktapāṇinayanamukhapādakarodbhavaḥ || 26 ||
kṣīṇamadhyaścārudataḥ pramattagajagaṃdhanaḥ ||
praphulapadmapatrākṣaḥ keśaratrāṇatarpaṇaḥ || 27 ||
kaṃbugrīvo mīnaketuḥ prāṃśurmakaravāhanaḥ ||
paṃcapuṣpāyudho vegī puṣpakodaṃḍamaṃḍitaḥ || || 28 ||
kāṃtaḥ kaṭākṣapātena bhramayannayanadvayam ||
sugaṃdhimāruto tāta śṛṃgārarasasevitaḥ || 29 ||
taṃ vīkṣya puruṣaṃ sarve dakṣādyā matsutā śca te ||
autsukyaṃ paramaṃ jagmurvismayāviṣṭamānasāḥ || 30 ||
abhavadvikṛtaṃ teṣāṃ matsutānāṃ mano drutam ||
dhairya naivālabhattāta kāmākulitaceta sāṃm || 31 ||
māṃ sopi vedhasaṃ vīkṣya sraṣṭāraṃ jagatāṃ patim ||
praṇamya puruṣaḥ prāha vinayānatakaṃdharaḥ || 32 || ||
puruṣa uvāca ||
kiṃ kariṣyāmyahaṃ karma brahmastatra niyojaya ||
mānyodya puruṣo yasmāducitaḥ śobhito vidhe || 33 ||
abhimānaṃ ca yogyaṃ ca sthānaṃ patnī ca yā mama ||
tanme vada

