ato manassusaṃyamya samyagutsṛjya vismayam ||
avocatpuruṣaṃ brahmā tatkāmaṃ ca samāvahan || 36 || ||
brahmovāca ||
anena tvaṃ svarūpeṇa puṣpabāṇaiśca paṃcabhiḥ ||
mohayan puruṣān strīṃśca kuru sṛṣṭi sanātanīm || 37 ||
asmiñjīvāśca devādyāstrailokye sacarācare ||
ete sarve bhaviṣyanti na kṣamāstyavalaṃbane || 38 ||
ahaṃ vā vāsudevo vā sthāṇurvā puruṣottamaḥ ||
bhaviṣyāmastava vaśe kimanye prāṇadhārakāḥ || 39 ||
pracchannarūpo jaṃtūnāṃ praviśan hṛdayaṃ sadā ||
sukhahetuḥ svayaṃ bhūtvā sṛṣṭiṃ kuru sanātanīm ||40||
tvatpuṣpavāṇasya sadā sukhalakṣyaṃ manodbhutam ||
sarveṣāṃ prāṇināṃ nityaṃ sadā madakaro bhavān ||41||
iti te karma kathitaṃ sṛṣṭiprāvartakaṃ punaḥ ||
nāmānyete vadiṣyaṃti sutā me tava tattvataḥ||42||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvāhaṃ suraśreṣṭha svasutānāṃ mukhāni ca ||
ālokya svāsane pājhe propaviṣṭo'bhavaṃ kṣaṇam || 43 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃ hitāyāṃ dvitīye satīkhaṃḍe kāmaprādurbhāvo nāma dvitīyo'dhyāyaḥ || 2 || ||
brahmovāca ||
tataste munayaḥ sarve tadabhiprāyavedinaḥ ||
cakrustaducitaṃ nāma marīcipramukhāssutāḥ || 1 ||
mukhāvalokanādeva jñātvā vṛttāṃtamanyataḥ ||
dakṣādayaśca sraṣṭāraḥ sthānaṃ patnīṃ ca te daduḥ || 2 ||
tato niścitya nāmāni marīcipramukhā dvijāḥ ||
ūcussaṃgatametasmai puruṣāya mamātmajāḥ || 3 || ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
yasmātpramathase tattvaṃ jātosmākaṃ yathā vidheḥ ||
tasmānmanmathanāmā tvaṃ loke khyāto bhaviṣyasi || 4 ||
jagatsu kāmarūpastvaṃ tvatsamo nahi vidyate ||
atastvaṃ kāmanāmāpi khyāto bhava mano bhava || 5 ||
madanānmadanākhyastvaṃ jāto darpātsadarpakaḥ ||
tasmātkaṃdarpanāmāpi loke khyāto bhaviṣyasi || 6 ||
tvatsamaṃ sarvadevānāṃ yadvīrye na bhaviṣyati ||
tataḥ sthānāni sarvāṇi sarvavyāpī bhavāṃstataḥ ||7||
dakṣoyaṃ bhavataḥ patnī svayaṃ dāsyati kāminīm ||
ādyaḥ prajāpatiyoṃ hi yatheṣṭaṃ puruṣottamaḥ ||8||
eṣā ca kanyakā cārurūpā brahmamanobhavā ||
saṃdhyā nāmneti vikhyātā sarvaloke bhaviṣyati ||9||
brahmaṇo dhyāyato yasmātsamyak jātā varāṃganā ||
atassaṃdhyeti vikhyātā krāṃtābhā tulyamallikā ||10|| ||
brahmovāca ||
kausumāni tathāstrāṇi paṃcādāya manobhavaḥ ||
pracchannarūpī tatraiva ciṃtayāmāsa niścayam ||11||
harṣaṇaṃ rocanākhyaṃ ca mohanaṃ śoṣaṇaṃ tathā ||
māraṇaṃ cati proktāni munermohakarāṇyapi || 12 ||
brahmaṇā mama yatkarma samuddiṣṭaṃ sanātanam ||
tadihaiva kariṣyāmi munīnāṃ sannidhau vidhe || 13 ||
tiṣṭhati munayaścātra svayaṃ cāpi prajāpatiḥ ||
eteṣāṃ sākṣibhūtaṃ me bhaviṣyaṃ tyadya niścayam || 14 ||
saṃdhyāpi brahmaṇā proktā cedānīṃ preṣayedvacaḥ ||
iha karma parīkṣyaiva prayogānmohayāmyaham || 15 ||
brahmovāca ||
