i saṃcitya manasā niścitya ca manobhavaḥ ||
puṣpajaṃ puṣpajātasya yojayāmāsa mārgaṇaiḥ || 16 ||
ālīḍhasthānamāsādya dhanurākṛṣya yatnataḥ ||
cakāra balayākāraṃ kāmo dhanvivarastadā ||17||
saṃhite tena kodaṃḍe mārutāśca sugaṃdhayaḥ ||
vavustatra suniśreṣṭha samyagāhādakāriṇaḥ || 18 ||
tatastānapi dhātrādīn sarvāneva ca mānasān ||
pṛthak pṛṣpaśaraistīkṣṇaimahiyāmāsa mohanaḥ || 19 ||
tataste munayassarve mohitāścāpyahaṃ mune ||
saṃhito manasā kaṃcidvikāraṃ prāpurāditaḥ || 20 ||
saṃdhyāṃ sarve nirīkṣaṃtassavikāraṃ muhurmuhuḥ ||
āsan pravṛddhamadanāḥ strī yasmānmadanaidhinī || 21 ||
tataḥ sarvān se madano mohayitvā punaḥpunaḥ ||
yathendriyavikāraṃ te prāpustānakarottathā || 22 ||
udīriteṃdriyo dhātā vīkṣyāhaṃ sa yadā ca tām ||
tadaiva conapaṃ cāśadbhāvā jātāśśarīrataḥ || 23 ||
sāpi taivakṣyamāṇātha kaṃdarpaśarapātanāt ||
cakre muhurmuhurbhāvān kaṭākṣāvaraṇādikān || 24 ||
nisargasuṃdarī saṃdhyā tān bhāvān mānasodbhavān ||
kuvaityatitarāṃ reje svarṇadīva tanūrmibhiḥ || 25 ||
atha bhāvayutāṃ saṃdhyāṃ vīkṣyākārṣa prajāpatiḥ ||
dharmābhi pūritatanurabhilāṣamahaṃ mune || 26 ||
tataste munayassarve marīcyatrimukhā api ||
dakṣādyāśca dvijaśreṣṭha prāpurvaikārikendriyam || 27 ||
dṛṣṭvā tathāvidhā dakṣamarīcipramukhāśca mām ||
saṃdhyāṃ ca karmaṇi nije śraddadhe madanastadā || 28 ||
yadidaṃ brahmaṇā karma mamoddiṣṭaṃ mayāpi tat ||
kartuṃ śakyamiti hyaddhā bhāvitaṃ svabhruvā tadā || 29 ||
itthaṃ pāpagatiṃ vīkṣya bhrātṝṇāṃ ca pitustathā ||
dharmassasmāra śaṃbhuṃ vai tadā dharmāvanaṃ prabhum || 30 ||
saṃsmara nmanasā dharmaṃ śaṃkaraṃ dharmapālakam ||
tuṣṭāva vividhairvākyaidano bhūtvājasaṃbhavaḥ || 31 ||
dharma uvāca ||
devadeva mahādeva dharmapāla namostu te ||
sṛṣṭisthitivināśānāṃ kartā śaṃbho tvameva hi || 32 ||
sṛṣṭau brahmā sthitau viṣṇuḥ pralaye hararūpadhṛk ||
rajassattvatamobhiśca striguṇairaguṇaḥ prabho || 33 ||
nistraiguṇyaḥ śivaḥ sākṣātturyaśca prakṛteḥ paraḥ ||
nirguṇo nirvikārī tvaṃ nānā līlāviśāradaḥ || 34 ||
rakṣarakṣa mahādeva pāpānmāṃ dustarā ditaḥ ||
matpitāyaṃ tathā ceme bhrātaraḥ pāpabuddhayaḥ ||35||
brahmovāca ||
iti stuto maheśāno dharmeṇaiva paraḥ prabhuḥ ||
