dattvā mune tasmin śaṃbhāvaṃtarhite tadā ||
saṃdhyāpyagacchattatraiva yatra medhātithirmune || 1 ||
tatra śaṃbhoḥ prasādena na kenāpyupalakṣitā ||
sasmāra varṇinaṃ taṃ vai svopadeśakaraṃ tapaḥ || 2 ||
vasiṣṭhena purā sā tu varṇā bhūtvā ruṣā mune ||
upadiṣṭā tapaścartu vacanātparameṣṭhinaḥ || 3 ||
tameva kṛtvā manasā tapa ścaryopadeśakam ||
patitvena tadā saṃdhyā brāhmaṇaṃ brahmacāriṇam || 4 ||
samiddhenau mahāyajñe munibhinapalakṣitāṃ ||
dṛṣṭā śaṃbhuprasādena sā viveśa vidhe ssutā || 5 ||
tasyāḥ puroḍāśamayaṃ śarīraṃ tatkṣaṇāttataḥ ||
dagdhaṃ puroḍāśagaṃdhaṃ tastāra yadalakṣitam || 6 ||
vahnistasyāḥ śarīraṃ tu dugdhvā sūryasya maṃḍalam ||
śuddhaṃ praveśayāmāsa śaṃbhorevājñayā punaḥ || 7 ||
sūryo vyarthaṃ vibhajyātha taccharīraṃ tadā rathe ||
svakeśaṃ sthāpayāmāsa prītaye pitṛdevayoḥ || 8 ||
tadūrddhabhāgastasyāstu śarīrasya munīśvara ||
prātassaṃdhyābhavatsā tu ahorātrādimadhyagā || 9 ||
taccheṣabhāgastasyāstu ahorātrāṃtamadhya gā ||
sā sāyamabhavatsaṃdhyā pitṛprītipradā sadā || 10 ||
sūryodayāttu prathamaṃ yadā syādaruṇodayaḥ ||
prātassaṃdhyā tadodeti devānāṃ prītikāriṇī || || 11 ||
astaṃ gate tataḥ sūyye śoṇipadmanibhe sadā ||
udeti sāyaṃsaṃdhyāpi pitṝṇāṃ modakāriṇī ||12||
tasyāḥ prāṇāstu manasā śaṃbhunātha dayālu nā ||
divyenaṃ tu śarīreṇa cakrire hi śarīriṇaḥ || 13 ||
muneryajñāvasāne tu saṃprāpte muninā tu sā ||
prāptā putrī vahnimadhye taptakāṃcanasuprabhā || 14 ||
tāṃ jagrāha tadā putrīṃ munirāmodasaṃyutaḥ ||
yajñārthaṃ tāntu saṃkhāpya nijakoḍe dadhau mune ||15||
aruṃdhatī tu tasyāstu nāma cakre mahāmuniḥ ||
śiṣyaiḥ parivṛtastatra mahāmodamavāpa ha || 16 ||
viruṇaddhi yato dharma sā kasmā dapikāraṇāt ||
atastriloke viditaṃ nāmasaṃprāpa tatsvayam || 17 ||
yajñaṃ samāpya sa muniḥ kṛtakṛtyabhāvamāsādya saṃpadayutastanayāpralaṃbhāt ||
tasminnijāśramapade saha śiṣyavargastāmeva saṃtatamasau dayite surarṣe || 18 ||
atha sā vavṛdhe devī tasmin munivarāśrame ||
candrabhāgā nadītīre tāpasāraṇyasaṃjñake || 19 ||
saṃprāpte pañcame varṣe candrabhāgāṃ tadā guṇaiḥ ||
tāpasāra ṇyamapi sā pavitramakarotsatī || 20 ||
vivāhaṃ kārayāmāsustasyā brahmasutena vai ||
vasiṣṭhena hyaruṃdhatyā brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ || 21 ||
tadvivāhe maho tsāho babhūva sukhavarddhanaḥ ||
sarve surāśca munayassukhamāpuḥ paraṃ mune || 22 ||
brahmaviṣṇumaheśānāṃ karanissṛtatoyataḥ ||
saptanadya ssamutpannāśśiprādyāssu pavitrakāḥ || 23 ||
aruṃdhatī mahāsādhvī sādhvīnāṃ pravarottamā ||
vasiṣṭhaṃ prāpya saṃreje medhātithisutā mune || 24 ||
yasyāḥ putrātsamutpannāḥ śreṣṭhā śśaktyādayaśśubhāḥ ||
vasiṣṭhaṃ prāpya taṃ kāṃtaṃ saṃreje munisattama || 25 ||
evaṃ saṃdhyācaritraṃ te kathitaṃ munisattama ||
