ahaṃ vimohitastāta yadaivatarhitaḥ purā ||
aciṃtayaṃ sadāhaṃ tacchaṃbhuvākyaviṣārditaḥ || 8 ||
citayitvā ciraṃ citte śivamāyāvimohitaḥ ||
śive cerṣyāmakārṣa hi tacchṛṇuṣva vadāmi te || 9 ||
athāhamagamaṃ tatra yatra dakṣādayaḥ sthitāḥ ||
