kā vā nārī trilokesmin yā bhavettanmanāḥ sthitā ||
yogamārgamavajñāpya tasya mohaṃ kariṣyati || 17 ||
manmathopi samarthoṃ no bhaviṣyatyasya mohane ||
nitāṃtayogī rāmāṇāṃ nāmāpi sahate na saḥ || 18 ||
agṛhīteṣu nā caiva hareṇa kathayādinā ||
madhyamā ca bhavetsṛṣṭistadvācā nānyavāritā || 19 ||
bhuvi kecidbhaviṣyāṃta māyāvadhvā mahāsurāḥ ||
vadhvā keciddharernūnaṃ kecicchaṃbhorupāyataḥ || 20 ||
saṃsāra vimukhe śaṃbhau tathaikāṃtavirāgiṇi ||
asmādṛte na karmānyat kariṣyati na saṃśayaḥ || 21 ||
ityuktvā tanayaścāhaṃ dakṣādīna sunirīkṣya ca ||
sarati madanaṃ tatra sānaṃdamagadaṃ tataḥ || 22 || ||
brahmovāca ||
matputra vara kāmaṃ tvaṃ sarvathā sukhadāyakaḥ ||
madvaca śṛṇu suprītyā svapatnyā pitṛvatsala ||23||
anayā sahacāriṇyā rājase tvaṃ manobhava ||
