tacca bhrūyugalaṃ brahman hāvabhāvayutaṃ muhuḥ ||
nānābhāvānakāṃrṣīcca dāṃpatyakrama muttamam || 17 ||
nīlakaṃṭha mahādevaṃ sagaṇaṃ tatpurasthitāḥ ||
akārṣumohitaṃ bhāvaṃ mṛgāśca pakṣiṇastathā || 18 ||
mayūramithunaṃ tatrākārṣīdbhāvaṃ rasotsu kam |
vividhāṃ gatimāśritya pārśve tasya purastathā || 19 ||
nālabhadvivaraṃ tasmin kadācidapi maccharaḥ ||
satyaṃ bravīmi lokeśa mama śaktirna mohane || 20 ||
madhurapyakarotkarma yuktaṃ yattasya mohane ||
tacchṛṇuṣva mahābhāga satyaṃ satyaṃ vadāmyaham || 21 ||
caṃpakānkeśarānbālānkāraṇānpā ṭalāṃ stathā ||
nāgakeśarapunnāgānkiśukānketakānkarān || 22 ||
māgaṃdhi mallikāparṇabhārān kurabakāṃstathā ||
utphullayati tatra sma yatra tiṣṭhati vai haraḥ || 23 ||
sarasyutphullapadmāni vījayan malayānilaiḥ ||
yatnātsugaṃdhīnyakarodtīva giriśāśrame || 24 ||
latāssarvāssumanaso dhattūrāṃkurasaṃ cayāḥ ||
vṛkṣāṃkaṃ cirabhāvena veṣṭayaṃtisma tatra ca || 25 ||
tānvṛkṣāṃśca supuṣpaughān taiḥ sugaṃdhisamīraṇaiḥ ||
.

--- Page 69 [opus] ---
dṛṣṭvā kāmavaśaṃ yātā munayo'pi pare kimu || 26 ||
evaṃ satyapi śaṃbhorne dṛṣṭaṃ mohasya kāraṇam |
bhāvamātramakārṣīnno kopo mayyapi śaṅkaraḥ || 27 ||
iti sarvamahaṃ dṛṣṭvā jñātvā tasya ca bhāvanām |
vimukho'haṃ śaṃbhumohānnipataṃ te vadāmyaham || 28 ||
tasya tyaktasamādhestu kṣaṇaṃ no dṛṣṭigocare |
kvanuśāyāmo vayaṃ sthātuṃ taṃ rudraṃ ko vimohayet || 29 ||
jvaladagniprakāśākṣaṃ yoddhārāśikarālinam |
śṛṅgiṇaṃ vīkṣya kasthātuṃ brahman śaknoti tatpuraḥ || 30 ||

||
brahmovāca ||
manobhavavacaśśrutvā caturānanaḥ |
vivakṣurapi nāvocaṃ cintāviṣṭo'bhavaṃ tadā || 31 ||
mohenāhaṃ samartho na harasyeti manobhavaḥ |
vacaḥ śrutvā mahāduḥkhānnirśvasamahaṃ mune || 32 ||
niśvāsamārutā me hi nānārūpamahābalāḥ |
jātā gatā lolajihvā lolāścātibhayaṅkarāḥ || 33 ||
avādyaṃta te sarve nānāvādyānasaṃkhyakān |
paṭahādigaṇāstāṃstān vikarālānmahāravān || 34 ||
atha te mama niśvāsasaṃbhavāśca mahāgaṇāḥ |
mārayacchedayetyūcurbrahmaṇo me puraḥ sthitāḥ || 35 ||
teṣāṃ tu vadatāṃ tatra mārayacchedayeti mām |
vacaḥ śrutvā vidhiḥ kāmaḥ pravaktumupacakrame || 36 ||
munetha māṃ samābhāṣya tān dṛṣṭvā madano gaṇān |
uvāca vārayan brahman gaṇānāmayata smaraḥ || 37 ||

||
kāma uvāca ||
he brahman he prajānātha sarvasṛṣṭipravartakaḥ |
utpannāḥ ka ime vīrā vikarālā bhayaṅkarāḥ || 38 ||
kiṃ kaiṃ ete kariṣyanti kutra sthāsyanti vā vidhe |
kinnāmadheyā ete tadbrūhi tatra niyojaya || 39 ||
niyojya tānbrūhi kṛtye sthānaṃ dattvā ca nāma ca |
mamājñāpaya deveśa kṛpāṃ kṛtvā yathocitam || 40 ||

||
brahmovāca ||
iti tadvākyamākarṇya munerahaṃ lokakārakaḥ |
tamavocaṃ ha madanaṃ teṣāṃ karmādikaṃ diśan || 41 ||

||
brahmovāca ||
eta utpannamātrā hi mārayetyavadan vacaḥ |
muhurmuhurutomīṣāṃ nāma māreti jāyatām || 42 ||
sadaiva viśvaṃ jantūnāṃ kariṣyanti gaṇā ime |
vinā nijācenaṃ kāma nānākāmaratātmanāḥ || 43 ||
tavānugamanaṃ karma mukhyameṣāṃ manobhava |
sahāyino bhaviṣyanti sadā tava na saṃśayaḥ || 44 ||
yatrayatra bhavān yātā svakarmārthe yadā yadā |
gantāstatra tva naite sahāyārthe tadā tadā || 45 ||
cittabhrāntiṃ kariṣyanti tvadarśavaśavartināṃ |
jñānināṃ jñānamārge ca vighnayiṣyanti sarvathā || 46 ||

||
brahmovāca ||
ityākarṇya vaco me hi smaratissamahānugaḥ |
kiṃcitprasannavadano babhūva munisattama || 47 ||
śrutvā te'pi gaṇāssarve madanaṃ māṃ ca saṃvṛtaḥ |
parivāryya yathākāmaṃ tasthustatra nijākṛtim || 48 ||
atha brahmā smaraṃ prītyāgadaṃ me kuru śāsanam |
ebhissahaiva gaccha tvaṃ punaśca haramohane || 49 ||
mana ādhāya yatnāni kuru māra gaṇaissaha |
moho bhavedyathā śaṃbhordurgrahaṇaheto || 50 ||
ityākarṇya vacaḥ kāmaḥ provāca vacanaṃ punaḥ |
deveśe gauravaṃ matvā praṇamya vinayena mām || 51 ||

||
kāma uvāca ||
mayā samyak kṛtaṃ karma mohane tasya

--- Page 70 [gcv] ---
yatnataḥ ||
tanmoho nābhavattāta na bhaviṣyati nādhunā || 52 ||
tava vāggauravaṃ matvā dṛṣṭvā māragaṇānapi ||
gamiṣyāmi punastatra samārohaṃ svadā jñayā || 53 ||
mano niścitametaddhi tanmoho na bhaviṣyati ||
bhasma kuryyānna me dehamiti śaṃkāsti me vidhe ||54||
ityuktvā samadhuḥ kāmassaratissa bhaya stadā ||
yayau māragaṇaiḥ sārddhaṃ śivasthānaṃ munīśvara ||55 ||
pūrvavat svaprabhāvaṃ ca cakre manasijastadā ||
bahūpāyaṃ sa hi madhurvividhāṃ buddhimāvahan || 66 ||
upāyaṃ sa cakārāti tatra māragaṇo'pi ca ||
mohobhavanna vai śaṃbhorapi kaścitparātmanaḥ ||57||
nivṛtya punarāyāto mama sthānaṃ smarastadā ||
āsīnmāragaṇe gava'haṣoṃ mepi purassthitaḥ || 58 ||
kāmaḥ provāca māṃ tāta praṇamya ca nirutsavaḥ ||
sthitvā mama puro'gavoṃ māraiśva madhunā tadā || 59 ||
kṛtaṃ pūrvādadhikataḥ karma tanmohane vidhe ||
nābhavattasya mohopi kaśviddhayānaratātmanaḥ || 60 ||
na dagdhā me tanuścaiva tatra tena dayālunā ||
kāraṇaṃ pūrvapuṇyaṃ ca nirvikārī sa vai prabhuḥ || 61 ||
ceṃdraraste haro bhāryāṃ gṛhṇīyāditi padmajaḥ ||
paropāyaṃ kuru tadā vigarva iti me matiḥ || 62 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā saparīvāro yayau kāmassvamāśramam ||
praṇamya māṃ smaran śaṃbhuṃ garvadaṃ dīnavatsalam || 63 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitī yāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ dvitīye satīkhaṃḍe satyupākhyāne kāmaprabhāvamāragaṇotpattivarṇano nāma navamo'dhyāyaḥ || 9 ||
nārada uvāca ||
brahman vidhe mahā bhāga dhanyastvaṃ śivaśaktadhīḥ ||
kathitaṃ sucaritraṃ te śaṃkarasya parātmanaḥ || 1 ||
nijāśrame gate kāme sagaṇe sarattau tataḥ ||
kimāsītkimakārṣīstvaṃ taccaritraṃ vadādhunā || 2 || ||
brahmovāca ||
śṛṇu nārada suprītyā caritraṃ śaśimaulinaḥ ||
yasya śravaṇamātreṇa nirvikāro bhavennaraḥ || 3 ||
nijā śramaṃ gate kāme parivārasamanvite ||
yadvabhūva tadā jātaṃ taccaritraṃ nibodha me || 4 ||
naṣṭobhūnnārada mado vismayo'bhūcca me hṛdi ||
nirānaṃdasya ca mune'pūrṇe nijamanorathe || 5 ||
aśocaṃ bahudhā citte gṛhṇīyātsa kathaṃ striyam ||
niāvakārī jitātma sa śaṃkaro yogatatparaḥ || 6 ||
itthaṃ vicārya va hudhā tadāhaṃ vimado mune ||
hariṃ taṃ so'smaraṃ bhaktyā śivātmānaṃ svadehadam || 7 ||
astava ca śubhastotrairdānavākyasamanvitaiḥ ||
tacchrutvā bhagavā nāśu babhūvāvirhi me purā || 8 ||
caturbhujoraviṃdākṣaḥ śaravājaigadādharaḥ ||
lasatpītapaṭaśśyāmatanurbhaktapriyo hariḥ || 9 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā tādṛśamahaṃ suśa raṇyaṃ muhurmuhuḥ ||
astavaṃ ca punaḥ preṇmā bāṣpagadgadayā girā || 10 ||
harirākarṇya tatstotraṃ suprasanna uvāca mām ||
duḥkhahā nijabhaktānāṃ brahmāṇaṃ śa raṇaṃ gatam || 11 || ||
hariruvāca || ||
vidhe brahman mahāprājña dhanyastvaṃ lokakāraka ||
kimarthaṃ smaraṇaṃ medya kṛtaṃ ca kriyate nutiḥ || 12 ||
kiṃ jātaṃ te mahadduḥkhaṃ madagre tadvadādhunā ||
śamayiṣyāmi tatsavai nātra kāryyā vicāraṇā || 13 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
iti viṣṇorvacaśśrutvā kiṃciduccha .

