sitānanaḥ ||
avocaṃ vacanaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇamya sukṛtāṃjaliḥ || 14 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
deva deva ramānātha madvāta śṛṇu mānada ||
śrutvā ca karuṇāṃ kṛtvā hara duḥkhaṃ kamāvaha || 15 ||
rudrasaṃmohanārthaṃ hi kāmaṃ preṣitavānaham ||
parivārayutaṃ viṣṇo samāramadhubāṃdhavam || 16 ||
cakruste vividhopāyān niṣphalā abhavaṃśca te ||
nābhavattasya saṃmoho yoginassamadarśinaḥ || 17 ||
ityākarṇya vaco me sa harimī prāha vismitaḥ ||
vijñātākhiladajñānī śivatattvaviśāradaḥ || 18 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
kasmāddhetoriti matistava jātā pitāmaha ||
sarvaṃ vicārya sudhiyā brahman satyaṃ hi tadvad || 19 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
śṛṇu tāta caritraṃ tat tava māyā vimohinī ||
tadadhīnaṃ jagatsarvaṃ sukhaduḥkhāditatparam || 20 ||
yayaiva preṣitaścāhaṃ pāpaṃ kartuṃ samudyataḥ ||
āsaṃ tacchṛṇu deveśa vadāmi tava śāsanāt || 21 ||
sṛṣṭiprāraṃbhasamaye daśa putrā hi jajñire ||
dakṣādyāstanayā caikā vāgbhavāpyatisu ndarī || 22 ||
dharmoṃ vakṣaḥsthalātkāmo manasonyopi dehataḥ ||
jātāstatra sutāṃ dṛṣṭvā mama moho bhavaddhare || 23 ||
kudṛṣṭayā tāṃ samadrākṣaṃ tava māyā vimohitaḥ ||
tatkṣaṇāvara āgatya māmanindatsutānapi || 24 ||
dhikkāraṃ kṛtavān sarvān nijaṃ matvā paraprabhum ||
jñāninaṃ yoginaṃ nāthā bhoginaṃ vijitendriyam || 25 ||
putro bhūttvā mama hare'nindaṃ māṃ ca samakṣataḥ ||
iti duḥkhaṃ mahanmehi taduktaṃ tava sannidhau || 26 ||
gṛhṇīyādyadi patnīṃḥ sa svāṃ sukhī naṣṭaduḥkhadhīḥ ||
etadarthaṃ samāyātaśśaraṇaṃ tava keśava || 27 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
ityākarṇya vaco mehi brahmaṇo madhusūdanaḥ ||
vihasya māṃ drutaṃ prāha harṣayanbhavakārakam || 28 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca || ||
vidhe śṛṇu hi madvākyaṃ sarvaṃ bhramanivāraṇam ||
sarve vedāgamādīnāṃ saṃmataṃ paramārthataḥ || |||| 29 ||
mahāmūḍhamatiścādya saṃjātosi kathaṃ vidhe ||
vedavaktāpi nikhilalokakartā hi durmatiḥ || 30 ||
jaḍatāṃ tyaja mandātman kuru tvaṃ nedṛśīṃ matim ||
kiṃ brurvatyakhilā vedāḥ stutyā tatsmara saddhiyā || 31 ||
rudraṃ jānāsi dubundai svasutaṃ parameśvaram ||
vedavaktāpi vijñānaṃ vismṛtaṃ tekhilaṃ vidhe || 32 ||
śaṃkaraṃ surasāmānyaṃ matvā drohaṃ karoṣi hi ||
subuddhirvigatā tedyāvirbhūtā kumatistathā || 33 ||
tattvasiddhāṃtamākhyātaṃ śṛṇu sadbuddhimā vaha ||
yathārtha nigamākhyātaṃ nirṇīya bhavakārakam || 34 ||
śivassarvasvakartā hi bhartā hartā parātparaḥ ||
parabrahma pareśaśca nirguṇo nitya eva ca || ||35||
anirdeśyo nirvikārī paramātmā'dvayocyutaḥ ||
anaṃtoṃtakara svāmī vyāpakaḥ parameśvaraḥ || 36 ||
sṛṣṭisthitivināśānāṃkṛttistriguṇabhāvibhuḥ ||
brahmaviṣṇumaheśākhyo rajassattvatamaḥ paraḥ || 37 ||
māyābhinno nirīhaśca māyo māyī viśāradaḥ ||
saguṇopi svataṃtraśca nijānaṃdo vikalpakaḥ|| 38 ||
ātmārāmo hi nirdvadvī bhaktādhīnastuvigrahaḥ ||
yogī yogarato nityaṃ yogamārgapradarśakaḥ || 39 ||
garvāpahārī lokeśassarvadā dīnavatsalaḥ ||
etā

--- Page 72 [gcv] ---
dṛśo hi yaḥ svāmī svaputraṃ manyase hi tam || 40 ||
īdṛśaṃ tyaja kujñānaṃ śaraṇaṃ vraja tasya vai ||
bhaja sarvātmanā śambhuṃ santuṣṭaśśaṃ vidhāsyati || || 41 ||
gṛhṇīyācchaṃkaraḥ patnīṃ vicāro hṛdi cettava ||
śivāmuddiśya sutapaḥ kuru brahmanaṃ śivaṃ smaran || 42 ||
kuru dhyānaṃ śivāyāstvaṃ kāmamuddiśya taṃ hṛdi ||
sā cetprasannā deveśī sarve kārya vidhāsyati || 43 ||
kṛtvāvatāraṃ saguṇā yadi syānmānuṣī śivā ||
kasyacittanayā loke sā tatpatnī bhaveddhruvam || 44 ||
dakṣamājñāpaya brahman tapaḥ kuryyātprayatnataḥ ||
tāmutpādayituṃ patnīṃ śivārthaṃ bhaktitassvataḥ || 45 ||
bhaktādhīnau ca tau tāta suvi jñeyau śivāśivau ||
svecchayā saguṇau jātau parabrahmasvarūpiṇau || 46 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
ityuktvā tatkṣaṇaṃ meśaśśivaṃ sasmāra svaprabhum ||
kṛpayā tasya saṃprāpya jñānamūce ca māṃ tataḥ || 47 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca || ||
vidhe smara puroktaṃ yadvacanaṃ śaṃkareṇa ca ||
prārthitena yadāvābhyāmutpa nnābhyāṃ tadicchayā || 48 ||
vismṛtaṃ tava tatsarvaṃ dhanyā yā śāṃbhavī parā ||
tayā saṃmohitaṃ sarve durvijñeyā śivaṃ vinā || 49 ||
yadā hi saguṇo jātassvecchayā nirguṇaśśivaḥ ||
māmutpādya tatastvāṃ ca svaśaktyā suvihārakṛt || 50 ||
upādideśa tvāṃ śambhussṛṣṭikāryaṃ tadā prabhuḥ ||
tatpā lanaṃ ca māṃ brahman somassūtikaro'vyayaḥ || 51 ||
tadā vāṃ veśma saṃprāptausāṃjalī natamastakau ||
bhava tvamapi sarveśā'vatārī guṇarūpadhṛk || 52 ||
ityuktaḥ prāhaṃ sa svāmī vihasya karuṇānvitaḥ ||
divamudvīkṣya suprītyā nānālīlāviśāradaḥ || 53 ||
manṛpaṃ paramaṃ viṣṇo īdṛśaṃ jhaṃgato vidheḥ ||
prakaṭībhavitā loke nāmnā rudraḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 54 ||
pūrṇarūpassame pūjyassadā vāṃ sarvakāmakṛt ||
layakarttā guṇādhyakṣo nirviśeṣaḥ suyogakṛt || || 55 ||
tridevā api me rūpaṃ haraḥ pūrṇo viśeṣataḥ ||
umāyā api rūpāṇi bhaviṣyaṃti tridhā sutau || 56 ||
lakṣmīrnāma hareḥ patnī brahmapatnī sara svatī ||
pūrṇarūpā satī nāma rudrapatnī bhaviṣyati || 57 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca || ||
ityuktvāṃtarhito jātaḥ kṛpāṃ kṛtvā maheśvaraḥ ||
abhūtāṃ sukhi nāvāvāṃ svasvakāryaparāyaṇau || 58 ||
samayaṃ prāpya sastrīkāvāvāṃ brahmannaśaṃkaraḥ ||
avatīrṇassvayaṃ rudranāmā kailāsasaṃśrayaḥ || 59 ||
avatīrṇo śivābhūtsā satīnāma prajeśvara ||
tadutpādanahetorhi yatnotaḥ kārya eva vai || 60 ||
ityuktvāṃtardadhe viṣṇuḥ kṛtvā sa karuṇāṃ parām ||
prāpnuvaṃ pramudaṃ cātha hyadhikaṃ gatamatsaraḥ || 61 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ dvitīye satīkhaṇḍe brahmaviṣṇusaṃvādo nāma daśamo' dhyāyaḥ || 10 || ||
nārada uvāca || ||
brahman tāta mahāprājña vada no vadatāṃ vara ||
gate viṣṇau kimabhavadakārṣīki vidhe bhavān || 1 ||
. ||
brahmo vāca || ||
vipranandanavarya tvaṃ sāvadhānatayā śṛṇu ||
viṣṇau gate bhagavati yadakārṣamahaṃ khalu || 2 ||
vidyāvidyātmikāṃ śuddhāṃ parabrahmasvarūpiṇīm ||
