tvadyate tasya no kācidbhaviṣyati manoharā || 23 ||
tasmāttvameva rūpeṇa bhavasva haramohinī ||
sutā bhūtvā ca dakṣasya rudrapati śive bhava || 24 ||
yathādhṛtaśarīrā tvaṃ lakṣmīrūpeṇa keśavam ||
āmodaya si viśvasya hitāyaitaṃ tathā kuru || 25 ||
kāṃtābhilāṣamātraṃ me dṛṣṭvā'niṃdadvṛṣadhvajaḥ ||
sa kathaṃ vanitāṃ devi svecchayā saṃgṛhīṣyati || 26 ||
