kṛtvā jāgaraṇaṃ niśi |
viśeṣatassamānārcaṃ śailūṣaissarvayāmasu || 19 ||
caitre śuklacaturdaśyāṃ palāśairdamanaiśśivam |
apūjayaddivārātrau saṃsmaran sā nināya tam || 20 ||
rādhaśuklatṛtīyāyāṃ tilāhāryavodanaiḥ |
pūjayitvā satī rudraṃ navyaimāṃsaṃ nināyatam || 21 ||
jyeṣṭhasya pūrṇimāyāṃ vai rātrau saṃpūjya śaṅkaram |
vasanairbṛhatīpuṣpairnirāhārā nināya tam || 22 ||
āṣāḍhasya caturdaśyāṃ śuklāyāṃ kṛṣṇavāsasā |
bṛhatīkusumaiḥ pūjā rudrasyākāri vai tathā || 23 ||
śrāvaṇasya sitāṣṭabhyāṃ caturdaśyāṃ ca sā śivam |
yajñopavītavāsobhiḥ pavitrairapyapūjayat || 24 ||
bhādre kṛṣṇatrayodaśyāṃ puṣpairnānāvidhaiḥ phalaiḥ |
saṃpūjya ca caturdaśyāṃ cakāra jalabhojanam || 25 ||
nānāvidhaiḥ phalaiḥ puṣpaissasyaistatkālasaṃbhavaiḥ |
cakre suniyatāhārāśvinamāse śivārcanam || 26 ||
sarvamāse sarvādine śivārcanaratā satī |
dṛḍhavratā bhaveddevī svecchādhṛtanarākṛtiḥ || 27 ||
itthaṃ nandāvrataṃ kṛṣṇa samāpya susamāhitā |
dadhyau śivaṃ satī premṇā niścalābhūdananyadhīḥ || 28 ||
etasminnantare devā munayaścākhilā mune |
viṣṇuṃ māṃ ca puraskṛtya yayurdraṣṭuṃ satītapaḥ || 29 ||
dṛṣṭāgatya satī devairbhūto siddhirivāparā |
śivadhyānamahātmā siddhāvasthāṃ gatā tadā || 30 ||
cakruḥ sarve surāssatyā mudā sāñjalayo natim |
munayaśca natskandhā viṣṇvādyāḥ prītamānasāḥ || 31 ||
atha sarve suprasannāḥ viṣṇvādyāśca surarṣayaḥ |
praśaśaṃsustapastasyāssatyāstasmātsavismayāḥ || 32 ||
tataḥ praṇamya tāṃ devīṃ punaste munayassurāḥ |
jagmurgirivaraṃ sadyaḥ kailāsaṃ śivavallabham || 33 ||
sāvitrīsahitaścāhaṃ saha lakṣmyā mudānvitaḥ |
vāsudevopi bhagavāñjagāmātha harāntikam || 34 ||
gatvā tatra prabhuṃ dṛṣṭvā supraṇamya susaṃbhramāḥ |
tuṣṭuvurvividhaistotraiḥ karau baddhvā vinamrakāḥ || 35 ||
devā ūcuḥ |
namo bhagavate tubhyaṃ yat etaccarācaram |
puruṣāya maheśāya pareśāya mahātmane || 36 ||
ādibījāya sarveṣāṃ cidrūpāya parāya ca |
brahmaṇe nirvikārāya prakṛteḥ puruṣasya ca || 37 ||
ya idaṃ pratipañcyedaṃ yenedaṃ vicakāsti hi |
yasmādidaṃ yataścedaṃ yasyedaṃ tvaṃ ca yatrataḥ || 38 ||
yo'smātparasmācca nirvikārī mahāprabhuḥ |
īkṣate yastvātmanīdaṃ taṃ natāḥ sma svayaṃsuvam || 39 ||
aviddhadṛk paraḥ sākṣī sarvātmānekarūpadhṛk |
ātmabhūtaḥ parabrahma tarpaṃ śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ || 40 ||
na yasya devā ṛṣayaḥ siddhāśca na viduḥ padam |
kaḥ punarjaiturapūro jñātumarhati vai ritum || 41 ||
didṛkṣavo yasya padaṃ muktasaṅgāssusādhavaḥ |
caranti sugatinastvaṃ sa lokavratamatraṇam || 42 ||
majjanmā divikārā no vidyate kepi duḥkhadāḥ |
tathāpi māyayā tvaṃ hi gṛhṇāsi kṛpayā ca tān || 43 ||
tasmai namaḥ pareśāya tubhyamāścaryakarmaṇe |
namo girāṃ vidūrāya brahmaṇe paramātmane || 44 ||
arūpāyorurūpāya parāyānantaśaktaye |
trilokapataye sarvasākṣiṇe sarvagāya ca || 45 ||
nama ātmapradīpāya

