nirvāṇasukhasaṃpade ||
jñānātmane namaste'stu vyāpakāyeśvarāya ca || 46 ||
naiṣkamryeṇa sulabhyāya kaivalyapataye namaḥ ||
puruṣāya pareśāya namaste sarva dāya ca || 47 ||
kṣetrajñāyātmarūpāya sarvapratyayahetave ||48||
sarvādhyakṣāya mahate mūlaprakṛtaye namaḥ ||
puruṣāya pareśāya namaste sarvadāya ca ||49||
trinetrāyeṣuvakāya sadābhāsāya te namaḥ ||
sarvendriyaguṇadraṣṭre niṣkāraṇa namostu te || 90 ||
trilokakāraṇāyāthāpavargāya namonamaḥ ||
apavargapradāyāśu śaraṇāgatavāriṇe || 51 ||
sarvāmnāyāgamānāṃ codadhaye parameṣṭhine |
parāyaṇāya bhaktānāṃ guṇānāṃ ca namostu te || 52 ||
namo guṇāraṇicchannacidūṣmāya maheśvara ||
mūḍhaduṣprāptarūpāya jñānihṛdvāsine sadā || 53||
paśupāśavimokṣāya bhaktasanmuktidāya ca ||
svaprakāśāya nityāyā'vyayāyājasrasaṃvide ||54||
pratyadraṣṭre'vikārāya paramaiśvaryadhāriṇe ||
yaṃ bhajanticaturvargaṃ kāmayatīṣṭasadgatim ||
so'bhūda karuṇastvaṃ naḥ prasanno bhava te namaḥ||55||
ekāṃtitaḥ kaṃcanārthaṃ bhaktā vāṃchaṃti yasya na ||
kevalaṃ caritaṃ te te gāyaṃti paramaṃgalam || 56 ||
akṣaraṃ paramaṃ brahma tamavyaktākṛtiṃ vibhum ||
adhyātmayogagamyaṃ tvāṃ paripūrṇa stumo vayam ||57||
atīṃdriyamanādhāraṃ sarvādhāramahetukam ||
anaṃtaṃmādyaṃ sūkṣmaṃ tvāṃ praṇamāmo'khileśvara || 58 ||
haryādayo'khilādevāstathā lokā śvarācarāḥ ||
nāmarūpavimedena phalgvyā ca kalayā kṛtāḥ || 59 ||
yathāciṣognessavituti niryāti vāsakṛt ||
gabhastayastathāyaṃ vai pravāṃhoṃ gauṇa ucyate || 60 ||
na tvaṃ devo'suro matyoṃ na tiryak na dvijaḥ prabho ||
na strī. na. paṃḍho na pumānkuryāssadasanna kiṃcanaṃ || 61 ||
niṣedhaśeṣassarvaṃ tvaṃ |
viśvakṛdviśvapālakaḥ ||
viśvalayakṛdviśvātmā praṇatāssmastamīśvaram || 62 ||
yogaraṃdhitakarmāṇo yaṃ prapaśyaṃti yoginaḥ ||
yogasaṃbhāvite ciṃtte yo geśaṃ tvāṃ natāvayam || 63 ||
namostu te'sahyavegaṃ śaktitraya trayīmaya |
namaḥ prasannapālāya namaste bhūriśaktaye || 64 ||
kadidriyāṇāṃ durgeśāna vāpyaparavartmane ||
bhaktoddhāraratāyātha namaste gūḍhavarcase || 65 ||
yacchaktyāhaṃ dhiyātmānaṃ iṃta veda na mūḍhadhīḥ ||
taṃ duratyayamāhātmyaṃ tvāṃ natāḥ smo mahāprabhum || 66 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti stutvā mahādevaṃ sarve viṣṇvādikāssurāḥ ||
tūṣṇīmāsanprabhora sadbhaktinatakaṃdharāḥ || 67 ||
iti śrī śivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ dvitīye satīkhaṃḍe naṃdāvratavidhānaśivastutivarṇanaṃ nāma paṃcadaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 15 || ||
brahmo vāca ||
itiḥ stutiṃ ca haryādikṛtāmākarṇya śaṃkaraḥ ||
babhūvātiprasanno hi vijahāse ca sūtikṛt || 1 ||
brahmaviṣṇū tu dṛṣṭvā tau satrīko saṃgatau haraḥ ||
yathocitaṃ samābhāṣya papracchāgamanaṃ tayoḥ || 2 ||
rudra uvāca ||
hehare he vidhe devā munayaścādyanirbhayāḥ ||
nijāgamanahetuṃ hi kathaṃyadhvaṃ suta ttvataḥ || 3 ||
kimarthamāgatā yūyaṃ kiṃ kāryaṃ ceha vidyate |
tatsarvaṃ śrotumicchāmi bhavatstutyā prasannadhīḥ || 4 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti pṛṣṭe hareṇāhaṃ sarvalokapitāmahaḥ ||
mune'vocaṃ mahādevaṃ viṣṇunā paricoditaḥ || 5 || ||
brahmovāca ||
devadeva mahādeva karuṇāsāgara prabho ||
