tacchṛṇu tvaṃ surarṣibhiḥ || 6 ||
viśeṣatastavaivārthamāgatā vṛṣabhadhvaja ||
sahārthinassadāyogyamanyathā na jagadbhavet || 7 ||
kecidbhaviṣyatyamurā rudra saṃ0 2 mama vadhyā maheśvara ||
harervadhyāstathā keṃcidbhavataścāpi kecana ||8||
kecittvadvīyajatasya tanayasya mahāprabho ||
māyābadhyāḥ prabho keṃcidbhaviṣyatyasu rāssadā || 9 ||
tavaiva kṛpayā śaṃbhossurāṇāṃ sukhamuttamam ||
nāśayitvā surān ghorāñjagatsvāsthyaṃ sadābhayam || 10 ||
yogayukte tvayi sadā rāga dveṣavivarjite ||
dayāmātraikanirate na vadhyā hyathavā tava || 11 ||
ārādhiteṣu teṣvīśaḥ kathaṃ sṛṣṭistathā sthitiḥ ||
ataśca bhavitā yuktaṃ nityanityaṃ vṛṣadhvaja || 12 ||
sṛṣṭisthityaṃtakarmāṇi na kāryāṇi yadā tadā ||
śarīrabhedamasmākaṃ māyāyāśca na yujyate || 13 ||
ekasvarūpā hi vayaṃ bhinnāḥ kāryasya bhedataḥ ||
kāryabhedo na siddhadrūpabhedo'prayojanaḥ || 14 ||
eka evaṃ tridhā bhinnaḥ paramātmā maheśvaraḥ ||
māyāsvākāraṇādeva svataṃtro līlayā prabhuḥ || 19 ||
vāmāṅgajo haristasya dakṣiṇāṃgabhavo hyaham ||
śivasya hṛdayājjātastvaṃ hi pūrṇataṃtuśśivaḥ || 16 ||
itthaṃ vayaṃ tridhā bhūtāḥ prabho bhinnasvarūpiṇaḥ ||
śivāśivasutāstattvaṃ hṛdā viddhi sanātana || 17 ||
ahaṃ viṣṇuśca sastrīko saṃjātau kāryahetutaḥ ||
lokakāryakarau prītyā tava śāsanataḥ prabho || 18 ||
tasmādviśvahitārthāya surāṇāṃ sukhahetave ||
parigṛhṇīṣvaṃ bhāryārthe rāmāmekāṃ suśobhanām || 19 ||
anyacchṛṇu mahe śāna pūrvavṛttaṃ smṛtaṃ mayā ||
yannau puraḥ purāproktaṃ tvayaiva śivarūpiṇā || 20 ||
madrūpaṃ paramaṃ brahmannīdṛśaṃ bhavadaṃgataḥ ||
prakaṭībhavitā loke nānā rudraḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 21 ||
sṛṣṭikartā'bhava brahmā hariḥ pālanakārakaḥ ||
layakārī bhaviṣyāmi rudrarūpo guṇākṛtiḥ || 22 ||
striyaṃḥ vivāhya lokasya karivye kāryamuttamam ||
iti saṃsmṛtya svaproktaṃ pūrṇa kuru nijaṃ paṇam || 23 ||
nideśastava ca svāminnahaṃ sṛṣṭikaro hariḥ ||
pālako laya |
hetustvamāvirbhūtassvayaṃ śivaḥ || 24 ||
tvāṃ vinā na samarthauhi āvāṃ ca svasvakarmaṇi ||
lokakāryaratāṃ tasmādekāṃ gṛhṇīṣva kāminīm || 25 ||
yathā padmālayā viṣṇossāvitrī ca yathā mama ||
tathā sahacarī śaṃbho kāṃtāṃ gṛhṇīṣva saṃprati || 26 ||
brahmovāca ||
iti śrutvā vaco me hi brahmapāḥ purato hareḥ ||
sa māṃ jagāda lokeśaḥ smerānanamukho haraḥ || 27 ||
īśvara uvāca ||
he brahman hehare me hi yuvāṃ priyatarau sadā ||
dṛṣṭvā vāṃ ca mamānaṃdo bhavatyatitarāṃ khalu || 28 ||
yuvāṃ suraviśiṣṭauṃ hi tribhavasvāminau kila ||
kathanaṃ vā gariṣṭhoti bhavakāryaratātmanoḥ || 29 ||
ucitaṃ na suraśreṣṭhau vivāhakaraṇaṃ mama ||
taporataviraktasya sadā viditayoginaḥ || 30 ||
yo nivṛttisumārgasthaḥ svātmārāmo niraṃjanaḥ ||
ava || 70 ||
dhūtatanurjñānī : svadraṣṭā kāmavarjitaḥ || 31 ||
