" dhunā || 32 ||
kevalaṃ yogalagnasya mamānaṃdassadāsti vai ||
jñānahīnastu puruṣo manute bahu kāmakam || 33 ||
vivāhakaraṇaṃ loke vijñeyaṃ paravaṃ dhanam ||
tasmāttasya rucinoṃ me satyaṃ satyaṃ vadāmyaham || 34 ||
na svārtha me pravṛttirhi samyaksvārthaviciṃtanāt ||
tathāpi tatkariṣyāmi bhavaduktaṃ jagaddhitam || 35 ||
matvā vaco gariṣṭhaṃ vā niyoktiparipūrtaye ||
kariṣyāmi vivāhaṃ vai bhaktavaśyassadā hyaham || 36 ||
paraṃtu yādṛśīṃ kāṃtāṃ grahīṣyāmi yathāṃ paṇam ||
tacchṛṇuṣva hare brahman yuktameva vaco mama || 37 ||
yā me tejassamarthī hi grahītuṃ syādvibhāṃ gaśaḥ ||
tāṃ nideśaya bhāyārthe yoginīṃ kāmarūpiṇīm || 38 ||
yogayukte mayi tathā yoginyeva bhaviṣyati ||
kāmāṃsakte mayi tathā kāminyeva bhavi ṣyati || 39 ||
yamakṣaraṃ vedavido nigradaṃti manīṣiṇaḥ ||
jyotīrūpaṃ śivaṃ te ca ciṃtayiṣye sanātanam || 40 ||
taccitāyāṃ yadā sakto brahman gacchā mi bhāvinīm ||
tatra yā vighnajananī na bhavitrī hatāstu me || 41 ||
tvaṃ vā viṣṇurahaṃ vāpi śivasya brahmarūpiṇaḥ ||
aṃśabhūtā mahābhāgā yogyaṃ tadanu ciṃtanam || 42 ||
tañcitayā vinodvāhaṃ sthāsyāmi kamalāsana ||
