aviśvāso madukteceṃnmayā tyaktā bhaviṣyati || 44 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti tasya vacaśśrutvāhaṃ sa viṣṇurharasya ca ||
sasmitaṃ modita mano'vocaṃ ceti vinamrakaḥ || 45 ||
śṛṇu nātha maheśāna mārgitā yādṛśī tvayā ||
nivedayāmi suprītyāṃ tāṃ striyaṃ tādṛśīṃ prabho || 46 ||
umā sā bhinnarūpeṇa saṃjātā kāryasādhinī ||
sarasvatī tathā lakṣmī dvidhā rūpā purā prabho || 47 ||
padmā kāṃtā'bhavadviṣṇostathā mama sarasvatī ||
tṛtī yarūpā sā nobhūlokakāryāhitaiṣiṇī || 48 ||
dakṣasya tanyā yābhūtsatī nāmnā tu sā vibho ||
saivedṛśī bhavedbhāryā bhaveddhi hitakāriṇī || 49 ||
sā tapasya tiṃ deveśa tvadatha hi dṛḍhavratā ||
tvāṃ patiṃ prāptukāmā vai mahātejovatī satī || 50 ||
dātuṃ gaccha varaṃ tasyai kṛpāṃ kuru maheśvara ||
tāṃ vivāhaya suprī tyā varaṃ datvā ca tādṛśam || 51 ||
harermama ca devānāmiyaṃ vāñcchāsti śaṃkara ||
paripūraya sadṛṣṭyā paśyāmotsavamādarāt || 52 ||
maṃgalaṃ paramaṃ bhūyātrilokeṣu sukhāvaham ||
sarvajvaro vinaśyedvai sarveṣāṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 53 ||
athavāsmadvacaśśeṣevadataṃ madhusūdanaḥ ||
līlājākṛtimīśānaṃ bhaktava tsalamacyutaḥ || 54 || ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
devadeva mahādeva karuṇākara śaṃkara ||
yaduktaṃ brahmaṇā sarva maduktaṃ tanna saṃśayaḥ || 55 ||
tatkuruṣvaṃ mahe śāna kṛpāṃ kṛtvā mamopari ||
sanārthaṃ kuru sadṛṣṭayā trilokaṃ suvivāhya |
tām || 56 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā bhagavān viṣṇustūṣṇīmāsa muneṃ sudhīḥ ||
tathā stutiṃ vihasyāha sa prabhurbhaktavatsalaḥ ||57||
tatastvāvāṃ ca saṃprāpya cājñāṃ sa munibhissuraiḥ ||
agacchāvasveṣṭadeśaṃ sastrīko paraharṣitau || || 58 ||
