śapto yadbhikṣuko rudro bhavadbhirmunibhistadā || 23 ||
śaptenāpi ca rudreṇa yatkṛtaṃ vismṛtaṃ katham ||
taliṃgenākhilaṃ dagdhaṃ bhuvanaṃ sacarācaram || 24 ||
sarve mūḍhāśca saṃjātā viṣṇubrahmādayassurāḥ ||
sunayo'nye vinā śaṃbhumāgatā yadihādhvare || 25 ||
sarve vedāśca saṃbhūtā sāṃgāśśāstrāṇi vāgyataḥ ||
yoso vedāṃtagaśśaṃbhuṃḥ kaśvijjñātuṃ na pāryate || 26 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityanekavidhā vāṇīragadajjagadambikā ||
kopānvitā satī tatraṃ hṛdayane vidū yatā || 27 ||
viṣṇvādayokhilā devā munayo ye ca tadvacaḥ ||
maunībhūtāstadākarṇya bhayavyākulamānasāḥ||28||
atha dakṣassamākarṇya svaputryāstādṛśaṃ vacaḥ ||
vilokya krūradṛṣṭyā tāṃ satīṃ kruddho'bravīdvacaḥ || 29 ||
dakṣa uvāca ||
tava kiṃ bahunoktena kāryaṃ nāstīha sāṃpratam ||
gaccha vā tiṣṭha vā bhadre kasmāttvaṃ hi samāgatā || 30 ||
amaṃgalastu te bhartā śivosau gamyate budhaiḥ ||
akulīkā vedabāhyo bhūtapretapiśācarāṭ || 31 ||
tasmānnāhvā rito rudro yajñārthaṃ sukuleṣabhṛt ||
devarṣisaṃsadi mayā jñātvā putri vipaścitāṃ || 32 ||
vidhinā preritena tvaṃ dattā maṃdena pāpinā ||
rudrāyā viditārthāya coddhatāya durātmane || 33 ||
tasmātkopaṃ parityajya svasthā bhava śucismite |
yadyāgatāsi yasmin dāyaṃ gṛhṇīṣva cātmanā || 34 ||
brahmo vāca ||
dakṣeṇokteti sā putrī satī trailokyapūjitā ||
niṃdāyuktaṃ svapitaraṃ dṛṣṭvāsīḍuṣitā bhṛśam || 35 ||
aciṃtayattadā seti kathaṃ yāsyāmi

--- Page 114 [gcv] ---
śaṃkaram ||
śaṃkaraṃ dṛṣṭukāmāhaṃ pṛṣṭā vakṣye kimuttaram || 36 ||
atha provāca pitaraṃ dakṣaṃ taṃ duṣṭamānasam ||
niśvasaṃtī ruṣāviṣṭā sā· satī trijagatprasūḥ || 37 ||
satyuvāca ||
yo niṃdati mahādevaṃ niṃdyamānaṃ śṛṇoti vā ||
tāvubhau narakaṃ yātau yāvaccandradivākarau || 38 ||
tasmāttyakṣyāmyahaṃ dehaṃ prave kṣyāmi hutāśanam ||
kiṃ jīvitena me tāta śṛṇvaṃtyānādaraṃ prabhoḥ || 39 ||
yadi śaktassvayaṃ śaṃbhornidakasya viśeṣataḥ ||
chiṃdyāt prasahya rasanāṃ tadā śuddhayenna saṃśayaḥ || 40 ||
yadyaśakto janastatra nirayātsupidhāya vai ||
karṇau dhīmān tataśśuddhayeddhadaṃtīdaṃ budhānvarān || 41 ||
brahmovāca ||
itthamuktvā dharmanīti paścāttāpamavāpa sā ||
asmaracchāṃkaraṃ vākyaṃ dūyamānena cetasā || 42 ||
tatassaṃkruddhya sā dakṣaṃ niśśaṃkaṃ prāha tānapi ||
sarvānviṣṇvā dikāndevānmunīnapi satī dhruvam || 43 ||
satyuvāca ||
tāta tvaṃ niṃdakaśśaṃbhoḥ paścāttāpaṃ gamiṣyasi ||
iha bhuktvā mahāduḥkhamaṃte yāsyasi yātanām || 44 ||
yasya loke'priyo nāsti priyaścaiva parātmanaḥ ||
tasminnavaire śarvaismin tvāṃ vinā kaḥ pratīpakaḥ || 45 ||
mahadviniṃdā nāśvaryaṃ sarvadā' satsu serṇyakam ||
mahaṃdaṃghrirajodhvastatamassu saiva śobhanā || 46 ||
śiveti vyaṃkṣaraṃ yasya nṛṇāṃ nāma gireritam |
sakṛtprasaṃgātsakalamaghamāśu vihaṃti tat || 47 ||
pavitrakīrtitamalaṃ bhavān dveṣṭi śivetaraḥ ||
alaṃghyaśāsanaṃ śaṃbhumaho sarveśvaraṃ khalaḥ || 48 ||
yatpādapadmaṃ mahatāṃ manolisuniṣevitam ||
sarvārthadaṃ brahmarasaiḥ sarvārthibhirathādarāt || 49 ||
yadvarṣatyarthinaśśīghraṃ lokasya śiva ādarāt ||
bhavān druhyati mūrkhatvāttasmai cāśeṣabaṃdhave || 52 ||
kiṃ vā śivākhyamaśivaṃ tvadanye na vidurbudhāḥ ||
brahmādayastaṃ munayassanakādyāstathā pare||51||
avakīrya jaṭā bhūtaiśśmaśāne sa kapāladhṛk ||
tanmālyabhasma vā jñātvā prītyāvasadudāradhīḥ || 52 ||
ye mūrddhabhirdadhati taccaraṇotsṛṣṭamādarāt ||
nirmālyaṃ munayo devāssaśivaḥ parameśvaraḥ || 53 ||
pravṛttaṃ ca nivṛttaṃ ca dvividhaṃ karma coditam ||
vede vivicya vṛttaṃ ca tadvicārya manīṣibhiḥ || 54 ||
virodhiyaugapadyekakartṛke ca tathā dvayam ||
parabrahmāṇi śaṃbhau tu karmacchati na kicana || 55 ||
mā vaḥ padavyassma pitaḥ yā asmadāsthitāssadā ||
yajñaśālāsu vo dhūmravartmabhuktojjhitāḥ param || 56 ||
noḍa vyaktaliṃgassatatamavadhūtasusevitaḥ ||
abhimānamato na tvaṃ kuru tāṃta kubuddhidhṛk || 57 ||
ki vahūktena vacasā duṣṭastvaṃ sarvathā kudhīḥ ||
tvadudbha vena dehena na me kiṃcitprayojanam || 58 ||
tajjanmadhigyo mahatāṃ sarvathāvadyakṛtkhalaḥ ||
parityājyo viśeṣeṇa tatsaṃbaṃdho vipaścitā || 59 ||
gotraṃ tvadīyaṃ bhagavān yadāha vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ ||
dākṣāyaṇīti sahasāhaṃ bhavāmi sudurmanāḥ || 60 ||
tasmāttvadaṃgajaṃ dehaṃ kuṇapaṃ. garhitaṃ sadā ||
vyutsṛjya mūnama dhunā bhaviṣyāmi sukhāvahā || 61 ||
he surā munayassarve yūyaṃ śṛṇuta madvacaḥ ||
sarvathānucitaṃ karma yuṣmākaṃ duṣṭacetasām || 62 ||
sarve yūyaṃ vimūḍhā

