brahmovāca ||
maunībhūtā satī devī smṛtvā svapatimādarāt ||
kṣitāvudīcyāṃ sahasā niṣasāda praśāṃtadhīḥ ||2||
jalamācamya vidhivat saṃvṛtā vāsasā śuciḥ ||
dṛnimīlya patiṃ smṛtvā yogamārga samāviśat || 3 ||
kṛtvā samānāvanilau prāṇāpānau sitānanā ||
utthāpyodānamatha ca yatnātsā nābhicakrataḥ || 4 ||
hṛdi sthāpyorasi dhiyā sthitaṃ kaṃṭhādbhuvossatī ||
aniṃditānayanmadhyaṃ śaṃkaraprāṇavallabhā || 9 ||
evaṃ svadehaṃ sahasā dakṣako pājjihāsatī ||
dagdhe gātre vāyuśucidhāraṇaṃ yogamārgataḥ || 6 ||
tatassvabhartuścaraṇaṃ ciṃtayaṃtī na cāparam ||
apaśyatsā satī tatra yogamārganiviṣṭadhīḥ || 7 ||
hatakalmaṣataddehaḥ prāpatañcaḥ tadagninā ||
bhasmasādabhavatsadyo muniśreṣṭha tadicchyā || 8 ||
tatpaśyatāṃ ca khe bhūmau vādo'bhūtsumahāṃstadā ||
hāheti soḍataścitrassurādīnāṃ bhayāvahaḥ || 9 ||
ta priyā parā śaṃbhodevī daivatamasya hi ||
ahādasūna satī kena suduṣṭena prakopitā || 10 ||
aho tvanātmyaṃ sumahadasya dakṣasya paśyata ||
carācaraṃ prajā yasya yatputrasya prajāpateḥ || 11 ||
ahā dyadvimanā'bhūtsā satī devī manasvinī ||
vṛṣadhvajapriyā'bhīkṣṇaṃ mānayogyā satāṃ sadā || 12 ||
soyaṃ durmarṣahṛdayo brahmakū sa prajāpatiḥ ||
mahatīmapa kīrti hi prāpsyati tvakhile bhave || 13 ||
yatsvāṃgajāṃ sutāṃ śaṃbhudviṭ nyaṣedhatsamudyatām ||
mahānarakabhogī sa mṛtaye no'parādhataḥ || 14 ||
vaṃdatyevaṃ jane satyā dṛṣṭvā'sutyāgamadbhutam ||
drutaṃ tatpārṣadāḥ krodhādudatiṣṭhannudāyudhāḥ || 19 ||
dvāri sthitā gaṇāssarve rasāyutamitā ruṣā ||
śaṃkarasya prabho ste vā'krudhyannatimahābalāḥ || 16 ||
hāhākāramakuvaiste dhidhika na iti vādinaḥ ||
uccaissarve'sakṛdvīrāśśaṃkarasya gaṇādhipāḥ || 17 ||
hāhā kāreṇa mahatā vyāptamāsīddigantaram ||
sarve prāpana bhayaṃ devā munayonyepi testhitāḥ || 18 ||
gaṇāssaṃmaṃtrya te sarve'bhūvan kruddhā udāyudhāḥ ||
kurvantaḥ pralayaṃ vādyaśastrairvyāptaṃ digaṃtaram || 19 ||
śastrairaghnannijāṃgāni kecittatra śucākulāḥ ||
śiromukhāni devarṣe sutīkṣṇaiḥ prāṇanāśibhiḥ || 20 ||
itthaṃ te vilayaṃ prāptā dākṣāyaṇyā samaṃ tadā ||
gaṇāyute dve ca tadā tadadbhutamivābhavat || 21 ||
gaṇā nāśā'vaśiṣṭā ye śaṃkarasya mahātmanaḥ ||
dakṣaṃ || 86||
taṃ krodhitaṃ hantuṃ mudātiṣṭhannudāyudhāḥ || 22 ||
teṣāmāpatatāṃ vegaṃ niśamya bhagavān bhṛguḥ ||
yajñaghnaghnena yajuṣāṃ dakṣiṇāgnau juhonmune || 23 ||
