kecidviṣṇuṃ prabhuṃ tatraṃ prārthayantassamantataḥ ||
udvignā mantrayaṃtaśca vinābhāvaṃ muhurmuhuḥ || 29 ||
suvicāryodarkaphalamaho dvignāssubuddhayaḥ||
suraviṣṇvādayobhūvan tannāśadrāvaṇānmuhuḥ || 30 ||
evaṃ bhūtastadā yajño vighno jāto durātmanaḥ|
