. tmanā ||
apamānaḥ kṛtassatyā'nādaro nirjaraistathā || 7 ||
tubhyaṃ bhāgamadānno sa devebhyaśca pradattavān ||
durvacāṃsyavadatproccairduṣṭo dakṣassugarvitaḥ || 8 ||
tato dṛṣṭvā na te bhāgaṃ yajñe'kupyatsaṃtī prabho ||
viniṃdya bahuśastātamadhākṣīt svatanuṃ tadā || 9 ||
gaṇāstvayutasaṃkhyākā mṛtāstatra vilajjayā ||
svāṃgānyāchiya śastraiśca krudhyāma hyapare vayam || 10 ||
tadyajñaṃ dhvaṃsituṃ vegātsannaddhāstu bhayāvahāḥ : ||
tiraskṛtā hi bhṛguṇā svaprabhāvādvirodhinā || 11 ||
te vayaṃ śaraṇaṃ prāptāstava viśvaṃbhara prabho ||
