tvāṃ praśasyātha sa svāmī satyā vārttā ca pṛṣṭavān ||
dakṣayajñagatayā vai paraṃ ca caritaṃ tathā || 17 ||
pṛṣṭena śaṃbhunā tāta tvayāśveva śivātmanā ||
tatsarvaṃ kathitaṃ vṛttaṃ jātaṃ dakṣādhvare hi yat || 18 ||
tadāṃkaṇyaiśvaro vākyaṃ mune tattvanmukhoditam ||
cukopātidbhutaṃ rudro mahāraudraparākramaḥ || 19 ||
utpāṭyaikāṃ jaṭāṃ rudro lokasaṃhārakārakaḥ||
āsphālayāmāsa ruṣā parvatasya tadopari || 20 ||
todanāṃcca dvidhā bhūtā sā jaṭā ca sune prabhoḥ ||
saṃbabhūva mahārāvo mahāpralayabhīṣaṇaḥ || 21 ||
tajaṭāyāssamudbhūtoṃ vīrabhadro |
mahābalaḥ ||
pūrvabhāgena devarṣe mahābhīmo gaṇāgraṇīḥ || 22 ||
sa bhūmiṃ viśvato vṛtyātyatiṣṭhaddaśāṃgulam ||
pralayānala saṃkāśaḥ pronnato dossahasravān || || 23 ||
kopaniḥśvāsatastatra mahārudrasya ceśituḥ ||
jātaṃ jvarāṇāṃ śatakaṃ saṃnipātāstrayodaśa || 24 ||
mahākālī samutpannā tajjaṭāparabhā gataḥ ||
mahābhayaṃkarā tāta bhūtakoṭibhirāvṛtā || 25 ||
sarve mūrttidharā krūrāḥ jvarā lokabhayaṃkarāḥ ||
svatejasā prajvalaṃto dahaṃta iva sarvataḥ || 26 ||
atha vīro vīrabhadraḥ praṇamya parameśvaram ||
kṛtāṃjalipuṭaḥ prāha vākyaṃ vākyaviśāradaḥ || 27 ||
vīrabhadra uvāca ||
mahārudra mahāraudra somasūryāgni locana ||
kiṃ kartavyaṃ mayā kārya śīghramājñāpaya prabho || 28 ||
śoṣaṇīyāḥ kimīśāna kṣaṇārddhenaiva siṃghavaḥ ||
peṣaṇīyāḥ kimīśāna kṣaṇādai naiva parvatāḥ || 29||
kṣaṇena bhasmasātkuryyāṃ brahmāṃḍata kiṃ hara ||
kṣaṇena bhasmasātkuryāmmurānvā kiṃ munīśvarān || 30 ||
vyāśvāsaḥ sarvalokānāṃ kimu kāryoṃ hi śaṃkara ||
kartavyaṃ kimuteśāna sarvaprāṇivihiṃsanam || 31 ||
mamāśakyaṃ na kutrāpi tvatprasādānmadeśvara ||
parākrameṇa mattalyo na bhūto na bhaviṣya ti||32||
yatra yatkāryamuddiśya preṣayiṣyasi māṃ prabhau |
tatkāryaṃ sādhayāmyeva satvaraṃ tvatprasādataḥ||33||
kṣudrāstaraṃti lokābdhi śāsanācchaṃkarasya te ||
