maheśvara uvāca ||
śṛṇu madvacanaṃ tāta vīrabhadra sucetasā |
karaṇīyaṃ prayatnena tadvarttuṃ me pratoṣakam || 46 ||
yāgaṃ karttuṃ samudyukto dakṣo vidhisutaḥ khalaḥ |
madvirodhī viśeṣeṇa mahāgarvo'budho'dhunā || 47 ||
tanmakhaṃ bhasmasāt kṛtvā sayāgaparivārakam |
punarāyāhi matsthānaṃ satvaraṃ gaṇa satvaram || 48 ||
surā bhavantu gandharvā yakṣā vānye ca kecana |
