api cābhaiva tānsarvānpātayasva prayatnataḥ || 50 ||
surā bhavantu gandharvā yakṣā vānye ca kecana |
tānapyevaiva sahasā bhasmasātkuru satvaram || 51 ||
dadhīcicakṛtacchandyaṃ śapathaṃ mayi tatra ye |
