raṇaṃ hitvā gatāḥ pūrvaṃ te drutaṃ punarāyayuḥ || 8 ||
vīrabhadragaṇaisteṣāṃ lokapālāssavāsavāḥ ||
yuddhāñcakrustathā siṃhanādaṃ kṛtvā balānvitāḥ || 5 ||
gaṇānāṃ lokapālānāṃ dvaṃdvayuddhaṃ bhayāvaham ||
abhavattatra tumulaṃ garjatāṃ siṃha nādataḥ || 6 ||
nandinā yuyudhe śakro'nalo vai vaiṣṇavāstathā ||
kuberopi hi kūṣmāṃḍapatiśca yuyudhe balī || 7 ||
tadendreṇa hato nandī vajreṇa śataparvaṇā || 8 ||
nandinā ca hataśśatriśūlena stanāṃtare || 9 ||
balinau dvāvapi prītyā yuyudhāte parasparam ||
nānācā tāni kurvatau nandiśakau jigīṣayā || 10 ||
śaktyā jaghāna cāśmānaṃ śuciḥ paramakopanaḥ ||
sopi śūlena taṃ vegācchitadhāreṇa pāvakam || 11 ||
yamena saha saṃgrāmaṃ mahāloko gaṇāgraṇīḥ ||
cakāra tumulaṃ vīro mahādevaṃ smaranmudā || 12 ||
nairṛtena samāgamya caṃḍaśca balavattaraḥ ||
yuyudhe paramāstraiśca nairṛtiṃ niviḍaṃbayan || 13 ||
varuṇena samaṃ vīro muṃḍaścaiva mahābalaḥ ||
yuyudhe parayā śaktyā trilokīṃ visma yanniva || 14 ||
vāyunā ca hato bhṛṃgī, svāstreṇa paramojasā ||
bhṛṃgiṇā ca hato vāyutriśūlena pratāpināḥ || 19 ||
kuberaṇaiva saṃgamya kūṣmāṃḍapati rādarāt ||
yuyudhe balavān vīro dhyātvā hṛdi maheśvaram || 16 ||
yoginīcakrasaṃyukto bhairavīnāyako mahān ||
vidāryyaṃ devānakhilān papau śoṇi taṃmadbhutam || 17 ||
kṣetrapālāṃstathā tatra bubhukṣuḥ surapuṃgavān ||
kāṃlī cāpi vidāryaiva tānpapau rudhiraṃ bahu || 18 ||
atha viṣṇurmahātejā yuyudhe taiśca śatruhā ||
cakraṃ cikṣepa vegena dahanniva diśo daśa || 19 ||
kṣetrapālassamāyāṃtaṃ cakramālokya vegataḥ ||
tatrāgatyāgato vīraśvāgrasatsahasā balī ||
