tasya cakraṃ mahāraudraṃ kālādityasamaprabham ||
vyaṣṭaṃbhayadadīnātmā vīrabhadraśśivaḥ prabhuḥ || 35 ||
mune śaṃbhoḥ prabhāvāttu māyeśasya mahāprabhoḥ ||
na cacāla hareśvakaṃ karasthaṃ staṃrbhitaṃ dhruvam || 36 ||
atha viṣṇuṃ gaṇe śena· vīrabhadreṇa bhāṣatā ||
atiṣṭhatstaṃbhitastena śṛṃgavāniva niścalaḥ || 37 ||
tato viṣṇuḥ staṃbhito hi vīrabhadreṇa nārada |
yajvopamaṃtraṇama nā nīrastaṃbhanakārakam || 38 ||
tatastaṃbhananirmuktaḥ śārṅgadhanvā rameśvaraḥ ||
