jñātvā ca tatsarvamidaṃ bhaviṣyaṃ satī kṛtaṃ duṣprasahaṃ pareṣām ||
gatāḥ svalokaṃ svagaṇānvitāstu smṛtvāṃ śivaṃ sarvapatiṃ svataṃtram || 42 ||
satyalokagataścāhaṃ putraśokena pīḍitaḥ ||
acitayaṃ suduḥkhārto mayā kiṃ kāryamadya vai || 43 ||
viṣṇau mayi gate caiva devāca munibhissaha |
vinirjitā gaṇaissarve ye te yajñopajīvinaḥ || 44 ||
samupadravamālakṣya vidhvastaṃ ca mahāmakham ||
mṛgasvarūpo yajño hi mahābhīto'pi dudraveṃ || 45 ||
