mṛtyuṃjayāya śokāya triguṇāya guṇātmane ||
candrasūryāgninetrāya sarvakāra setave || 41 ||
bhavatā hi jagatsarvaṃ vyāptaṃ svenaiva tejasā ||
parabrahma nirvikārī cidānaṃdaḥ prakāśavān || 42 ||
brahmaviṣṇvadracandrādipramukhāssa kalāssurāḥ ||
sunayaścāpare tvattassaṃprasūtā maheśvara || 43 ||
yato bibharṣi sakalaṃ vibhajya tanumaṣṭadhā ||
aṣṭamūrtiritīśaśca tvamādyaḥ karuṇā mayaḥ || 44 ||
tvadbhayādvāti vātoyaṃ dahatyagnirbhayāttava ||
sūryastapati te bhītyā mṛtyurdhāvati sarvataḥ || 45 ||
dayāsindho maheśāna prasīda parame śvara ||
rakṣa rakṣa sadaivāsmān yasmānnaṣṭān vicetasaḥ || 46 ||
rakṣitāḥ satataṃ nātha tvayaiva karuṇānidhe ||
nānāpadbhyo vayaṃ śaṃbho tathaivādya prapāhi naḥ || 47 ||
yajñasyoddharaṇaṃ nātha kuru śīghraṃ prasādakṛt ||
asamāptasya durgeśa dakṣasya ca prajāpateḥ || 48 ||
bhagokṣiṇī prapadyeta yajamānaśca jīvatu ||
pūṣṇo daṃtāśva rohaṃtu bhṛgoḥ śmaśrūṇi pūrvavat || 49 ||
bhavatānugrahītānāṃ devādīnāṃ ca sarvaśaḥ ||
ārogyaṃ bhagnagātrāṇāṃ śaṃkaratvāyudhāśmābhiḥ || 50 ||
pūrṇabhāgostu te nātha vasiṣṭho dhvarakarmaṇi ||
rudrabhāgena yajñaste kalpito nānyathā kvacit || 51 ||
ityuktvā saprajeśaśca. rameśaśca kṛtāṃjaliḥ ||
daṃḍavatpatito bhūmau kṣamāpayitumudyataḥ || 52 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ dvitīye satīkhaṃḍe devastutivarṇanaṃ nāmai kacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 41 || ||
