paraṃ dveṣṭi pareṣāṃ yadātmanastadbhaviṣyati || 5 ||
pareṣāṃ kledanaṃ karma na kārya tatka dācana ||
paraṃ dveṣṭi pareṣāṃ yadātmanastadbhaviṣyati || 6 ||
