mitranetreṇa saṃpaśyedyajñabhāgaṃ bhagassuraḥ || 7 ||
pūṣābhidhassurastātau dadbhiryajñasupiṣṭak ||
yājamānairbhagnadaṃtassatyametanmayoditam ||8||
bastaśmaśrurbhavedeva bhṛgurmama virodhakṛt ||
devāḥ prakṛti sarvāṃgā ye ma ucchedanaṃ daduḥ ||9||
bāhubhyāmaśvinau pūṣṇo hastābhyāṃ kṛtavāhakaḥ ||
bhavatvadhvaryavaśvānye bhavatprītyā mayoditam || 10||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā parame śāṃno virarāma dayānvitaḥ ||
carācarapatirdevaḥ samrāṭ vedānusārakṛt || 11||
tadā sarve surādyāste śrutvā śaṃkarabhāṣitam||
sādhu sādhviti saṃprocuḥ parituṣṭāḥ saviṣṇujāḥ ||12||
tataśśaṃbhuṃ samāmaṃtrya mayā viṣṇussurarṣibhiḥ||
bhūyastaddevayajanaṃ yayau ca parayā mudā || 13||
evaṃ teṣāṃ prārthanayā viṣṇuprabhṛtibhissuraiḥ ||
