. ||
nārada uvāca ||
viṣṇuśiṣya mahāśaiva samyaguktaṃ tvayā vidhe ||
caritaṃ paramaṃ hyetacchivāyāśca śivasya ca || 1 ||
kastārakāsuro brahmanyena devāḥ prapīḍitāḥ ||
kasya putrassa vai brūhi tatkathāṃ ca śivāśrayām || 2 ||
bhasmīcakāra sa kathaṃ śaṃkaraśca smaraṃ vaśī ||
tadapi brūhi suprītyādbhutaṃ tacca ritaṃ vibhoḥ || 3 ||
kathaṃ śivā tapo'tyugraṃ cakāra sukhahetave ||
kathaṃ prāpa patiṃ śaṃbhumādiśaktirjagatparā || 4 ||
etatsarvamaśeṣeṇa viśeṣeṇa mahā budha ||
brūhi me śraddadhānāya svaputrāya śivātmane || 5 || ||
brahmovāca ||
putravarya mahāprājña surarṣe śaṃsitavrata ||
vacmyahaṃ śaṃkaraṃ smṛtvā sarvaṃ tacca ritaṃ śṛṇu || 6 ||
prathamaṃ tārakasyaiva bhavaṃ saṃśṛṇu nārada |
yadvadhārthaṃ mahāyatnaḥ kṛto devaiśśivāśrayaiḥ || 7 ||
mama putro marīciryaḥ kaśyapastasya cātmajaḥ ||
trayodaśamitāstasya striyo dakṣatāśca yāḥ || 8 ||
ditijrjyeṣṭhā ca tatstrī hi suṣuve sā sutadvayam ||
hiraṇya kaśipujyaiṣṭho 'hiraṇyākṣo'nujastataḥ || 9 ||
tau hatā. viṣṇunā daityo nṛsiṃhakroḍarūpataḥ ||
suduḥkhadau tato devāḥ sukhamāpuśca nirbhayāḥ || || 10 ||
ditiśca duḥkhitāsītsā kaśyapaṃ śaraṇaṃ gatā ||
punassaṃsevya taṃ bhaktyā garbhamādhatta suvratā || 11 ||
tadvijñāya maheṃdro'pi labdhacchidro mahodyamī ||
tadgarbhe vyacchinattaṃtraṃ praviśya pavinā muhuḥ || 12 ||
tadvatasya prabhāveṇa na tadbhoṃ mamāra ha ||
svapatyā daivayogena. sapta saptābhavansutāḥ || 13 ||
devā āsansutāste ca 'nāmato maruto'khilāḥ ||
svargaḥ yayustadendreṇa devarājātmasātkṛtāḥ || 14 ||
punarditiḥ patiṃ bheje'nutaptā nijakarmataḥ ||
cakāra suprasannaṃ taṃ muniṃ paramasevayā || 15 || ||
kaśyapa uvāca ||
tapaḥ kuru śucirbhūtvā brahmaṇaścāyutaṃ samāḥ ||
cedbhaviṣyati tatpūrvaṃ bhavitā te sutastadā || 16 ||
tathā dityā kṛtaṃ pūrṇa tattapaśśraddhayā mune ||
tataḥ patyuḥ prāpya garbha suṣuve tādṛśaṃ sutam || || 17 ||
vajrāṃganāmā so'bhṛdvai ditiputro'maropamaḥ ||
nāmatulyata nuvarassupratāpyudbhavādvalī || 18 ||
jananīśāsanātsadyassa suto nirjarādhipam ||
valāddhṛtvā dadau daṃḍaṃ vividhaṃ nirjarānapi || 19 ||
ditissukhamatīvāpa dṛṣṭvā śakrādidurdaśām ||
amarā api śakrādyā jagmurduḥkhaṃ svakarmataḥ || 20 ||
tadāhaṃ kaśyapenāśu tatrāgatya susāmagīḥ ||
devānatyājayaṃstasmātsadā devahite rataḥ || 21 ||
devānmuktvā sa vatrāṃ gastataḥ provāca sādaram ||
śivabhakto'tiśuddhātmā nirvikāraḥ prasannadhīḥ || 22 || ||
vajrāga uvāca ||
iṃdro duṣṭaḥ prajāghātī mārtumai svārthasādhakaḥ ||
saḥ phalaṃ prāptavānadya svarājyaṃ hi karotu saḥ || 23 ||
māturājñāvaśādrahmankṛtametanmayākhilam ||
na me bhogābhilāṣo vai kasyacidbhuvanasya hi ||24||
tattvasāraṃ vidhe brūhi mahyaṃ vedavidāmvara ||
yena syāṃ susukhī nityaṃ nirvikāraḥ prasannadhīḥ || 25 ||
tacchrutvā mune'vocaṃ sāttviko bhāva ucyate ||
tattva

