atha tatsevanādāśu saṃtuṣṭo'bhūnmahāprabhuḥ ||
sa vajrāṃgaḥ patistasyā' uvāca vacanaṃ tadā || 30 || ||
vajrāṃga uvāca ||
kimicchasi priye brūhi kiṃ te manasi vartate ||
tacchrutvānamya taṃ prāha sā patiṃ svamanoratham || 31 || ||
varāṃgyu vāca ||
cet prasanno'bhavastvaṃ vai sutaṃ me dehi satpate ||
mahābalaṃ trilokasya jetāraṃ hariduḥkhadam || 32 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti śrutvā priyāvākyaṃ vi smito'bhūtsa ākulaḥ ||
uvāca hṛdi sa jñānī sāttriko vairavarjitaḥ || 33 ||
priyecchati virodhaṃ vai surairme na hi rocate ||
kiṃ kuryā hi ka gaccheyaṃ kathaṃ naśyenna me paṇaḥ || 34 ||
priyāmanorathaścaiva pūrṇassyātrijagadbhavet ||
keśayunitarāṃ bhūyo devāśca munayastathā || 35 ||
na pūrṇassyāṃtpriyā kāmastadā me narako bhavet ||
dvidhāpi dharmahānirvai bhavatītyanuśuśruvān || 36 ||
vajrāṃga itthaṃ babhrāma saṃ mune dharmasaṃkaṭe ||
balābalaṃ dvayostatra vicici ta ca buddhitaḥ || 37 ||
śivecchayā sa hi mune vākyaṃ mene striyo budhaḥ ||
tathāstviti vacaḥ prāha priyāṃ prati sa daityarāṭ || 38 ||
tadarthamakarottīvaṃ taponyaduṣkaraṃ sa tu ||
māṃ samuddiśya suprītyā bahuvarṣe jiteṃdriyaḥ || 39 ||
varaṃ dātumagāṃ tasmai dṛṣṭvāhaṃ tattapo mahat ||
varaṃ brūhi hyavocaṃ taṃ suprannena cetasā || 40 ||
vajrāṃgastu tadā prītaṃ māṃ dṛṣṭvā khe sthitaṃ vibhum ||
supraṇamya bahu stutvā varaṃ vatre priyāhitam || 41 ||
vajrāṃga uvāca ||
sutaṃ dehi svamāturme mahāhitakaraṃ prabho ||
mahābalaṃ supratāpaṃ susamartha taponidhim || 42 ||
brahmovāca ||
ityākarṇya ca tadvākyaṃ tathāstvitya bruvaṃ sune ||
aryāṃ svadhāma taddatvā vimanāssaṃsmaracchidam || 43 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṃḍe tārakotpa tau vajrāṃgotpatitapovarṇanaṃ nāma caturddaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 14 ||
brahmovāca ||
atha sā garbhamādhatta varāṃgī tatpurādarāt ||
sa vavarddhābhyatare hi bahu varṣaiḥ sutejasā || 1 ||
tataḥ sā samaye pūrṇe varāṃgī suṣuve sutam ||
mahākāyaṃ mahāvīrya prajvalaṃta diśo daśa || 2 ||
tadaiva ca mahotpātā babhūvurduḥkhahe tavaḥ ||
jāyamāne sute tasminvarāṃgyāssuraduḥkhade || 3 ||
divi suvyaṃtarikṣe ca sarvalokabhayaṃkarāḥ ||
anarthasūcakāstāta trividhāstānbravīmyaham || 4 ||
solkāśvāśanayaḥ peturmahāśabdā bhayaṃkarāḥ ||
udayaṃ cakrurutkṛṣṭāḥ ketavo duḥkhadāyakāḥ || 5 ||
cacāla vasudhā sādirjajvalussakalā diśaḥ ||
cakṣukṣussaritassarvāḥ sāgarāśca viśeṣataḥ || 6 ||
hūtkārānīrayandhīrānkharasparśo marudravauṃ ||
unmūlayanmahāvṛkṣānvātyānīko

