mahībhravivarebhyaśca nirghātā bhayasūcakāḥ ||
rathanirhrādatulyāśca jajñire'vasare tataḥ || 9 ||
sṛgālolūkaṭaṃkārairvamantyo mukhato'nalam ||
aṃtargrāmeṣu vikaṭaṃ praṇeduraśivā śśivāḥ || 10 ||
