saṃgītavadrodanavadvayamuṃ canvividhānravān || 11 ||
khārkārarabhasā mattāḥ khuraighnato rasāṃ kharāḥ ||
varūthaśastadā tāta paryadhāvannitastataḥ || 12 ||
khagā udayatannīḍādrāsabhatrastamānasāḥ ||
krośaṃto vyagracittāśca sthitimāpurna kutracit || 13 ||
śakṛnmūtramakārṣuśca goṣṭhe'raṇye bhayākulāḥ ||
babhramuḥ sthitimāpuna paśavastāḍitā iva || 14 ||
gāvo'trasannasṛgdohā bāṣpanetrā bhayākulāḥ ||
toyadā abhavaṃstatra bhayadāḥ pūyavarṣiṇaḥ || 15 ||
vyarudanpratimāstatra devānāmutpatiṣṇavaḥ ||
vinā'nilaṃ drumāḥ peturgrahayuddhaṃ babhūva khe || 16 ||
ityādikā bahutpātā jajñire munisattama ||
ajñānino janāstatra menire viśvasaṃplavam || 17 ||
atha prajāpatirnāmākarottasyāsurasya vai ||
