atha sa tārako daityo mahābalaparākramaḥ |
tapaḥ kartuṃ jananyāśvājñāṃ yayāce mahāmanāḥ || 20 ||
prāptājñaḥ sa mahāmāyī māyināmapi mohakaḥ ||
sarvadevajayaṃ kartuṃ taporthaṃ mana ādadhe || 21 ||
madhorvanamupāgamya gurvājñāpratipālakaḥ ||
vidhimuddi śya vidhivattapastepe sudāruṇam || 22 ||
ūrddhabāhuścaikapādo raviṃ paśyansa cakṣuṣā ||
śatavarṣa tapaścakre dṛḍhacito dṛḍhavrataḥ ||23||
aṃguṣṭhena bhuvaṃ spṛṣṭvā śatavarṣe ca tādṛśaḥ ||
tepe tapo dṛḍhātmā sa tārako'surarāṭ prabhuḥ || 24 ||
śatavarṣaṃ jalaṃ prāśnañcchatavarṣe ca vāyuyuk ||
śatavarṣe jale tiṣṭhañcchataṃ ca sthaṃḍi letapat || 25 ||
śatavarṣaṃ tathā cāgnau śatavarṣamadhomukhaḥ ||
śatavarṣe tu hastasya talena ca bhuvaṃ sthitaḥ || 26 ||
śatavarṣe tu vṛkṣasya śākhāmālaṃbya vai suneḥ ||
padābhyāṃ śucidhūmaṃ hi pibaṃścādhomukhastathā || 27 ||
evaṃ kaṣṭataraṃ tepe sutapassa tu daityarāṭ ||
kāmamuddiśya - vidhivacchṛṇvatāmapi dussaham || 28 ||
tatraivaṃ tapatastasya mahattejo vinissṛtam ||
śirasassarvasaṃsarpi mahopadravakṛnsune || 29 ||
tenaiva devalokāste dagdhaprāyā babhūvire ||
abhito duḥkhamāpannāssarve devarṣayo sune || 30 ||
iṃdraśva bhayamāpede'dhikaṃ deveśvarastadā ||
tapasyatyadya kaśvidvai matpadaṃ dharṣayiṣyati || 31 ||
akāṃḍaṃ caiva brahmāṇḍaṃ saṃhariṣyatyayaṃ prabhuḥ ||
iti saṃśayamāpannā niścayaṃ nopalebhire || 32 ||
tatassarve susaṃmantrya mithaste nirjararṣayaḥ ||
mallokamagamanbhītā dīnā māṃ samupasthitāḥ || 33 ||
māṃ praṇamya susaṃstūya sarve te kliṣṭacetasaḥ ||
kṛtasvaṃjalayo mahyaṃ

