advitīyaḥ prabhuścāsīdrājyaṃ cakre'dbhutaṃ vaśī || 54 ||
nissārya, sakalānde vāndaityānasthāpayattataḥ ||
svayaṃ niyojayāmāsa devayonissvakarmaṇiḥ || 55 ||
atha tadvādhitā devāssarve śakrapurogamāḥ ||
sune māṃ śaraṇaṃ jagmura nāthā ativihvalāḥ || 56 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṃḍe tārakāsurataporājyavarṇanaṃ nāma paṃcadaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 15 || ||
brahmovāca ||
atha te nirjarāssarve supraṇamya prajeśvaram ||
tuṣṭuvuḥ parayā bhaktyā tārakeṇa prapīḍitāḥ || 1 ||
ahaṃ śrutvāmaranutiṃ yathārthī hṛdayaṃgamām ||
suprasannataro bhūtvā pratyavocaṃ divaukasaḥ || 2 ||
svāgataṃ svādhikārā vai nirvighnāḥ saṃti vassurāḥ ||
kimarthamāgatā yūya

--- Page 170 [gcv] ---
matra sarve vadaṃtu me ||3||
iti śrutvā vaco me te natvā sarve divaukasaḥ||
māmūcurnatakā dīnāstārakeṇa prapīḍitāḥ ||4||
devā ūcuḥ||
lokeśa tārako daityo vareṇa tava darpitaḥ ||
nirasyāsmānhaṭhātsthānānyagrahīnno balātsvayam ||5||
bhavataḥ kimu na jñātaṃ duḥkhaṃ yantra upasthitam ||
tadduḥkhaṃ nāśaya kṣipraṃ vayaṃ te śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ||6||
aharniśaṃ bādhatesmānyatra tatrāsthitānsa vai ||
palāyamānāḥ paśyāmo yatra tatrāpi tārakam ||7||
tārakānnaśca yadduḥkhaṃ saṃbhūtaṃ sakale śvara ||
tena sarve vayaṃ tāta pīḍitā vikalā ati || 8 ||
agniryamo'thaṃ varuṇo nirṛtirvāyureva ca ||
anye dikpatayaścāpi sarve yadvaśagāminaḥ||9||
sarve manuṣyadharmāṇassarvaiḥ parikarairyutāḥ ||
sevate taṃ mahādaityaṃ na svataṃtrāḥ kadācana || 10 ||
evaṃ tenārditā devā vaśagāstasya sarvadā ||
tadicchākā ryyaniratāssava tasyānujīvinaḥ || 11 ||
yāvatyo vanitāssarvā ye cāpyapsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ ||
sarvāstānagrahī daityastārako'sau mahābalī || 12 ||
na yajñāssaṃpravartate na tapasyati tāpasāḥ ||
dānadharmādikaṃ kiṃcinna lokeṣu pravarttate || 13||
tasya senāpatiḥ krauṃco mahāpāpyasti dānavaḥ ||
sa pātāla talaṃ gatvā bādhatetyaniśaṃprajāḥ || 14 ||
tena nastārakeṇedaṃ sakalaṃ bhuvanatrayam ||
hṛtaṃ haṭhājjagaddhātaḥ pāpenākaruṇātmanā || 15 ||
vayaṃ ca tatra yāsyāmo yatsthānaṃ tvaṃ vinirdiśeḥ||
svasthāstadvāritāstena lokanātha surāriṇā ||16||
tvaṃ no gatiśca śāstā ca dhātā trātā tvameva hi ||
vayaṃ sarve tārakākhyavahnau dagdhāssuvihvalāḥ ||17||
tena krūrā upāyā nassarve hatabalāḥ kṛtāḥ ||
vikāre sāṃnipāte vā vīryavatyauṣadhāni ca || 18||
yatrāsmākaṃ jayārśī hi haricakre sudarśane ||
tatkuṃṭhitamabhūttasya kaṃṭhe puṣpamivārpitam || 19||
brahmovāca ||
ityetadvacanaṃ śrutvā nirjarāṇāmahaṃ mune ||
pratyavocaṃ surānsava statkālasadṛśaṃ vacaḥ || 20 ||
brahmovāca ||
mamaiva vacasā daityastārakākhyassamedhitaḥ ||
na mattastasya hananaṃ yujyate hi divaukasaḥ ||21||
tatoṃ naiva vadho yogyo yato vṛddhimupāgataḥ ||
viṣavṛkṣo'pi saṃvardhya svayaṃ chettumasāṃpratam || 22 ||
yuṣmākaṃ cākhileṃ kārya kartuṃ yogyo hi śaṃkaraḥ ||
kintu svayaṃ na śakto hi pratikartuṃ pracoditaḥ || 23 ||
tārakākhyastu pāpenaḥ svayameṣyati saṃkṣayam ||
yathā yūyaṃ saṃvidadhvamupadeśakarastvaham || 24 ||
naṃ mayā tārako vadhyo hariṇāpi hareṇa ca ||
nānyenāpi surairvāpi madvarātsatyamucyate || 25||
śivavīyryyasamutpanno yadi syāttanayassurāḥ ||
sa eva tāra kākhyasya haṃtā daityasya nāparaḥ|| 26||
yamupāyamahaṃ vacmi taṃ kurudhvaṃ surottamāḥ ||
mahādeva prasādena siddhimeṣyati sadhruvam ||27||
satī dākṣāyiṇī pūrva tyakta dehā tu yābhavat. ||
sotpannā menakāgarbhātsā kathā viditā hi vaḥ||28||
tasyā avaśyaṃ giriśaḥ kariṣyati karagraham ||
tatkurudhvamupāyaṃ ca tathāpi tri divaukasaḥ ||29||
tathā vidhadhvaṃ sutarāṃ tasyāṃ tu pariyatnataḥ||
pārvatyāṃ mainakāyāṃ vai retaḥpratinipātane ||30||
tamūrddhareta saṃ śaṃbhuṃ saiva pracyutaretasam ||
