. . kartuṃ samarthā nānyāsti tathā kāpyabalā balāt || 31 ||
sā sutā girirājasya sāṃprataṃ prauḍhayauvanā ||
tapasyaṃtaṃ himagirau nityaṃ saṃsevate haram || || 32 ||
vākyāddhimavataḥ kālī svapiturhaṭhataśśivā ||
sakhībhyāṃ sevate sārddhaṃ dhyānasthaṃ parameśvaram || 33 ||
tāmagrato'rddhamānāṃ vai trailokye varavarṇi nīm ||
dhyānasakto maheśo hi manasāpi na hīyate || 34 ||
bhāyyau samīheta yathā sa kālīṃ candraśekharaḥ ||
tathā vidhadhvaṃ tridaśā na cirādeva yatnataḥ || 35 ||
sthānaṃ gatvātha daityasya tamahaṃ tārakaṃ tataḥ ||
nivārayiṣye kuhaṭhātsvasthānaṃ gacchatāmarāḥ || 36 ||
ityukvāhaṃ surāṃnśī tārakā khyāsurasya vai ||
upasaṃgamya suprītyā samābhyāṣyedamantravam || 37 || ||
brahmovāca || ||
tejosāramidaṃ svarga rājyaṃ tvaṃ paripāsi naḥ ||
yadarthaṃ sutapa staptaṃ vāñchasi tvaṃ tato'dhikam || 38 ||
varaśvāpyavaro datto na mayā svargarājyatā ||
tasmātsvargaṃ parityajya kṣitau rājyaṃ samācara || 39 ||
devayo gyāni tatraiva kāryyāṇi nikhilānyapi ||
bhaviṣyatyasuraśreṣṭha nātra kāryyā vicāraṇā || 40 ||
ityuktvāhaṃ ca saṃbodhyāsuraṃ taṃ sakaleśvaraḥ ||
smṛtvā śivaṃ ca saśivaṃ tatrāṃtardhānamāgataḥ || 41 ||
tārako'pi parityajya svargaṃ kṣitimathābhyagāt ||
śoṇitākhyapure sthitvā sarvarājyaṃ cakāra saḥ || 42 ||
devāssarve'pi tacchrutvā madvākyaṃ supraṇamya mām ||
śakrasthānaṃ yayuḥ prītyā śakreṇa susamāhitāḥ || 43 ||
tatra gatvā militvā ca vicāryya ca paraspa ram ||
te sarve marutaḥ prītyā maghavaṃtaṃ vaco'bruvan || 44 || ||
devāūcuḥ || ||
śambhoyyathā śivāyāṃ vai rucirjāyetaṃ kāmataḥ ||
maghavaṃste prakartavyaṃ brahmokaṃ sarvameva tat || 45 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityevaṃ sarvavṛttāṃtaṃ vinivedya sureśvaram ||
jagmuste sarvato devāḥ svaṃ svaṃ sthānaṃ mudānvitāḥ || 46 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatī khaṃḍe devasāṃtvanavarṇanaṃ nāma ṣoḍaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 16 || ||
brahmovāca ||
gateṣu teṣu deveṣu śakraṃ sasmāra vai smaram ||
pīḍitastāra kenātidaityena ca durātmanā || 3 ||
āgatastatkṣaṇātkāmassavasaṃto ratipriyaḥ ||
sāvalepo yuto ratyā trailo kyavijayī prabhuḥ || 2 ||
praṇāmaṃ ca tataḥ kṛtvā sthitvā tatpuratassmaraḥ ||
mahonnatamanāstāta sāṃjaliśśakramabravīt || 3 || ||
kāma uvāca ||
kiṃ kāryyaṃ te samutpannaṃ smṛto'haṃ kena hetunā ||
tattvaṃ kathaya deveśa tatkartuṃ samupāgataḥ || 4 || ||
brahmovāca ||
tacchrutvā vacanaṃ tasya kaṃdarpasya sure śvaraḥ ||
uvācaṃ vacanaṃ prītyā yuktaṃ yuktamiti stuvan || 6 || ||
śakra uvāca ||
taṃva sādhu samārambho yanme kāryyamupasthitam ||
ta tkartumudyato'si tvaṃ dhanyo'si makaradhvaja || 6 ||
prastutaṃ śṛṇumadvākyaṃ kathayāmi tavāgrataḥ ||
madīyaṃ caiva yatkāryyaṃ tvadīyaṃtanna cānyathā || 7 ||
miṃtrā ṇi mama saṃtyeva bahūni sumahati ca ||
paraṃ tu smara sanmitraṃ tvattalyaṃ na hi kutracit || 8 ||
jayāthai me iyaṃ tāta nirmitaṃ vajramuttamam ||
vajraṃ ca niṣphalaṃ

--- Page 172 [gcv] ---
• syādvai tvaṃ tu naiva kadācana || 9 ||
yato hitaṃ prajāyeta tataḥ ko nu priyaḥ paraḥ ||
tasmānmitravarastvaṃ hi matkāyyai kartumarhasi || 10 ||
mama duḥkhaṃ samutpannamasādhyaṃ cāpi kālajam ||
kenāpi naiva tacchakyaṃ dūrīkartuṃ tvayā vinā || 11 ||
dāṃtuḥ parīkṣā durbhikṣe raṇe śūrasya jāyate ||
āpa tkāle tu mitrasyāśaktau strīṇāṃ kulasya hi || 12 ||
vinaye saṃkaṭe prāpte'vitathasya parokṣataḥ ||
susnehasya tathā tāta nānyathā satyamīritam || 13||
prāptāyāṃ vai mamāpattāvavāryāyāṃ pareṇa hi ||
parīkṣā ca tvadīyā'dya mitravarya bhaviṣyati || 14 ||
na kevalaṃ madīyaṃ ca kāryyamasti sukhāvaham ||
kiṃ tuṃ sarvasurādīnāṃ kāryyametanna saṃśayaḥ || || 15 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityetanmaghavadvākyaṃ śrutvā tu makaradhvajaḥ ||
uvāca premagaṃbhīraṃ vākyaṃ susmitapūrva kam || 16 || ||
kāma uvāca ||
kimarthamitthaṃ vadasiṃ nottaraṃ vacyahaṃ tava ||
upakṛtkṛtrimaṃ loke dṛśyate kathyate na ca || 17 ||
saṃkaṭe bahu yo brūteṃ sa kiṃ kāryyaṃ kariṣyati ||
tathāpi ca mahārāja kathayāmi śṛṇu prabho || 18 ||
padaṃ te karṣituṃ yo vai tapastapati dāruṇam ||
pātayiṣyāmyahaṃ taṃ ca śatruṃ te mitra sarvathā || 19 ||
kṣaṇena bhraṃśayiṣyāmi kaṭākṣeṇa varastriyāḥ ||
devarṣidānavādīṃśca narāṇāṃ gaṇanā na me || 20 ||
vajraṃ tiṣṭhatu dūre vai śastrā ṇyanyānyanekaśaḥ ||
kiṃ te kāryaṃ kariṣyati mayi mitra upasthite || 21 ||
brahmāṇaṃ vā hariṃ vāpi bhraṣṭaṃ kuyyoṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||
anyeṣāṃ gaṇanā nāsti pātayeyaṃ haraṃ tvapi || 22 ||
paṃcaiva mṛdavo bāṇāste ca puṣpamayā mama ||
cāpastridhā puṣpamayaśśijinī bhramarācitā ||
valaṃ sudayitā me hi vasaṃtaḥ saciva ssmṛtaḥ || 23 ||
ahaṃ pañcabalo devā mitraṃ mama sudhānidhiḥ || 24 ||
senādhipaśca śṛṃgāro hāvabhāvāśva sainikāḥ ||
sarve me mṛdavaḥ śakra ahaṃ cāpi tathāvidhaḥ || 25 ||
yadyena pūyryaṃte kāryyaṃ dhīmāṃstattena yojayet ||
mama yogyaṃ tu yatkāryaṃ sarvaṃ tanme niyojaya || 26 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityevaṃ tu vacastasya śrutvā śakrassuharṣitaḥ |
uvāca prāṇamanvācā kāmaṃ kāṃtāsukhāvaham || 27 || ||
śakra uvāca ||
yatkāryyaṃ manasoddiṣṭaṃ mayā tāta manobhava ||
karttuṃ tattvaṃ samartho'si nānyasmāttasya sambhavaḥ || 28 ||
śṛṇu kāma pravakṣyāmi yathārtha mitrasattama ||
yadarthe ca spṛhā jātā tava cādya manobhava ||29||
tārakākhyo mahādaityo brahmaṇo varamadbhutam ||
abhūdajeyassaṃprāpya sarveṣāmapi duḥkhadaḥ ||30||
tena saṃpīḍayate loko naṣṭā dharmā hyane kaśaḥ |
duḥkhitā nirjarāssarve ṛṣayaśca tathākhilāḥ ||31||
devaiśca sakalaistena kṛttaṃ yuddhaṃ yathābalam||
sarveṣāṃ cāyudhānyatra viphalānyabhavanpurārā||33||
bhagnaḥ pāśoṃ jaleśasya haricakraṃ sudarśanam ||
tatkuṇṭhitamabhūttasya kaṇṭhe kṣiptaṃ ca viṣṇunā || 33||
etasya maraṇaṃ proktaṃ prajeśena durātmanaḥ ||
śambhorvīyadbhavādvā lānmahāyogīśvarasya hi || 34 ||
etatkāryyaṃ tvayā sādhu kartavyaṃ suprayatnataḥ ||
tatassyānmitravaryyāti devānāṃ naḥ paraṃ sukham || 35 ||
