gurūṇāṃ vacanaṃ sa tyamiti yeṣāṃ dṛḍhā matiḥ ||
teṣāmihāmutra sukhaṃ paramaṃ nāsukhaṃ kvacit || 59 ||
gurūṇāṃ vacanaṃ satyamitiḥ yaddhṛdaye na dhīḥ ||
ihāmutrāpi teṣāṃ hi duḥkhaṃ na ca sukhaṃ kvacit || 60 ||
sarvathā na parityājyaṃ gurūṇāṃ vacanaṃ dvijāḥ ||
gṛhaṃ vasedvā śūnyaṃ syānme haṭhassukhadassadā || 61 ||
yadbhavadbhissa bhaṇitaṃ vacanaṃ munisattamāḥ ||
tadanyathā tadvivekaṃ varṇayāmi samāsataḥ || 62 ||
guṇālayo vihārī ca viṣṇussatyaṃ prakīrtitaḥ ||
sadāśivo'guṇaḥ proktastatra kāraṇamucyate || 63 ||
śivo brahmā vikāraḥ sa bhaktahetordhṛtākṛtiḥ ||
prabhutāṃ laukikīṃ naiva saṃdarśayitumicchati || 64 ||
ataḥ paramahaṃ sānāṃ dhāryate supriyā gatiḥ ||
avadhūtasvarūpeṇa parānaṃdena śaṃbhunā || 65 ||
bhūṣaṇādirucirmāyāliptānāṃ brahmaṇo na ca ||
sa prabhurnirguṇo'jo nirmāyo 'lakṣya gatirvirāṭ || 66 ||
dharmajātyādibhiśśambhurnānugṛhṇāti vai dvijāḥ ||
guroranugraheṇaiva śivaṃ jānāmi tattvataḥ ||67||
cecchivassa hi me viprā vivāhaṃ na kariṣyati ||
avivāhā sadāhaṃ syāṃ satyaṃ satyaṃ vadāmyaham || 68 ||
udayati yadi bhānuḥ paśvime digvibhāge pracalati yadi meruśśītatāṃ yāti vahniḥ ||
vikasati yadi padmaṃ parvatāgre śilāma na hi calati haṭho me satyametadbravīmi || 69 ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā tānpraṇamyāśu munīnsā parvatātmajā ||
virarāma śivaṃ smṛtvā nirvikāraṇa cetasā || 70 ||
ṛṣayo'pītyamājñāya girijāyāssuniścayam ||
procurjayagiraṃ tatra dadau cāśiṣaṃ muttamām || 71 ||
atha praṇamyaṃ tāṃ devīṃ sunayo hṛṣṭamānasāḥ ||
śivasthānaṃ drutaṃ jagmuḥ tatparīkṣākarā mune || 72 ||
tatra gatvā śivaṃ natvā vṛttāṃtaṃ vinivedya tat ||
tadājñāṃ samanuprāpya svarlokaṃ jagmurādarāt || 73 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīyeḥ pārvatīkhaṃḍe saptarṣikṛta parīkṣāvarṇano nāma paṃcaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 25 || ||
brahmovāca ||
gateṣu teṣu muniṣu svaṃ lokaṃ śaṃkaraḥ svayam ||
parīkṣituṃ tapo devyā aicchatsū tikaraḥ prabhuḥ || 1 ||
parīkṣāṃchadmanāḥ śaṃbhudraṣṭuṃ tāṃ tuṣṭamānasaḥ ||
jāṭilaṃ rūpamāsthāya sa yayau pārvatīvanam || 2 ||
atīva sthaviro vipradehadhārī svatejasā ||
prajvalanmanasā hṛṣṭo daṃḍī chatrī babhūva saḥ || 3 ||
tatrāpaśyātsthitāṃ devīṃ sakhībhiḥ parivāritām ||
vedikopari śuddhāṃ tāṃ śivāmiva vidhoḥ kalām || 4 ||
śaṃbhurnirīkṣya tāṃ devīṃ brahmacārisvarūpavān ||
upakaṃṭhaṃ yayauṃ prītyā tadā'saubhaktavatsalaḥ || || 5 ||
āgataṃ taṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā brāhmaṇaṃ tejasādbhutam ||
apūjayacchivā devī sarvapūjopahārakaiḥ || 6 ||
susatkṛtaṃ saṃvidhārmiḥ pūjitaṃ parayā mudā ||
pārvatī kuśalaṃ prītyā papraccha dvijamādarāt || 7 || ||
pārvatyuvāca ||
brahmacārisvarūpeṇa kastvaṃ hi kuta āgataḥ ||
idaṃ vanaṃ bhāsa yase vada vedavidāṃ vara || 8 || ||
vipra uvāca ||
ahamicchābhigāmī ca vṛddho vipratanussudhīḥ ||
