mayā khyātaṃ ca tatprītyā kimanyacchrotumicchati || 41 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityevaṃ vacanaṃ śrutvā vijayāyā yathārthataḥ ||
mune sa jaṭilo rudro vihasanvākyamabravīt || 42 || ||
jaṭila uvāca ||
sakhyedaṃ kathitaṃ tatra parihāsonu bhīyate ||
yathārtha cettadā devī svamukhenābhibhāṣatām || 43 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityukte ca tadā tena jaṭilena dvijanmanā ||
uvāca pārvatī devī svamukhenaiva taṃ dvijam ||44||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe śivājaṭilasaṃvādo nāma ṣaḍviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ||26||
pārvatyuvāca ||
śṛṇu dvijendra jaṭila madṛttaṃ nikhilaṃ khalu ||
sakhyuktaṃ me'dya yatsatyaṃ tattathaiva na cānyathā || 1 ||
manasā vacasā sākṣātkarmmaṇā yati bhāvataḥ ||
satyaṃ bravīmi no'satyaṃ vṛto vai śaṃkaro mayā || 2 ||
jānāmi durlabhaṃ vastu kathamprāpyaṃ mayā bhavet ||
tathāpi manaautsukyāttapyate'dya tapoṃ mayā || 3 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā vacanantasmai sthitā sā girijā tadā ||
uvāca brāhmaṇastatra tacchrutvā pārvatīvacaḥ || 4 || ||
brāhmaṇaṃ uvāca ||
etāvatkālaparyyantammamecchā mahatī hyabhūt ||
kiṃ vastu kāṃkṣatī devī kurute sumahattapaḥ ||5||
tajjñātvā nikhilaṃ devi śrutvā tvanmukhapaṅka jāt ||
ito gacchāmyahaṃ sthānādyarthecchasi tathā kuru || 6 ||
na kathyate tvayā mahyaṃ mitratvaṃ niṣphalambhavet ||
yathā kāryyaṃ tathā bhāvi kathanīyaṃ sukhena ca || 7 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā vacanaṃ tasya yāvadgantumiyeṣa saḥ ||
tāvacca pārvatī devī praṇamyovāca taṃ dvijam || 8 || ||
pārvatyuvāca kiṃ gamiṣyasi viprendra sthito bhava hitaṃ vada ||
ityukte ca tayā tatra sthitvovāca sa daṇḍadhṛk || 9 || ||
dvija uvāca ||
yadi śrotumanā devi māṃ sthāpayasi bhaktitaḥ ||
vadāmi tattvaṃ tatsarvaṃ yena te vayunambhavet || 10 ||
jānāmyahaṃ mahādevaṃ sarvathā gurudharmmataḥ ||
pravadāmi yathārtha hi sāvadhānatayā śṛṇu || 11 ||
vṛṣadhvajo mahādevo bhasmadigdho jaṭādharaḥ ||
vyāghracarmāṃbaradharaḥ saṃvīto gajakṛttinā || 12 ||
kapāladhārī sapauṃ vaissarvagātreṣu veṣṭitaḥ||
viṣadigdho'bhakṣyabhakṣo virūpākṣo bibhīṣaṇaḥ || 13 ||
avyaktajanmā satataṃ gṛhabhogavivarjitaḥ ||
