caṃdanaṃ ca tvadīyāṃge citābhasma śivasya ca ||
kka dukūlaṃ tvadīyaṃ vai śāṃkaraṃ kva gajājina m || 27 ||
kka bhūṣaṇāni divyāni va sarpāśśaṃkarasya ca ||
kva carā devatāssarvāḥ kva ca bhūtabalipriyaḥ || 28 ||
kka vā mṛdaṃgavādaśva kva ca taḍḍamaru stathā ||
kva ca bherīkalāpaśca kva ca bhṛṃgaravo'śubhaḥ || 29 ||
kva ca ḍhakkāmayaḥ śabdo galanādaḥ kva cāśubhaḥ ||
bhavatyāśca śivasyaiva na yuktaṃ rūpamu ttamam || 30 ||
yadi dravyaṃ bhavettasya kathaṃ syātsa digaṃbaraḥ ||
