. . • se pārvatī ||
uvāca kruddhamanasā śivanindāparaṃ dvijam || 39 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṃḍe brahmacāripratāraṇa vākyavarṇanaṃ nāma saptaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 27 ||
pārvatyuvāca ||
etāvaddhi mayā jñātaṃ kaścidanyoyamāgataḥ ||
idānīṃ sakalaṃ jñātamavadhyastvagviśeṣataḥ || 1 ||
tvayoktaṃ viditaṃ deva tadalīkaṃ nacānyathā ||
yadi tvayoditaṃ syādvai viruddhaṃ nocyate tvayā || 2 ||
kadācidṛśyate tādṛk veṣadhārī maheśvaraḥ ||
svalīlayā parabrahma svarāgopāttavigrahaḥ || 3 ||
brahmacārisvarūpeṇa pratārayitumudyataḥ ||
āgataśchala saṃyuktaṃ vacovādīḥ kuyuktitaḥ || 4 ||
śaṃka rasya svarūpaṃ tu jānāmi suviśeṣataḥ ||
śivatattvamato vacmi suvicāryyaṃ yathārhataḥ ||5||
vastuto nirguṇo brahma saguṇaḥ kāraṇena saḥ ||
kuto jāti bhavettasya nirguṇasya guṇātmanaḥ || 6 ||
sa sarvāsāṃ hi vidyānāmadhiṣṭhānaṃ sadāśivaḥ ||
kiṃ tasya vidyayā kāryyaṃ pūrṇasyaḥ paramātmanaḥ || 7 ||
vedā ucchāsarūpeṇa purādattāśca viṣṇave ||
śaṃbhunā tena kalpādau tatsamaḥ ko'sti suprabhuḥ || 8 ||
sarveṣāmādibhūtasya vayomānaṃ kutastataḥ ||
prakṛtistu tato jātā kiṃ śaktastasya kāraṇam || 9 ||
ye bhajaṃti ca taṃ prītyā śaktīśaṃ śaṃkaraṃ sadā ||
tasmai śaktitrayaṃ śaṃbhuḥ sa dadāti sadāvyayam || 10 ||
tasyaiva bhajanājjīvo mṛtyuṃ jayati nirbhayaḥ ||
tasmānmṛtyuṃjayannāma prasiddhambhuvanatraye || || 11 ||
tasyaiva pakṣapātena viṣṇurviṣṇutvamāpnuyāt ||
brahmatvaṃ ca yathā brahmā devā devatvameva ca || 12 ||
darśanārtha śivasyādau yathāgacchati devarāṭ ||
bhūtādayastatparasya dvārapālāśśivasya tu || 13 ||
daṇḍe'śva mukuṭaṃ viddhaṃ mṛṣṭaṃ bhavati sarvataḥ ||
kiṃ tasya bahupakṣeṇasvayameva mahāprabhuḥ || 14 ||
kalyāṇarūpiṇastasya sevayeha na kiṃ bhavet ||
kiṃ nyūnaṃ tasya devasya māmicchati sadāśivaḥ || 15 ||
saptajanmadaridraḥ syā tsevedyo yadi śaṃkaram ||
tasyaitatsevanāchoke lakṣmīḥ syādanapāyinī || 16 ||
yadaye siddhayoṣṭau ca nityaṃ nṛtyaṃti toṣitum ||
avāṅmukhāssadā tatra taddhitaṃ durlabhaṃ kutaḥ || 17 ||
yadyasya maṃgalānīha sevate śaṃkarasya na ||
tathāpi maṃgalantasya smaraṇādeva jāyate || 18 ||
yasya pūjāprabhāveṇa kā māssidhyanti sarvaṃśaḥ ||
kuto vikārastasyāsti nirvikārasya sarvadā ||19||
śiveti maṃgalannāma mukhe yasya nirantaram ||
tasyaiva darśanādanye pavi trāssanti sarvadā || 20 ||
yadyapūtambhavedbhasma citāyāśca tvayoditam ||
nityamasyāṃgagaṃ devaiśśirobhirddhayate katham ||21||
yo devo jagatāṃ kartā bhartā hartā guṇānvitaḥ ||
nirguṇaśśivasaṃjñaśca sa vijñeyaḥ kathambhavet||22||
aguṇaṃ brahmaṇo rūpaṃ śivasya paramātmanaḥ |
