tvañca śapto mayā'jñānātstrīsvabhāvāḍa thā vṛṣa || 35 ||
kā vyavasthā bhavettasya cintayāmīti sāmpratam ||
citte sphuratu sā buddhiryayā śaṃ sahabhāmi vai || 36 ||
ākāśosau diśassaba yadi naśyantu vāyavaḥ ||
tathāpi sādhvīśāpastu na naśyati kadācana || 37 ||
satye pūrṇaścatuṣpādaḥ paurṇamāsyāṃ yathā śaśī ||
virājate deva rāja sarvakālaṃ divāniśam || 38 ||
tvañca naṣṭo bhavasi cetsṛṣṭināśo bhavettadā ||
itikartavyatāmūḍhā vṛthāpi ca vadāmyaham || 39 ||
pādakṣayaśca bhavitā tretāyāṃ ca surottama |
pādopare dvāpare ca tṛtīyo'pi kalau vibho || 40 ||
kaliśeṣe'khilāśchinnā bhaviṣyanti tavāṃtrayaḥ ||
punassatve samā yāte paripūrṇo bhaviṣyasi || 41 ||
satye sarvavyāpakastvaṃ tadanyeṣu ca kutracit ||
yugavyavasthayā sa tvaṃ bhaviṣyasi tathā tathā || 42 ||
ityeva vacanaṃ satyaṃ mamāstu sukhadaṃ tava |
yāmyahaṃ patisevāyai gaccha tvaṃ svagṛhaṃ vibho || 43 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityākarṇya vacastasyāssantuṣṭo bhūdṛṣassa vai ||
tadevaṃvādinīṃ sādhvīmuvāca vidhinandana || 44 || ||
dharma uvāca ||
dhanyāsi patibhaktāsi svasti testu pativrate ||
varaṃ gṛhāṇaṃ tvatsvāmī tatparitrāṇa kāraṇāt || 45 ||
yuvā bhavatu te bhartā ratiśūraśca dhārmikaḥ ||
rūpavān guṇavānvāgmī saṃtatasthirayauvanaḥ || 46 ||
cirañjīvī sa bhavatu mārkaṇḍe yāttparaśśubhe ||
kuberāddhanavā~ścaivaṃ śakrādaiśvaryyavānapi || 47 ||
śivabhaktoḥ harisamassiddhastu kapilātparaḥ ||
buddhaṃyā bṛhaspatisamassamatvena vidhe ssamaḥ || 48 ||
svāmisaubhāgyasaṃyuktā bhava tvaṃ jīvanāvadhi ||
tathā ca subhage devi tvaṃ bhava sthirayauvanā || 49 ||
mātā tvaṃ daśaputrāṇāṃ guṇināṃ cirajīvinām ||
svabharturadhikānāṃ ca bhaviṣyasi na saṃśayaḥ || 50 ||
gṛhī bhavantu te sādhvi sarvasampatsamanvitāḥ ||
prakāśamantassatataṃ kuberabhava nādhikāḥ || 51 || ||
vasiṣṭha uvāca ||
ityevamuktvā santasthau dharmassa girisattama ||
sā taṃ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya praṇamya svagṛhaṃ yayau || 52 ||
dharma stathāśiṣo datvā jagāma nizamandiram ||
praśaśaṃsa ca tāṃ prītyā padmāṃ saṃsadi saṃsadi || 53 ||
sā reme svāmināsārddhaṃ yūnā rahāsa santatam ||
paścā dvabhṛvussatputrāstvadbharturadhikā guṇaiḥ || 54 ||
babhūva sakalā sampadampatyoḥ sukhavarddhinī ||
sarvānandavṛddhikarā paratreha ca śarmaṇe || 55 ||
śailendra

