tā maṃgalaṃ mudā cakrurbhūṣitā bhūṣaṇaiḥ svayam ||
puradvijastriyo hṛṣṭā lokācāraṃ pracakrire || 18 ||
sotsavaṃ vividhaṃ tatre sumaṃgalapurassaram ||
himālayo'pi hṛṣṭātmā kṛtvācāraṃ sumaṃgalam || 19 ||
sarvabhāvena suprīto bandhuvargāgamotsukaḥ ||
etasminnantare tasya vāndhavāśca nimantritāḥ || 20 ||
ājagmussastriyo hṛṣṭāssasutāssaparicchadāḥ ||
tadeva śṛṇu devarṣe gigamanamāhataḥ || 21 ||
varṇayāmi samā sena śivaprītivivṛddhaye ||
devālayagiriyoṃ hi divyarūpadharo mahān || 22 ||
nānāratnaparibhrājatsamājassaparicchadaḥ ||
