śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśo yathāṃ nandī tathaiva saḥ || 18 ||
tasyopari mahādivyampuṣpakaṃ ratnabhūṣitam ||
rājitaṃ pallavaiśśutraiścāmaraiśca suśobhitam || 19 ||
vāmapārśve gajau dvau ca śuddhakāśmī rasannibhau ||
caturdantau ṣaṣṭivarṣo bhedamānau mahāprabhau || 20 ||
tathaivārkanibhau tena kṛtau cāvau mahāprabhau ||
cāmarālaṅkṛtau divyau divyālaṅkārabhū ṣitau ||21||
daṃśitā vararatnāḍhyā lokapālāstathaiva ca ||
sarve devā yathārtha vaiṃ kṛtā vai viśvakarmaṇā || 22 ||
tathā hi ṛṣayassarve bhṛgvādyāśca tapo dhanāḥ ||
anye hyupasurāstadvatsiddhāścānye'pi vai kṛtāḥ || 23 ||
viṣṇuśca pārṣadaissarvairgaruḍākhyaissamanvitaḥ ||
kṛtrimo nirmitastadvatparamāścarya rūpavān || 24 ||
tathaivāhaṃ sutaivaidessidvaiśca parivāritaḥ ||
kṛtrimo nirmitastadvatpaṭhansūktāni nārada || 25 ||
airāvatagajārūḍhaśśaka ssvadalasaṃyutaḥ ||
kṛtrimo· nirmitastadvatparipūrṇendusaṃnibhaḥ || 26 ||
kiṃ bahūtana devarṣe sarvo vai viśvakarmaṇā ||
himāgapreritenāśu kḷpta ssurasamājakaḥ || 27 ||
evaṃbhūtaḥ kṛtastena maṇḍapo divyarūpavān ||
anekāścaryasambhūto mahāndevavimohanaḥ || 28 ||
athājñapto girīśena viśvakarmā mahāmatiḥ ||
nivāsārthaṃ surādīnāṃ tattokān hi yatnataḥ || 29 ||
tatraiva ca mahāmañcāḥ suprabhāḥ paramādbhutāḥ ||
racitāssukhadā divyā steṣāṃ vai viśvakarmaṇā || 30 ||
tathāptasaptalokaṃ vai virece kṣaṇato'dbhutam ||
dīdhyā parāmayā yukta nivāsārtha svayambhuvaḥ || 31 ||
tathaiva viṣṇo stvaparaṃ vaikuṇṭhākhyaṃ mahojvalam ||
virece kṣaṇato divyaṃ nānāścaryasamanvitam || 32 ||
amareśagṛhandivyaṃ tathaivādbhutamuttamam ||
virece viśvakarmāsau sarvaiśvaryasamanvitam || 33 ||
gṛhāṇi lokapālānāṃ virece sundarāṇi ca ||
tadvatsa prītito divyānyadbhutāni mahānti ca || 34 ||
anyeṣāmama rudra saṃ0 2 pā0 khaṃ0 3 a0.38 ||136||
