rāṇāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ kramaśastathā ||
sadanāni vicitrāṇi racitāni ca tena vai || 35 ||
viśvakarmā mahābuddhiḥ prāptaśambhumahāvaraḥ ||
virece kṣaṇataḥ savai śivatuṣṭyarthameva ca || 36 ||
tathaiva citraṃ paramaṃ mahojjvalaṃ mahāprabhandevavaraissupūjitam ||
girīśacihnaṃ śivalokasaṃsthitaṃ suśobhitaṃ śambhugṛhaṃ cakāra || 37 ||
evambhūtā kṛtā tena racanā viśvakarmaṇā ||
vicitrā śivatuṣṭyarthaṃ parāśvaryā mahojjvalā || 38 ||
evaṃ kṛtvākhilaṃ cedaṃ vyavahāraṃ ca laukikam ||
payyaikṣiṣṭa mudā śambhavāgamanaṃ sa himācalaḥ || 39 ||
iti proktamaśeṣeṇa vṛttāntampramudāvaham ||
himālayasya devarṣe kimbhūyaḥ śro tumicchasiṃ. || 40 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe maṇḍapādira canāvarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 38 || ||
nārada uvāca || ||
vidhe tāta mahāprājña viṣṇuśiṣya namo'stu te ||
adbhuteyaṃ kathāśrāvi tvatto'smābhiḥ kṛpānidhe || 1 ||
idānīṃ śrotumi cchāmi caritaṃ śaśiṃmaulinaḥ ||
vaivāhikaṃ sumāṅgalyaṃ sarvāghaughavināśanam || 2 ||
kiṃ cakāra mahādevaḥ prāpya maṅgalapatrikām ||
tāṃ śrāvaya kathā divyāṃ śaṅkarasya parātmanaḥ || 3 || ||
brahmovāca ||
śṛṇu vatsaṃ mahāprājña śāṅkaramparamaṃ yaśaḥ ||
yaccakāra mahādevaḥ prāpya maṅgalapatrikām || || 4 ||
atha śambhurgṛhītvā tāṃ mudā maṃgalapatrikām ||
vijahāsa prahṛṣṭātmā mānanteṣāṃ vyadhādvibhuḥ || 5 ||
vācayitvā ca tāṃ samyaksvī, cakāra vidhānataḥ ||
tajjanānyāpayāmāsa bahusammānya cādṛtaḥ || 6 ||
uvāca sunivargāstānkāryyaṃ samyak kṛtaṃ śubham ||
āgantavyaṃ vivāhe me vivāhassvīkṛto mayā || 7 ||
ityākarṇya vacaśśambhoḥ prahṛṣṭāste praṇamya tam ||
parikramya yayurdhāma śaṃsantaḥ svaṃ vidhimparam || 8 ||
atha deveśvaraśśambhuslāmarastvāṃ mune drutam ||
laukikācāramāśritya mahālīlākaraḥ prabhuḥ || 9 ||
tvamāgataḥ paraprītyā praśaṃsaṃstvaṃ vidhimparam ||
praṇamaṃśca nataskandho vinītātmā kṛtāñjaliḥ || 10 ||
astaussujayaśabdāni samuccāya muhurmuhuḥ ||
nideśaṃ prārthayaṃstasya praśaṃsaṃstvaṃ vidhi mmune || 11 ||
tataśśambhuḥ prahṛṣṭātmā darśayalaukikīṃ gatim ||
uvāca munivarya tvāṃ prīṇayañchubhayā girā || 12 || ||
śiva uvāca ||
prītyā śṛṇu muniśreṣṭha hyasmato'dyavadāmi te ||
bruve tattvāṃ priyo me yadbhaktarājaśiromaṇiḥ || 13 ||
kṛtaṃ mahattapo devyā pārvatyā tava śāsanāt ||
tasyai varo mayā dattaḥ patitve toṣitena vai || 14 ||
kariṣye'haṃ vivāhaṃ ca tasyā vaśyo hi bhaktitaḥ ||
saptarṣibhissādhitañca tacanaṃ śodhitañca taiḥ || 15 ||
adya tasaptame cāhni tat bhaviṣyati nārada |
mahotsavaṃ kariṣyāmi laukikīṃ gatimāśritaḥ || 16 || ||
brahmovāca ||
