viṣṇuprabhṛtidevā~śca munī siddhānapi dhruvam ||
tvannimantraya madvāṇyā sune'nyānapi sarvataḥ || 21 ||
sarva āyāntu sotsāhāssarvaśobhāsamanvitāḥ ||
