tralo vāca ||
itīśājñāṃ tato dhṛtvā bhavāñchaṅkaravallabhaḥ ||
sarvānnimantrayāmāsa taṃ taṃ gattvā drutaṃ mune || 24 ||
śambhūpakaṇṭhamāgatya drutaṃ munivaro bhavān taddhūtyāttatra santasthau tadājñāmprāpya nārada || 25 ||
śivo'pi tasthau sotkaṇṭhastadāgamanalālasaḥ ||
svagaṇaissotsavai sarvairnṛtyadbhissarvato diśam || 26 ||
etasminneva kāle tu racayitvā svaveṣakam ||
ājagāmācyutaśśīghraṃ kailāsaṃ suparicchadaḥ || 27 ||
śivampraṇamya sadbhaktyā sadārassadalo mudā ||
tadājñāmprāpya santasthau susthāne prītamānasaḥ || 28 ||
tathāhaṃ svagaṇairāśu kailāsamagamaṃ khudā ||
prabhumpraṇamyātiṣṭhaṃ vai sānandassvagaṇā nvitaḥ || 29 ||
indrādayo lokapālā āyayussaparicchadāḥ ||
tathaivālaṃkṛtāssarve sotsavāṃssakalatrakāḥ || 30 ||
tathaiva sunayo - nāgāssiddhā upasurāstathā ||
āyayuśvāpare'pīha sotsavāssunimantritāḥ || 31 ||
maheśvarastadā tatrāgatānāṃ ca pṛthak pṛthak ||
sarveṣāmamarādyānāṃ satkāraṃ vyadadhānmudā || 32 ||
athotsavo mahānāsītkailāse paramodbhutaḥ ||
nṛtyādikantadā cakuryathāyogyaṃ surastriyaḥ || 33 ||
etasminsamaye devā viṣṇvādyā ye samāgatāḥ ||
yātrāṃ kārayituṃ śambhostatroṣṣuste'khilā mune || 34 ||
śivājñaptāstadā sarve madīyamiti yantritāḥ ||
śivakāryamidaṃ sarva cakrire śivasevanam || 35 ||
mātarassapta tāstaṃtra śivabhūṣāvidhimparam ||
cakrire ca mudāyuktā yathāyogyantathā punaḥ || 36 ||
tasya svābhāviko veṣa bhūṣāvidhirabhūttadā ||
tasyecchayā muniśreṣṭha parameśasya suprabhoḥ || 37 ||
indraśca mukuṭasthāne sānnidhyamakarottadā ||
locanaṃ sundaraṃ hyāsīttṛtī yantilakaṃ śubham || 38 ||
karṇābharaṇarūpau ca yau hi sapauṃ prakīrtitau ||
kuṇḍale'bhavatāntasya nānāratnānvite mune || 39 ||
anyāṃgasaṃsthitā ssarpāstadaṃgābharaṇāni ca ||
babhūvuratiramyāṇi nānāratnamayāni ca || 40 ||
vibhūtiraṃgarāgo'bhūccandanādisamudbhavaḥ ||
taṃdukūlamabhūddivyaṃ gajacarmādi sundaram ||41||
īdṛśaṃ sundaraṃ rūpaṃ jātaṃ varṇātiduṣkaram ||
īśvaro'pi svayaṃ sākṣādaiśvaryaṃ labdhvavānsvataḥ || 42 ||
