viṣṇuruvāca ||
devadeva mahādeva śaraṇāgatavatsala |
kāryakarttā svabhaktānāṃ vijñaptiṃ śṛṇu me prabho || 46 ||
gṛhyeoktavidhinā śambho sva vivāhasya śaṃkara |
girīśasutayā devyā karma kartumihārhasi || 47 ||
