evamuktastadā śambhurviṣṇunā parameśvaraḥ ||
laukikācāranirato vidhinā taccakāra saḥ || 50 ||
ahaṃ hyadhikṛtastena sarvamabhyudayocitam ||
akuvai munibhiḥ prītyā tatra tatkarmacādrāt || 51 ||
kaśyapo'trirvasiṣṭhaśca gautamo bhāgurirguruḥ ||
kaṇvo bṛhaspatiśśaktirjamadagniḥ parāśaraḥ || 52 ||
mārkaṇḍeyaśśilāpāko 'ruṇapālo'kṛtaśramaḥ ||
agastyacyavano gargaśśilādo'tha mahāmune || 53 ||
dadhīcirūpamanyuśca bharadvājo'kṛtavraṇaḥ ||
pippalādo'tha kuśikaḥ kautso vyāsaḥ saśiṣyakaḥ || 54 ||
ete cānye ca bahava āgatāśśivasannidhim ||
mayā sunoditāstatra cakuste vidhiva kriyām || 55 ||
vedoktavidhinā sarve vedavedāṃgapāragāḥ ||
rakṣāṃ cakrurmaheśasya kṛtvā kautukamaṃgalam || 56 ||
ṛgyajussāmasūktaistu tathā nānāvidhaiḥ paraiḥ ||
maṃgalāni ca bhūrīṇi cakruḥ prītyarṣayo'khilāḥ ||57||
grahāṇāṃ pūjanaṃ prītyā cakuste śambhunā mayā ||
maṇḍalasthasurāṇāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ vighnaśāntaye || 58 ||
tataśśivassusantuṣṭaḥ kṛtvā savai yathocitam ||
laukikaṃ vaidikaṃ karma nanāma ca sudā dvijān || 59 ||
atha sarveśvaro viprāndevānkṛtvā purassarān ||
nissasāra muddā tasmātkailāsātparvatottamāt || 60 ||
bahiḥ kailāsakudharaṃ śambhustasthau mudānvitaḥ ||
devaissaha dvijaiścaiva nānā svīkārakaḥ prabhuḥ || 61 ||
tadotsavī mahānāsīttatra devādibhiḥ kṛtaḥ ||
santuṣṭayarthaṃ maheśasya gānavādyasunṛtyakaḥ || 62 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe devanimantraṇadevāgamanaśivayātrāvarṇanaṃ nāmaikonacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 39 ||
