ṇānāṃ samahotsavaḥ ||
aṣṭakoṭyā ca vikṛto gaṇānāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ || 5 ||
catuṣkoṭyā viśākhaśca gaṇānāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ ||
pārijātaśca navabhiḥ ko ṭibhirgaṇapuṃgavaḥ || 6 ||
ṣaṣṭissarvāntakaḥ śrīmāntathaiva vikṛtānanaḥ ||
gaṇānāndundubhoṣṭābhiḥ koṭibhirgaṇanāyakaḥ || 7 ||
pañcabhiśca kapālākhyo gaṇeśaḥ koṭibhistathā ||
nissandārako vīroṃ gaṇānāṃ koṭibhirmune || 8 ||
koṭikoṭibhireveha kandukaḥ kuṇḍakastathā ||
viṣṭambho gaṇapo'ṣṭābhi gaṇānāṃ koṭibhistathā || 9 ||
sahasrakoṭyā gaṇapaḥ pippalo sudito yayau ||
tathā sanādako vīro gaṇeśo munisattama || 10 ||
āveśanastathā |
ṣṭābhiḥ koṭibhirgaṇanāyakaḥ ||
mahākeśassahasreṇa koṭīnāṃ gaṇapo yayau || 11 ||
kuṇḍo dvādaśakoṭyā hi tathā parvatako sune ||
aṣṭābhiḥ koṭi bhirvīrassamagāccandratāpanaḥ || 12 ||
kālaśva kālakaścaiva mahākālaśśatena vai ||
koṭīṃnā gaṇanātho hi tathaivāśikanāsakaḥ || 13 ||
koṭyāni mukha evāgād guṇānāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ ||
ādityamūrddhā koṭyā ca tathā caiva ghanāvahaḥ || 14 ||
sannāhaśśatakoṭyā hi kumudo gaṇapastathā ||
amoghaḥ ko kilaścaiva śatakoṭyā gaṇādhipaḥ || 15 ||
sumantraḥ koṭikoṭyā'ca gaṇānāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ ||
kākayādodaraḥ koṭiṣaṣṭyā santānakastathā || 16 ||
mahābalaśca navabhirmadhupiṃgaśca kokilaḥ ||
nīlo navatyā koṃṭīnāṃ pūrṇabhadrastathaiva ca || 17 ||
saptakoṭyā caturvatkaḥ karaṇo viṃśakoṭibhiḥ ||
yayau navatikoṭayā tu gaṇeśānohiromakaḥ || 18 ||
yajvākṣaśśatamanyuśca meghamanyuśca nārada ||
tāvatkoṭayā yayussarve gaṇeśā hi pṛthakpṛthak || 19 ||
kāṣṭhāṣṭaścatuṣṣaṣṭyā koṃṭīnāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ ||
virūpākṣassukeśaśca vṛṣābhaśca sanātanaḥ || 20 ||
tālaketuḥ ṣaḍāsyaśca cañcāsyaśca sanātanaḥ ||
sambartakastathā caitro lakulīśa svayamprabhuḥ || 21 ||
lokāntakaśca dīptātmā tathā daityāntako mune ||
devo bhṛṃgiriṭi śrīmāndevadeva priyastathā || 22 ||
aśanirbhānukaścaiva catuṣṣaṣṭayā sahasraśaḥ ||
yayuśśivavivāhārthaṃ śivena sahasotsavāḥ || 23 ||
bhūtakoṭisaha sreṇa pramathāḥ koṭibhi stribhiḥ ||
vīrabhadraścatuṣaṣṭyā romajānāntri koṭibhiḥ || 24 ||
koṭikoṭisahasrāṇāṃ śatairviṃśatibhirvṛtāḥ || 25 ||
tatra jagmuśca nandyādyā gaṇapāśśaṃkarotsave || 25 ||
kṣetrapālo bhairavaśca koṭikoṭigaṇairyutaḥ ||
udvāhaśśaṃkarasyetyāyayauṃ prītyā maho tsavaḥ || 26 ||
ete cānye ca gaṇapā asaṅkhyātā mahābalāḥ ||
tatra jagmurmahāprītyā sotsāhāśśaṃkarotsavai || 27 ||
sarve : sahasrahastāśca jaṭāmu kuṭadhāriṇaḥ ||
candrarekhāvataṃsāśca nīlakaṇṭhātrilocanāḥ || 28 ||
rudrākṣābharaṇāssarve tathā sadbhasmadhāriṇaḥ ||
hārakuṇḍalakeyūramukuṭādyairalaṅkṛtāḥ || ||29||
brahmaviṣṇvandvasaṃkāśā aṇimādiguṇairyutāḥ ||
sūryya koṭipratīkāśāstatra rejurgaṇeśvarāḥ || 30 ||
pṛthivīcāriṇaḥ kecitḥ kecitpātālacāriṇaḥ ||
