kecidvyomacarāḥ kecitsaptasvargacarā mune || 31 ||
kimbahūktena devarṣe sarvalokanivāsinaḥ ||
āyayussvagaṇāśśambhoḥ prītyā vai śaṅkarotsave || 32 ||
itthandevairgaṇaiścānyaissahitaśśaṅkaraḥ prabhuḥ ||
yayau himagiripuraṃ vivāhārthaṃ nijasya vai || 33 ||
yadā jagāma sarveśo vivāhārthaṃ surādibhiḥ ||
tadā tatra hyadvṛttaṃ tacchṛṇu tvaṃ munīśvara || 34 ||
rudrasya bhaginī bhūtvā caṇḍī sūtsavasaṃyutā ||
tatrājagāma suprītyā pareṣāṃ subhayāvahā || 35 ||
pretāsa nasamārūḍhā sarpābharaṇabhūṣitā ||
pūrṇa kalaśamādāya haimaṃ mūrdhni mahāprabham || 36 ||
straparīvārasaṃyuktā dīptāsyā dīptalocanāṃ ||
kutūhalamprakurvantī jātahaṣī mahābalā || 37 ||
tatra bhūtagaṇā divyā virūpāḥ koṭiśo mune ||
virājante sma bahuśastathā nānāvidhāstadā || 38 ||
taissametā grata caṇḍī jagāma vikṛtānanā ||
kutūhalānvitā prītā prītyupadravakāriṇī || 39 ||
caṇḍyā sarve rudragaṇāḥ pṛṣṭhataśca kṛtāstadā ||
koṭyekādaśasaṃkhyākā raudrarudrapriyāśca te || 40 ||
tadā ḍamarunirghoṣairvyāptamāsījjagatrayam ||
bherījhaṃkāraśabdena śaṃkhānāṃ ninadena ca || 41 ||
tathā dundubhinirghoṣaiśśabdaḥ kolāhalo'bhavat ||
kurvañjaganmaṃgalaṃ ca nāśayenmaṃgaletarat || 42 ||
gaṇānāṃ pṛṣṭhato bhūtvā sarve devāssamutsukāḥ ||
anvayussarvasiddhāśca loka pālādikā mune || 43 ||
madhye vrajan rameśoṃ'tha garuḍāsanamāśritaḥ |
śuśubhe triyamāṇena chatreṇa mahatā mune || 44 ||
cāmarairvījyamāno'sau svagaṇaiḥ parivāritaḥ ||
pārṣadairvilasadbhiśca svabhūṣāvidhibhūṣitaḥ || 45 ||
tathā'hamapyaśobhambai vrajanmārge virājitaḥ ||
vedairmūrtidharaiśśāstraiḥ purāṇairāga maistathā || 46 ||
sanakādimahāsiddhaissaprajāpatibhissutaiḥ ||
parivāraissaṃyuto hi śivasevanatatparaḥ || 47 ||
svasainyamadhyagaśśaka airā vatagajasthitaḥ ||
nānāvibhūṣito'tyantaṃ vrajan reje sureśvaraḥ || 48 ||
tadā tu vrajamānāste ṛṣayo bahavaśva te ||
virejurati sotkaṇṭhā śivasyodvāhanamprati || 49 ||
śākinyo yātudhānāśca vetālā brahmarākṣasāḥ ||
bhūtapretapiśācāśca tathānye pramathādayaḥ || 50 ||
tumbururnārado hāhā hūhūśvetyādayo varāḥ ||
gandharvāḥ kinnarā jagmuvādyānādhmāya harṣitāḥ || 51 ||
jagato mātarassarvā devakanyāśca sarvaśaḥ ||
gāyatrī caiva sāvitrī lakṣmī ranyāssurastriyaḥ ||52||
etāścānyāśca devānāṃ patnayo bhavamātaraḥ ||
udvāhaśśaṃkarasyeti jagmussarvā mudānvitāḥ ||53||
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśo vṛṣabha ssarvasundaraḥ ||
yo dharma ucyate vedaiśśāstraissiddhamaharṣibhiḥ || 54 ||
tamārūḍho mahādevo vṛṣabhaṃ dharmavatsalaḥ ||
śuśubhetīva devarṣisevitassakalairvajan || 55 ||
ebhissamaitassakalairmaharṣibhirbabhau maheśo bahuśotyalaṃkṛtaḥ ||
himālayāhnasya dharasya sambrajan pāṇigrahārthe sadanaṃ śivāyāḥ || 56 ||
ityuktaṃ śambhucaritaṃ gamanamparamotsavam ||
himālayapurodbhūtaṃ sadvṛttaṃ śṛṇu nārada || 57 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāntṛtīye
24
