nārada uvāca ||
tvaṣṭrā kṛtantadvikṛtaṃ vicitraṃ vimohanaṃ sarvadivaukasāṃ hi ||
yenaiva sarvānsa vimohituṃ surānsamicchati premata evaṃ yuktayā || 25 ||
purā kṛtantasya vimohanantvayā suvismṛtantat sakalaṃ śacīpate ||
