brahmovāca |
athākarṇya girīśasya nijapuryupakaṇṭhataḥ |
prāptamīśaṃ sarvagaṃ vai mumude himālayaḥ || 1 ||
atha sambhṛtasambhāraḥ sambhāṣāṃ kartumīśvaram |
śailānprasthāpayāmāsa brāhmaṇānāpi sarvaśaḥ || 2 ||
svayaṃ jagāma sadbhaktyā prāṇeṣundraṣṭumīśvaram |
bhaktyudgatamanāḥ śailaḥ praśaṃsan svavidhimmudā || 3 ||
devasenāṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā himavānvismayaṃ gataḥ |
jagāma sammukhastatra dhanyo'hamiti cintayan || 4 ||
devā hi tadbalaṃ dṛṣṭvā vismayamparamaṃ gatāḥ |
ānandamparamaṃ prāpurdevāśca girayastathā || 5 ||
parvatānāṃ mahāsenā devānāṃ ca tathā mune |
militvā virājeva pūrvapaścimasāgarau || 6 ||
parasparaṃ saṃmilitā devāśca parvatāstathā |
kṛtakṛtyantathātmānammenire parayā mudā || 7 ||
atheśvarampuro dṛṣṭvā praṇanāma himālayaḥ |
sarve praṇemurgirayo brāhmaṇāśca sadāśivam || 8 ||
vṛṣabhasthamprasannāsyannānābharaṇabhūṣitam |
divyāvayavalāvaṇyaprakāśitadigantaram || 9 ||
susūkṣmātatasatpaṭṭavastraśobhitavigraham |
sadratnavilasanmaulimvibhasantaṃ śuciprabham || 10 ||
bhūṣābhūtāhiyuktāṅgamadbhutāvayavaprabham |
divyadyutiṃ sureśaiśca sevitāṅgaracāmaraiḥ || 11 ||
vāmasthitācyutandakṣabhāvasthitavibhumprabhum |
pṛṣṭhasthitaharrim pṛṣṭhapārśvasthitasurādikam || 12 ||
nānāvidhasurādyaiśca saṃstutaṃ lokaśaṃkaram |
svahetvāttatanumbrahma sarvaiśvaradāyakam || 13 ||
saguṇaṃ nirguṇaṃ cāpi bhaktādhīnaṃ kṛpākaram |
prakṛteḥ puruṣasyāpi paraṃ saccitsukhātmakam || 14 ||
prabhordakṣiṇabhāge tu dadarśa harimacyutam |
vinatātanayārūḍhaṃ nānābhūṣaṇabhūṣitam || 15 ||
prabhośca vāmabhāge tu mune māṃ sandadarśa ha |
caturmukhaṃ mahāśobhaṃ svaparīvārasaṃyutam || 16 ||
etau sureśvarau dṛṣṭvā śivasyātipriyau sadā |
praṇanāma girīśaśca saparivāra ādarāt || 17 ||
tathā śivasya pṛṣṭhe ca pārśve

