atha śambhuḥ prasannātmā sadūtaṃ svagaṇaiḥ suraiḥ |
svairantyairgirerdhāma jagāma sagaṇairhṛḍalam || 1 ||
menāpi strīgaṇaistaiśca himācalavarapriyā |
tata utthāya svagṛhābhyantaraṃ sā jagāma ha || 2 ||
