sarvābhiḥ strīgaṇaiḥ sākamagacchaddvārato'rāt || 3 ||
tatrāgataṃ maheśānaṃ śaṃkaraṃ girijāvaram |
dadarśa prītito menā sevitaṃ sakalaiḥ suraiḥ || 4 ||
cārucampakavarṇābhamekavaktraṃ trilocanam |
īṣaddhāsyaprasannāsyaṃ ratnasvarṇādibhūṣitam || 5 ||
mālatīmālasaṃyuktaṃ sadratnamukuṭojjvalam |
satkaṇṭhābharaṇaṃ cāruvalayāṅgadabhūṣitam || 6 ||
vahniśaucenātulena tvatisūkṣmeṇa cāruṇā |
amūlyavastrayugmena vicitreṇātirājitam || 7 ||
candanāgarukastūrīcārukuṅkumabhūṣitam |
ratnadarpaṇahastaṃ ca kajjalojjvalalocanam || 8 ||
sarvasvaprabhayācchannamatīva sumanoharam |
atīva taruṇaṃ ramyaṃ bhūṣitāṅgaiśca bhūṣitam || 9 ||
kāminīkāntamavyagraṃ koṭicandrānanāmbujam |
koṭismarādhikatanucchavaṃ sarvāṅgasundaram || 10 ||
īdṛgvidhaṃ sudevaṃ taṃ sthitaṃ svapurataḥ prabhum |
dṛṣṭvā jāmātaraṃ menā jahau śokamudānvitā || 11 ||
praśaśaṃsa svabhāgyaṃ sā girijāṃ bhūdharaṃ kulam |
mene kṛtārthamātmānaṃ jaharṣa ca punaḥ punaḥ || 12 ||
nīrājanaṃ cakārāsau praphullavadanā satī |
avalokaparā tatra menā jāmātaraṃ mudā || 13 ||
girijoktamanusmṛtya menā vismayamāgatā |
manasaiva jubhāva ce'daṃ harṣaphullānanāmbujā || 14 ||
yadyatpuroktaṃ ca tayā pārvatyā mama tatra ca |
tato'dhikaṃ prapaśyāmi saundaryaṃ parameśituḥ || 15 ||
maheśasya sulāvaṇyamanirvācyaṃ ca samprati |
evaṃ vismayamāpannā menā svagṛhamāyayau || 16 ||
praśaśaṃsuryuvatayo dhanyā dhanyā gireḥ sutā |
durgā bhagavatītyevamūcuḥ kāścana kanyakāḥ || 17 ||
