tataḥ śailaṃvaraḥ sopi prītyā durgopavītakam ||
kārayāmāsa sotsāhaṃ vedamaṃtrośśavasya ca || 1 ||
atha viṣṇvādayo devā munayassakutūhalam ||
himācalaprārthanayā viveśāntaṃgṛhaṃ gireḥ || 2 ||
śrutyācāraṃ bhavācāraṃ vidhāya ca yathārthataḥ ||
śivāmalaṃkṛtāṃ cakruśśivadattavibhūṣaṇaiḥ || 3 ||
prathamaṃ strāpayitvā tāṃ bhūṣayitvātha sarvaśaḥ ||
nīrājitā sakhībhiśca viprapa nībhireva ca || 4 ||
ahatāmbarayugmena śobhitā varavarṇinī ||
virarāja mahāśailaduhitā śaṅkarapriyā || 5 ||
kaṃcukī paramā divyā nānāratnānvitā drutā |
vidhṛtā ca tayā devyā vilasantyādhikaṃ mune || 6 ||
sā babhāra tadā hāraṃ divyaratnasamanvitam ||
valayāni mahārhāṇi śuddhacāmīkarāṇi ca || || 7 ||
sthitā tatraiva subhagā dhyāyantī manasā śivam ||
śuśubheti mahāśailakanyakā trijagatprasūḥ || 8 ||
tadotsavo mahānāsīdubhayatra mudāvahaḥ ||
dānaṃ babhūva vividhaṃ brāhmaṇebhyo vivarṇitam ||9||
anyeṣāṃ dravyadānaṃ ca babhūva vividhammahat ||
gītavādyavinodaśca tatrotsavapurassaram ||10||
atha viṣṇurahaṃ dhātā śakādyā amarāstathā ||
munayaśca mahāprītyā nikhilāssotsavā muddā || 11 ||
supraṇamya śiva bhaktyā smṛtvā śivapadāmbujam ||
samprāpya himagiryyājñāṃ svaṃ svaṃ sthānaṃ samāśritāḥ || 12 ||
etasminnantare tatra jyotiḥśāstraviśāradaḥ ||
himavantaṃ girīṃdraṃ taṃ gargo vākyamabhāṣata || || 13 || ||
