nartakyoṃ nanṛtussarvā nānātālasamanvitāḥ ||34||
ebhissameto jagadeka bandhuryayau tadānīṃ parameśavarcasā ||
susevyamānassakalaissureśvarairvikīryamāṇaḥ kusumaiśca harṣitaiḥ || 36 ||
sampūjitastadā śambhuḥ praviṣṭo yajñamaṇḍapam ||
saṃstūyamāno bahvībhiḥ stutibhiḥ parameśvaraḥ || 36 ||
vṛṣāduttārayāmāsurmaheśamparvatottamāḥ ||
ninyurgṛhāntaramprītyā mahotsavapurassaram || 37 ||
himā layospi samprāptaṃ sadevagaṇamīśvaram ||
praṇamya vidhivadbhaktyā nīrājanamathākarot || 38 ||
sarvānsurānmunaninyānpraṇamya, samahotsavaḥ ||
sammāna makarotteṣāṃ praśaṃsansvavidhimmudā || 39 ||
so'gassācyutamīśānaṃ supādyārghyapurassaram ||
sadevamukhyavargaṃ ca nināya svālayāntaram || 40 ||
prāṅgaṇe sthāpayāmāsa ratnasiṃhāsaneṣu tān ||
sarvānviṣṇuṃ ca māmīśaṃ viśiṣṭāṃśca viśeṣataḥ || 41 ||
sakhībhirmenayā prītyā brāhmaṇastrībhireva ca ||
anyābhi

--- Page 236 [gcv] ---
va purandhrībhiścakre nīrājanammudā || 42 ||
purodhasā kṛtyavidā śaṅkarāya mahātmane |
madhuparkādikaṃ yadyatkṛtyaṃ tattatkṛtaṃ mudā || 43||
mayā sa nodita statra purodhāḥ kṛtabā~stadā ||
sumaṃgalīca yatkarmma prastāvasadṛśammune || 44 ||
antarvedyāṃ mahāprītyā sampraviśya himādriṇā ||
yatra sā pārvatī kanyā sarvābharaṇabhūṣitā || 45 ||
vedikopari tanvaṃgī saṃsthitā suvirājitā ||
taṃtra nīto mahādevo viṣṇunā ca mayā saha || 46 ||
lagnannirīkṣa māṇāste vācaspatipurogamāḥ ||
kanyādānocitantatraṃ babhūvuḥ paramotsavāḥ || 47 ||
tatropaviṣṭo gargaśca yatrāsti ghaṭikālayam ||
yāvaccheṣā ghaṭī tāvatkṛtampraṇava bhāṣaṇam || 48 ||
puṇyāhampravadangargassamādatre'ñjalimmudā ||
pārvvatyākṣatapūrṇa ca vavṛṣe caṃ śivopari || 49 ||
tayā sampūjito rudro dadhyakṣatakuśāmbubhiḥ||
paramodāḍhyayā tatra pārvatyā rucirāsyayā ||50||
vilokayantīṃ taṃ śambhuṃ yasyārthe paramantapaḥ ||
kṛtampurā mahāprītyā virarāja śivāti sā ||51||
mayā mune tadoktastu gargādimunibhiśca saḥ ||
samānarca śivāṃ śambhulaukikācārasaṃrataḥ || 52 ||
evaṃ parasparaṃ tau vai pārvvatīparame śvarau |
arcayantau tadānīñca śuśubhāte jaganmayau ||53||
trailokyalakṣmyā saṃvītau nirīkṣantau parasparam ||
tadā nīrājitau lakṣmyādibhistrībhirviśe pataḥ || 54 ||
tathā parā vai dvijayoṣitaśca nīrājayāmāsuratho purastriyaḥ ||
śivāñca śambhuñca vilokayantyo'vāpumudantāssakalā mahotsavam ||55||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe śivahimagirigṛhābhyantaragamanotsavavarṇanaṃ nāma saptacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 47 || ||
brahmovāca ||
etasminnaṃtare tatra gargācāryyapraṇoditaḥ ||
himavānmenayā sārddhaṃ kanyāṃ dātuṃ pracakrame || 1 ||
haimaṃ kalaśamādāya menā: cārddhāṃgamā śritā ||
himādreśca mahābhāgā vastrābharaṇabhūṣitā || 2 ||
pādyādibhistataḥ śailaḥ prahṛṣṭaḥ sapurohitaḥ ||
taṃ varaṃ varayāmāsa vastracaṃdanabhūṣaṇaiḥ || 3 ||
tato himādriṇā proktā dvijāstithyādikīrtane ||
prayogo bhaṇyatāṃ tāvadasminsamaya āgate ||4||
tatheti coktvā te sarve kālajñā dvijasattamāḥ ||
tithyā dikīrtanaṃ cakruḥ prītyā paramanirvṛtāḥ || 5 ||
tato himācalaḥ prītyā śaṃbhunā prerito hṛdā ||
sūtīkṛtaḥ peraśana vihasaśaṃbhumabravīt ||6||
svagotraṃ kathya tāṃ śambho pravaraśvakulaṃ tathā ||
nāma vedaṃ tathā śākhāṃ mākārṣīssamayātyayam || 7 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityākarṇya vacastasya himādreśśaṃkara stadā ||
susukhāvimukhaḥ sadyo'pyaśocyaḥ śocyatāṃ gataḥ || 8 ||
evaṃvidhassuravarairmunibhistadānīṃ gaṃdharvayakṣagaṇasiddhagaṇaistathaiva ||
