bhagavānmaheśo'kārṣīssuhāsyamatha tatra sa nāradaḥ tvam || 9 ||
vīṇāmavādayastvaṃ hi brahmavijño'tha nārada ||
śivena preritastatra manasā śaṃbhumānasaḥ || || 10 ||
tadā nivārito dhīmānparvateṃdreṇa vai haṭhāt ||
viṣṇunā ca mayā devairmunibhiścākhilaistathā || 11 ||
na nivṛtto'bhavastvaṃ hi sa yadā śaṃkarecchayā ||
iti prokto'driṇā tarhi vīṇāmāvādayādhunā || 12 ||
suniṣiddho haṭhāttena devarṣe tvaṃ yadā budha ||
pratyavoco girīśaṃ taṃ susaṃsmṛtya maheśvaram || 13 || ||
nārada uvāca ||
tvaṃ hi mūḍhatvamāpanno na jānāsi ca kiṃcana ||
vācye maheśaviṣaye'tīvāsi tvaṃ vahirmukhaḥ || 14 ||
tvayā pṛṣṭo harassākṣātsvagotrakathanaṃ prati ||
samaye'smi~tadatyaṃtamupahāsakaraṃ vacaḥ || 15 ||
asya gotreṃ kulaṃ nāma naiva jānaṃti parvata ||
viṣṇubrahmādayo'pīha pareṣāṃ kā kathā smṛtā || 16 ||
yasyaikadivase, śaila brahmakoṭirlayaṃ gatā ||
sa eva śaṃkarastedya dṛṣṭaḥ kālītapobalāt || 17 ||
arūpo'yaṃ parabrahma nirguṇaḥ prakṛteḥ paraḥ ||
nirākāro nirvikāro māyādhīśaḥ parātparaḥ || 18 ||
agotrakulanāmā hi svataṃtra bhaktavatsalaḥ ||
tadicchayā hi saṃguṇassutanu bahunāmabhṛt || 19 ||
sugotrī gotrahīnaśca kulahīnaḥ kalīnakaḥ ||
pārvatītapasā so'dya jā mātā te na saṃśayaḥ || 20 ||
līlāvihāriṇā tena mohitaṃ ca carācaram |
no jānāti śivaṃ ko'pi prājño'pi girisattamaṃ || 21 ||
liṃgākṛtermahe śasya kena dṛṣṭaṃ na mastakam ||
viṣṇurgatvāhi pātālaṃ tadenaṃ nāpa vismitaḥ ||22||
kiṃvahūktyā nagaśreṣṭha śivamāyā duratyayā ||
tadadhīnāstrayo lokā haribrahmā dayopi ca || 23 ||
tasmāttvayā śivātāta suvicārya prayatnataḥ ||
na kartavyo vimarśo'tra tvevaṃvidhavare manāk || 24 ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā tvaṃ sune jñānī śivacchākāryakārakaḥ ||
pratyavocaḥ punastaṃ vai śaileṃdraṃ harṣayan girā || 25 ||
nārada uvāca ||
śṛṇu tāta mahāśaila śivājanaka madracaḥ ||
tacchrutvā tanayāṃ devīṃ dehi tvaṃ śaṃkarāya hi || 26 ||
saguṇasya maheśasya līlayā rūpadhāriṇaḥ ||
gotraṃ kulaṃ vijānīhi nādameva hi kevalam ||27||
śivo nādamayaḥ satyaṃ nādaśśivamayastathā ||
ubhayoraṃtaraṃ nāsti nādasya ca śivasya ca || 28||
sṛṣṭau prathamajatvāddhi līlāsaguṇarūpiṇaḥ ||
śivānnā dasya śaileṃdra sarvotkṛṣṭastatassa hi || 29 ||
ato hi vāditā vīṇā preritena mayādya vai ||
sarveśvareṇa manasā śaṃkareṇa himālaya || 30 ||
brahmovāca ||
etacchrutvā tava mune vacastattu giriśvaraḥ||
himādristopamāpanno gatavismayamānasaḥ ||31||
atha viṣṇuprabhṛtayassurāśca munayastathā ||
sādhusādhviti te sarve procurvigatavismayāḥ || 32 ||
maheśvarasya gāṃbhīrya jñātvā sarve vicakṣaṇāḥ ||
savismayā mahāmodānvitāḥ procuḥ parasparam || 33 ||
yasyā jñayā jagadidaṃ ca viśālameva jātaṃ parātparataro nijabodharūpaḥ ||
śarvaḥ svataṃtragati kṛtparabhāvagamyasso'sau trilokapatiradya ca nassudṛṣṭaḥ || 34 ||
--- Page 238 [gcv] ---
atha te parvataśreṣṭhā mervādyājātasaṃbhramāḥ ||
ūcuste caikapadyena himavaṃtaṃ nageśvaram || 35 ||
parvatā ūcuḥ ||
kanyādāne sthīyatāṃ cādya śailanātheoktayā kiṃ kāryanāśastavaiva ||
satyaṃ brūmo nātra kāryoṃ vimarśastasmātkanyā dīyatāmīśvarāya || 36 ||
brahmovāca ||
tacchrutvā vacanaṃ teṣāṃ suhṛdāṃ sa himā layaḥ ||
svakanyādānamakarocchivāya vidhinoditaḥ || 37 ||
imāṃ kanyāṃ tubhyamahaṃ dadāmi parameśvara |
bhāyārthaṃ parigṛhṇīṣva prasīda sakaleśvara || 38 ||
tasmai rudrāya mahate maṃtreṇānena dattavān ||
himācalo nijāṃ kanyāṃ pārvatīṃ trijagatprasūm || 39 ||
itthaṃ śivākaraṃ śailaṃ śivahaste nighāya ca ||
mumodātīva manasi tīrṇakāmamahārṇavaḥ || 40 ||
vedamaṃtreṇa giriśo girijākarapaṅkajam ||
jagrāha svakareṇāśu prasannaḥ parameśvaraḥ || 41 ||
kṣitiṃ saṃspṛśya kāmasya kodāditi manuṃ mune ||
papāṭha śaṃkaraḥ prītyā darśayadyaukikīṃ gatim || 42 ||
mahotsavo mahānāsītsarvatra pramudāvahaḥ ||
babhūva jayasaṃrāvo divi bhramyaṃtarikṣa ke || 43 ||
sādhuśabdaṃ namaḥ śabdaṃ cakrussarve'ti harṣitā |
gaṃdharvāssujaguḥ prītyā nanṛtu śvāpsarogaṇāḥ || 44 ||
himācalasya paurā hi mumuduścati cetasi ||
maṃgalaṃ mahadāsīdvai mahotsavapurassaram || 45 ||
ahaṃ viṣṇuśca śakraśca nirjarā munayo'khilāḥ ||
harṣitā hyabhavaśvātipraphullavadanāmbujāḥ || 46 ||
atha śailavarassodātsuprasanno himācalaḥ ||
śivāya kanyādānasya sāṃgatāṃ suyatho citām || 47 ||
tato bandhujanāstasya śivāṃ sampūjya bhaktitaḥ ||
daduśśivāya saddravyaṃ nānāvidhividhānataḥ || 48 ||
himālayastuṣṭamanāḥ pārvatī śivaprītaye ||
nānāvidhāni dravyāṇi dadau tatra sunīśvara || 49 ||
kautukāni dadau tasmai ratnāni vividhāni ca ||
cāruratnavikārāṇi pātrāṇi vividhāni ca || 50 ||
gavāṃ lakṣaṃ hayānāṃ ca sajjitānāṃ śataṃtathā ||
dāsīnāmanuraktānāṃ lakṣaṃ sadravyabhūṣitam || 51 ||
nāgānāṃ śatalakṣaṃ hi sthānāṃ ca tathā sune ||
suvarṇajaṭitānāṃ ca ratnasāravinirmitam ||52||
itthaṃ himālayo datvā svasutāṃ girijāṃ śivām ||
śivāya parameśāya vidhinā S'pakṛtārthatām ||53||
atha śailavaro mādhyaṃdinoktastotrato mudā |
tuṣṭāva parameśānaṃ sagirā sukṛtāñjaliḥ || 54 ||
tato vedavidā tenājñaptā muni gaṇāstadā ||
śiro'bhiṣekaṃ cakruste _śivāyāḥ paraṃmotsavāḥ || 55 ||
devābhidhānamuccāryya paryukṣaṇavidhiṃ vyadhuḥ ||
mahotsavastadā cāsīnmahānandakaro mune || 56 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ tṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe kanyādānavarṇanaṃ * nāmāṣṭacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 48 || ||
