C . śivaḥ ||
lājāñjaliṃ dadau kālībhrātā mainākasaṃjñakaḥ || 2 ||
atha kālī śivaśvobhau cakraturvidhivanmudā ||
vahnipradakṣiṇāṃ tāta . lokācāraṃ vidhāya ca || 3 ||
tatrādbhutamalañcake caritaṃ girijāpatiḥ ||
tadeva śṛṇu devarṣe tavasnehāṃdbravīmyaham || 4 ||
tasminnavasare cāhaṃ śivamāyāvimohitaḥ ||
apa śyañcaraṇe devyā nakhenduñca manoharam || 5 ||
darśanāttasya ca tadā 'bhūvaṃ deva mune hyaham ||
madanena samāviṣṭo'tīva kṣubhitamāna saḥ || 6 ||
muhurmuhurapaśyaṃ vai tadaṃgaṃ smaramohitaḥ ||
tatastadarśanātsadyo vīrya me prācyutadbhuvi || 7 ||
retasā kṣaratā tena lajjito haṃ pitāmahaḥ ||
sune vyamarda tacchinaṃ caraṇābhyāṃ hi gopayan || 8 ||
tajjñātvā ca mahādevaścukopātīva nārada ||
hantumaicchattadā śīghraṃ māṃ vidhi kāmamohitam || 9 ||
hāhākāro mahānāsīttatra sarvatra nārada ||
janāścakampire sarvve bhayamāyāti viśvabhṛt || 10 ||
tatastantuṣṭuvuśśambhuṃ viṣṇvādyā nirjarā mune ||
sakopamprajvalantantantejasā hantumudyatam || 11 ||
devā ūcuḥ || ||
devadeva jagadvyāpinparameśa sadāśiva ||
jagadīśa jagannātha samprasīda jaganmaya || 12 ||
sarveṣāmapi bhāvānāntvamātmā heturīśvaraḥ |
nirvikāro'vyayo nityo nirvikalpo'kṣaraḥ paraḥ || 13 ||
ādyantāvasya yanmadhyamidamanyadahambahiḥ ||
yato'vyayaḥ sanaitāni tatsatyambrahma cidbhavān ||14||
tavaiva caraṇāmbhojammuktikāmā dṛḍhavratāḥ ||
visṛjyo bhayatassaṃgaṃ munayassamupāsate || 15 ||
tvambrahma pūrṇamamṛtaṃ viśoka nirguṇamparam ||
ānaṃdamātramavyagramavikāramanātmakam || 16 ||
viśvasya hetu rudayasthitisaṃyamanasya hi ||
tadapekṣatayātmeśo'napakṣassarvadā vibhuḥ || 17 ||
ekastvameva sadasaddayamaddayameva ca ||
svarṇa kṛtākṛtamiva vastubhedo nacaiva hi || 18 ||
ajñānatastvayi janairvikalpo vidito yataḥ ||
tasmāddhamapratīkāro nirupādherna hi svataḥ|| 19 ||
dhanyā vayaṃ maheśāna tava darśanamā trataḥ ||
dṛḍhabhaktajanānandapradaśśambho dayāṃ kuru || 20 ||
tvamādistvamanādiśva prakṛtestvaṃ paraḥ pumān ||
viśveśvaro jagannātho nirvikāraḥ parātparaḥ || 21 ||
yo'yaṃ brahmāsti rajasā viśvamūrttiḥ pitāmahaḥ ||
tvatprasādātprabho viṣṇussattvena puruṣottamaḥ || 22 ||
kālāgnirudrastamasā paramātmā guṇaiḥ paraḥ ||
sadāśivo maheśānassarvavyāpī maheśvaraḥ || 23 ||
vyaktaṃ mahacca bhūtādistanmātrāṇīndriyāṇi ca ||
tvayairvādhiṣṭhitānyeva viśvamūrte mahe śvara || 24 ||
mahādeva pareśāna karuṇākara śaṅkara ||
prasīda devadevaśa prasīda puruṣottama || 29 ||
vāsāṃsi sāgarāssaptaṃ diśaścaiva mahābhujāḥ ||
dyaurmū ddhī te vibhornābhiḥ khaṃ vāyurnāsikā tataḥ || 26 ||
cakṣūṃṣyaśrī ravissomaḥ keśā meghāstava prabho ||
nakṣatratārakādyāśva grahāścaiva vibhūṣaṇam || 27 ||
