• A kathaṃ stoṣyāmi deveśa tvāṃ vibho parameśvara ||
vācāmagocaro'si tvaṃ manasā cāpi śaṅkara || 28 ||
pañcāsyāya ca rudrāya pañcāśatkoṭimūrtaye ||
tryadhipāya variṣṭhāya vidyātattvāya te namaḥ || 29 ||
anirdeśyāya nityāya vidyujjvālāya rūpiṇe ||
agnivarṇāya devāya śaṃkarāya namonamaḥ || 30 ||
vidyutkoṭipratakiāśamaṣṭakoṇaṃ suśobhanam ||
rūpamāsthāya loke'sminsaṃsthitāya namo namaḥ || 31 ||
brahmovāca || ||
ityākarṇya vaca steṣāṃ prasannaḥ parameśvaraḥ ||
brahmaṇo me dadau śīghramabhayaṃ bhaktavatsalaḥ || 32 ||
atha sarve surāstatra viṣṇvādyā sunayastathā ||
abhavatsusmitāstāta cakruśca paramotsavam ||33||
mama tadetasā tāta marditena muhurmuhuḥ ||
abhavankaṇakāstatra bhūriśaḥ paramo'jjvalāḥ || 34 ||
ṛṣayo bahavo jātā bālakhi lyāssahasraśaḥ ||
kaṇakaistaiśca vīryasya prajvaladbhiḥ svatejasā || 35 ||
atha te hyṛṣayassarve upatasthustadā mune ||
mamāntikaṃ paraprītyā tāta tāteti cābruvam || 36 ||
īśvarecchāprayuktena proktāste nāradena hi ||
bālakhilyāstu te taṃtra kopayuktena cetasā || 37 ||
nārada uvāca ||
gacchadhvaṃ saṃgatā yūyaṃ parvataṃ gandhamādanam ||
na sthātavyambhavadbhiśva na hi vo'tra prayojanam || 38 ||
tatra tatvā tapaścāti bhavitāro munīśvarāḥ ||
sūryyaśiṣyāśśivasyaivājñayā me kathitantvidam || 39 || ||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktāste tadā sarve bālakhilyāśca parvatam ||
satvaramprayayurnatvā śaṃkaraṃ gandhamādanam || 40 ||
viṣṇvādibhistadābhūvaṃ śvāsitohaṃ munīśvara ||
nirbhayaḥ parameśānapreritaistairmahātmabhiḥ || 41 ||
astavañcāpi sarveśaṃ śaṃkara mbhaktavatsalam ||
sarvakāryakaraṃ jñātvā duṣṭagarvāpahārakam ||42||
devadeva mahādeva karuṇāsāgara prabho ||
tvameva kartā sarvasya bhartā harttā ca sarvathā ||43||
tvadicchayā hi sakalaṃ sthitaṃ hi sacarācaram ||
tantyāṃ yathā balīvardā mayā jñātaṃ viśeṣataḥ || 44 ||
ityevamuktvā sohaṃ vai prāṇamaṃ ca kṛtāñjaliḥ ||
anye'pi tuṣṭuvussarve viṣṇvādyāstaṃ maheśvaram || 45 ||
athākarṇya nutiṃ śuddhāṃ mama dīnatayā tadā ||
viṣṇvādīnāñca sarveṣāṃ prasanno'bhūnmaheśvaraḥ || || 46 ||
dado sotivaraṃ mahyamabhayaṃ prītamānasaḥ ||
sarve sukhamatīvāpuratyamoda mahaṃ sune || 47 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitā yāntṛtīye pārvatīkhaṇḍe vidhimohavarṇanaṃ nāma navacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 49 || ||
brahmovāca ||
tataścāhaṃ munigaṇaiśśeṣakṛtyaṃ śivājñayā ||
akārṣa nārada prītyā śivāśivavivāhataḥ || 1 ||
tayośśiro'bhiṣekaśca babhūvādaratastataḥ ||
dhruvasyaṃ darśanaṃ viprāḥ kārayāmāsurādarāt || 2 ||
hṛdayālambhanaṃ karma babhūva tadanantaram ||
svastipāṭhaśca viprendra mahotsavaṃpurassaraḥ || 3 ||
śivāśirasi sindūraṃ dadau śambhurdvijājñayā ||
tadānīṃ girijābhikhyādbhu 1 ātmanepadamārṣam |
