tato viprājñayā tau dvāvekāsanasamāsthitau ||
lebhāte paramāṃ śobhāṃ bhaktacittamudāvahām || 5 ||
tataḥ svasthānamāgatya saṃśravaprāśanaṃ mudā ||
cakratustau nideśānme'dbhutalīlākarau sune || 6 ||
itthaṃ nivṛtte vidhivadyājñe vaivāhike śivaḥ ||
brahmaṇe pūrṇapātraṃ me dadau loka kṛte prabhuḥ || 7 ||
godānaṃ vidhivacchambhurācāryāya dadau tataḥ ||
mahādānāni ca prītyā yāni maṅgaladāni vai || 8 ||
tataśśatasuvarṇa ca viprebhyassa dadau pṛthak ||
bahubhyo ratnakoṭīśca nānādravyāṇyanekaśaḥ ||9||
tadānīmamarāssarve pare jīvāścarācarāḥ ||
muduścetasātīva babhūvāti jayadhvaniḥ||10||
maṅgalaṃghvanigānañca babhūva bahu sarvataḥ ||
vādyadhvanirabhūdramyo sarvānandapravarddhanaḥ || 11 ||
harirmayātha devāśca munayaścāpare'khilāḥ ||
girimāmantrya suprītyā svasthānamprayayurddhatam || 12 ||
tadānīṃ śailanagare striyaśca muditā varam ||
śivāśivau samānīyaṃ yayuḥ kuhavarālayam || 13 ||
laukikā cāramājahustāḥ striyastatra cāhatāḥ ||
mahotsāho babhūvātha sarvataḥ pramudāvahaḥ || 14 ||
atha tāstau samānīya dampatījanaśaṃkarau ||
vāsālayaṃmmahā divyaṃ bhavācāraṃ vyadhurmudā || 15 ||
atho samīpamāgatya śailendranagarastriyaḥ ||
nirvṛtya maṅgalaṃ karma prāpayandampatī gṛham || 16 ||
kṛtvā jayadhvaniṃ cakkuryanthinimacanādikam ||
sasmitāssakaṭākṣāśca pulakāṃñcitavigrahāḥ|| 17||
vāsagehaṃ sampraviśya mumuhuḥ kāminīvarāḥ ||
praśaṃsantyassvabhāgyāni paśyantaḥ parameśvaram || 18 ||
mahāsurūpaveṣañca sarvalāvaṇyasaṃyutam ||
navīnayauvanasthañca kāminīcittamohanam ||19||
īṣaddhāsyaprasa nnāsyaṃ sakaṭākṣaṃ susundaram ||
susūkṣmavāso vibhrāṇaṃ nānāratnavibhūṣitam|| 20 ||
tadānīndivyanāryaśca ṣoḍaśāraṃ samāyayuḥ||
tau dampatī ca draṣṭuṃ mahā darapurassaram ||21||
sarasvatī ca lakṣmīśca sāvitrī jāhnavī tathā ||
aditiśca śacī caiva lopāmudrāpyarundhatī || 22 ||
ahalyā tulasī svāhā rohiṇī ca vasundharā ||
śatta rūpā ca saṃjñā ca ratiretāssurastriyaḥ||23||
devakanyā nāgakanyā' sunikanyā manoharāḥ||
tatra yā yāḥ sthitāstāsāṃ saṅkhyāṃ kartuṃ ca kaḥ kṣamaḥ|| 24 ||
tābhī ratnāsane datte tatrovāsa śivo mudā ||
tamūcuḥ kramato devyassuhāsaṃ madhuraṃ vacaḥ || 25 ||
sarasvatyuvāca ||
prāptā satī mahādevādhunā prāṇādhikā mudā ||
dṛṣṭvā priyāsyañcandrābhaṃ santāpantyaja kāmuka || 26 ||
kālaṃ gamaya kāleśa satīsaṃśleṣapūrvakam ||
viśleṣastena bhavitā sarvakālaṃ mamāśritā ||27|| ||
lakṣmīruvāca ||
lajjāṃ vihāya deveśa satīṃ kṛtvā svavakṣasi ||
tiṣṭha tāmprati kā lajjā prāṇā yānti yayā vinā || 28 ||
sāvitryuvāca ||
bhoja yitvā satīṃ śambho śīghraṃ tvaṃ bhuṃkṣvamākhidaḥ ||
tadācamya sakarpūrantāṃbūlaṃ dehi sādaram || 29 ||
jāhnavyuvāca ||
svarṇakāntikarāṃ dhṛtvā keśānmārjaya yoṣitaḥ ||
kāminyāssvāmisaubhāgyasukhaṃ nātaḥ paraṃ bhavet || 30 ||
aditiruvāca ||
bhojanānte śivāṃ śambhuṃ mukhaṃ śuddhayarthamādarāt ||
