lapsyase sarvaśastrāṇi tārakākhyaṃ || 53 ||
tvaṃ viśvasaṃhastviāṃ prāmuñcākṣamā imāḥ ||
nāgniṃ goptuṃ yathā śaktaśśuṣkavṛkṣasscakoṭare || 54 ||
dīptavāṃstvaṃ ca viśveṣu nāsāṃ geheṣu śobhase ||
yathā patanmahākūpe dvijarājo na rājate || 55 ||
karoṣi ca yathāsslokaṃ nā''cchanno'smāsu tejasā ||
yathā sūryaḥ kalāchanno na bhavenmānavasya ca || 96 ||
viṣṇustvaṃ jagatāṃ vyāpī nānyo jātosi śāṃbhava ||
yathā na keṣāṃ vyāpyaṃ ca tatsarvaṃ vyāpakaṃ nabhaḥ || 57 ||
yogīndro nā'nuliptaśca bhāgī cetparipoṣaṇe ||
naiva lipto yathātmā ca karmayogeṣu jīvinām || 58 ||
viśvāraṃbhastvamīśaśca nāsu te saṃbhavet sthitiḥ ||
guṇānāṃ tejasāṃ rāśiryathātmānaṃ ca yoginaḥ || 59 ||
bhrātayai tvāṃ na jānaṃti te narā hatabuddhayaḥ ||
nādriyante yathā bhekāstvekavāsāśca paṃkajān || 60 ||
kārtikeya uvāca || ||
bhrātassarvaṃ vijānāsi jñānaṃ traikālikaṃ ca yat ||
jñānī tvaṃ kā praśaṃsā te yato mṛtyuñjayāśritaḥ || 61 ||
karmaṇāṃ janma yeṣāṃ vā yāsu yāsu ca yoniṣu ||
tāsu te nirvṛtiṃ bhrātaḥ prāpnuvatīha sāṃpratam || 62 ||
kṛttikā jñāna vatyaśca yoginyaḥ prakṛteḥ kalāḥ ||
stanyenāsāṃ varddhito'hamupakāreṇa saṃtatam || 63 ||
āsāmahaṃ poṣyaputro madaṃśā yoṣitastvimāḥ ||
tasyāśca prakṛteraṃśāstatastatsvāmivīryajaḥ || 64 ||
na mahaṃgo ha śailendrakanyāyā nandikeśvara ||
sā ca me dharmato mātā yathemāssarvasaṃmatāḥ || 65 ||
śambhu nā preṣitastvaṃ ca śaṃbhoḥ putrasamo mahān |
āgacchāmi tvayā sārddhaṃ drakṣyāmi devatākulam || 66 ||
ityevamuktvā taṃ śīghraṃ saṃbodhya kṛttikāgaṇam ||
kārttikeyaḥ pratasthe hi sārddhaṃ śaṃkarapārṣadaiḥ || 67 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ caturthe kumārakhaṇḍe kārttikeyānveṣaṇana ndisaṃvādavarṇanaṃ nāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ || 4 ||
brahmovāca ||
etasminnaṃtare tatra dadarśa rathamuttamam ||
adbhutaṃ śobhitaṃ śaśvadviśvakarmāvinirmitam || || 1 ||
śatacakraṃ suvistīrṇa manoyāyi manoharam ||
prasthāpitaṃ ca pārvatyā veṣṭitaṃ pārṣadairvairaiḥ || 2 ||
samārohattato'naṃto hṛdayena vidūyatā ||
kārtikaḥ paramajñānī parameśānavīryajaḥ || 3 ||
tadaiva kṛttikāḥ prāpya muktakeśyaśśucā''turāḥ ||
unmattā iva tatraiva vakkumārebhire vacaḥ || 4 ||
--- Page 262 [gcv] ---
na kṛttikā ūcuḥ ||
vihāyā'smān kṛpāsindho gacchasi tvaṃ hi nirdayaḥ ||
nāyaṃ dharmo mātṛvargān pālitoḥ yat sutastyajet || 5 ||
snehena varddhito'smābhiḥ putro'smākaṃ ca dharmataḥ ||
kiṃ kurmaḥ kva ca yāsyāmo vayaṃ kiṃ karavāma ha || 6 ||
ityuktvā kṛtikāssarvāḥ kṛtvā vakṣasi kārtikam ||
drutaṃ mūrcchāmavāpustāssutavicchedakāraṇāt || 7 ||
tāḥ kumāro bodhayitvā adhyātmavacanena vai ||
tābhiśca pārṣadaissārddhamāruroha rathaṃ mune || 8 ||
dṛṣṭvā śrutvā maṃgalāni bahūni sukhadāni vai ||
kumāraḥ pārṣadaissārddhaṃ jagāma pitṛmandiram || 9 ||
dakṣeṇa naṃdiyuktaśca manoyāyirathena ca ||
kumāraḥ prāpa kailāsaṃ nyagrodhā'kṣayamūlake || 10 ||
tatra tasthau kṛttikābhiḥ pārṣadapravaraiḥ saha ||
kumāraśśāṃkariḥ prīto nānālīlāviśāradaḥ ||11||
tadā sarve suragaṇā ṛṣayaḥ siddhacāraṇāḥ ||
viṣṇunā brahmaṇā sārddhaṃ samācakhyustadāgamam || 12 ||
tadā dṛṣṭvā ca gāṃgeyaṃ yayau pramuditaśśivaḥ ||
anyai rusameto hariṇā brahmaṇā ca surarṣibhiḥ || 13 ||
śaṃkhāśca bahavo nedubhairītūryāṇyanekaśaḥ ||
utsavassumahānāsīddevānāṃ tuṣṭacetasām || 14 ||
tadā nīmeva taṃ sarve vīrabhadrādayo gaṇāḥ ||
kurvantaḥ svanvayuḥ keliṃ nānātāladharasvarāḥ ||15||
stāvakāḥ stūyamānāśca cakruste guṇakīrttanam ||
jayaśabda namaśśabdaṃ kurvāṇāḥ prītamānasāḥ||
draṣṭuṃ yayustaṃ śarajaṃ śivātmajamanuttamam || 16 || 17 ||
pārvatī maṃgalaṃ cakre rājamārga manoharam ||
padmarāgādima ṇibhi ssaṃskṛtaṃ paritaḥ puram || 18 ||
patiputravatībhiśva sādhvībhiḥ strībhiranvitāḥ ||
lakṣmyāditriṃśadevīśca puraḥ kṛtvā samāyayau || 19 ||
rambhādyapsarasoṃ divyāssasmitā veṣasaṃyutāḥ ||
saṃgītanartanaparā babhruvuśca śivājñayā || 20 ||
ye taṃ samīkṣayāmāsurgāṃgeyaṃ śaṃkaro pamam ||
dardṛśuste mahattejo vyāptamāsījjagatraye || 21 ||
tattejasā vṛtaṃ bālaṃ taptacāmīkaraprabham ||
vavaṃdire drutaṃ sarve kumāraṃ sūryavarcasam || 22 ||
jahaṣurvinataskaṃdhā namaśśabdaratāstadā ||
parivāryopatasthuste vāmadakṣiṇamāgatāḥ || 23 ||
ahaṃ viṣṇuśca śakraśca tathā devādayo'khilāḥ ||
daṇḍava tpatitā bhūmau parivāryyaṃ kumārakam ||24||
etasminnantare śaṃbhurgirijā ca mudānvitā ||
mahotsavaṃ samāgamya dadarśa tanayaṃ mudā || 25 ||
putraṃ nirīkṣya ca tadā jagadekabaṃdhuḥ prītyānvitaḥ paramayā parayā bhavānyā ||
snehānvito bhujagabhogayuto hi sākṣātsarveśvaraḥ parivṛtaḥ pramathaiḥ pareśaḥ || 26 ||
atha śaktidharaḥ skando dṛṣṭvā tau pārvatīśivau ||
avaruhya rathāttūrṇaṃ śirasā praṇanāma ha || 27 ||
upaguhya śivaḥ prītyā kumāraṃ mūrdhni śaṃkaraḥ ||
jatrau premṇā pareśānaḥ prasannaḥ snehakartṛkaḥ || 28 ||
upaguhya guhaṃ tatra pārvatī jātasaṃbhramā ||
prasrutaṃ pāyayāmāsa stanaṃ snehapariplutā || 29 ||
tadā nīrā 168 jito devaissakalatrairmudānvitaiḥ ||
jayaśabdena mahatā vyāptamāsīnnabhastalam || 30 ||
ṛṣayo brahmaghoṣeṇa gītenaiva ca gāyakāḥ ||
vādyaiśca bahavastatro .

