balaina bahu kurvantaḥ siṃhanādaṃ visismiyuḥ ||4||
tadā nabho''ṅganā vāṇīṃ jagādopari satvaram ||
śaṅkarapreritā. sadyo haryādīnakhilān surān ||5 || ||
vyomavāṇyuvāca ||
kumāraṃ ca puraskṛtya surā yūyaṃ samudyatāḥ ||
daityān vijitya saṃgrāme jayino'tha bhaviṣyatha || 6 || ||
brahmovāca ||
vācaṃ tu khecaroṃ śrutvā devāssarve samutsukāḥ ||
vīraśabdān prakurvato nirbhayā hyabhavaṃstadā || 7 ||
kumāraṃ ca puraskṛtya sarve te jātasādhvasāḥ ||
yoddhukāmāssurā jagmurmahīsāgara saṃgamam || 8 ||
ājagāma drutaṃ tatra yatra devāssatārakaḥ ||
sainyena mahatā sārddhaṃ surairbahubhirāvṛtaḥ || 9 ||
raṇaduṃdubhayo neduḥ pralayāṃbudanissvanāḥ ||
karka śāni ca vādyāni parāṇi ca tadāgame || 10 ||
garjamānāstadā daityāstārakeṇāsureṇa ha ||
kaṃpayanto bhuvaṃ pādakramaivalgunakārakāḥ || 11 ||
tacchu tvā ravamatyugraṃ sarve devā vinirbhayāḥ ||
aikapadyena cottasthuyauddhakāmāśca tārakam || 12 ||
gajamāropya devendraḥ kumāraṃ hyagrato'bhavat ||
surasainyena mahatā lokapālaissamāvṛtaḥ || 13 ||
tadā duṃdubhayo nedurbherītūryāṇyanekaśaḥ ||
vīṇāveṇumṛdaṃgāniḥ tathā gaṃdharvanissvanāḥ || 14 ||
gajaṃ datvā mahe ndrāya kumāro yānamāruhat ||
anekāścaryasaṃbhūtaṃ nānāratnasamanvitam ||15||
vimānamāruhya tadā mahāyaśāstra śāṃkarissarvaguṇairupetaḥ||
śriyā sametaḥ parayā babhau mahān saṃvījyamānaśvamarairmahāprabhaiḥ || 16 ||
prācetasaṃ chatramatīvasuprabhaṃ ratnairupetaṃ vividhairvirājitam ||
dhṛtaṃ tadā tacca kumāramūrdhni vai hyanantacāndraiḥ kiraṇairmahāprabhaiḥ || 17 ||
militāste tadā sarve devāśśakrapurogamāḥ ||
svaiḥsvairbalaiḥ parivṛtā yuddhakāmā mahābalāḥ || 18 ||
evaṃ devāśca daityāśca yoddhukāmāḥ sthitā avi ||
sainyena mahatā tena vyūhaṃ kṛtvā pṛthak pṛthak || 19 ||
te sene suradaityānāṃ śuśubhāte para sparam ||
haṃtukāme tadānyonyaṃ stūyamāne ca vandibhiḥ || 20 ||
ubhe sene tadā teṣāmagarjeta vanopame ||
bhayaṃkare'tyavīrāṇāmitareṣāṃ sukhāvahe || 21 ||
etasminnantare tatra balonmattāḥ parasparam ||
daityā devā mahāvīrā yuyudhuḥ krodhavihvalāḥ || 22 ||
