. yuddhaṃ devadaityasamākulam ||
ruṇḍamuṃḍāṃkitaṃ sarvaṃ kṣaṇena samapadyata || 23 ||
bhūmau nipatitāstatra śataśo'tha sahasraśaḥ ||
nikṛttāṃgā mahāśastrairnihatā vīrasaṃmatāḥ || 24 ||
keṣāṃcidvāhavaśchinnāḥ khaḍgapātaissudāruṇaiḥ ||
keṣāṃcidūravaśchinnā vīrāṇāṃ mānināṃ mṛdhe || 25 ||
kecinmathita sarvāṃgā gadābhirmudgaraistathā ||
kecinnibhinnahṛdayāḥ pāśairbhalaiśca pātitāḥ ||26||
kecidvidāritāḥ pṛṣṭhe kuṃtaiṛṣṭibhiraṃkuśaiḥ ||
chinnānyapi śirāṃsyeva patitāni ca bhūtale ||27||
bahūni ca kabaṃdhāni nṛtyamānāni tatra vai ||
valgamānāni śataśo udyatāstrakarāṇi ca || 28||
nadyaḥ pravartitā statra śataśo'sṛṅkahāstadā ||
bhūtapretādayastatra śataśaśca samāgatāḥ || 29 ||
gomāyavaśśivāstatra bhakṣayantaḥ palaṃ bahu ||
tathā gṛdhravaṭāśśyenā vā yasā māṃsabhakṣakāḥ ||
burbhujaḥ patitānāṃ caṃ palāni subahūni vai || 30 ||
etasminnantare tatra tārakākhyo mahābalaḥ |
sainyena mahatā sadyo yayau yoddhuṃ surān prati || 31 ||
devā dṛṣṭvā samāyāntaṃ tārakaṃ yuddhadurmadam ||
yoddhukāmaṃ tadā sadyo yayuśśakrādayastadā ||
babhūvātha mahonnādassenayorubhayorapi || || 32 ||
athābhūdvaṃdvayuddhaṃ hi surāsuravimardanam ||
yaṃ dṛṣṭvā harṣitā vīrāḥ kkībāśva bhayamāgatāḥ || 33 ||
tārako yayudhe yuddhe śakreṇa ditijo balī |
agninā saha saṃhrādo jaṃbhenaiva yamaḥ svayam || 34 ||
mahāprabhunairṛtena pāśī saha balena ca ||
suvīro vāyunā sārddhaṃ pavamānena guhyarāṭ || 35 ||
īśānena samaṃ śaṃbharyuyudhe raṇavittamaḥ ||
śuṃbhaśśeṣeṇa yuyudhe kuṃbhaścandreṇa dānavaḥ || 36 ||
kuṃjaro mihireṇāzau mahābalaparākramaḥ ||
yuyudhe paramāstraiśca nānāyuddhaviśāradaḥ || 37 ||
evaṃ indrena yuddhena mahatā ca surāsurāḥ ||
saṃgare yuyudhussarve balena kṛtaniścayāḥ || 38 ||
anyonyaṃ sparddhamānāste'ma rādaityā mahābalāḥ ||
tasmindevāsure yuddhe durjayā abhavanmune || 39 ||
tadā ca teṣāṃ suradānavānāṃ babhūva yuddhaṃ tumulaṃ jayaiṣiṇam ||
sukhāvahaṃ vīramanasvināṃ vai bhayāvahaṃ caiva tathetareṣām || 40 ||
mahī mahāraudratarā vinaṣṭakaissurāsurairvai patitairanekaśaḥ ||
tasminnagamyātibhayānakā tadā jātā mahā saukhyavahā manasvinām || 41 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ caturthe kumārakhaṇḍe yuddhaprāraṃbhavarṇanaṃ nāma saptamo'dhyāyaḥ || 7 ||
brahmovāca ||
iti te varṇitastāta devadānavasenayoḥ ||
saṃgrāmastumulo'tīva tatprabhvoḥ śṛṇu nārada || 1 ||
evaṃ yuddhe'titumule devadānavasaṃkṣaye ||
tārakeṇaiva devendraśśaktyā paramayā saha || 2 ||
sadyaḥ papāta nāgācca dharaṇyāṃ mūrcchito' bhavat ||
paraṃ kaśmalamāpede vajradhārī sureśvaraḥ || 3 ||
tathaiva lokapāssarve'suraiśca balavattaraiḥ ||
parājitā raṇe tāta mahāraṇaviśāradaiḥ || 4 ||
