iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ caturthe kumārakhaṃḍe devadaityasāmānyayuddhavarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭamo'dhyāyaḥ || 8|| ||
brahmovāca ||
devadeva guha svāmiśāṃkare pārvatīsuta ||
na śobhate raṇo viṣṇutā rakāsurayorvṛthā || 1 ||
viṣṇunā na hi vadhyo'sau tārako.. valavānati ||
mayādattavarastasmātsatyaṃ satyaṃ vadāmyaham || 2||
nānyo haṃtāsya, pāpasya tvāṃ vinā pārvatīsuta ||
tasmāttvayā hi kartavyaṃ vacanaṃ me mahāprabho || 3 ||
sannaddho bhava daityasya vadhāyāśu paraṃtapa ||
tadvadhārthaṃ samutpannaḥ śaṃkarāttvaṃ śivāsuta || 4 ||
rakṣa rakṣa mahāvīra tridaśānvyathitānraṇe ||
na vālastvaṃ yuvā naiva kiṃtu sarveśvaraḥ prabhuḥ || 5 ||
śakraṃ paśya tathā viṣṇuṃ vyākulaṃ ca

--- Page 270 [gcv] ---
surān gaṇān ||
evaṃ jahi mahādaityaṃ trailokyaṃ sukhitaṃ kuru || 6 ||
anena vijitaśvendro lokapālaiḥ purā saha ||
viṣṇuścāpi mahāvīro tarjitasta paso balāt || 7 ||
trailokyaṃ nirjitaṃ sarvamasureṇa durātmanā ||
idānīṃ tava sānnidhyātpunaryuddhaṃ kṛtaṃ ca taiḥ || 8 ||
tasmāttvayā nihatavyastārakaḥ pāpapūruṣaḥ ||
anyavadhyo na caivāyaṃ bhadvarācchaṃkarātmaja || 9 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti śrutvā mama vacaḥ kumāraḥ śaṃkarātmajaḥ ||
vijahāsa prasa nnātmā tathāstviti vaco'bravīt || 10 ||
viniścityāsuravadhaṃ śāṃkarissa mahāprabhuḥ ||
vimānādavatīryātha padātirabhavattadā || 11 ||
padbhyāṃ tadāsau paridhāvamāno reje'tivīraḥ śivajaḥ kumāraḥ ||
kare samādāya mahāprabhāṃ tāṃ śaktiṃ maholkāmiva dīptidīptām || 12 ||
dṛṣṭvā tamāyāṃtamatipracaṃḍa mavyākulaṃ ṣaṇmukhamaprameyam ||
daityo babhāṣe surasattamānsa kumāra eṣa dviṣatāṃ prahaṃtā || 13 ||
anena sākaṃ hyahamekavīro yotsye ca sarvānahameva vīrān ||
gaṇāṃśca sarvānapi ghātayāmi salokapālānharināyakāṃśca || 14 ||
ityevamuktvā sa tadā mahābalaḥ kumārasu diśya yayau ca yoddhum ||
jagrāha śaktiṃ paramādbhutāṃ ca sa tārako devavarānvabhāṣe || 15 || ||
tāraka uvāca ||
kumāro me'grataścādya bhavadbhiśva kathaṃ kṛtaḥ ||
yūyaṃ gatatrapā devā viśeṣācchakrameśvarau || 16 ||
puraitābhyāṃ kṛtaṃ karma viruddhaṃ vedamārgataḥ ||
tacchṛṇudhvaṃ mayā prokta varṇayāmi viśeṣataḥ || 17 ||
tatra viṣṇuśchalī doṣī hyavivekī viśeṣataḥ ||
baliyaina purā baiśchalamāśritya pāpataḥ || 18 ||
tenaiva yatnataḥ pūrvamasurau madhukaiṭabhau ||
śirohīnau kṛtau dhaurtyādvedamāgavivarjitaḥ || 19 ||
mohinīrūpa to'nena paṃktibhedaḥ kṛto hi vai ||
devāsurasudhāpāne vedamārgoṃ vigarhitaḥ || 20 ||
rāmo bhūtvā hatā nārī vālī vidhvaṃsito hi saḥ ||
puna vaiśravaṇovipro hato nītirhatā śruteḥ || 21 ||
pāpaṃ vinā svakīyā strī tyaktā pāparatena yat ||
tatrāpi śrutimārgaśca dhvaṃsitassvārthahetave || 22 ||
svajananyāśśiraśchinnamavatāre rasākhyake ||
guruputrāpamānaśca kṛto'nena durātmanā || 23 ||
kṛṣṇo bhūtvānyanāryaśca dūṣitāḥ kuladharmataḥ ||
śrutimārga parityajya svavivāhāḥ kṛtā stathā || 24 ||
punaśca vedamāgoṃ hi niṃdito navame bhave ||
sthāpitaṃ nāstikamataṃ. vedamārgavirodhakṛt || 25 ||
evaṃ yena kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ vedamārga visṛjya vai ||
sa kathaṃ vijayedyuddhe bhaveddharmavatāṃ varaḥ || 26 ||
bhrātā jeṣṭhaśca yastasya śakraḥ pāpī mahānmataḥ ||
tena pāpānyanekāni kṛtāni nijahetutaḥ || 27 ||
nikṛtto hi ditergarbhassvārthahetorviśeṣataḥ ||
dharṣitā gautamastrī vai hato vṛtraśca viprajaḥ || 28 ||
viśvarūpadvijāte vaibhāgineyasya yadvaroḥ ||
