iti śrīśiva mahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ caturthe kumārakhaṃḍe tārakāsuravadhadevotsavavarṇanaṃ nāma daśamo'dhyāyaḥ || 10 || ||
brahmovāca ||
etasminnaṃtare tatra krauṃcanāmāṃcalo sune ||
ājagāma kumārasya śaraṇaṃ bāṇapīḍitaḥ || 1 ||
palāyamāno yo yuddhādasoḍhā teja aiśvaram ||
tutodātīva sa kau koṭyāyutabalānvitaḥ || 2 ||
pratipatya kumārasya sa bhaktyā caraṇāmbujam ||
premanirbharayā vācā tuṣṭāva guhamādarāt || 3 || ||
krauca uvāca ||
kumāra skaṃda deveśa tārakāsuranāśaka ||
pāhi māṃ śaraṇāpannaṃ bāṇāsuranipīḍitam ||4||
saṃgarāte mahāsena samucchinnaḥ palāyitaḥ ||
nyapīḍayacca māga tya hā nātha karuṇākara || 5 ||
tatpīḍitaste śaraṇamāgato'haṃ suduḥkhitaḥ ||
palāyamāno deveśa śarajanmandayāṃ kuru || 6 ||
daityaṃ taṃ nāśaya vibho bāṇāhvaṃ māṃ sukhīkuru ||
daityannastvaṃ viśeṣeṇa devāvanakarassvarāṭ || 7 || ||
brahmovāca ||
iti krauṃcastutasskandaḥ prasanno bhaktapālakaḥ ||
gṛhītvā śaktimatulāṃ svāṃ sasmāra śivo dhiyā || 8 ||
cikṣepa tāṃ samuddiśya sa bāṇaṃ śaṃkarātmajaḥ ||
mahāśabdo vabhūvātha jajvaluśca diśo nabhaḥ || 9 ||
sabalaṃ bhasmasātkṛtvāsuraṃ taṃ kṣaṇamātrataḥ ||
guhopakaṃṭhaṃ śaktissājagāma paramā sune || 10 ||
tataḥ kumāraḥ provāca krauṃcaṃ girivaraṃ prabhuḥ ||
nirbhaya ssvagṛhaṃ gaccha naṣṭassa sabalo'suraḥ || 11 ||
tacchrutvā svāmivacanaṃ mudito girirīṃdra tadā ||
stutvā guhaṃ tadārātiṃ svadhāma pratyapadyata || 12 ||
tataḥ skando maheśasya mudā sthāpitavānsune ||
trīṇi liṃgāni tatraiva pāpaghnāni vidhānataḥ || 13||
pratijñeśvaranāmādau kapāleśvaramādarāt ||
kumāreśvarame vātha sarvasiddhipradaṃ trayam ||14||
punassarveśvarastatra jayastaṃbhasamīpataḥ||
staṃbheśvarābhidhaṃ liṃgaṃ guhaḥ sthāpitavānmudā || 15 ||
tatassarve surāstatra viṣṇu prabhūta yo mudā |
liṃgaṃ sthāpitavaṃtaste devadevasya śūlinaḥ || 16||
sarveṣāṃ śivaliṃgānī mahimābhūttadādbhutaḥ ||
sarvakāmapradaścāpi muktido bhaktikāriṇām || 17||
tatassarve surā viṣṇupramukhāḥ prītamānasāḥ ||
aichangirivaraṃ gaṃtuṃ puraskṛtya guruṃ mudā || 18 ||
tasminnavasare śeṣaputraḥ kumudanāmakaḥ ||
ājagāma kumā rasya śaraṇaṃ daityapīḍitaḥ || 19 ||
pralaṃbākhyo'suro yo hi raṇādasmātpalāyitaḥ ||
sa tatropadravaṃ cakre prabalastārakāṃnugaḥ || 20 ||
so'tha śeṣasya tanayaḥ kumudo'hi yatermahān ||
kumāraśaraṇaṃ prāptastuṣṭāva girijātmajam || 21 || ||
kumadaṃ uvāca ||
devadeva mahādevavaratāta mahāprabho ||
