tapasvināṃ mahābhāgaḥ phalado hi bhaviṣyati || 11 ||
devā ūcuḥ ||
evaṃ datvā varānhatvā tārakaṃ cāsurādhipam ||
tvayā kṛtāśca sukhino vayaṃ sarve carācarāḥ || 12 ||
idānīṃ khalu suprītyā kailāsaṃ giriśālayam ||
jananījanako draṣṭuṃ śivāśaṃbhū tvamarhasi || 13||
brahmovāca ||
ityuktvā nikhilā devā viṣṇvādyāḥ prāptaśāsanāḥ ||
kṛtvā mahotsavaṃ bhūri sakumārā yayurgirim || 14 ||
kumāre gacchati vibhau kailāsaṃ śaṃkarālayam ||
mahāmaṃgalasu ttasthau jayaśabdo vabhūva ha || 15 ||
āruroha kumāro'sau vimānaṃ paramarddhimat ||
sarvato'laṃkṛtaṃ ramyaṃ sarvopari virājitam || 16 ||
ahaṃ viṣṇuśva samudau tadā cāmaradhāriṇau ||
gurumūrdhni mahāprītyā sune'bhūva taṃdritau || 17 ||
indrādyā amarāssarve kurvato guhasevanam ||
yathocitaṃ caturdikṣu jagmuśca pramudāstadā || 18 ||
śaṃbhorjayaṃ prabhāṣataḥ prāpuste śaṃbhuparvatam ||
sānaṃdāḥ viviśustatroccarito maṃgaladhvaniḥ || 19 ||
dṛṣṭvā śivaṃ śivāṃ caiva sarve viṣṇvādayo drutam ||
praṇamyaṃ śaṃkaraṃ bhaktyā karau baddhavinamrakāḥ || 20 ||
kumāro'pi vinītātmā vimānādavatīrya ca ||
praṇanāma mudā śaṃbhuṃ śivāṃ siṃhāsanasthitām || 21 ||
atha dṛṣṭvā kumāraṃ taṃ tanayaṃ prāṇavallabham ||
tau daṃpatī śivau devau mumudāte'ti nārada || 22 ||
mahāprabhussamutthāpya tamutsaṃge nyaveśayet ||
mūrdhni jatrau khudā snehāttaṃ pasparśa kareṇa ha || 23 ||
mahānaṃdabharaḥ śaṃbhuścakāra mukhacuṃbanam ||
kumāra sya mahāsnehāt tārakārermahāprabhoḥ || 24 ||
śivāpi taṃ samutthāpya svotsaṃge saṃnyaveśayat ||
kṛttvā mardhni mahāsnehāt tanmukhābjaṃ cucumba hi || || 25 ||
tayostadā mahāmodo vavṛdhetīva nārada ||
