. bhinattu nagarāṇi naḥ ||
nirvairaḥ kṛttivāsāstu yosmākamiti nityaśaḥ || 52 ||
vaidyaḥ pūjyobhivādyaśca sosmākaṃ nirdahetkatham ||
iti cetāsa saṃghāya tādṛśo bhuvi durlabhaḥ || 53 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
etacchrutvā vacasteṣāṃ brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ ||
evamastīti tān prāha sṛṣṭikarttā smaraśivam || 54 ||
ājñāṃ dadau mayasyāpi kuru tvaṃ nagaratrayam ||
kāṃcanaṃ rājataṃ caiva āyasaṃ ceti bho maṃya || 55 ||
ityādiśya mayaṃ brahmā pratyakṣaṃ prāviśaddivam ||
teṣāṃ nārakaputrāṇāṃ paśyatāṃ nijadhāma hi || 56 ||
tato mayaśca tapasā cakre dhīraḥ purāpyatha ||
kāṃcanaṃ tārakākṣasya kamalākṣasya rājatam || 57 ||
vidyunmālyāyasaṃ caiva trividhaṃ durgamuttamam ||
svagrge vyomni ca bhūmau ca kramājjñeyāni tāni vai || 58 ||
datvā tebhyo surebhyaśca purāṇi trīṇi vai mayaḥ ||
praviveśa svayaṃ tatra hitakāmaparāyaṇaḥ || 59 ||
evaṃ putratrayaṃ prāpya praviṣṭāstārakātmajāḥ ||
bubhujussakalānbhogān mahābalaparākramāḥ || 60 ||
kalpadrumaiśca saṃkīrṇaṃ gajavājisamākulam ||
nānāprā sādasaṃkīrṇa maṇijālasamāvṛtam || 61 ||
sūrya maṇḍalasaṃkāśairvimānaissarvatomukhaiḥ ||
padmarāgamayaiścaiva śobhitaṃ candrasannibhaiḥ || 62 ||
prāsādaigopure rdivyaiḥ kailāsaśikharopamaiḥ ||
divya strījana saṃkīrṇaigadharvaissiddhacāraṇaiḥ || 63 ||
rudrālayaiḥ pratigṛhamagnihotraiḥ pratiṣṭhitaiḥ ||
dvijottamaiśśāstravijñaiśśi vabhaktirataissadā || 64 ||
vāpīkūpataḍāgeśca dīrghikābhissuśobhitam ||
udyānavana vṛkṣaiśca svargacyuta guṇottamaiḥ || 65 ||
nadīnadasarinmukhyapuṣkaraiḥ śobhitaṃ sadā ||
sarvakāmaphalādyaiśvānekairvṛkṣairmanoharam || 66||
mattamātaṃgayūthaiśca turaṃgeśca suśobhanaiḥ ||
rathaiśca vividhākāraiśśibikābhiralaṃkṛtam || 67 ||
samayādiśikaiścaiva krīḍāsthānaiḥ pṛthakpṛthak ||
vedādhyayanaśālābhirvividhābhiḥ pṛthakpṛthak || 68 ||
adṛṣṭaṃ manasā vācā pāpānvitanarai ssadā ||
mahātmabhiśśubhācāraiḥ puṇyavadbhiḥ pravakṣyate || 69 ||
pativratābhiḥ sarvatra pāvitaḥ sthalamuttamam ||
patisevanaśīlābhirvimukhābhiḥ kudharmataḥ || 70 ||
daityaśūrairmahābhāgerasadāressa sutairdvijaiḥ ||
śrautasmārtārthatattvajñaissvadharmaniratairyutam || 71 ||
vyūḍhoraskai vṛṣaskaṃdhaissāmayuddhadharaissadā ||
praśāṃtaiḥ kupitaiścaiva kubjairvāmanakaistathā || 72 ||
nīlotpaladalaprakhyairnīla kuṃcitamūrddhajaiḥ ||
mayena rakṣitessa vaiśikṣitairyuddhalālasaiḥ ||73||
varasamarara taissamaṃtā dajaśivapūjanayā viśuddhavīryaiḥ ||
ravimarutamahendrasaṃnikāśaissuramarthanaismudṛḍhaissusevitaṃ yat || 74 ||
śāstravedapurāṇeṣu yeye dharmāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||
śivapriyāssadā daivāste dharmāstatra sarvataḥ || 75 ||
evaṃ labdhavarāste tu daiteyāstārakātmajāḥ ||
śaivaṃ mayamupāśritya nivasaṃti sma tatra ha || 76 ||
sarva trailokyamutsārya praviśya nagarāṇi te ||
kuvaiti sma mahadrājyaṃ śivamārgaratāssadā || 77 ||
tato mahāna gataḥ kālo vasatāṃ puṇyakarmaṇām ||
