bhītebhyaścābhayaṃ deyaṃ vyādhitebhyastathaiauṣadham ||
deyā vidyārthināṃ vidyā deyamannaṃ kṣudhāture ||23||
yāni yānīha dānānī vahu sunyuditāni ca ||
jīvābhayapradānasya kalāṃ nārhati ṣoḍaśīm || 24 ||
avicitya prabhāvaṃ hi maṇimaṃtrauṣadhaṃ balam ||
tadabhyasyaṃ prayatnena nāmārthopārjanāya vai || 25 ||
arthānupāye bahuśo vai dvādaśāyatanāni vai ||
paritaḥ paripūjyāni kimanyairiha pūjitaiḥ || 26 ||
paṃcakarmendriyagrāmaḥ paṃca buddhīṃdriyāṇi ca ||
mano buddhiriha proktaṃ dvādaśāyatanaṃ śubham || 27 ||
ihaiva svarganarako prāṇināṃ nānyataḥ kvacit ||
sukhaṃ svargaḥ samākhyāto duḥkhaṃ narakameva hi || 28 ||
sukheṣu bhujyamāneṣu yatsyāddehavisarjanam |
ayameva paro mokṣo vijñeyastatvacitakaiḥ || 29 ||
vāsanāsahite kkeśasamucchede sati dhruvam ||
ajñāno paramo mokṣo vijñeyastattvaciṃtakaiḥ || 30 ||
prāmāṇikī śrutiriyaṃ procyate vedavādibhiḥ ||
na hiṃsyātsarvabhūtāni nānyā hiṃsā pravartikā || || 31 ||
agnīṣṭomīyamiti yā bhrāmikā sā'satāmiha ||
na sā pramāṇaṃ jñātṝṇāṃ paśvālaṃbhanakārikā || 32 ||
vṛkṣāṃśchitvā paśūnhatvā kṛtvā rudhirakarddamam ||
dagdhvā vahnau tilājyādi citraṃ svargo'bhilaṣyate || 33 ||
ityevaṃ svamataṃ procya yatistripuranāyakam ||
śrāvayitvā khilān paurānuvāca punarādarāt || 34 ||
dṛṣṭārthapratyayakarāndehasaukhyaikasādhakān ||
bauddhāgamavinirdiṣṭāndharmānvedaparāstataḥ || 35 ||
ānaṃda brahmaṇo rūpaṃ śrutyaivaṃ yannigadyate ||
tattathaiveha maṃtavyaṃ mithyā nānātvakalpanā || 36 ||
yāvatsvasthamidaṃ varṣma yāvannendriyaviklavaḥ ||
yāvajjarā ca dūre'sti tāvatsaukhyaṃ prasādhayet || 37 ||
asvāsthyendriyavaikalye vārddhakye tu kutassukham ||
śarīramapi dātavyamarthibhyo'tassukhepsubhiḥ || || 38 ||
yācamānamanovṛttiprīṇane yasya no janiḥ|
tena bhūbhīravatyeṣā samudrāgadrumairna hi || 39||
satvaraṃ gatvāro dehaḥ saṃcayāssaṃparityayāḥ ||
iti vijñāya vijñātā dehasaukhyaṃ prasādhayet || 40 ||
śvavāyasakṛmīṇāṃ ca prātarbhojyamidaṃ vapuḥ ||
bhasmāṃtaṃ taccharīraṃ ca vede satyaṃ prapaṭhyate || || 41 ||
sudhā jātivikalpoyaṃ lokeṣu parikalpyate ||
mānuṣye sati sāmānye ko'dharmaḥ ko'tha cottamaḥ || 42 ||
brahmādisṛṣṭireṣeti procyate vṛddhapuruṣaiḥ ||
tasya jātau sutau dakṣamarīcī ceti viśrutau || 43 ||
mārīcena kaśyapena dakṣakanyāssulocanāḥ ||
