surān vijñāya vikalān hanyatāṃ tripu rāṇi ca || 33 ||
rakṣāsmānparameśāna dīnabaṃdho kṛpākara ||
svayaiva rakṣitā devāssadāpadbhyo muhurmuhuḥ || 34 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktaṃ vacanaṃ teṣāṃ śrutvā saṃharivedhasām ||
vihasyāṃtastadā brahmanmaheśaḥ punarabravīt || 33 || ||
madeśa uvāca ||
he hare he vidhe devā munayaścākhilā vacaḥ ||
madīyaṃ śṛṇutādṛtya naṣṭaṃ matvā puratrayam || 36 ||
rathaṃ ca sārathiṃ divyaṃ kārmukaṃ śaramuttamam ||
pūrvamaṃgīkṛtaṃ sarvamupapādayatāciram || 37 ||
he viṣṇo he vidhe tvaṃ hi trilokādhipatirdhruvam ||
sarvasamrāṭ prakāraṃ me kartumarhasi yatnataḥ || 38 ||
naṣṭaṃ puratrayaṃ matvā devasāhāyyamityuta ||
kariṣyathaḥ prayatnenādhikṛtau sargapālane || 39 ||
ayaṃ maṃtro mahāpuṇyo matprītijanakaśśubhaḥ ||
bhuktimuktipradassarvakāmadaśśaivakīvahaḥ || 40 ||
dhanyo yaśasya āyuṣyaḥ svargakāmārthināṃ nṛṇām ||
apavargoṃ hyakāmānāṃ muktānāṃ bhuktimuktidaḥ || 41 ||
ya imaṃ kīrtayenmaṃtraṃ śucirbhūtvā sadā naraḥ ||
śṛṇuyācchrā vayedvāpi sarvānkāmānavāpnuyāt || 42 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacastasya śivasya paramātmanaḥ ||
sarve devā khudaṃ prāpuharirbrahmādhika tathā || 43 ||
sarvadevamayaṃ divyaṃ rathaṃ paramaśobhanam ||
racayāmāsa viśvāthai viśvakarmā tadājñayā || 44 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃ hitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe devastutivarṇanaṃ nāma saptamo'dhyāyaḥ || 7 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
sanatkumāra sarvajña śaivaśvara sanmate ||
adbhuteyaṃ kathā - tāta śrāvitā parimeśituḥ || 1||
idānīṃ rathanirmāṇaṃ brūhi devamayaṃ param ||
śivārthaṃ yatkṛtaṃ divyaṃ dhīmatā viśvakarmaṇā ||2||
sūta uvāca ||
ityākarṇya vacasta sya vyāsasya sa munīśvaraḥ ||
sanatkumāraḥ provāca smṛtvā śivapadāṃbujam || 3 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca || ||
śṛṇu vyāsa mahāprājña rathādenirmiti mune ||
yathāmati pravakṣye'haṃ smṛtvā śivapadāmbujam || 4 ||
atha devasya rudrasya nirmito viśvakarmaṇā ||
