iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe rathādiyuddhaprakāravarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭamo'dhyāyaḥ || 8 || ||
