īdṛgvidhaṃ mahādivyaṃ nānāścaryamayaṃ ratham ||
saṃnahya nigamānaśvāṃstaṃ brahmā prārpayacchitram || 1 ||
śaṃbhave'sau nivedyādhiropayāmāsa śūlinam ||
bahuśaḥ prārthya deveśaṃ viṣṇvā disurasaṃmatam || 2 ||
tatastasminrathe divye rathaprākārasaṃyute ||
sarvadevamayaḥ śaṃbhurāruroha mahāprabhuḥ || 3 ||
ṛṣibhiḥ stūyamānaśca devagaṃdharva pannagaiḥ ||
viṣṇunā brahmaṇā cāpi lokapālairbabhūva ha ||4||
upāvṛtaścāpsarasāṃ gaṇairgītaviśāradaiḥ |
śuśubhe varadaśśumbhussa taṃ prekṣya ca sārathim ||5||
tasminnāro hati rathaṃ kalpitaṃ. lokasaṃbhṛtam ||
śirobhiḥ patitā bhūmau turaṃgā vedasaṃbhavāḥ || 6 ||
cacāla vasudhā celussakalāśca mahīdharāḥ ||
cakaṃpe sahasā śeṣo'soḍhā tadbhāramāturaḥ || 7 ||
athādhaḥ sa rathasyāsya bhagavāndharaṇīdharaḥ ||
vṛṣendrarūpī cotthāya sthāpayāmāsa vai kṣaṇam || 8 ||
kṣaṇāṃtare vṛṣe ndro'pi jānubhyāmagamaddharām ||
rathārūḍhamaheśasya sutejassoḍhumakṣamaḥ || 9 ||
abhīṣuhasto bhagavānudyamya ca hayāṃstadā |
sthāpayāmāsa devasya vaca nādvai rathaṃ varam || 10 ||
tato'sau nodayāmāsa manomārutaraṃhasaḥ ||
brahmā hayānvedamayānnaddhānrathavaraitaḥ || 11 ||
purāṇyudiśya vai trīṇi teṣāṃ kha sthāni tāni hi ||
adhiṣṭhite maheśe tu dānavānāṃ tarasvinām || 12 ||
athāha bhagavānnudro devānālokya śaṃkaraḥ ||
paśūnāmādhipatyaṃ me dhaddhaṃ hanmi tato'surān || 13 ||
pṛthak paśutvaṃ devānāṃ tathānyeṣāṃ surottamāḥ ||
kalpayitvaiva vadhyāste nānyathā daityasattamāḥ || 14 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacastasya devadevasya dhīmataḥ|
viṣādamagamansavai paśutvaṃ pratiśaṃkitāḥ || 15 ||
teṣāṃ bhāvamatha jñātvā devadevo'mbikāpatiḥ ||
vihasya. kṛpayā devācchaṃstānidamabravīt || 16 || ||
śaṃbhuruvāca ||
mā vo'stu paśubhāve'pi pāto vibudhasaṃttamāḥ ||
