naiṣṭhikaṃ dvādaśābdaṃ vā tadarddha varṣakatrayam ||
śuśrūṣāṃ kārayedyastu sa paśu svādvimucyate || 20 ||
tasmātparamidaṃ divyaṃ cariṣyatha surottamāḥ ||
