tiścaiva paśupāśavimocakaḥ || 23 ||
tadā paśupatītyetattasya nāma maheśituḥ ||
prasiddhamabhavadradhvā sarvalokeṣu śarmadam || 24 ||
sudā jayeti bhāṣeta ssarve devarṣayastadā ||
amudaṃścāti deveśo brahmā viṣṇuḥ pare'pi ca || 25 ||
tasmiṃśca samaye yacca rūpaṃ tasya mahātmanaḥ ||
jātaṃ tadvarṇituṃ śakyaṃ na hi varṣaśatairapi || 26 ||
evaṃvidho maheśāno maheśānyakhileśvaraḥ |
jagāma tripuraṃ hetuṃ sarveṣāṃ sukhadāyakaḥ || 27 ||
taṃ devadevaṃ tripuraṃ nirhatuṃ tadā nu sarve tu raviprakāśāḥ ||
gajairhayaissiṃhavarai rathaiśca vṛṣairyayuste'mararājamukhyāḥ || 28 ||
halaiśca śāḻemuśalabhuśuḍagarīndrakalpaigirisaṃnibhāśca ||
nānāyu dhaissaṃyutabāhavaste tato nu hṛṣṭāḥ prayayussureśāḥ || 29 ||
nānāyudhāḍhyāḥ paramaprakāśāḥ mahotsavāśśaṃbhujayaṃ vadataḥ ||
yayuḥ purastasya maheśva rasya tadendrapadmodbhavaviṣṇumukhyāḥ || 30 ||
jahaṣurmunayassarve daṃḍahastā jaṭādharāḥ ||
vavṛtuḥ puṣpavarṣāṇi khecarāssiddhacāraṇāḥ || 31 ||
putratrayaṃ viprendrā vrajansarve gaṇeśvarāḥ ||
