gaṇeśvarairdevagaṇaiśca bhṛṃgī samāvṛtassarvagaṇendravaryaḥ ||
jagāma yogāṃstripuraṃ nihaṃtuṃ vimānamāruhya yathā mahendraḥ || 33 ||
keśo vigatavāsaśca mahākeśo mahājvaraḥ ||
somavallīsavarṇaśca somapassanakastathā || || 34 ||
somadhṛk sūryavarcāśca sūryapreṣaṇakastathā ||
sūryākṣassūrināmā ca surasundara eva ca || 35 ||
praskaṃdaḥ kundaracaṃḍaḥ kaṃpanaścātikaṃpanaḥ ||
indravendra jayaścaiva yaṃtā himakarastathā || 36 ||
śatākṣaścaiva paṃcākṣaḥ sahasrākṣo mahodaraḥ ||
satījahuśśatāsyaśca raṃkaḥ karpūrapūtanaḥ || 37 ||
dviśikha striśikhaścaiva tathāhaṃkārakārakaḥ ||
ajavattro'ṣṭavatkraśca hayavakro'rddhavacakaḥ || 38||
ityādyā gaṇapā vīrā bahavo'parimeyakāḥ|
prayayuḥ parivāyaiśa lakṣya lakṣaṇavarjittāḥ || 39 ||
samāvṛtya mahādevaṃ tadāpuste pinākinam ||
dagdhuṃ samarthā manasā kṣaṇena sacarācaram || 40 ||
dagdhuṃ jagatsarvamidaṃ samarthāḥ kiṃtvaṃca dagdhuṃ tripuraṃ pinākī ||
rathena kiṃ cātra śareṇa tasya gaṇaiśca kiṃ devagaṇaiśca śaṃbhoḥ || 41 ||
sa eva dagdhuṃ tripurāṇi tāni devadviṣāṃ vyāsa pinākapāṇiḥ ||
svayaṃ gatastatra gaṇaiśca sārddhaṃ nijaissurāṇāmapi so'dbhutotiḥ || 42 ||
kiṃ tatra kāraṇaṃ cānyadvacmi te ṛṣisattama |
lokeṣu khyāpa nārthe vai yaśaḥ paramalāpaham || 43 ||
anyacca kāraṇaṃ hyetaduṣṭānāṃ pratyayāya vai ||
sarveṣvapi ca deveṣu yasmānnānyo viśiṣyate || 44 ||
iti śrī śivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe śivayātrāvarṇanaṃ nāma navamo'dhyāyaḥ || 9 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
atha śaṃbhumahādevo rathasthassarvasaṃyutaḥ ||
tripuraṃ sakalaṃ dagdhumudyato'bhūtsuradviṣām || 1||
śīrṣa sthānakamāsthāya saṃdhāya ca śarottamam ||
sannaṃ tatkārmukaṃ kṛtvā pratyālīḍhaṃ mahādbhutam || 2 ||
niveśya dṛḍhamuṣṭau ca dṛṣṭiṃ dṛṣṭau niveśya ca ||
atiṣṭaniścalastatra śataṃ varṣasahasrakam ||3||
tatoḍuṣṭhe gaṇādhyakṣassa tudatyaniśaṃ sthitaḥ||
