arddhadagdhā vibuddhāśca babhramumahamūcchitāḥ ||
tena nāsītsusūkṣmo'pi ghoratripuravahninā ||38||
avidagdho vinirmuktaḥ sthāvaro jaṃgamopi vā ||
varjayitvā mayaṃ daityaṃ viśvakarmāṇamavyayam|| 39 ||
aviruddhaṃ tu devānāṃ rakṣitaṃ śaṃbhutejasā ||
vipatkā lepi sadbhakta maheśaśaraṇāgatam || 40 ||
sannipāto hi yeṣāṃ no vidyate nāśakārakaḥ ||
daityānāmanyasattvānāṃ bhāvābhāve kṛtākṛte ||41||
tasmādyatna ssusaṃbhāvyaḥ sadbhiḥ kartavya eva hi ||
garhaṇātkṣīyate loko na tatkarma samācaret || 42 || ||
na saṃyogo yathā teṣāṃ bhūyātripuravāsinām ||
matametaddhi sarveṣāṃ daivādyadi yato bhavet || 43 ||
ye pūjayaṃtastatrāpi daityā rudraṃ sabāṃdhavāḥ||
gāṇapatyaṃ yayussarve śivapūjāvidherbalāt || 44 ||
iti śrīśivamahā purāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe tripuradāhavarṇanaṃ nāma daśamo'dhyāyaḥ || 10 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
brahmaputra mahāprājña dhanyastvaṃ śaiva sattama ||
kimakārṣustato devā dagdhe ca tripure'khilāḥ || 1||
mayaḥ kutra gato dagdho patayaḥ kutra te gatāḥ ||
tatsarvaṃ me samācakṣva yadi śaṃbhukathāśrayam || || 2 ||
sūta uvāca || ||
ityākarṇya vyāsavākyaṃ bhagavānbhavakṛtsutaḥ ||
sanatkumāraḥ provāca śivapādayugaṃ smaran || 3 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca || ||
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe pārāśarya mahośituḥ ||
caritaṃ sarvapāpannaṃ lokalīlānusāriṇaḥ || 4 ||
maheśvareṇa sarvasmiṃstripure daityasaṃkule ||
dagdhe viśeṣatastatra 'vismitāste'bhavansurāḥ || 5 ||
na kiṃcidanuvandevāḥ sendropeṃdrādayastadā ||
mahātejasvinaṃ rudraṃ sarvaṃ vīkṣya sa saṃbhramāḥ || 6 ||
mahābhayaṃkaraṃ raudraṃ prajva lataṃ diśo daśa ||
koṭisūryapratīkāśaṃ pralayānalasannibham || 7 ||
bhayāddevaṃ nirīkṣyaiva devīṃ ca himavatsutām ||
biyire nikhilā devapramukhāstasthu rānatāḥ || 8 ||
dṛṣṭvānīkaṃ tadā bhītaṃ devānāmṛṣipuṃgavāḥ ||
na kiṃcidūcussaṃtasthuḥ praṇemuste samaṃtataḥ || 9 ||
atha brahmāpi saṃbhīto dṛṣṭvā rūpaṃ ca śāṃkaram ||
tuṣṭāva tuṣṭahṛdayo devaissaha samāhitaḥ || 10 ||
viṣṇunā ca sabhītena devadevaṃ bhavaṃ haram ||
tripurāriṃ sagirijaṃ bhaktādhīnaṃ maheśvaram ||11||
brahmovāca ||
