bṛhaspatiriti stutvā śaṃkaraṃ lokaśaṃkaram ||
pādayoḥ pātayāmāsa tasyeśasya puraṃdaram || 38 ||
pātayitvā ca deveśamiṃdraṃ nataśirodharam ||
bṛhaspatiruvācedaṃ praśrayāvanataśśivam || 39 || ||
bṛhaspatiruvāca ||
dīnanātha mahā deva praṇataṃ tava pādayoḥ ||
samuddhara ca śāṃtaṃ tvaṃ krodhaṃ nayanajaṃ kuru ||40||
tuṣṭo bhava mahādeva pāhīṃdraṃ śaraṇāgatam ||
agnireṣa śamaṃ yātu bhālanetrasamudbhavaḥ || ||41||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityākarṇya gurorvākyaṃ devadevo maheśvaraḥ|
uvāca karuṇāsindhurmeghanirhrādayā girā || 42||
maheśvara uvāca ||
krodhaṃ ca nissṛtaṃ netrā dvāra yāmi bṛhaspateḥ||
kathaṃ hi kañcukīṃ sarpassaṃdhatte nojjhitāṃ punaḥ||43||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacastasya śaṃkarasya bṛhaspatiḥ|
uvāca kliṣṭa rūpaśca bhayavyākulamānasaḥ || 44 ||
bṛhaspatiruvāca ||
deva he bhagavanbhaktā anukaṃpyāḥ sadaiva hi ||
bhaktavatsalanāmeti tvaṃ satyaṃ kuru śaṃkara || 45 ||
kṣenumanyatra deveśa svatejo'tyugramarhasi ||
uddhartassarvabhaktānāṃ samuddhara puraṃdaram || 46 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityukto guruṇā rudro bhaktavatsalanāma bhāk ||
pratyuvāca prasannātmā surejyaṃ praṇatārttihā || 47 ||
śiva uvāca ||
prītaḥ stutyānayā tāta dadāmi varamuttamam ||
indrasya jīvadānena jīveti tvaṃ prathāṃ vraja || 48 ||
samudbhūto'nalo yo'yaṃ bhālanetrātsureśahā ||
enaṃ tyakṣyāmyahaṃ dūre yathendraṃ naiva pīḍayet || 49 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā taṃ kare dhṛtvā : svatejo'nalamadbhutam ||
bhālanetrātsamudbhūtaṃ prākṣipallavaṇāṃbhasi || 50 ||
tataścāṃtardadhe rudro mahālīlākaraḥ prabhuḥ ||
guruśakau bhayānmukto jagmatuḥ sukhamuttamam || 51 ||
yadarthe gamanādyuktau darśanaṃ prāpya tasya vai ||
kṛtārthau guruśakrau hi svasthānaṃ jagmaturmudā || 52 ||
