kalpavṛkṣastvayānīto nidhayo dhanadasya ca ||
haṃsayuktavimānaṃ ca tvayā nītaṃ hi vedhasaḥ || 36 ||
ityevaṃ vararatnāni divi pṛthvyāṃ rasātale ||
yāni daityendra te bhāṃti gṛhe tāni samastataḥ || 37 ||
tvatsamṛddhimimāṃ paśyansampūrṇī vividhāmaham ||
prasanno 'smi mahā vīra gajāśvādisuśobhitām || 38 ||
jāyāratnaṃ mahāśreṣṭhaṃ jalaṃdhara na te gṛhe ||
tadānetuṃ viśeṣeṇa strīratnaṃ vai tvamarhasi || || 39 ||
yasya gehe suratnāni sarvāṇi hi jalaṃdhara ||
jāyāratnaṃ na cettāni na śobhate vṛthā dhruvam || 40 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityevaṃ vacanaṃ śrutvā nāradasya mahātmanaḥ ||
uvāca daityarājo hi madanākulamānasaḥ || 41 ||
jalaṃdhara uvāca ||
bhobho nārada devarṣe namaste stu mahāprabho ||
jāyāratnavaraṃ kutra vartate tadvadādhunā || 42 ||
brahmāṃḍe yatra kutrāpi tadratnaṃ yadi varttate ||
tadāneṣye tato brahmansatyaṃsatyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || || 43 ||
nārada uvāca || ||
kailāse hyatiramye ca sarvaddhiṃsusamākule |
yogirūpadharaśśaṃbhurasti tatra digambaraḥ || 44 ||
tasya bhāryā suramyā sarvalakṣaṇalakṣitā ||
sarvāṃgasundarī nāmnā pāvatīti manoharā ||15||
tadīdṛśaṃ rūpamananyasaṃgataṃ dṛṣṭaṃ na kutrāpi kutūhalāḍhyam |
atyadbhutaṃ mohanakṛtsu yogināṃ sudarśanīyaṃ paramarddhikāri || 46 ||
svacitte kalpayāmyadya śivādanyassamṛddhimān |
jāyāratnānvitādvīra trilokyāṃ na jalaṃdhara || 47 ||
yasyā lāvaṇyajaladhau nimagnaśvaturānanaḥ ||
svadhaiyyai mumuce pūrva tayā kānyopamayite || 48 ||
gatarāgo'pi hi yayā madanārissvalīlayā ||
nijataṃtro'pi hi yatassa svātmavaśagaḥ kṛtaḥ || 49 ||
yathā strīratnasaṃbhoktussamṛddhistasya sābhavat ||
tathā na tava daityendra sarva .

