iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe jalaṃdharavadhopākhyāne devarṣijalaṃdharasaṃvādo nāmāṣṭadaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 18 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
