atho'bhajyataṃ. daityānāṃ senā gaṇabhayārditā ||
vāyuvegahatā yadvatprakīrṇā tṛṇasaṃhatiḥ || 57 ||
bhagnāṃ gaṇabhayāddaitya senāṃ dṛṣṭvātimarṣitāḥ ||
niśuṃbhaśubhau senānyau kālanemiśca cukudhuḥ || 58 ||
trayaste vārayāmāsurgaṇasenāṃ mahābalāḥ ||
mrucaṃtaśśaravarṣāṇi prāvṛṣīva balāhakāḥ || 59 ||
tato daityaśaraughāste śalabhānāmiva vrajāḥ ||
rurudhuḥ khaṃ diśassarvā gaṇasenāmakaṃpayan || 60 ||
gaṇāśśaraśatairbhinnā rudhirāsāravarṣiṇaḥ ||
vasaṃtakiṃśukābhāsā na prājāna nhi kiṃcana || 61 ||
tataḥ prabhagnaṃ svabalaṃ vilokya nandyādilaṃbodarakārttikeyāḥ ||
tvarānvitā daityavarānprasahya nivārayāmāsuramarṣaṇāste || 62 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe jalaṃdharavadhopākhyāne sāmānyagaṇāsurayuddhavarṇanaṃ nāma viṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 20 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
te gaṇādhipatīndṛṣṭvā nandībhasukhaṣaṇmukhān ||
amarṣādabhyadhāvaṃta dvaṃdvayuddhāya dānavāḥ || 1||
nandinaṃ kālanemiśca śuṃbho laṃbodaraṃ tathā ||
niśuṃbhaḥ ṣaṇmukhaṃ devamabhyadhāvata śaṃkitaḥ || 2 ||
niśuṃbhaḥ kārtikeyasya mayūraṃ paṃcabhiśśaraiḥ ||
hṛdi vivyādha vegena mūrcchitassa papāta ha ||3||
tataḥ śaktidharaḥ kruddho bāṇaiḥ paṃcabhireva ca ||
vivyādha syaṃdane tasya hayānyantārameva ca || 4 ||
śareṇānyena tīkṣṇena niśuṃbhaṃ devavairiṇam ||
jaghāna tarasā vīro jagarja raṇadurmadaḥ || 5 ||
asuro'pi niśuṃbhākhyo mahāvīro'tivīryavān ||
jaghāna kārtikeyaṃ taṃ garjataṃ sveṣuṇā raṇe || 6 ||
tataśśaktiṃ kārtikeyo yāvajjagrāha roṣataḥ ||
tāvanniśuṃbho vegena svaśaktyā tamapātayat || 7 ||
evaṃ babhūva tatraiva kārtikeyaniśuṃbhayoḥ ||
āhavo hi mahānvyāsa vīraśabdaṃ pragarjatoḥ||8||
tato nandīśvaro bāṇaiḥ kālanemimavidhyata ||
saptabhiśca hayānketuṃ rathaṃ sārathimāṃcchinat||9||
kālanemiśca saṃkruddho dhanuścicche

--- Page 338 [gcv] ---
da naṃdinaḥ||
svaśarāsanāniyuktairmahātīkṣṇaiśśilīmukhaiḥ ||10||
atha nandīśvaro vīraḥ kālanemiṃ mahāsuram||
tamapāsya ca śūlena vakṣasyabhyahanaṃdṛḍham ||11||
sa śūla bhinnahṛdayo hatāśvo hatasārathiḥ|
adreḥ śikharamutpāṭya nandinaṃ samatāḍayat || 12||
atha śuṃbho gaṇeśaśca rathamūṣakavāhanau ||
yudhyamānau śaratrātaiḥ parasparamavidhyatām || 13 ||
gaṇeśastu tadā śubhaṃ hṛdi vivyādha patriṇā ||
sārathiṃ ca tribhirbāṇaiḥ pātayāmāsa bhūtale || 14 ||
tato'tikruddha śśuṃbho'pi bāṇavṛṣṭayā gaṇādhipam ||
mūṣakaṃ ca tribhirviddhā nanāda jaladasvanaḥ || 15 ||
mūṣakaśśarabhinnāṅgaśvacāla dṛḍhavedanaḥ ||
lambodaraśca patitaḥ padātirabhavatsa hi || 16 ||
tato lambodaraśśuṃbhaṃ hatvā paraśunā hṛdi ||
apātayattadā bhūmau mūṣakaṃ cāruroha saḥ || 17 ||
samarāyodyataścā bhūtpunargajamukho vibhuḥ ||
prahasya |
jaghnatuḥ krodhāttotreṇaiva mahādvipam || 18 ||
kālanemirniśuṃbhaśva śubhau laṃbodaraṃ śaraiḥ ||
yugapañcakhnatuḥ krodhādāśī viṣasamairddhatam || 19 ||
taṃ pīḍyamānamālokya vīrabhadro mahābalaḥ ||
abhyadhāvata vegena koṭibhūtayutastathā || 20 ||
kūṣmāṃḍā bhairavāścāpi vetālā yoginīgaṇāḥ ||
piśācā ḍākinīsaṃghā gaṇāścāpi samaṃ yayuḥ || 21 ||
tataḥ kilakilāśabdassiṃhanādaissaghargharaiḥ ||
vināditā ḍamarukaiḥ pṛthivī samakaṃpata || 22 ||
tato bhūtāḥ pradhāvato bhakṣayati sma dānavān ||
utpatya pātayaṃti sma nanṛtuśca raṇāṃgaṇe || 23 ||
etasminnatare vyāsābhūtāṃ nandī guhaśca tau ||
utthitāvāptasaṃjñau hi jagarjaturalaṃ raṇe ||24||
sa nandī kārtikeyaśca samāyātau tvarānvitau ||
jannatuśca raṇe daityā niraṃtara śaravrajaiḥ || 25 ||
chinnabhinnahatairdaityaiḥ pātitairbhakṣitaistathā ||
vyākulā sābhavatsenā viṣaṇṇavadanā tadā || 26 ||
evaṃ nandī kārtikeyo vikaṭaśca pratāpavān ||
vīrabhadro gaṇāścānye jagarjussamare'dhikam || 27 ||
niśuṃbhaśuṃbhau senānyau sindhuputrasya tau tathā ||
kālane mirmahādaityo'surāścānye parājitāḥ || 28 ||
pravidhvastāṃ tatassenāṃ dṛṣṭvā sāgaranandanaḥ ||
rathenātipatākena gaṇānabhiyayau balī || 29 ||
tataḥ parājitā daityā apyabhūvanmahotsavāḥ ||
jagarjuradhikaṃ vyāsa samarāyodyatāstadā || 30 ||
sarve rudragaṇāścāpi jagarjurjayaśālinaḥ ||
nandi kārtikadatyāsya vīrabhadrādikā mune || 31 ||
hastyaśvarathasaṃhrādaśśaṃkha bherīravastathā ||
abhavatsiṃhanādaśva senayorubhayostathā || 32 ||
jalaṃdharaśaratrāta nahārapaṭalairiva ||
dyāvāpṛthivyorācchannamaṃtaraṃ samapadyata || 33 ||
śailādi paṃcabhirviddhā gaṇeśa paṃcabhiśśaraiḥ ||
