śi0 pu0 ||198||
vīrabhadraṃ ca viṃśatyā nanāda jaladasvanaḥ || 34 ||
kārtikeyastato daityaṃ śaktyā vivyādha satvaram ||
jalaṃdharaṃ mahāvīro rudraputrā nanāda ca || 35 ||
sa ghūrṇanayano daityaśaktinirbhinnadehakaḥ ||
papāta bhūmau tvaritamudatiṣṭhanmahābalaḥ || 36 ||
tataḥ krodhaparītātmā kārtikeyaṃ jalaṃdharaḥ ||
gadayā tāḍayāmāsa hṛdaye daityapuṃgavaḥ || 37 ||
gadāprabhāvaṃ saphalaṃ darśayanśaṃkarātmajaḥ ||
vidhidattavarādvyāsa sa . tūrṇa bhūtale'patat || || 38 ||
tathaiva naṃdī hyapatadbhūtale gadayā hṛtaḥ ||
mahāvīro'pi ripuhā kiṃcidvayākulamānasaḥ || 39 ||
tato gaṇeśvaraḥ kruddhassmṛtvā śivapadāmbu jam ||
saṃprāpyātibalo daityagardā paraśunācchinat ||40||
vīrabhadrastribhirbāṇairhṛdi vivyādha dānavam ||
saptabhiśva hayānketuṃ dhanuśchatraṃ ca cicchide || || 41 ||
tato'tikruddho daityendraśśaktimudyamya dāruṇām ||
gaṇeśaṃ pātayāmāsa rathamanyaṃ samāruhat || 42 ||
abhyagādatha vegena sa daityendro mahābalaḥ ||
vigaṇayya hṛdā taṃ vai vīrabhadraṃ ruṣānvitaḥ || 43 ||
vīrabhadraṃ jaghānāśu tīkṣṇenāśīviṣeṇa tam ||
nanāda ca mahāvīro daityarājo jalaṃ gharaḥ || 44 ||
vīrabhadro'pi saṃkruddhassitadhāreṇa ceṣuṇā ||
ciccheda taccharaṃ caiva taṃ vivyādha maheṣuṇā || 45 ||
tatastau sūryasaṃkāśau yuyudhāte parasparam ||
nānāśastraistathāstraiśca ciraṃ vīravarottamau || 46 ||
vīrabhadrastatastasya hayānbāṇairapātayat ||
dhanuściccheda rathinaḥ patākāṃ cāpi vegataḥ || 47 ||
atha sa daityarājo hi pupluve parighāyudhaḥ ||
vīrabhadropakaṃṭhaṃ sa drutamāpa mahābalaḥ || 48 ||
parighenātimahatā vīrabhadraṃ jaghāna haṃ ||
mahābalosbdhitanayo mūrdhni vīro jagarja ca || 49 ||
parighenātimahatā bhinnamūrddhā gaṇādhipaḥ ||
vīrabhadraḥ papātoya mumoca rudhiraṃ bahu || 50 ||
patitaṃ vīrabhadraṃ tu dṛṣṭvā rudragaṇā bhayāt ||
āpāgacchatraṇaṃ hitvā krośamānā maheśvaram || 51 ||
atha kolāhalaṃ śrutvā gaṇānāṃ candraśekharaḥ ||
nija : pārśvasthitān vīrānapṛcchadguṇasattamān || 52 || ||
śaṃkara uvāca ||
kimarthaṃ madguṇānāṃ hi mahākolāhalo'bhavat ||
vicāryatāṃ mahāvīrāśśāṃtiḥ kāryā mayā dhruvam || 53 ||
iti yāvatsa deveśo gaṇānpapraccha sādaram ||
tāvadguṇavarāste hi samāyātāḥ prabhuṃprati || 54 ||
tāndṛṣṭvā vikalānnudraḥ papracchaṃ kuśalaṃ prabhuḥ ||
yathāvatte gaṇā vṛttaṃ samācakhyuśca vistarāt || 55 ||
