--- Page 340 [gcv] ---
tacchrutvā bhagavānnrudro mahālīlākaraḥ prabhuḥ ||
abhayaṃ dattavāṃstebhyo mahotsāhaṃ pravarddhayan || 56 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcamai yuddhakhaṃḍe jalaṃdharopākhyāne viśeṣayuddhavarṇanaṃ nāmaikaviṃśatitamo'dhyāyaḥ || 21 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
atha vīragaṇai rudro raudrarūpo mahāprabhuḥ ||
abhyagādṛṣamārūḍhassaṃgrāmaṃ prahasanniva || 1 ||
rudramāyāṃtamālokya siṃhanādairgaṇāḥ punaḥ ||
nivṛttāssaṃgareḥ raudrā ye hi pūrva parājitāḥ || 2||
vīraśabdaṃ ca kurvantaste'pyanye śāṃkarā gaṇāḥ ||
sotsavāssāyudhā daityānnijaghnuśśaravṛṣṭibhiḥ || 3 ||
daityā hi bhīṣaṇaṃ rudraṃ sarve dṛṣṭvā vidudruvuḥ ||
śāṃkaraṃ puruṣaṃ dṛṣṭvā pātakānīva tadbhayāt || 4 ||
atho jalaṃdharo daityānnivṛttānprekṣya saṃgare ||
abhyadhāvatsa caṃḍīśaṃ muṃcanbāṇānsahasraśaḥ || 5 ||
niśuṃbhaśuṃbhapramukhā daityendrāśca sahasraśaḥ ||
abhijagmuśśivaṃ vegādroṣātsaṃdaṣṭadacchadāḥ || 6 ||
kālanemistathā vīraḥ khaḍgaromā balāhakaḥ ||
ghasmaraśca pracaṃḍaścāpare cāpi śivaṃ yayuḥ || 7 ||
bāṇaissaṃchādayāmāsurddhataṃ rudragaṇāṃśca te ||
aṃgāni cicchidurvīrāśśuṃbhādyā nikhilā mune || 8 ||
bāṇāṃdhakārasaṃchannaṃ dṛṣṭvā gaṇabalaṃ haraḥ ||
tadvāṇajālamācchidya bāṇairāvavṛte namaḥ || 9 ||
daityāṃśca vāṇavātyābhiḥ pīḍitānakarottadā ||
pracaṃḍabāṇajālaughairapātayata bhūtale || 10 ||
khaṃḍgaromaśiraḥ kāyāttathā paraśunācchinat ||
balāhakasya ca śiraḥ khaḍḍāṃgenākaroddidhā || 11 ||
sa baddhā ghasmaraṃ daityaṃ pāśenābhyahanadbhuvi ||
mahā vīraṃ pracaṃḍa ca cakartta triśikhena ha || 12 ||
vṛṣabheṇa hatāḥ kecitkecidvāṇairnipātitāḥ ||
na śekurasurāḥ sthātuṃ gajāriṃsahārditā iva || 13||
tataḥ krodhaparītātmā daityāndhik kṛtavānraṇe ||
śubhādikānmahādaityaḥ prahasanprāha dhairyavān || 14 ||
jalaṃdhara uvāca ||
kiṃ ve uccaritairmāturghāvadbhiḥ pṛṣṭhato hataiḥ ||
na hi bhītavadhaḥ ślāghyaḥ svargadaḥ śūramāninām || 15 ||
yadi vaḥ pradhane śraddhā sāro vā kṣullakā hṛdi |
agre tiṣṭhata mātraṃ me na cedrāmya sukhe spṛhā || 16 ||
raṇe mṛtyurvaraśvāsti sarvakāmaphalapradaḥ||
yaśaḥprado viśeṣeṇa mokṣado'pi prakīrttitaḥ ||17||
sūryasya maṃḍalaṃ bhittvā yāyādvaiḥ paramaṃ padam ||
parivāda paramajñānī raṇe yassaṃmukhe hataḥ || 18 ||
mṛtyorbhayaṃ na kartavyaṃ kadācitkutracidudhaiḥ ||
anirvāya yato hyeṣa upāyairnikhilerapi || || 19 ||
mṛtyurjanmavatāṃ vīrā dehena saha jāyate ||
adya vābdaśatāṃte vā mṛtyurvai prāṇināṃ dhruvaḥ || 20 ||
tanmṛtyubhayamutsārya yudhyadhvaṃ samare sudā ||
sarvathā paramānanda ihāmutrāpyasaṃśayaḥ || 21 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ityuktvā bodhayāmāsa svavīrānbahuśassa hi ||
dhairya dadhurna te bhītā apalāyaṃta raṇāhutam || 22 ||
atha dṛṣṭvā svasainyaṃ tatpalāyanaparāyaṇam ||
cukrodhāti mahāvīrassidhuputro jalaṃdharaḥ || 23 ||
tataḥ krodhaparī 1 yuṣmābhirityarthe vasādeśaṃ ārṣaḥ |
