śi0 pu0 ||199||
tātmā krodhādudaṃ jalaṃdharaḥ ||
āhvāpayāmāsa raṇe tīvrāśanisamasvanaḥ || 24 || ||
jalaṃdhara uvāca ||
yuddhasvādya mayā sārddhaṃ kimebhirnihataistava ||
yacca kiñcidvalaṃ te'sti taddarśaya jaṭādhara || 25 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā bāṇasaptatyā jaghāna vṛṣabhadhvajam ||
jalaṃdharo mahādaityaśśaṃbhumakkiṣṭa kāriṇam || 26 ||
tānaprāptānmahādevo jalaṃdharaśarāndrutam ||
nijairhi niśitairbāṇaiściccheda prahasanniva || 27 ||
tato hayāndhvajaṃ chatraṃ dhanu viccheda saptabhiḥ ||
jalaṃdharasya daityasya na taccitraṃ hare mune || 28 ||
sa cchinnadhanvā virathaḥ pāthodhitanayo'suraḥ ||
abhyadhāvacchivaṃ kruddho gadā mudyamya vegavān || 29 ||
prabhurgadāṃ ca tatkṣiptāṃ sahasaiva maheśvaraḥ ||
pārāśaryya mahālīlo drutaṃ bāṇairdvidhākarot || 30 ||
tathāpi muṣṭimudyamya mahākruddho mahāsuraḥ ||
abhyudyayau mahāvegānaṃ taṃ tajjighāṃsayā || 31 ||
tāvadeveśvareṇāśu bāṇaughaissa jalaṃdharaḥ ||
akliṣṭakarmakāreṇa krośamātra mapākṛtaḥ || 32 ||
tato jalaṃdharo daityo rudraṃ matvā balādhikam ||
sasarja māyāṃ gāṃdharvīmadbhutāṃ rudramohinīm || 33 ||
tasya māyāprabhāvāttu gaṃdharvāpsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ ||
āvirbhūtā aneke ca rudramona hahetave || 34 ||
tato jaguśva nanṛturgaṃdhavāpsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ ||
tālaveṇumṛdaṃgāṃśca vādayanti sma cāpare || 35 ||
taddṛṣṭvā mahadāścaryaṃ gaṇai rudro vimohitaḥ ||
patitānyapi śastrāṇi karebhyo na viveda saḥ || 36 ||
ekāgrībhūtamā lokya rudraṃ daityo jalaṃdharaḥ ||
kāmatassa jagāmāśu yatra gaurī sthitābhavat || 37 ||
yuddhe śuṃbhaniśuṃbhākhyau sthāpayitvā mahābalau |
daśadordaṇḍa paṃcāsyastrinetraśca jaṭādharaḥ ||38||
mahāvṛṣabhamārūḍhassarvathā rudrasaṃnibhaḥ ||
āsuyya māyayā vyāsa sa babhūva jalaṃdharaḥ ||39||
atha rudraṃ samāyāṃtamālo kya bhavavalabhā ||
abhyāyayo sakhīmadhyāttaddarśanapathe'bhavat || 40 ||
yāvaddadarśa cāvaigīṃ pārvatīṃ danujeśvaraḥ ||
tāvatsa vīrya mumuce jaḍāṃga vābhavattadā ||41||
atha jñātvā tadā gaurī dānavaṃ bhayavihvalā ||
jagāmāṃtarhitā vegātsā tadottaramānasam || 42 ||
tāmadṛśya tato daityaḥ kṣaṇā dvidyullatāmiva ||
javenāgātpunaryoddhuṃ yatra devo maheśvaraḥ|| 43 || |
pārvatyapi mahāviṣṇuṃ sasmāra manasā tadā ||
tāvaddadarśa taṃ devaṃ sopaviṣṭaṃ samīpagam || 44 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā pārvatī viṣṇuṃ jaganmātā śivapriyā ||
prasannamanasovāca praṇamataṃ kṛtāṃjalim || 45 || ||
pārvatyuvāca ||
viṣṇo jalaṃdharo daityaḥ kṛta vānparamādbhutam ||
tatkiṃ na viditaṃ te'sti ceṣṭitaṃ tasya durmateḥ || 46 ||
tacchrutvā jagadambāyā vacanaṃ garuḍadhvajaḥ ||
pratyuvāca śivāṃ natvā sāṃjalirnamrakaṃdharaḥ || 47 || ||
śrībhagavānuvāca ||
bhavatyāḥ kṛpayā devi tadvṛttaṃ viditaṃ mayā ||
yadājñāpaya māṃ mātastatkuryyāṃ tvadanujñayā ||48||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tacchrutvā viṣṇuvacanaṃ punarapyāha pārvatī ||
hṛṣīkeśaṃ jaganmātā dharmanītiṃ suśikṣayan || 49 ||
--- Page 342 [gcv] ---
darśitaḥ panthā budhyasvaṃ tvaṃ tathaiva hi ||
tatstrī pātitrataṃ dharmaṃ bhraṣṭaṃ kuru madājñayā || 50 ||
nānyathā sa mahādaityo bhavedvadhyo rameśvara ||
pātivratasamo nānyo dharmo'sti pṛthivītale || 51 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityanujñāṃ samākarṇya śirasādhāya tāṃ hariḥ ||
chalaṃ karttuṃ jagāmāśu punarjālaṃdharaṃ puram || 52 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe jalaṃdharavadhopākhyāne jalaṃdharayuddhavarṇanaṃ nāma dvāviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ ||22||
vyāsa uvāca ||
sanatkumāra sarvajña vada tvaṃ vadatāṃ vara ||
kimakārṣīddharistatra dharme tatyāja sā katham || 1 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
viṣṇu jalaṃdharaṃ gatvā daityasya puṭabhedanam ||
pātivratyasya bhaṃgāya vṛndāyāścākaronmatim || 2 ||
vṛdāṃ sa darśayāmāsa svanaṃ māyāvināṃ varaḥ ||
svayaṃ tanna garodyānamāsthito'dbhutavigrahaḥ || 3 ||
atha vṛndā tadā devī tatpatnī niśi suvratā ||
harermāyāprabhāvāttu dussvapnaṃ sā dadarśa ha || 4 ||
svapnamadhye hi sā viṣṇumāyayā pradadarśa ha ||
bharttāraṃ mahipārūḍhaṃ tailābhyaktaṃ digaṃbarama || 5 ||
kṛṣṇaprasūnabhūṣāḍhyaṃ kravyādagaṇasevitam ||
dakṣiṇāśāṃ gataṃ muṃḍaṃ tamasā ca vṛtaṃ tadā || 6 ||
svapuraṃ sāgare manaṃ sahasaivātmanā saha ||
ityādi bahudussvamānniśati sā dadarśa ha || 7 ||
tataḥ prabudhya sā bālā taṃ svanaṃ svaṃ vicinvatī ||
dadaśoditamādityaṃ sacchidraṃ niḥprabhaṃ muhuḥ ||8||
tadaniṣṭamidaṃ jñātvā rudaṃtī bhayavihvalā ||
kutracinnāpa sā śarma gopurāṭṭālabhūmiṣu || 9 ||
tatassakhīdvayayutā nagarodyānamāgamat |
