śāradā vipratanayāḥ bālavaidhavyamāgatā ||
tavabhakteḥ prabhāvātta putra saubhāgyavatyabhūt || 26 ||
bindugo dvijamātro hi veśyābhogī ca tatpriyā ||
vaṃcukā tvadyaśaḥ śrutvā paramāṃ gatimāyayau || 27 ||
ityādi bahava siddhiṃ gatā jīvāstava prabho ||
bhaktibhāvānmaheśāna dīnabandho kṛpālaya || 28 ||
tvaṃ paraḥ prakṛterbrahma puruṣātparameśvara ||
nirguṇastriguṇādhāro brahmaviṣṇuharātmakaḥ || 29 ||
nānākarmakaro nityaṃ nirvikāro'khileśvaraḥ ||
vayaṃ brahmādayassarve tava dāsā maheśvara || 30 ||
prasanno bhava deveśa rakṣā smānsarvadā śiva ||
tvatprajāśca vayaṃ nātha sadā tvaccharaṇaṃ gatāḥ || 31 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca || ||
iti stutvā ca te devā brahmādyāssa munīśvarāḥ tūṣṇīṃ babhūvurhi tadā śivāṃtridvandvacetasaḥ || 32 ||
atha śaṃsurmaheśānaḥ śrutvā devastutiṃ śubhām ||
dattvā varānvarānsadyastatraivāṃtardadhe prabhuḥ || 33 ||
devāssarve'pi muditā brahmādyā hataśatravaḥ ||
svaṃ svaṃ dhāma yayuḥ prītāḥ gāyataḥ śivasadyaśaḥ || 34 ||
idaṃ paramamākhyānaṃ jalaṃdharavimardanam ||
maheśacaritaṃ puṇyaṃ mahāghaughavināśanam || 35 ||
devastutiriyaṃ puṇyā sarvapāpapraṇāśinī ||
sarvasaukhyapradā nityaṃ maheśānaṃdadāyinī || 36 ||
yaḥ paṭhetpāṭhayedvāpi samākhyānāmidandrayam ||
sa bhuktveha paraṃ saukhyaṃ gāṇapatyamavāpnuyāt || 37 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe jalaṃdharavadhopākhyāne devastutivarṇanaṃ nāma paṃcaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 25 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
brahmaputra namaste'stu dhanyastvaṃ śaivasattama ||
