iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe śaṃkhacūḍatapaḥkaraṇavivāhavarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ ||28||
