. devadeva jagannātha vaikuṃṭhādhipate prabho ||
rakṣāsmāñśaraṇāpannāñchrīhare trijagadvaro || 38 ||
tvameva jagatāṃ pātā trilokeśācyuta prabho ||
lakṣmīnivāsa govinda bhaktaprāṇa namo'stu te || 39 ||
iti stutvā surāssarve ruruduḥ purato hareḥ ||
tacchrutvā bhagavānviṣṇurbrahmāṇa midamabravīt || 40 ||
viṣṇuruvāca ||
kimarthamāgatosi tvaṃ vaikuṃṭhaṃ yogidurlabham ||
kiṃ kaṣṭaṃ te samudbhūtaṃ tattvaṃ vada mamāgrataḥ || 41 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā harervākyaṃ praṇamya ca muhurmuhuḥ ||
baddhāñjalipuṭo bhūtvā vinayānatakandharaḥ || 42 ||
vṛttāṃtaṃ katha yāmāsa śaṃkhacūḍakṛtaṃ tadā ||
devakaṣṭasamākhyānaṃ puro viṣṇoḥ parātmanaḥ || 43 ||
haristadvacanaṃ śrutvā sarvatassarvabhāvavit ||
prahasyovāca bhagavāṃstadvahasyaṃ vidhiṃ prati || 44 ||
śrībhagavānuvāca ||
śaṃkhacūḍasya vṛttāṃtaṃ sarvaṃ jānāmi padmaja ||
madbhaktasya ca gopasya mahātejasvinaḥ purā || 45 ||
śṛṇu tatsarvavṛttāntamitihāsaṃ purātanam ||
saṃdeho naiva kartavyaśśaṃ kariṣyati śaṅkaraḥ || 46 ||
sarvopari ca yasyāsti śivalokaḥ parā tparaḥ ||
yatra saṃrājate śaṃbhuḥ parabrahma pareśvaraḥ || 47 ||
prakṛteḥ puruṣasyāpi yodhiṣṭhātā triśaktidhṛk ||
nirguṇassaguṇassopi paraṃ jyotiḥ svarūpa vān ||48||
yasyāṃgajāstu vai brahmastrayassṛṣṭyādikārakāḥ ||
sattvādiguṇasaṃpannā viṣṇubrahmahārābhidhāḥ || 49 ||
sa eva paramātmā hi viharatyumayā saha ||
yatra māyāvinirmukto nityānityaprakalpakaḥ ||50||
tatsamīpe ca goloko gośālā śaṃkarasya vai ||
tasyecchayā ca madrūpaḥ kṛṣṇo vasati tatra ha || 51 ||
tadbhavāṃ rakṣaṇārthāya tenājñaptassadā sukhī ||
tatsaṃprāptasukhassopi saṃkrīḍati vihāravit || 52 ||
tasya nārī samākhyātā rādheti jagada .mbikā ||
prakṛteḥ paramā mūrtiḥ paṃcamī suvihāriṇī || 53 ||
bahugopāśca gopyaśca tatra saṃti tadaṃgajāḥ ||
suvihāra parā nityaṃ rādhākṛṣṇānuvartinaḥ || || 54 ||
sa eva līlayā śaṃbhoridānīṃ mohito'nayā |
saṃprāpto dānavīṃ yoniṃ sudhā śāpātsvaduḥkhadām || 55 ||
rudraśūlena tanmṛtyuḥ kṛṣṇena vihitaḥ purā ||
tatassvadehamutsṛjya pārṣadassa bhaviṣyati || 56 ||
iti vijñāya deveśa na bhayaṃ kartumarhasi ||
śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇaṃ yāvassa sadyaśśaṃ vidhāsyati || 57 ||
ahaṃ tvaṃ cāmarāssarvaṃ tiṣṭhatīha visādhvasāḥ || || 58 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā savidhirviṣṇuḥ śivalokaṃ jagāma ha ||
saṃsmara nmanasā śaṃbhuṃ sarveśaṃ bhaktavatsalam || 59 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe śaṃkhacūḍavadhopākhyāne śaṃkhacūḍarājya karaṇavarṇanapūrvaka tatpūrvabhavavṛttacaritravarṇanaṃ nāmaikonatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 29 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
gatvā tadaiva sa vidhistadā vyāsa rameśvaraḥ ||
śivalokaṃ mahādivyaṃ nirādhāramabhautikam || 1 ||
sāhādobhyantaraṃ viṣṇurjagāma suditānanaḥ ||
nānāratnaparikṣiptaṃ vilasaṃtaṃ mahojjvalam || 2 ||
