J saṃprāpya prathamaṃ dvāraṃ vicitraṃ gaṇasevitam ||
śobhitaṃ parayā lakṣmyā mahoccamatisundaram || 3 ||
dadarśa dvārapālāṃśca ratnāsiṃhāsanasthitān ||
śobhitā śvetavastraiśca ratnabhūṣaṇabhūṣitān || 4 ||
pañcavaktratrinayanāngaurasundaravigrahān ||
triśūlādidharānvīrān bhasmarudrākṣaśobhitān || 5 ||
sa brāhmaṇa rameśaśca tān praṇamya vinamrakaḥ ||
kathayāmāsa vṛttāntaṃ prabhusaṃdarśanārthakam ||6||
tadājñāṃ ca dadustasmai praviveśa tadājñayā ||
paraṃ dvāraṃ mahāramyaṃ vicitraṃ paramaprabham || 7 ||
prabhūpakaṃṭhagatyarthaṃ vṛttātaṃ saṃnyavedayat ||
taddārapāya cājñaptastenānyaṃ praviveśa ha || 8 ||
evaṃ paṃcadaśadvārānpraviśya kamalo dbhavaḥ ||
mahodvāraṃ gatastatra nandinaṃ pradadarśa ha || 9||
samyaṅ natvā ca taṃ stutvā pūrvavattena nandinā ||
ājñaptaśca śanairviṣṇurviveśābhyaṃtaraṃ mudā ||10||
dadarśa gatvā tatroccaissabhāṃ śaṃbhossamutprabhām ||
sā pārṣadaiḥ parivṛtāṃ lasaddehaissubhūṣitām || 11 ||
maheśvarasya rūpaiśca digbhujaiśśubhakāṃtibhiḥ ||
pañca vastrinayanaiśśitikaṃṭhairmahojjvalaiḥ || 12 ||
sadratnayuktarudrākṣa bhasmābharaṇabhūṣitaiḥ ||
navendumaṃḍalākārāṃ caturasrāṃ manoharām || 13 ||
maṇīndrahāra nirmāṇahīrasārasuśobhitām ||
amūlyaratnaracitāṃ padmapatraiśca śobhitām || 14 ||
māṇikyajālamālābhirnānācitravicitritām ||
padmarāgendrara citāmadbhutāṃ śaṃkarecchayā || 15 ||
sopānaśatakairyuktāṃ syamaṃtakavinirmitaiḥ ||
svarṇasūtragranthiyuktaiścārucandanapallavaiḥ || 16 ||
indranīlamaṇistaṃ bhairveṣṭitāṃ sumanoharām ||
susaṃskṛtāṃ ca sarvatra vāsitāṃ gaṃdhavāyunā || 17 ||
sahasrayojanāyāmāṃ supūrṇāṃ bahukiṃkaraiḥ ||
dadarśa śaṃkaraṃ sāṃbaṃ tatra viṣṇu ssureśvaraḥ || 18 ||
vasaṃtaṃ madhyadeśe ca yathendutārakāvṛtam ||
amūlya ratnanirmāṇacitra siṃhāsana sthitam || 19 ||
kirīṭinaṃ kuṃḍalinaṃ ratnamālāvi bhūṣitam ||
bhasmoddhūlitasarvāṅgaṃ bibhrataṃ kelipaṃkajam || 20 ||
purato gītanṛtyañca paśyaṃtaṃ sasmitaṃ mudā || 21 ||
śāṃtaṃ prasannamanasamākati maho lasam ||
devyā pradattatāmbūlaṃ bhuktavaṃtaṃ suvāsitam || 22 ||
gaṇaiśca parayā bhaktyā sevitaṃ śvetacāmaraiḥ ||
stūyamānaṃ ca-siddhaiśca bhaktinamrātmakaṃdharaiḥ || || 23 ||
guṇātītaṃ pareśānaṃ tridevajanakaṃ vibhum ||
nirvikalpaṃ nirākāraṃ sākāraṃ svecchayā śivam || 24 ||
amāyamajamādyañca māyādhīśaṃ parātpa ram ||
prakṛteḥ puruṣasyāpi paramaṃ svaprabhuṃ sadā || 25 ||
evaṃ viśiṣṭaṃ taṃ dṛṣṭvā paripūrṇatamaṃ samam ||
viṣṇurbrahmā tuṣṭuvatuḥ praṇamya sukṛtāṃjalī || 26 ||
viṣṇuvidhī ūcatuḥ ||
devadeva mahādeva parabrahmākhileśvara ||
triguṇātīta nirvyaya tridevajanaka prabho || 27 ||
vayaṃ te śaraṇāpannā rakṣāsmānduḥkhitā vibho ||
śaṃkhacūḍārditānviṣṭānsannāthānparameśvara || 28 ||
ayaṃ yo'dhiṣṭhito loko goloka iti sa smṛtaḥ ||
adhiṣṭhātā tasya vibhuḥ kṛṣṇo'yaṃ tvadadhiṣṭhitaḥ || 29 ||
pārṣadapravarastasya sudāmā devayaṃtritaḥ ||
rādhāśapto vabhūvātha śaṃkhacūḍaca dānavaḥ || 30 ||
tena nissāritāḥ śaṃbho pīḍyamānāḥ

