rajasā sṛṣṭisamaye tvaṃ brahmā sṛṣṭi kṛtprabho ||
sattvena pālane viṣṇustribhuvāvanakāraka || 34 ||
tamasā pralaye rudro jagatsaṃhārakārakaḥ ||
nitraiguṇye śivākhyātastuyyoṃ jyotiḥsvarūpakaḥ||35||
