śāpoddhāraṃ kariṣye'haṃ yuvayossamaye khalu ||
maduktamiti saṃghārya śirasā rādhayā saha || 13 ||
śrīkṛṣṇo'modadatyaṃtaṃ svasthānamagamatsudhīḥ ||
nyaṣṭārtā sabhayaṃ tatra madārādhanatatparau || 14 ||
matvākhilaṃ madadhīnamasvatantraṃ nijaṃ ca vai ||
