rudrākṣābharaṇāssarve tathāsadbhasmadhāriṇaḥ ||
hārakuṃḍalakeyūramukuṭācairalaṃkṛtāḥ || || 29 ||
brahmendra viṣṇusaṃkāśā aṇimādiguṇairvṛtāḥ ||
sūryakoṭipratīkāśāḥ pravīṇā yuddhakarmaṇi || 30 ||
pṛthivīcāriṇaḥ kecitkecitpātālacā riṇaḥ ||
keṃcidvyomacarāḥ kecitsaptasvargacarā mune || 31 ||
kiṃ bahūktena devarṣe sarvalokanivāsinaḥ ||
yayuśśivagaṇāssarve yuddhārtha dānavaissaha || || 32 ||
aṣṭau ca bhairavā raudrā rudrācaikādaśāśu ye ||
vasavo'ṣṭau vāsavaśvādityā dvādaśa te drutam || 33 ||
hutāśanaśca candraśva viśvakarmāśvinau ca tau ||
kuberaśca yamaścaiva nirṛtirnalakūbaraḥ || 34 ||
vāyuśca varuṇaścaiva budhaśca maṃgalaśca vai ||
grahāścānye mahaśena kāmadevaśca vīryavān || 35 ||
ugradaṃṣṭra vāyadaṇḍaḥ koraṭaḥ koṭabhastathā ||
svayaṃ śatabhujā devī bhadrakālī maheśvarī || 36 ||
ratnendrasāranirmāṇavimānopari saṃsthitā ||
raktavastraparīdhānāḥ raktamālyānulepanā ||37||
nṛtyaṃtī ca hasaṃtī ca gāyaṃtī susvaraṃ mudā ||
abhaya dadatī svebhyo bhayaṃ cāribhya eva sā ||38||
bibhratī vikaṭāṃ jihvāṃ sulolāṃ yojanāyatām ||
śaṃkhacakragadāpadmakhaṅgacarmadhanuśśarān || 39 ||
kharparaṃ vartulākāraṃ gaṃbhīraṃ yojanāyatam ||
triśūlaṃ gagana sparśa śaktiṃ ca yojanāyatām || 40 ||
mudgaraṃ musalaṃ vajraṃ khaṅgaṃ phalakamulbaṇam ||
vaiṣṇavāstraṃ vāruṇāstraṃ vāyavyaṃ nāgapāśakam || 41 ||
nārāya ṇāstraṃ gāṃdharva brahmāstraṃ gāruḍaṃ tathā ||
pārjanyaṃ ca pāśupataṃ jṛṃbhaṇāstraṃ caṃ pārvatam || 42 ||
mahāvīraṃ ca sauraṃ ca kālakālaṃ mahānalam ||
maheśvarāstraṃ yāmyaṃ ca daṃḍaṃ saṃmohanaṃ tathā || 43 ||
samarthamastrakaṃ divyaṃ divyāstraśatakaṃ param ||
bibhratī ca karaissarvairanyānyapi ca sā tadā || 44 ||
āgatya tasthau sā tatra yoginīnāṃ trikoṭibhiḥ ||
sārddhaṃ ca ḍākinīnāṃ vai vikaṭānāṃ trikoṭibhiḥ || 45 ||
bhūtapretapiśācāśca kūṣmāṇḍā brahmarākṣasāḥ ||
vetālā rākṣasāścaiva yakṣāścaiva sakinnarāḥ || 46 ||
taiścaivābhivṛtaḥ skaṃdaḥ praṇamya candraśekharam ||
pituḥ pārśve sahāyoyaḥ samuvāsa tadājñayā || 47 ||
atha śaṃbhussamānīya svasainyaṃ sakalaṃ tadā ||
yuddhārthamagamadbhuda śaṃkhacūḍena nirbhayaḥ || 48 ||
candrabhāgānadītīre vaṭamūle manohare ||
tatra tasthau mahā devo devanistārahetave || 49 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe śaṃkhacūḍavadhe mahādevayuddhayātrāvarṇanaṃ nāma trayodaśo'

