śaṅkhacūḍa uvāca ||
śambhudūtamukhād devi yuddhāyāhaṃ samudyataḥ |
tena gacchāmy ahaṃ yoddhuṃ śāsanaṃ kuru me dhruvam || 4 ||
ity evam uktvā sa jñānī nānābodhanataḥ priyām |
krīḍāṃ cakāra harṣeṇa tām anādṛtya śaṅkaram || 5 ||
tau dampatī cikrīḍāte nimagnau sukhasāgare |
nānākāmakalābhiśca niśi cāṭuśatair api || 6 ||
