putraṃ kṛtvā ca rājendraṃ sarveṣu dāneṣu ca |
putre samarpya bhāryāṃ ca sa rājyaṃ sarvasaṃpadam || 8 ||
priyām āśvāsayāmāsa sa rājā rudatīṃ punaḥ |
niṣedhantīṃ ca gamanaṃ nānāvārtāprakathya ca || 9 ||
nijasenāpatiṃ vīraṃ samāhūya samāhataḥ |
ādideśa sa sannaddhassaṃgrāmaṃ kartum udyataḥ || 10 ||
śaṅkhacūḍa uvāca ||
adya senāpate vīrāssarve samaraśālinaḥ |
sannaddhākhilakarmāṇo nirgacchantu raṇāya ca || 11 ||
daityāśca dānavāḥ śūrāḥ ṣaḍaśītirudāyudhāḥ |
kaṅkānāṃ balināṃ śīghraṃ senā niryātu nirbhayāḥ || 12 ||
pañcāśadasurāṇāṃ hi nirgacchantu kulāni vai |
koṭivīryāṇi yuddhārthaṃ śambhunā devapakṣiṇā || 13 ||
sannaddhāni ca ghoṣrāṇāṃ kulāni ca śataṃ drutam |
nirgacchantu raṇārthaṃ hi śambhunā mama śāsanāt || 14 ||
kālakeyāśca mauryāśca dauhṛdāḥ kālakāstathā |
sajjā niryāntu yuddhāya rudreṇa mama śāsanāt || 15 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ity ājñāpya surapatir dānavendro mahābalaḥ |
nirjagāma mahāsainyaḥ sahasrair bahubhir vṛtaḥ || 16 ||
tasya senāpatiścaiva yuddhaśāstraviśāradaḥ |
mahāratho mahāvīro rathināṃ pravaro raṇe || 17 ||
trilakṣākṣauhiṇīyukto māṇḍalyaṃ ca cakāra ha |
bahirbabhūva śibirād raṇe vīrabhayaṃkaraḥ || 18 ||
ratnendrasāranirmāṇaṃ vimānam abhiruhya saḥ |
guruvargaṃ puraskṛtya raṇārthaṃ prayayau kila || 19 ||
puṣpabhadrānadītīre yatrākṣayavaṭaḥ śubhaḥ |
siddhāśrame ca siddhānāṃ siddhikṣetraṃ susiddhidam || 20 ||
kapilasya tapaḥsthānaṃ puṇyakṣetraṃ ca bhārate |
paścimodadhipūrve ca malayasya hi paścime || 21 ||
śrīśailottarabhāge ca gandhamādanadakṣiṇe |
pañcayojanavistīrṇaṃ dairghye śataguṇastathā || 22 ||
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśā bhārate ca supuṇyadā |
puṣpabhadrā nadī ramyā jalapūrṇā sarasvatī || 23 ||
lavaṇodadhipriyā bhāryā śaśvatsaubhāgyasaṃyutā |
sarasvatīsaṃśritā ca nirgatā sā himālayāt || 24 ||
gomantaṃ vāmataḥ kṛtvā praviṣṭā paścimodadhau |
tatra gatvā śaṅkhacūḍaḥ śivasenāṃ dadarśa ha || 25 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṇḍe śaṅkha

