cūḍayātrāvarṇanaṃ nāma catustriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 34 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tatra sthitvā dānavendro mahāntaṃ dānaveśvaram ||
dūtaṃ kṛtvā mahāvijñaṃ preṣayā māsa śaṃkaram || 1 ||
sa tatra gatvāṃ dūtaśca candrabhālaṃ dadarśa ha |
vaṭamūle samāsīnaṃ sūryakoṭisamaprabham || 2 ||
kṛtvā yogāsanaṃ dṛṣṭayā mudrāyuktaṃ ca sasmitam ||
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśaṃ jvalaṃta brahmatejasā || 3 ||
triśūlapaṭṭiśadharaṃ vyāghracarmābarāvṛtam ||
bhaktamṛtyuharaṃ śatiṃ gaurīkāntaṃ trilocanam || 4 ||
tapasāṃ phaladātāraṃ karttāraṃ sarvasaṃpadām ||
āśutoṣaṃ prasannāsyaṃ bhaktānugrahakātaram || 5 ||
viśvanāthaṃ viśvabījaṃ viśvarūpaṃ ca viśvajam ||
viśvabharaṃ viśvakaraṃ viśvasaṃhārakāraṇam || 6 ||
kāraṇaṃ kāraṇānāṃ ca narakārṇavatāraṇam ||
jñānapradaṃ jñānabījaṃ jñānānandaṃ sanātanam || 7 ||
avaruhya rathāddūtastaṃ dṛṣṭvā dānaveśvaraḥ ||
śaṃkaraṃ sakumāraṃ ca śirasā praṇanāma saḥ || 8 ||
vāmato bhadrakālī ca skaṃdaṃ tatpurataḥ sthitam ||
lokāśiṣaṃ dadau tasmai kālī skaṃdaśca śaṃkaraḥ || 9 ||
athāsau śaṃkhacūḍasya dūtaḥ paramaśāstravit ||
uvāca śaṃkaraṃ natvā karau baddhā śubhaṃ vacaḥ || 10 ||
dūta uvāca ||
śaṃkhacūḍasya dūtohaṃ tvatsakāśamihāgataḥ ||
vartate te kimicchādya tattvaṃ brūhi maheśvara || 11 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā ca vacanaṃ śaṃkhacūḍasya śaṃkaraḥ ||
prasannātmā mahādevo bhagavāṃstamu vāca ha || 12||
mahādeva uvāca ||
śṛṇu dūta mahāprājña vaco mama sukhāvaham ||
kathanīyāmidaṃ tasmai nirvivādaṃ vicārya ca || 13||
vidhātā jagatī brahmā pitā dharmasya dharmavit ||
marīcistasya putraśca kaśyapastatsutaḥ smṛtaḥ || 14 ||
dakṣaḥ prītyā dadau tasmai nijakanyāstrayodaśa ||
tāsvekā ca danussādhvī tatsaubhāgyavivarddhinī || 15 ||
catvāraste danoḥ putrā dānavāstejasolvaṇāḥ ||
teṣveko vipracittistu mahābalaparākramaḥ || 16 ||
tatputro dhārmikoṃ daṃbho dānavendro mahāmatiḥ ||
tasya tvaṃ tanayaḥ śreṣṭho dharmātmā dānaveśvaraḥ || 17 ||
purā tvaṃ pārṣado gopo gopeṣveva ca dhārmikaḥ ||
adhunā rādhikāśāpājjātastvaṃ dānaveśvaraḥ || 18 ||
dānavīṃ yonimāyātastattvato na hi dānavaḥ ||
nijavṛttaṃ purā jñātvā devavaraṃ tyajādhunā ||19||
drohaṃ na kuru taissārddhaṃ svapadaṃ bhuṃkṣva sādaram ||
nādhikaṃ savikāraṃ ca kuru rājyaṃ vicārya ca || 20 ||
dehi rājyaṃ ca devānāṃ matprītiṃ rakṣa dānava ||
nijarājye sukhaṃ tiṣṭha tiṣṭhatu svapade surāḥ || 21 ||
alaṃ bhūtavirodhena devadrohaṇa kiṃ punaḥ ||
kulīnāśśuddhakarmāṇaḥ sarve kaśyapavaṃśajāḥ || 22 ||
yāni kāni ca pāpāni brahmahatyādikāni ca ||
jñātidrohajapāpasya kalāṃ nārhati ṣoḍaśīm || 23 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityādibahuvāttau ca śrutismṛti parāṃ śubhām ||
provāca śaṃkarastasmai bodhayan jñānamuttamam ||24||
śikṣita śaṃkhacūḍena sa dūtastarkavittamaḥ ||
