dūta uvāca ||
tvayā yatkathitaṃ deva nānyathā tattathā vacaḥ||
tathyaṃ kiṃcidyathārtha ca śrūyatāṃ meṃ nivedanam || 26 ||
jñātidrohe mahatpāpaṃ tvayoktamadhunā ca yat ||
tatkimīśāsurāṇāṃ ca na surāṇāṃ vada prabho || 27 ||
sarveṣāmiti cettadvai tadā vacmi vicārya ca ||
nirṇayaṃ brūhi tatrādya kuru saṃdehabhaṃjanam || 28 ||
madhukaiṭabhayordaityavarayoḥ pralayārṇave ||
śiraśchedaṃ cakārāsau kasmāccakrī maheśvara || 29 ||
tripuressaha saṃyuddhaṃ bhasmatvakaraṇaṃ kutaḥ ||
bhavāñcakāra giriśa. surapakṣīti viśrutam || 30 ||
gṛhītvā tasya sarvasvaṃ kutaḥ prasthāpito baliḥ ||
sutalādi samuddhartuṃ tadvāre ca gadādharaḥ || 31 ||
sabhrātṛko hiraṇyākṣaḥ kathaṃ devaiśva hiṃsitaḥ ||
śuṃbhādayo'surāścaiva kathaṃ devairnipātitāḥ || 32 ||
purā samudramathane pīyūṣaṃ bhakṣitaṃ suraiḥ ||
keśabhājo vayaṃ tatra te sarve phalabhoginaḥ || 33 ||
krīḍābhāṃḍamidaṃ viśvaṃ kālasya paramātmanaḥ ||
sa dadāti yadā yasmai tasyaiśvaryaṃ bhavettadā || 34 ||
devadānavayorvairaṃ śaśvannaimittikaṃ sadā ||
parājayo jayasteṣāṃ kālādhīnaḥ krameṇa ca || 35 ||
tavānayorvirodhe ca gamanaṃ niṣphalaṃ bhavet ||
samasabaṃdhināṃ tadvai rocate neśvarasya te || 36 ||
surāsurāṇāṃ sarveṣāmīśvarasya mahātmanaḥ ||
iyaṃ te rahitā lajjā sparddhāsmā bhissahādhunā || 37 ||
yatodhikā caiva kīrtihāniścaiva parājaye ||
tavaitadviparītaṃ ca manasā saṃvicāryatām || 38 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityetadvacanaṃ śrutvā saṃprahasya trilocanaḥ ||
yathocitaṃ ca madhuramuvāca dānaveśvaram || 39 ||
maheśa uvāca ||
vayaṃ bhaktaparādhīnā na svataṃtrāḥ kadāpi hi ||
tadicchayā tatkarmāṇaḥ na kasyāpi ca pakṣiṇaḥ || 40 ||
purā vidhiprārthanayā yuddhamādau harerepi ||
madhukaiṭabhayodaityavarayoḥ pralayārṇave || || 41 ||
devaprārthanayā tena hiraṇyakaśipoḥ purā ||
prahlādārtha vadho'kāri bhaktānāṃ hitakāriṇā || 42 ||
tripuressaha saṃyuddhaṃ bhasmatvakaraṇaṃ tataḥ ||
devaprārthanayākāri mayāpi ca purā śrutam || 43 ||
sarveśvaryāssarvamātudevaprārthanayā purā ||
āsīcchubhādibhiryuddhaṃ vadhasteṣāṃ tayā kṛtaḥ|| 44 ||
adyāpi tridaśāssarvaṃ brahmāṇaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ ||
sa sadevo harimau ca devaśśaraṇamāgataḥ || 45 ||
haribrahmādikānāṃ ca prārthanāvaśatopyaham ||
surāṇāmī śvaro dūta yuddhārthamagamaṃ khalu || 46 ||
pārṣadapravarastvaṃ hi kṛṣṇasya ca mahātmanaḥ ||
yeye hatāśca daiteyā na hi kepi tvayā samāḥ || 47 ||
kā lajjā mahatī rājan mama yuddhe tvayā saha ||
devakayārthimīśohaṃ vinayena ca preṣitaḥ || 48 ||
gaccha tvaṃ śaṃkhacūḍe vai kathanīyaṃ ca me vacaḥ ||
sa ca yuktaṃ karo tvatra surakārya karomyaham || 49 ||
ityuktvā śaṃkarastatra virarāma maheśvaraḥ ||
uttasthau śaṃkhacūṇasya dūto'gacchattadaṃtikam ||50||
iti śrīśivamahāpu rāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe śaṃkhacūḍavadhe śivadūtasaṃvādo nāma paṃcatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 35 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
