gatvā ca śivavākyaṃ jagāda ha ||
savistaraṃ yathārthaṃ ca niścayaṃ tasya tattvataḥ || 1 ||
tacchrutvā śaṃkhacūḍosau dānavendraḥ pratāpavān ||
aṃgīcakāra su prītyā raṇameva sa dānavaḥ || 2 ||
samāruroha yānaṃ ca sahāmātyaiśca satvaraḥ ||
ādideśa svasainyaṃ ca yuddhārtha śaṃkareṇa ca || 3 ||
śivassvasainyaṃ devāṃśva prerayāmāsa satvaraḥ ||
svayamapyakhileśopi saṃnaddhoca līlayā || 4 ||
yuddhāraṃbho babhūvāśu nedurvādyāni bhūriśaḥ ||
kolāhalaśva saṃjāto vīraśabdastathaiva ca || 5 ||
devadānavayoryuddhaṃ parasparamabhūnmune ||
dharmato yuyudhe tatra devadānavayorgaṇaḥ || 6 ||
svayaṃ mahendro yuyudhe sārddhaṃ ca vṛṣaparva ṇā ||
bhāskaro yuyudhe vipracittinā saha dharmataḥ || 7 ||
daṃbhena saha viṣṇuśca cakāra paramaṃ raṇam ||
kālāsureṇa kālaśca gokarṇena hutāśanaḥ || 8 ||
kuberaḥ kālakeyena viśvakarmā mayena ca ||
bhayaṃkareṇa mṛtyuśca saṃhāreṇa yamastathā || 9 ||
kālambikena varuṇaścaṃcalena samīraṇaḥ ||
budhaśva ghaṭa pṛṣṭhena raktākṣeṇa śanaiśvaraḥ || 10 ||
jayanto ratnasāreṇa vasavo varcasāṃ gaṇaiḥ ||
aśvinau dīptimadbhayāṃ ca dhūmreṇa nalakūbaraḥ || 11 ||
dhuraṃdhareṇa dharmaśva gaṇakāṃkṣeṇa maṃgalaḥ ||
śobhākareṇa vaiśvānaḥ pipiṭena ca manmathaḥ || 12 ||
gokāmukhena cūrṇena khaḍganānā sureṇa ca ||
dhūmreṇa saṃhalenāpi viśvena ca pratāpinā || 13 ||
palāśena dvādaśā'rkā yuyudhurdharmataḥ pare ||
asurairamarāssārddhaṃ śivasāhāyyaśālinaḥ || 14 ||
ekādaśa mahārudrāścaikādaśabhayaṃ karaiḥ ||
asurairyuyudhuvīrai mahābalaparākramaiḥ || 15 ||
mahāmaṇiśca yuyudhe cogracaṃḍādibhissaha ||
rāhuṇā saha candraśva jīvaḥ śukreṇa dharmataḥ || 16 ||
nandīśvarādayassarvaṃ dānavapravaraissaha ||
yuyudhuśca mahāyuddhe noktā vistarataḥ pṛthak || 17 ||
vaṭamūle tadā śaṃbhustasthau kālyāḥ sutena ca ||
sarve ca yuyudhussainyasamūhāssatataṃ mune || 18 ||
ratnasiṃhāsane ramye koṭidānavasaṃyutaḥ ||
uvāsa śaṃkhacūḍaśca ratnabhūṣaṇabhūṣitaḥ || 19 ||
mahāyuddho babhūvātha devāsuravimardanaḥ ||
nānāyudhāni divyāni calati sma mahāmṛdhe || 20 ||
gadaṣṭipaṭṭiśāścakrabhuśuṃḍiprāsamudgarāḥ ||
nitriṃśabhallaparighāḥ śaktayunmukhaparaśvadhāḥ || 21 ||
śaratomarakhaṅgāśca śatadbhyaśca sahasraśaḥ ||
bhidipālādayaścānye vīrahasteṣu śobhitāḥ || 22 ||
śirāṃsi cicchiduścaibhivarāstatra mahotsavāḥ ||
vīrāṇāmubhayoścaiva sainyayorgarjato raṇe || 23 ||
gajāsturaṃgā bahavaḥ syandanāśca padātayaḥ ||
sārohavāhā vividhāstaṃtrāsan suvikhaṃḍitāḥ || 24 ||
nikṛttabāhūrukarakaṭikarṇayugāṃtrayaḥ ||
saṃchinnadhvajabāṇāsitanutravarabhūṣaṇāḥ || 25 ||
samu ddhatakirīṭaiśca śirobhissaha kuṃḍalaiḥ ||
saṃraṃbhanaṣṭerāstīrṇā babhau bhūḥ karabhorubhiḥ || 26 ||
mahābhujaissā bharaṇaissaṃchinnaissāyudhaistathā ||
a~gairanyaiśva sahasā paṭalairvā sasāraṃghaiḥ || 27 ||
mṛdhe bhaṭāḥ pradhāvaṃtaḥ kabaṃdhān svaśirokṣibhiḥ ||
paśyaṃtastatra cotpeturudyatāyudhasagujaiḥ || 28 ||
