yugāṃtakālāgnisamaprabhāvaṃ jaganmayaṃ kiṃ bahubhirvacobhiḥ||
astaṃ khau'so'pi hi gacchatīśo gato'surāṇāṃ nagarīṃ mahātmā ||27||
kṛtvā ca yuddhaṃ prabalaissadaityaihatvātha tāndaityagaṇāngṛhītvā ||
babhrāma tatrādbhutavikramaśca vabhaṃja tāṃstānasurānnṛsiṃhaḥ || 28 ||
dṛṣṭassa daityairatulaprabhāvaste rebhire te hi tathaiva sarve ||
