prahlāda uvāca ||
eṣa praviṣṭo bhagavānanaṃto nṛsiṃhamātro nagaraṃ tvadaṃtaḥ ||
nivṛtya yuddhāccharaṇaṃ prayāhi paśyāmi siṃhasya karālamūrttim || 30 ||
yasmānna yoddhā bhuvanatraye'pi kuruṣva rājyaṃ vinamanmṛgendram ||
śrutvā svaputrasya vaco durātmā tamāha bhīto'si kimatra putra || 31 ||
uktveti putraṃ ditijādhinātho daityarṣabhānvīravarānsa rājā ||
gṛdvaṃtu vai siṃha mamuṃ bhavaṃto vīrā virūpabhrukuṭīkṣaṇaṃ tu || 32 ||
tasyājñayā daityavarāstataste grahītukāmā viviśurmṛgendram ||
kṣaṇena dagdhāśśalabhā ivāgniṃ rūpābhi lāṣātpravivikṣavo vai || 33 ||
daityeṣu dagdheṣvapi daityarājaśvakāra yuddhaṃ sa mṛgādhipena ||
śastraissamayairā khilaistathāstraiśśaktyaṣṭipāśāṃkuśapāvakāṃdyaiḥ || || 34 ||
saṃyudhyatoreva tayorjagāma brāhmaṃ dinaṃ vyāsa hi śastrapāṇyoḥ||
pravīrayorvīrairaveṇa garjatoḥ parasparaṃ krodhasuyuktacetasoḥ || 35 ||
tataḥ sa. daityassa isā vahūṃśca kṛtvā bhujāñchastrayutānnirīkṣya ||
nṛsiṃharūpaṃ prayayau mṛgendraṃ saṃyudhyamānaṃ sahasā samaṃtāt || 36 ||
tatassuyuddhaṃ tvatidussahaṃ tu śastressa mastaiśva tathākhilātraiḥ ||
kṛtvā mahādaityavaro nṛsiṃhaṃ kṣayaṃ gataiśśūladharo'bhyupāyāt || 37 ||
tato gṛhītassamṛgādhipena bhujairanekaigirisāravadbhiḥ ||
nidhāya jānau sa bhujāṃtareṣu nakhāṃkurairdānavamarmabhidbhiḥ || 38 ||
nakhāstrahṛtpadmamasṛgvimiśramutpādya jīvādvigataḥ kṣaṇena ||
tyaktastadānīṃ sa tu kāṣṭha bhūtaḥ punaḥ punaśvarṇitasarvagātraḥ || 39 ||
tasminhate devaripau prasannaḥ prahādamāmaṃtrya kṛtapraṇāmam ||
rājye'bhiṣicyādbhutavīryaviṣṇustataḥ prayāto gatimapratayam || 40 ||
tato'tihṛṣṭāssakalāssureśāḥ praṇamya viṣṇuṃ diśi vipra tasyām ||
yayuḥ svadhāmāniṃ pitāmahādyāḥ kṛtasvakāryaṃ bhaga vaṃtamīḍyam || 41 ||
pravarṇitaṃ tvaṃdhakajanma rudrāddhiraṇyanetrasya mṛtirvarāhāt ||
nṛsiṃhatastatsahajasya nāśaḥ prahādarājyāptiriti prasaṃgāt || || 42 ||
śṛṇu tvidānīṃ dvijavarya mattodhakaprabhāvaṃ bhavakṛtpralabdham ||
hareṇa yuddhaṃ khalu tasya paścādgaṇādhipatyaṃ giriśaṃsya tasya || 43 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṇḍe gāṇādhipataprātyaṃdhakajanmahiraṇyanetrahiraṇyakaśipuvadhavarṇanaṃ nāma trica

