daityendra sarvaṃ bhavitā tadetadvināśahetuṃ ca gṛhāṇa kiṃcit ||
yasmānna jāto naṃ janiṣyate vā yo na praviṣṭo mukhamaṃtakasya || 13||
atyantadīrgha khalu jīvitaṃ tu bhavādṛśāssatpuruṣāstyajaṃtu ||
etadvaca ssānunayaṃ niśamya pitāmahātprāha punasla daityaḥ ||14||
aṃdhaka uvāca ||
kālatraye yāśca bhavaṃti nāryaḥ śreṣṭhāśca madhyāśva tathā kaniṣṭhāḥ||
tāsāṃca madhye khalu ratnabhūtā mamāpi nityaṃ jananīva kācit || 15 ||
kāyena vācā manasāpyagamyā nārī nṛlokasya ca durlabhāya ||
tāṃ kāma yānasya mamāstu nāṃśo daityendra bhāvādbhagavānsvayaṃbhūḥ || 16 ||
vākyaṃ tadākarṇya sa padmayoniḥ suvismitaśśaṃkarapādapadmam ||
sasmāra saṃprāpya nideśa māśu śaṃbhostu taṃ prāha tatodhakaṃ vai || 17 || ||
brahmovāca ||
yatkāṃkṣase daityavarāstu te vai sarvaṃ bhavatyeva vacassakāmam ||
uttiṣṭha daityendra labhasva kāmaṃ sadaiva vīraistu kuruṣva yuddham || 18 ||
śrutvā tadetadvacanaṃ munīśa vidhāturāśu praṇipatya bhaktyā ||
lokeśvaraṃ hāṭakanetraputraḥ snāyvasthiśeṣastu tamāha devam || 19 || ||
aṃdhaka uvāca ||
kathaṃ vibho vairibalaṃ praviśya hyanena dehena karomi yuddham ||
snāyvasthiśeṣaṃ kuru māṃsapuṣṭaṃ kareṇa puṇye

--- Page 382 [gcv] ---
na ca māṃ spṛśādya ||20|| ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śrutvā vacastasya sa padmayoniḥ kareṇa saṃspṛśya ca taccharīram ||
gatassurendraissahitaḥ svadhāma saṃpūjyamāno munisiddhasaṃghaiḥ|| 21 ||
saṃspṛṣṭamātrassa ca daityarājassampūrṇa deho balavānbabhūva |
saṃjātanetrassubhago babhūva hṛṣṭassvamevaṃ nagaraṃ viveśa || 22||
utsṛjya rājyaṃ sakalaṃ ca tasmai prahlādamukhyāstvatha dānavendrāḥ ||
tamāgataṃ labdhavaraṃ ca matvā bhṛtyā babhūvurvaśagāstu tasya || 23 ||
tatondhakaḥ svarga magādvijetuṃ senābhiyuktassahabhṛtyavargaḥ ||
vijitya lekhānpradhane samastāṃnkarapradaṃ vajradharaṃ cakāra || 24 ||
nāgānsuparṇānvararākṣasāṃśca gaṃdharvayakṣāna pi mānuṣāṃstu ||
girīndravṛkṣānsamareṣu sarvāṃścatuṣpadaḥ siṃhamukhānvijigye || 25 ||
trailokyamataddhi carācaraṃ vai vaśaṃ cakārātmani saṃniyojya ||
tato nukūlāni sudarśanāni nārīsahasrāṇi bahūni gatvā || 26 ||
rasātale caiva tathā dharāyāṃ triviṣṭape yāḥ pramadāḥ surūpāḥ ||
tābhiryuto'nyeṣu sa parva teṣu rarāṃma ramyeṣu nadītaṭeṣu || 27 ||
krīḍāyamānassa tu madhyavartī tāsāṃ praharṣādatha dānavendraḥ ||
tatpītaśiṣṭāni pibanpravṛttyai divyāni peyānisumānu ṣāṇi || 28 ||
anyāni divyāni tu yaṃdrasāni phalāni mūlāni sugaṃdhavaṃti ||
saṃprāpya yānāni suvāhanāni mayena sṛṣṭāni gṛhottamāni || 29 ||
puṣpārdhadhūpānnavilepanaiśca suśobhitānyadbhutadarśanaiśca ||
saṃkrīḍamānasya gatāni tasya varṣāyutānīha tathadhakasya ||30||
jānāti kiṃcinna śubhaṃ paratra yadā tmanassaukhyakaraṃ bhaveddhi ||
sadāndhako daityavarassa mūṃḍhoṃ madāṃdhabuddhiḥ kṛtaduṣṭasaṃga || 31 ||
tataḥ pramattastu sutānpradhānānkutarkavādaira bhibhūya sarvān ||
cacāra daityaissahito mahātmā vināśayanvaidikasarvadharmān || 32 ||
vedāndvijānvittamadābhibhūto na manyate smāpyamarāngurūṃśca ||
reme tathā daivagato hatāyuḥ svasyairahobhirgamayanvayaśca || 33 ||
tataḥ kadācidrutavānsasainyo bahuprayātā pṛthivī tale'smin ||
anekasaṃkhyā api varṣakoṭyaḥ praharṣito maṃdaraparvataṃ tu || 34 ||
svarṇopamāṃ tatra nirīkṣya śobhāṃ babhrāma sainyaissaha mānamattaḥ ||
krīḍārthamāsādya ca taṃ girīndraṃ matiṃ sa vāsāya cakāra mohāt || 35 ||
śubhaṃ dṛḍhaṃ tatra puraṃ sa kṛtvā mudāsthito daityapatiḥ prabhāvāt ||
niveśayāmāsa punaḥ krameṇa atyadbhutaṃ mandara śailasānau || 36 ||
duryodhano vaidhasahastisaṃjñau tanmaṃtriṇo dānavasattamasya |
te vai kadāciddvirisusthale hi nārīṃ surūpāṃ dadṛśustrayo'pi || 37 ||
te śīghragā daityavarāstu harṣāddutaṃ mahādaityapatiṃ sametya ||
ūcuryathādṛṣṭamatīva prītyā tathāndhakaṃ vīravaraṃ hi sarve || 38 ||
maṃtriṇa ūcuḥ ||
guhāṃtare dhyāna nimīlitākṣo daityendra kaśvinmuniratra dṛṣṭaḥ ||
rūpānvitaścandrakalārddhacūḍaḥ kaṭisthale baddhagajendrakṛttiḥ || 39 ||
