śi0 pu0 ||220||
gātraḥ kapālamālābharaṇo jaṭālaḥ ||
sa śūlahastaśśaratūṇadhārī mahādhanuṣmānvivṛtākṣasūtraḥ || 40 ||
khaṅgī triśūlī lakuṭī kapadī: caturbhujo gauratarākṛtirhi ||
bhasmānulipto vilasatsutejāstapasvivaryo'dbhutasarvaveśaḥ || 41 ||
tasyāvidūre puruṣaśca dṛṣṭassa vānaro ghoramukhaḥ : karālaḥ ||
sarvāyudho rūkṣakaraśca rakṣansthiro jaradgovṛṣabhaśca śuklaḥ || 42 ||
tasyopaviṣṭasya tapasvinopi sucārurūpā taruṇī manojñā ||
nārī śubhā pārśvagatā hi tasya dṛṣṭvā ca kācidbhuvi ratnabhūtā || 43 ||
pravālamuktāmaṇihemaratnavastrāvṛtāṃ mālyaśubhopagūḍhā ||
sā yena dṛṣṭvā sa ca dṛṣṭimānsyāta dṛṣṭena cānyena kimatra kāryam || 44||
mānyā maheśasya ca divyanārī bhāryyāṃ muneḥ puṇyavataḥ priyā sā ||
yogyā hi draṣṭuṃ bhavataśca samyagānā yya daityendra suratnabhoktaḥ || 45 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śrutveti teṣāṃ vacanāni tāni kāmāturo ghūrṇitasarvagātraḥ ||
visarjayāmāsa munessakāśaṃ duryodhanādīnsahasā sa daityaḥ || 46 ||
āsādya te taṃ munimaprameyaṃ vṛhadrataṃ maṃtrivarā hi tasya ||
surājanītipra vaṇā munīśa praṇamya taṃ daityanideśamāduḥ || 47 ||
maṃtriṇa ūcuḥ ||
hiraṇyanetrasya suto mahātmā daityādhirājo'ndhakanāmadheyaḥ ||
trailokya nātho bhavakṛnnideśādihopaviṣṭo'dya vihāraśālī || 48 ||
tanmaṃtriṇo vai vayamaṃgavīrāstavopakaṃṭhaṃ ca samāgatāḥ sma ||
tatpreṣitāstvāṃ yaduvāca tadvai śṛṇuṣva saṃdattamanāstapasvin || 49 ||
tvaṃ kasya putro'si kimarthamatra sukhopaviṣṭo munivarya dhīman ||
kasyeyamīdṛktaruṇī surūpā deyā śubhā daityapatermunīndra ||
50 kvedaṃ śarīraṃ tava bhasmadigdhaṃ kapālamālābharaṇaṃ virūpam ||
tūṇīrasatkārmukavāṇakhaṅgabhuśuṃḍiśūlā śanitomarāṇi || || 51 ||
ka jāhnavī puṇyatamā jaṭāye kvāyaṃ śaśī vā kuṇapāsthikhaṇḍam ||
viṣānaloṃ dīrghamukhaḥ kva sarpaḥ kva saṃgamaḥ pīnapayodharāyāḥ || 52 ||
jaradgavārohaṇamapraśastaṃ kṣamāvatastasya na darśanaṃ ca ||
saṃdhyāpraṇāmaḥ kacideṣa dharmaḥ kkabhojanaṃ lokaviruddhametat ||53||
prayaccha nārīṃ mama sāntva pūrva striyā tapaḥ kiṃ kuruṣe vimūḍha ||
ayuktametattvayi nānurūpaṃ yasmādahaṃ ratnapatistriloke || 54 ||
vimuṃca śastrāṇi mayādya coktaḥ kuruṣva paścā tapa eva śuddham ||
ullaṃghya macchāsanamapradhṛṣyaṃ vimokṣyase sarvamidaṃ śarīram || 55 ||
satvadhikaṃ duṣṭamatiṃ pradhāno maheśvaro laukikabhāvaśīlaḥ ||
provācca daityaṃ smitapūrvamevamākarṇya sarve tvatha dūtavākyam || 56 ||
śiva uvāca ||
yadyasmi rudrastava kiṃ mayā syāt kimarthamevaṃ vadasīti mithyā ||
śṛṇu prabhāvaṃ mama daityanātha nyāyyaṃ na vaktuṃ vacanaṃ tvayaivam || 97 ||
nāhaṃ kvacitsvaṃ pitaraṃ smarāmi guhāṃtare ghoramananyacīrṇam ||
etadvataṃ pāśupataṃ carāmi na mātaraṃ tvajñatamo virūpaḥ || 58 ||
amūlametanmayi tu prasiddhaṃ sudustyajaṃ sarvamidaṃ mamāsti ||
bhāryā mameyaṃ taruṇī surūpā savai

--- Page 384 [gcv] ---
sahā sarvagatasya siddhiḥ || 59 ||
etarhi yadyaducitaṃ tavāsti gṛhāṇa tadvai khalu rākṣasa tvam ||
etāvaduktvā virarāma śaṃbhustapasviveṣaḥ puratastu teṣām || 60 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
gaṃbhīrametadvacanaṃ niśamya te dānavāstaṃ praṇipatya mūrdhnā ||
jagmustato daityavarasya sūnuṃ trailokyanāśāya kṛtapratijñam || 61 ||
babhāṣire daityapatiṃ pramattaṃ praṇamya rājānamadīnasattvāḥ ||
te tatra sarve jayaśabdapūrvaṃ ! rudreṇa yattatsmitapūrvamuktam || 62 || ||
maṃtriṇa ūcuḥ ||
niśācaraścaṃcalaśauryadhairyaḥ kva dānavaḥ kṛpaṇassattvahīnaḥ ||
krūraḥ kṛtaghnaśca sadaiva pāpī kiṃ dānavaḥ sūryasutādvibheti ||63||
rājatvamukto'khiladaityanāthastapasvinā tanmuninā vihasya ||
matvā svabuddhayāṃ tṛṇavattrilokaṃ mahaujasā vīravareṇa nūnam || 64 ||
kāhaṃ ca śastrāṇi ca dāruṇāni mṛtyośva saṃtrāsakaraṃ k yuddham ||
kka vīrako vānaravakratulyo niśācaro jarasā jarjarāṃgaḥ || 65 ||
kāyaṃ svarūpaḥ kva ca maṃdabhāgyo balaṃ tvadīyaṃ kvaca vīrūdho vā ||
śakto'pi cattvaṃ prayatasva yuddhaṃ kartuṃ tadā hyehi kuruṣva kiṃcit || 66 ||
vajrāśane stulyamihāsti śastraṃ bhavādṛśāṃ nāśakaraṃ ca ghoram ||
kva te śarīraṃ mṛdupadmatulyaṃ vicārya caivaṃ kuru rocate yat || 67 || ||
maṃtriṇa ūcuḥ ||
ityeva mādīni vacāṃsi bhadraṃ tapasvinoktāni ca dānaveśa ||
yuktaṃ na te tena sahātra yuddhaṃ tvāmāha rājansmayamāna eva || 68 ||
vivastuśūnyairbahubhiḥ pralāpai rasmābhiruktairyedi budhyase tvam ||
tapobhiyuktena tapasvinā vai smartāsi paścānmunivākyametat || 69 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tatassa teṣāṃ vacanaṃ niśamya jajvāla roṣeṇa sa maṃdabuddhiḥ ||
ājyāvasiktastviva kṛṣṇavarmā satyaṃ hitaṃ tatkuṭilaṃ sutīkṣṇam || 70 ||
gṛhītakhaṅgo varadānamattaḥ pracaṃḍavātānukṛtiṃ ca kurvan ||
gaṃtuṃ ca tatra smaravāṇaviddhassamudyato'bhūdviparītadaivaḥ || 71 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakher̤e aṃdhakagāṇatatyalābhopākhyāne dūtasaṃvādo nāma catuścatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 44 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
gatastato mattagajendra gāmī pītvā surāṃ ghūrṇitalocanaśca ||
mahānubhāvo bahusainyayuktaḥ pracaṃḍavīro varavīrayāyī || 1 ||
dadarśa daityaḥ smarabāṇaviddho guhāṃ tato vīrakaruddhamā gam ||
snigdhaṃ yathā vīkṣya pataṃgusaṃjñaḥ daśāpradīpaṃ ca kṛmirdyupetya || 2 ||
tathā pradaśyāśu punaḥpunaśca saṃpīḍyamānāpi sa vīrakeṇa ||
babhūva kāmāgnidagdhadehoṃ'dhako mahādaityapatiḥ sa mūḍhaḥ || 3 ||
pāṣāṇavṛkṣāśanitoyavahnibhujaṃgaśastrāstra vibhīṣikābhiḥ ||
saṃpīḍito'sau na punaḥ prapīḍyaḥ pṛṣṭaśva kastvaṃ samupāgatosi || 4 ||
niśamya tadāṃ svamataṃ sa tasmai cakāra yuddhaṃ sa tu vīrakeṇa ||
muhūrtamāśvaryavadaprameyaṃ saṃkhye jito vīratareṇa daityaḥ || 5 ||
tatastu saṃgrāmaśiro vihāya kṣutkṣāmakaṃṭhastṛṣito gato'bhūt ||
cūrṇīkṛte khaḍgavare ca khinne palāyamāno gatavi smayaḥ saḥ || 6 ||
cakrustadājiṃ saha vīrakeṇa prahlādamukhyā ditijapradhānāḥ ||
lajjāṃkuśākṛṣṭadhiyo babhruvussudāruṇāḥ śastraśatairanekaiḥ || 7 ||
viro

--- Page 385 [gcv] ---
śi• ||221||
canastatra cakāra yuddhaṃ bālaśca bāṇaśca sahasrabāhuḥ ||
bhajiḥ kujaṃbhastvatha śaṃbaraśca vṛtrādayaścāpyatha vīryavaṃtaḥ || 8 ||
te yuddhaṃmānā vijitāḥ samaṃ tādvidhākṛtā vai gaṇavīrakeṇa ||
śeṣe hatānāṃ bahudānavānāmuktaṃ jayatyeva hi siddhasaṃdhaiḥ || 9 ||
bheruṃḍajānābhinayapravṛtte medovasāmāṃsasupūyamadhye ||
kravyā dasaṃghātasamākule tu bhayaṃkare śoṇitakardame tu || 10 ||
bhagnaistu daityairbhagavān pinākī vrataṃ mahāpāśupataṃ sughoram ||
priye mayā yatkṛtapūrvamāsīddākṣā yaṇīṃ prāha susāṃtvayitvā || 11 || ||
śiva uvāca ||
tasmādvalaṃ yanmama tatpraṇaṣṭaṃ matyairamartyasya yataḥ prapātaḥ ||
puṇyakṣayāhī graha eva jāto divāniśaṃ devi tava prasaṃgāt || 12 ||
utpādya divyaṃ paramādbhutaṃ tu punarvaraṃ ghorataraṃ ca gatvā ||
tasmādvataṃ ghorataraṃ carāmi sunirbhayā sundari vai viśokāḥ || 13 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
etāvaduktvā vacanaṃ mahātmā utpādya ghoṣaṃ śanakaiścakāra ||
sa tatra gatvā vratamugradīpto gato vanaṃ puṇyatamaṃ sughoram || 14 ||
catu hi śakyaṃ tu surāsurairyanna tādṛśaṃ varṣasahasramātram ||
sā pārvatī maṃdaraparvatasthā pratīkṣyamāṇāgamanaṃ bhavasya || 15 ||
pativratā śīlaguṇopapannā ekākinī nityamatho bibhītā |
guhāṃtare duḥkhaparā vabhūva saṃrakṣitā sā mutavīrakeṇa || 16 ||
tatassa daityo varadānamatta stairyodhamukhyaissahito guhāṃ tām ||
vibhinnadhairyaḥ punarājagāma śilīmukhairmārasamudbhavaiśca || 17 ||
atyadbhutaṃ tatra cakāra yuddhaṃ hitvā tadā bhojana pānanidrāḥ|
rātriṃdivaṃ paṃcaśatāni paṃca kruddhassa sainyassaha vīrakeṇa || 18 ||
khadvaissa kutaissaha bhidipāle gadābhuśuṃḍībhiratho prakāṃḍaiḥ ||
śilīmukhairarddha śaśībhiruyairvitastiābhiḥ kūrmamukhaijvaladbhiḥ || 19||
nārācamukhyairniśitaiśca śūlaiḥ paraśvadhaistomara mudgaraiśca ||
khaṅgairguḍeḥ parvatapādapaiśca divyairathāstrairapi daitya saṃghaiḥ || 20 ||
nadīdhitibhinnatanuḥ papāta dvāraṃ guhāyā pihitaṃ samastam ||
tairāyudhai daityabhujaprayukairguhāmukhe mūrcchita eva paścāt || 21 ||
ācchāditaṃ vīrakamastrajālairdaityaiśva sarvaistu muhūrtamātram ||
apāvṛtaṃ kartumaśakyamāsīnnirīkṣya devī ditijān sughorān || 22 ||
bhayena sasmāra pitāmahantu |
devī sakhībhissahitā ca viṣṇum ||
sainyaṃ ca madvīravarasya sarve sa smārayāmāsa guhāṃtarasthā ||23||
brahmā tathā saṃsmṛtamātra eva strīrūpadhārī bhagavāṃśca viṣṇuḥ ||
indraiśva sarvaiḥ saha sainyakaiśva strīrūpamāsthāya samāgatāste || 24 ||
bhūtvā striyaste viviśustadānīṃ munīndrasaṃghāśca mahānubhāvāḥ ||
siddhāśca nāgāstvatha guhyakāśca guhāṃtaraṃ parvatarājaputryāḥ || 25 ||
yasmātsurājyāsanasaṃsthitānāmataḥpure saṃgamanaṃ viruddham ||
tatassahasrāṇi nitaṃvinīnāmanaṃta saṃkhyānyapi darśayatyaḥ || 26 ||
rūpāṇi divyāni mahādbhutāni gauryai guhāyāṃ tu savīrakāyai ||
striyaḥ prahṛṣṭā girirājakanyāṃ guhāṃtaraṃ parvatarājaputryā || 27 ||
strībhissahasraiśca śatairanekainaiduśva kalpāṃtara meghaghoṣāḥ ||
bheryyaśca saṃgrāmajayapradāstu ghmātāssuśaṃkhāḥ sunita mvinībhiḥ || 28 ||
mūrchā vihāyādbhuta caṃḍavīryassa vīrako vai purataḥ sthitastu ||
pragṛhya śastrāṇi mahārathānāṃ taireva śastrairditijaṃ jaghāna || 29 ||
