madapraharttā || 50 ||
śiva uvāca |
vyaktaṃ vacaste tadatīva caugraṃ proktaṃ hi tattvaṃ tvaritaṃ prayāhi |
kuruṣva yuddhaṃ hi mayā prasahya yadi praśaknoṣi balena hi tvam || 51 ||
yaḥ syādaśakto bhuvi tasya ko'rtho dāraidhanairvāsumanoharaiśca |
āyāntu daityāśca balena mattā vicāryaivaṃ tu kṛtaṃ mayaitat || 52 ||
śarīrayātrāpi kutastvaśakteḥ kurvantu yadyaddhitaṃ tu teṣām |
