iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṇḍe yuddhaprārambhabhūtasaṃvādavarṇanaṃ nāma pañcacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 45 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
tasyoṅgitajñaśca sa daityarājo gadāṃ gṛhītvā tvaritassasainyaḥ |
kṛtvātha sāṅge gilanāmadheyaṃ sudāruṇaṃ devavairairabhedyam || 1 ||
guhāmukhaṃ prāpya maheśvarasya bibheda śastrairaśanipratāpaiḥ |
anye tato vīrakameva śastrairavākiraṃśchelasutāṃ tathānye || 2 ||
dvāraṃ hi kecidvicairaṃ babhañjuḥ puṣpāṇi patrāṇi vināśayeyuḥ |
phalāni mūlāni jalaṃ ca hṛdyamudyānamārgānapi khaṇḍayeyuḥ || 3 ||
viloḍayeyurmuditāśca kecicchṛṅgāṇi śailasya ca bhānumanti |
tato harassaṃsmṛtavānsvasainyaṃ samāhvayankupitaḥ śūlapāṇiḥ || 4 ||
bhūtāni cānyāni sudāruṇāni devānsasainyānsaha viṣṇumukhyān |
āhūtamātrānugaṇāssasainyā rathairgajairvājivṛṣaiśca gobhiḥ || 5 ||
uṣṭraiḥ kharaiḥ pakṣivaraiśca siṃhaistesarvedevāḥ sahabhūtasaṃghaiḥ |
vyāghrairmṛgaissūkarasārasaiśca samīnamatsyaiśiśumāramukhyaiḥ || 6 ||
anyaiśca nānāvidhajīvasaṃghairviśīrṇaveśāḥ sphuṭitessmaśānaiḥ |
bhujaṃgamaiḥ pretaśatairpiśācairdivyairvimānaiḥ kamalākaraiśca || 7 ||
nadīnadaiḥ parvatavāhanaiśca samāgatāḥ prāñjalayaḥ praṇamya |
kapardinaṃ tasthuradīnasattvāssenāpatiṃ vīrakameva kṛtvā || 8 ||
visṛjayāmāsa raṇāya devānviśrāntavāhānatha tānpināki |
yuddhe sthiraṃ labdhajayaṃ pradhānaṃ saṃpreṣitāste tu maheśvareṇa || 9 ||
cakṣuryugāntapratimaṃ ca yuddhaṃ maryādahīnaṃ sāgilena sarvaiḥ |
daityendrasainyena sadaiva ghoraṃ krodhānnigīrṇāstridaśāstu saṃkhyāḥ || 10 ||
tasminkṣaṇe yudhyamānāśca sarve brahmendraviṣṇvarkaśaśāṅkamukhyāḥ |
āsannigīrṇā vighasena tena sainye nigīrṇo'sti tu vīrako hi || 11 ||
vihāya saṃgrāmaśiro guhāṃ tāṃ praviśya śarvaṃ praṇipatya mūrdhnā |
provāca duḥkhābhihataḥ smarāriṃ suvīrako vāgamiravo'tha vṛttam || 12 ||
nigīrṇaṃ te sainyaṃ vibhrasaditijenādya bhagavannigīrṇo'sau viṣṇustribhuvanagururdaityadalanaḥ |
nigīrṇau candrārkau dvirahasaghavāno ca varadau nigīrṇaste sarve yamavaruṇavātāśca dhanadaḥ || 13 ||
sthitosmyekaḥ prabhuḥ kimiha karaṇīyaṃ bhavatu me ajeyo daityendraḥ pramuditamanā

