daityasahitaḥ ||14||
ajeyaṃ tvāṃ prāptaḥ pratibhayamanā mārutagatissvayaṃ viṣṇurdevaḥ kanakakaśipuṃ kaśyapasutam ||
nakhaistīkṣṇairbhaktyā tadapi bhagavāñchi ṭavaśagaḥ pravṛttastrailokyaṃ vidhamatu malaṃ vyāttavadanaḥ || 15 ||
vasiṣṭhādyaiśśapto bhuvanapatibhissaptamunibhistathābhūte bhūyastvamiti suciraṃ daityasahitaḥ|| 16 ||
tatastenoktāste praṇayavacanairātmani hitaiḥ kadāsmādvai ghorādbhavati mama mokṣo munivarāḥ||
yataḥ kruddhairukto vighasaharaṇādyuddhasamaye tato ghorairbāṇairvidalita mukhe muṣṭibhiralam || 17||
badaryākhyāraṇye nanu harigṛhāpuṇyavasatau nisaṃstabhyātmānaṃ vigatakaluṣo yāsyasi param ||
tatasteṣāṃ vākyātpratidinamasau daitya gilanaḥ kṣudhārtassaṃgrāmāddhamati punarāmodamuditaḥ|| 18 ||
namasvedaṃ ghoraṃ jagaduditayossūryaśaśinoryathāśukrastubhyaṃ paramaripuratyaṃtavikaraḥ||
hatāndevairdaityā npunaramṛtavidyāstutipadaissavīryānsaṃhṛṣṭāntraṇaśataviyuktānprakurute || 19 ||
varaṃ prāṇāstyājyāstava mama tu saṃgrāmasamaye bhavānsākṣī bhūtaḥ kṣaṇamapi vṛtaḥ kāryakaraṇe || 20 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
itīdaṃ satputrātpramathapatirākarṇya kupitaściraṃ dhyātvā cakre tribhuvanapatiḥ prāganupamam ||
pragāyatsā mākhyaṃ dinakarakarākāravapuṣā prahāsāttannānnāṃ tadanuṃ nihataṃ tena ca tamaḥ || 21 ||
prakāśesmiloke punarapi mahāyuddhamakarodraṇe daityai ssārddhaṃ vikṛtava danaivarakamuniḥ ||
śilācūrṇe bhuktvā pravaramuninā yastu janitassa kṛtvā saṃgrāmaṃ puramapi purā yaśca jitavān ||22||
mahārudrassadyaḥ sa khalu diti jenātigilitastataścāsau nandī niśitaśaraśūlāsisahitaḥ ||
pradhāno yodhānāṃ munivaraśatānāmapi mahānnivāso vidyānāṃ śamadamamahādhairyasa hitaḥ || 23 ||
nirīkṣyaivaṃ paśvādvṛṣabhavaramāruhya bhagavānkapardī yuddhārthī vighasaditijaṃ sammukhamukhaḥ ||
japandivyaṃ mantraṃ nigalanavidhānodgilanaka sthitassajjaṃ kṛtvā dhanuraśanikalpānapi śarān || 24 ||
tato niṣkrāṃto'sau vighasavadanādvīrakamunigṛhītvā tatsarve svabalamatulaṃ viṣṇusahitaḥ ||
samudgīrṇāssarve kamalajabalārīndudinapāḥ prahṛṣṭaṃ tatsainyaṃ punarapi mahāyuddhamakarot || 25 ||
jite tasmiñchukrastadanu ditijānyuddhavihatān yadā vidyāvīryātpunarapi sajīvānprakurute ||
tadā baddhānītaḥ paśuriva gaṇairbhūtapataye nirgīrṇastenāsau tripuraripuṇādānavaguruḥ || 26 ||
vinaṣṭe śukrākhye suraripunivāsastadakhilo jito dhvasto bho bhṛśamapi suraiśvāpi dalitam ||
prabhūtairbhūtau cairditijakuṇapatrāsarasikai ssaruḍairmṛtyudbhirniśitaśa raśaktyuddhṛtakaraiḥ || 27 ||
pramattaivaitāssudṛḍhakaratuḍairapi khagairvṛkairnānā bhedeśśavakuṇapapūrṇāsyakavalaiḥ ||
vikīrṇa saṃgrāme kanakakaśiporvaṃśajanakaśviraṃ yuddhaṃ kṛtvā hariharamahendraiśca vijitaḥ || 28 ||
praviṣṭe pātāle girijaladhiraṃbhrāṇyapi tathā tatassainye kṣīṇe ditijavṛṣabhaśvāṃdhakavaraḥ ||
prakope devā nāṃ kadanadavaro viśvadalano gadāghātai caurai vaiidalitamadaścāpi hariṇā || 29 ||
