. pīḍitatanuḥ ||
tataśśastrāstraughaistarugirijalaiśvāśu vibudhāñji gāyoccairgarjanpramathapatimāhūya śanakaiḥ || 30 ||
sthito yuddhaṃ kurvatraṇapatitaśastrairbahu vidhaiḥ parikṣīṇaissarvaistadanu girijārudramatudat ||
tathā vṛkṣaissapairaśaninivahaiḥ śastrapaṭṭalairvirūpairmāyābhiḥ kapaṭaracanāśambaraśataiḥ || 31 ||
vijetuṃ śaileśaṃ kuhakamaparaṃ tatra kṛtavānmahāsattvo vīrastripurariputulyaśca matimān ||
na vadhyo devānāṃ varaśatamanonmādavivaśaḥ prabhūtaiśśastrāstraissapadi ditijo jarjaratamuḥ || 32 ||
tadīyādviṣyandātkṣititalagatairandhakagaṇairativyāptaṃ ghoraṃ vikṛvadanaṃ svātmasadṛśam ||
dadhatkalpatānipratimavapuṣā bhūtapatinā triśūlenodbhinnastripuraripuṇā dāruṇataram||33||
yadā sainyātsainyaṃ paśupatihatādanyadabhavadvaṇotthairatyuṣṇaiḥ piśitanissṛtairbindubhiralam ||
tadā viṣṇuyoṃ gātpramathapatimāhūya matimān cakāroyaṃ rūpaṃ vikṛtavadanaṃ straiṇamajitam || 34 ||
karālaṃ saṃśuṣkaṃ bahubhujalatākrāṃta kupito viniṣkrāṃtaḥkarṇādguṇaśirasi śaṃbhośca bhagavān ||35||
raṇasthā sā devī caraṇayugulālaṃkṛtamahī stutā devaissarvaistadanu bhagavān preritamatiḥ ||
kṣudhārtā tatsainyaṃ ditijanisṛtaṃ tacca rudhiraṃ papau sātyuṣṇaṃ tadraṇaśirasi satkardamamalam || 36 ||
tatastveko daityastadapi yuyudhe śuṣkarudhirastalāghātairghorairaśanisadṛśairjānucaraṇaiḥ ||
nakhaivai jrākārairmukhabhujaśirobhiśva giriśaṃ smaran kṣātraṃ dharmaṃ svakulavihitaṃ śāśvatamajam ||37||
raṇe śāṃtaḥ paścātpramathapatinā bhinnahṛdayatriśūle saṃproto nabha si vidhṛtassthāṇusadṛśaḥ ||
adhaḥ kāyaśśuṣka stapana kiraṇairjīrṇatanumā alāsārairmedhaiḥ pavanasahitaiḥ kveditavapuḥ || 38 ||
viśīrṇastigmāṃśostuhinaśa kalākāraśakalastathābhūtaḥ prāṇāṃstadapi na jahau daityavṛṣabhaḥ ||
tadā tuṣṭaśśaṃbhuḥ paramakaruṇāvāriṃdhirasau dadau tasmai prītyā gaṇapatipadaṃ tena vinutaḥ || ||39||
tato yuddhasyāṃte bhuvanapatayassārtharamaṇaistavainīnābhedaiḥ pramathapatimabhyarcya vidhivat ||
haribrahmādyāste paramanutibhistuṣṭuvuralaṃ nataskaṃdhāḥ prītā jaya jaya giraṃ procya sukhitāḥ || 40 ||
harastaistaissārddhaṃ girivaraguhāyāṃ pramudito visṛjyaikānaṃśān vividhabalinā pūjyasunagāna ||
cakārājñāṃ krīḍāṃ girivarasutāṃ prāpya muditāṃ tathā putraṃ ghorādvighasavadanānmuktamanagham || 41 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍa aṃdhakavadhopākhyāne aṃdhakayuddhavarṇanaṃ nāma ṣaṭcatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 46 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
tasminmahati saṃgrāme dāruṇe lomaharṣaṇe |
śukro daityapatirvidvānbhakṣitastripurāriṇā || 1 ||
iti śrutaṃ samāsānme tatpunabrūhi vistarāt ||
kiṃ cakāra mahāyogī jaṭharasthaḥ pinākinaḥ || || 2 ||
na dadāha kathaṃ śaṃbhośśukraṃ taṃ jaṭharānalaḥ ||
kalpāntadahanaḥ kālo dīptatejāśca bhārgavaḥ || 3 ||
viniṣkrāṃtaḥ kathaṃ dhīmāñchaṃbhorjaṭhara paṃjarāt ||
kathamārādhayāmāsa kiyatkālaṃ sa bhārgavaḥ || 1 ||
atha ca labdhavānvidyāṃ tāṃ mṛtyuśamanīṃ parām ||
kā sā vidyā parā tāta yayā . '

