mṛtyurhi vāryate || 5 ||
lebhendhako gāṇapatyaṃ kathaṃ śūlādvinirgataḥ ||
devadevasya vai śaṃbhormunerlīlāvihāriṇaḥ || 6 ||
etatsarvamaśeṣeṇa mahādhī mana kṛpāṃḥ kuru ||
śivalīlāmṛtaṃ tāta śṛṇvataḥ kathayasva me || 7 ||
brahmovāca ||
iti tasya vacaḥ śrutvā vyāsasyāmitatejasaḥ ||
sanatkumāraḥ provāca smṛtvā śivapadāṃbujam || 8 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe śivalīlāmṛtaṃ param ||
dhanyastvaṃ śaivamukhyosi mamānandakaraḥ svataḥ || 9 ||
pravartamāne samare śaṃkarāṃghakayostayoḥ ||
anirbhedyapavivyūhagirivyūhādhināthayoḥ || 10 ||
purā jayo babhūvāpi daityānāṃ balaśāli nām |
śivaprabhāvādabhavatpramathānāṃ mune jayaḥ || 11||
tacchrutvāsīdviṣaṇṇo hi mahādaityoṃdhakāsuraḥ ||
kathaṃ syānme jaya iti vicāraṇaparo'bhavat || 12 ||
apasṛtya tato yuddhādaṃdhakaḥ parabuddhimānaṃ ||
drutamabhyagamaṃdīra ekalaśśukrasannidhim || 13 ||
praṇamya svaguruṃ kāvyamavaruhya rathācca saḥ ||
babhāṣedaṃ vi cāryātha sāṃjalirnītivittamaḥ || 14 ||
aṃdhaka uvāca ||
bhagavaṃstvāmupāśritya gurobhāvaṃ vahāmahe ||
parājitā bhavāmo no sarvadā jayaśālinaḥ || || 15 ||
tvatprabhāvātsadā devānsamastānsānugānvayam ||
manyāmahe haropendramukhānapi hi katṛṇān || 16 ||
asmatto bibhyati surāssadā bhavadanugrahāt ||
gajā iva haribhyaśca tākṣryebhya iva pannagāḥ || 17 ||
anirbhedyaṃ pavivyūhaṃ viviśurdaityadānavāḥ ||
pramathānīkamakhilaṃ vidhūya tvadanugrahāt || 18 ||
vayaṃ tvaccharaṇā bhūtvā sadā gā iva niścalāḥ ||
sthitvā carāmo niśśaṃkamājāvapi hi bhārgava || 19 ||
rakṣa rakṣābhito vipra pratrajya śaraṇāgatān ||
asurāñchatrubhirvīrairarditāṃśca mṛtānapi || 20 ||
pramathairbhīmavikrāṃtaiḥ krāṃtānmṛtyupramāthibhiḥ ||
sūditānpa titānpaśya huṃḍāṃdīnmadguṇānvarān || 21 ||
yaḥ pītvā kaṇadhūmaṃ vai sahasraṃ śaradāṃ purā ||
tvayā prāptā vasa vidyātasyāḥ kāloyamāgataḥ || 22 ||
adya vidyāphalaṃ tatte sarve paśyaṃtu bhārgava |
pramathā asurānsarvān kṛpayā jīvayiṣyataḥ || 23 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
itthamandhakavākyaṃ sa śrutvā dhīro, hi bhārgavaḥ ||
tadā vicārayāmāsa dūyamānena cetasā || 24 ||
kiṃ kartavyaṃ mayādyāpi dakṣemaṃ me syātkathaṃ tviti ||
sannipātavidhirjīvaḥ sarvathānu cito mama || 25 ||
vidheyaṃ śaṃkarātprāptā tadguṇān prati yojaye ||
tadvaṇe marditānvīraiḥ pramathaiśśaṃkarānugaiḥ || 26 ||
śaraṇāgatadharmautha pravarassarvato hṛdā ||
vicārya śukreṇa dhiyā tadvāṇī svīkṛtā tadā || 27 ||
kiṃcitsmitaṃ tadā kṛtvā so'bravīddānavādhipam ||
bhārgavaśśivapādābjaṃ smṛtvā svasthe na cetasā || 28 || ||
śukra uvāca ||
yattvayā bhāṣitaṃ tāta tatsarvaṃ tathyameva hi ||
etadvidyopārjanaṃ hi dānavāyai kṛtaṃ mayā || 29 ||
dussahaṃ kaṇadhūmaṃ vai pītvā varṣasahasrakam |
vidyeyamīśvarātprāptā baṃdhūnāṃ sukhadā sadā || 30 ||
pramathairmathitāndaityānraṇehaṃ vidyayānayā ||
