mlānāni śasyāni jalamugyathā || 31 ||
natraṇānnīrujaḥ svasthāntveva punarusthitān ||
muhūrtesminsa draṣṭāsi daityāṃstānutthitānnijān ||32||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā soṃdhakaṃ śukro vidyāmāvartayatkaviḥ ||
ekaikaṃ daityamuddiśya smṛtvā vidyeśamādarāt || 33 ||
vidyāvartanamātreṇa te sarve daityadānavāḥ ||
uttasthuryugapadvīrāssuptā iva dhṛtāyudhāḥ || 34 ||
sadābhyastā yathā vedāssamare vā yathāṃmbudāḥ ||
śraddhayārthāstathā dattā brāhmaṇebhyo yathāpadi || 35 ||
ujjīvitāṃstu tāndṛṣṭvā huṃḍādīṃśca mahāsurān ||
vinedusurāssarve jalapūrṇā ivāṃbudāḥ || 36 ||
raṇodyatāḥ punaścāsangarjato vikaṭānravān ||
pramathaissaha nirbhītā mahābalaparākramāḥ || 37 ||
śukreṇojjīvitāndṛṣṭvā pramathā daityadānavān ||
visiṣmire tatassarve naṃdyādyā yuddhadurmadāḥ || 38 ||
vijñāpyamevaṃ karmaitadeveśe śaṃkare'khilam ||
vicārya buddhimaṃtaśca hyevaṃ te'nyonyamabruvan || 39 ||
āścaryarūpe pramatheśvarāṇāṃ tasmi stathā vartati yuddhayajñe ||
amarṣito bhārgavakarma dṛṣṭvā śilādaputro'bhyagamanmaheśam || 40 ||
jayeti coktvā jayayonimugramuvāca naṃdī kanakāvadā tam ||
gaṇeśvarāṇāṃ raṇakarma deva devaiśva sendrairapi duḥṣkaraṃ yat || 41 ||
tadbhārgaveṇādya kṛtaṃ vṛthā nassaṃjīvatāṃstāhni mṛtānvipakṣān ||
āvartya vidyāṃ mṛtajīvadātrīmekaikamuddiśya sahelamīśa || 42 ||
tuhuṃḍahuṃḍādikakuṃbhajaṃbhavipākapākādimahāsurendrāḥ ||
yamālayādadya punarnivṛttā vidrāvayaṃtaḥ pramathāṃśvaraṃti || 43 ||
yadi hyasau daityavararānnirastānsaṃjīvayedatra punaḥ punastān ||
jayaḥ kuto no bhavitā maheśa gaṇeśvarāṇāṃ kuta eva śāṃtiḥ || || 44 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityevamuktaḥ prathameśvareṇa sa naṃdinā vai pramatheśvareśaḥ ||
uvāca devaḥ prahasaṃstadānīṃ taṃ naṃdinaṃ sarvagaṇeśarājama 1184 11 ||
śiva uvāca ||
nandinprayāhi tvarito'timātraṃ dvijendravaryaṃ ditinandanānām ||
madhyātsamuddhṛtya tathānayāśu śyeno yathā lāvakamaṃḍa jātam || 46 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
sa evamukto vṛṣabhadhvajena nanāda naṃdī vṛṣasiṃhanādaḥ ||
jagāma tūrṇaṃ ca vigāhya senāṃ yatrābhavadbhārgavavaṃ śadīpaḥ || 47 ||
taṃ rakṣyamāṇaṃ ditijaissamastaiḥ pāśāsivṛkṣopalaśailahastaiḥ ||
vikṣobhya daityānbalavāahāra kāvyaṃ sa nandī śarabho yathebham || || 48 ||
srastāṃbaraṃ vicyutabhūṣaṇaṃ ca vimuktakeśaṃ balinā gṛhītam ||
vimocayiṣyaṃta ivānujagmuḥ surārayassiharavāṃstyajaṃtaḥ || 49 ||
daṃbholiśūlā siparaśvadhānāmuddaṃḍacakropalakaṃpanānām ||
naṃdīśvarasyopari dānavendrā varṣe vavarṣurjaladā ivotram || 90 ||
taṃ bhārgavaṃ prāpya gaṇādhirājoṃ mukhāgninā śastraśatāni dagdhvā ||
āyātpravṛddhe'suradevayuddhe bhavasya pārśve vyathitāripakṣaḥ || 51 ||
ayaṃ sa śukro bhagavannitīdaṃ nivedayāmāsa bhavāya śīghram ||
