iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṇḍe aṃdhakayuddhe śukranigīrṇanavarṇanaṃ nāma saptacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 47 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
śukre nigīrṇe rudreṇa kimakārṣuśca dānavāḥ ||
aṃdhakeśā mahāvīrā vada tattvaṃ mahāmune || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
kāvye nigīrṇe girijeśvareṇa daityā jayāśārahitā babhūvuḥ ||
hastairvimuktā iva vāraṇendrāḥ śṛṃgairvihīnā iva govṛṣāśca || 2 ||
śiroviddīnā iva dehasaṃghā dvijā yathā cādhyayanena hīnāḥ ||
nirudyamāssattvagaṇā yathā vai yathodyamā bhāgyavivarjitāśca || 3 ||
patyā vihīnāśca yathaiva yoṣā yathā vipakṣāḥ khalu mārgaṇaiaughāḥ ||
āyūṃṣi hīnāniṃ yathaiva puṇyairvratairvihīnāni yathā śrutāni || 4 ||
vinā yathā vaibhavaśaktimekāṃ bhavati hīnāssva phalaiḥ kriyaughāḥ||
yathā viśūrāḥ khalu kṣatriyāśca satyaṃ vinā dharmagaṇo yathaiva ||5||
nandinā ca hṛte śukre gilite ca viṣādinā ||
viṣādamagamandatyā yataṃmānaraṇotsavāḥ || 6 ||
tān vīkṣya vigatotsāhānaṃdhakaḥ pratyabhāṣata ||
daityāṃstu huḍahuṃḍādīnmahādhīraparākramaḥ||7||
aṃdhaka uvāca ||
kaviṃ vikramya nayatā nandinā vaṃcitā vayam ||
tanurvinā kṛtāḥ prāpṇāssarveṣāmadya no nanu || 8 ||
dhairya vīryaṃ gatiḥ kīrtistattvaṃ tejaḥ parākramaḥ ||
yugapanno hṛtaṃ sarvamekasmin bhārgave hṛte || 9 ||
dhigasmān kulapūjyo yairekopi kulasattamaḥ ||
gurussarvasamarthaśca trātā trāto na cāpadi || 10 ||
tadyūyamavilaṃbyeha yudhyadhvamārībhissaha ||
vīraistaiḥ pramathaivīrāḥ smṛtvā gurupadāṃbujam || 11 || ||
guroḥ kāvyasya sukhada smṛtvā caraṇapaṃkajau ||
sūdayiṣyāmyahaṃ sarvān pramathān saha nandinā || 12 ||
advaitān vivaśān hatvā sahadevaissavāsavaiḥ ||
bhārgavaṃ mocayiṣyāmi jīvaṃ yogīva karmataḥ || 13 ||
sa cāpi yogī yogena yadi nāma svayaṃ prabhuḥ ||
śarīrāttasya nirgacchedasmākaṃ śeṣapālitāḥ || 14 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityandhakavacaḥ śrutvā dānavā meghani ssvanāḥ ||
pramathā nirdeyāḥ prāhurmartavye kṛtaniścayāḥ || 15 ||
satyāyuṣi na no jātu śaktāsyuḥ pramathā balāt ||
asatyāyuṣi kiṃ gatvā tyaktvā svāminamāhave || 16 ||
ye svāminaṃ vihāyāto bahumānadhanā janāḥ ||
yāṃti te yāṃti niyatamaṃdhatāmisramālayam || 17 ||
ayaśastamasā khyātiṃ malinīkṛtya bhūriśaḥ ||
ihāmutrāpi sukhino na syurbhagnā raṇājire || 18 ||
kiṃ dānaiḥ kiṃ tapobhiśca kiṃ tīrthaṃparimajjanaiḥ ||
dhārātīrthe yadi snānaṃ punarbhavamalāpahe || 19 ||
saṃpradhāryeti tadvākyaṃ daityāste danujāstathā ||
mamaṃthuḥ pramathānājo raṇabherīṃ ninādya ca || 20 ||
tatra bāṇāsivajraughaiḥ kaṭhinaiśca śilāmayaiḥ ||
bhuśuṇḍibhidipālaiśca śaktibhalaparaśvadhaiḥ || 21 ||
khāgaiḥ paṭṭiśaiśśūlairlakuṭairmuśalairalam ||
