kka kṛpaṇo daityo'haṃ candraśekhara ||
tatsoḍhā nāhamaddhenducūḍa śaṃbho maheśvaram ||31||
kka bhavānparamodāraḥ kva cāhaṃ vivaśīkṛtaḥ ||
kāmakrodhādibhirdoṣa rjarasā mṛtyunā tathā || 32||
ayaṃ te vīrakaḥ putro yuddhaśauṃḍo mahābalaḥ ||
kṛpaṇaṃ māṃ samālakṣya mā manyuvaśamanvagāḥ || 33 ||
tuṣārahāraśītāṃśuśaṃkhakunde nduvarṇabhāk ||
paśyemāṃ pārvatīṃ nityaṃ mātaraṃ gurugauravāt || 34 ||
nityaṃ bhavabhyāṃ bhaktastu nirvairo daivataiḥ saha ||
nivaseyaṃ gaṇaissārddhaṃ śāṃtātmā yogaciṃtakaḥ || 35 ||
mā smareyaṃ punarjātaṃ viruddhaṃ dānavodbhavam ||
tvatkṛpāto maheśāna dehyetadvaramuttamam || 36 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
etāvaduktvā vacanaṃ daityendro maunamāsthitaḥ ||
