tato dṛṣṭastu rudreṇa prasannenaiva cakṣuṣā ||
smṛtavānpūrvavṛttāṃtamātma no janma cādbhutam || 38 ||
tasminsmṛte ca vṛttāṃte tataḥ pūrṇamanorathaḥ ||
praṇamya mātāpitarau kṛtakṛtyo'bhavattataḥ || 39 ||
pārvatyā sūryupātrāta śśaṃkareṇa ca dhīmatā ||
tathābhilaṣitaṃ lebhe tuṣṭādvālenduśekharāt ||40||
etadvassarvamākhyāta mandhakasya purātanam ||
gāṇapatyaṃ mahādevaprasādātparasau khyadam||41||
mṛtyuṃjayaśca kathito maṃtro mṛtyuvināśanaḥ||
paṭhitavyaḥ prayatnena sarvakāmaphalapradaḥ||42||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṇḍe aṃdhakagaṇajīvitaprāptivarṇanaṃ nāma ikonapañcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 49 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu vyāsa yathāprāptā mṛtyupraśamanī parā ||
vidyā kāvyena suninā śivānmṛtyuñjayābhidhāt || 1 ||
purāsau bhṛgudāyādo gatvā vāraṇāsī purīm ||
vahukālaṃ tapastepe ghyāyanviśveśvaraṃ prabhum ||2||
sthāpayāmāsa tatraiva liṃgaṃ śaṃbhoḥ parātmanaḥ ||
kūpaṃ cakāra sadamya vedavyāsa tadagrataḥ || 3 ||
paṃcāmṛtairdrauṇamitairlakṣakṛtvaḥ prayatnataḥ ||
snāpa yāmāsa deveśaṃ sugaṃdhasnapanairvahu || 4 ||
sahasrakṛtvo deveśaṃ candanairyakṣakadamaiḥ ||
samāliliṃpa suprītyā sugandhodvarttanānyatu || 5 ||
rājacaṃpaka dhattūraiḥ karavīrakuśeśayaiḥ ||
