mallikāśatapatrībhiriṃsadhuvāraissakiṃśukeḥ ||
bandhūkapuṣpaiḥ punnāgairnāga keśarakeśaraiḥ ||7||
nava mallī cibilikaiḥ kuṃdaissamucukundakaiḥ ||
mandārairbilvipatraiśca droṇairmaruvakairvṛkaiḥ ||
granthiparṇairdamanakaḥ suramyaiśvatapavaiḥ ||8||
tulasīdevagaṃdhārī bṛhatpatrī kuśāṃkuraiḥ ||
nadyāvatairagastyaiśca saśālairdevadārubhiḥ || 9 ||
kāṃcanāraiḥ kuravakairvīkura kuruṃṭakaiḥ ||
pratyekamebhiḥ kusumaiḥ pallavairaparairapi || 10 ||
patraiḥ sahasrapatraiśca ramyairnānāvidhaiśśubhaiḥ ||
sāvadhānena suprītyā sa samānace śaṃkaram || 11 ||
gītanṛtyopahāraiśca saṃstutaḥ stutibhirbrahu ||
nāmnāṃ sahasairanyaiśva stotraistuṣṭāva śaṃkaram || 12 ||
sahasraṃ pañcaśaradāmitthaṃ śukro maheśvaram ||
