tvatprasādādvalī cāhaṃ śṛṇu meṃ paramaṃ vacaḥ || 4 ||
dossahasraṃ tvayā dattaṃ paraṃ bhārāya me'bhavat ||
trilokyāṃ pratiyoddhāraṃ na labhe tvadṛte samam || 5 ||
he deva kimanenāpi sahasreṇa karomyaham ||
bāhūnāṃ giritulyānāṃ vinā yuddhaṃ vṛṣadhvajaṃ || 6 ||
kaḍūṃtyā nibhṛtaidarbhiryuyutsurdiggajānaham ||
purāṇyācūrṇayannadvīnbhītāstepi pradudruvuḥ || 7 ||
mayā yamaḥ kṛto yoddhā vahniśva kṛtako mahān ||
varuṇaścāpi gopālo gavāṃpālayitā tathā || 8 ||
gajādhyakṣaḥ kuberastu sairandhrī cāpi nirṛtiḥ ||
jitaśvākhaṃḍalo loke karadāyī sadā kṛtaḥ || 9 ||
yuddhasyāgamanaṃ brūhi yatraite bāhavo mama ||
śatruhastaprayuktaiśva śastrāstrerjarjarīkṛtāḥ ||10||
pataṃtu śatruhastādvā pātayantu sahasradhā ||
eta nmanorathaṃ me hi pūrṇa kuru maheśvara || 11 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tacchrutvā kupito rudrastvaṭṭahāsaṃ mahādbhutam ||
kṛtvā'bravīnmahāmanyurbhakta bādhā'pahārakaḥ || 12 || ||
rudra uvāca ||
dhigdhik tvaṃ sarvato garvinsarvadaityakulādhama ||
baliputrasya bhaktasya nocitaṃ vaca īdṛśam || 13 ||
darpasyāsya praśamanaṃ lapsyase cāśu dāruṇam ||
mahāyuddhamakasmādvai balinā matsamena hi || 14 ||
tatra te girisaṃkāśā bāhavo'nalakāṣṭhavat ||
chinnāṃ bhūmau patiṣyati śastrāstraiḥ kadalīkṛtāḥ || 15 ||
yadeṣa mānuṣaśiro mayūrasahito dhvajaḥ ||
vidyate tava duṣṭātmaṃstasya syātpatanaṃ yadā || 16 ||
sthāpitasyāyudhāgāre vinā vātakṛtaṃ bhayam ||
tadā yuddhaṃ mahāghoraṃ saṃprāptamiti cetasiṃ || 17 ||
nidhāya ghoraṃ saṃgrāmaṃ gacchethāḥ sarvasainyavān ||
--- Page 402 [gcv] ---
' sāṃprataṃ gaccha tadveśma yatastadvidyate śivaḥ || 18 ||
tathā tānsva mahotpātāṃstatra dṛṣṭvāsi durmate |
ityuktvā virarāmātha garvahṛdbhaktavatsalaḥ || 19 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tacchrutvā rudramabhyarcya divyairaṃjalikuḍmalaiḥ ||
praṇamya ca mahādevaṃ bāṇaśca svagṛhaṃ gataḥ ||20||
kuṃbhaṇḍāya yathāvṛttaṃ pṛṣṭaḥ provāca harṣitaḥ ||
paryaikṣiṣṭāsuro bāṇastaṃ yogaṃ hyutsukassadā || 21 ||
atha daivātkadācitsa svayaṃ bhagnaṃ dhvajaṃ ca tam ||
dṛṣṭvā tatrāsuro bāṇo hṛṣṭo yuddhāya niryayau || 22 ||
sa svasainyaṃ samāhūya saṃyuktaḥ sāṣṭabhirgaṇaiḥ ||
iṣṭiṃ sāṃgrāmikāṃ kṛtvā dṛṣṭvā sāṃgrāmikaṃ madhu || 23 ||
kakubha maṃgalaṃ sarva saṃprekṣya prasthito'bhavat ||
mahotsāho mahāvīro baliputro mahārathaḥ|| 24 ||
iti hṛtkamale kṛtvā kaḥ kasmādāgamiṣyati ||
yoddhā raṇapriyo yastuḥ nānāśastrāstra pāragaḥ || 25 ||
yastu vāhusahasraṃ me chinattvanalakāṣṭhavat ||
tathā śastrairmahātīkṣṇaichina śataśāstvidda ||26||
etasminnaṃtare kālaḥ saṃprāptaśśaṃkareṇa hi ||
yatra sā bāṇaduhitā sujātā kṛtamaṃgalā || 27 ||
mādhavaṃ mādhave māsi pūjayitvā mahāniśi ||
suptā catiḥpure gupte strībhāvamupalaṃbhitā || || 28 ||
gauryā saṃpreṣitenāpi vyākṛṣṭā divyamāyayā ||
kṛṣṇātmajātmajenātha rudaṃtī sāhyanāthavat || 29 ||
sa cāpi tāṃ balādbhukkā pārvatyāḥ sa khibhiḥ punaḥ ||
nītastu divyayogena dvārakāṃ nimiṣāṃtarāt || 30 ||
mṛditā sā tadotthāya rudaṃtī vividhā giraḥ ||
sakhībhyaḥ kathayitvā tu dehatyāge kṛtakṣaṇā ||31||
sakhyākṛtātmano doṣaṃ sā vyāsa smāritā punaḥ||
sarvaṃ tatpūrvavṛttāṃtaṃ tato dṛṣṭvā ca sābhavat || 32||
abravīccitralekhā ca tato madhurayā girā ||
ūṣā bāṇasya tanayā kuṃbhāṃḍatanayā mune || 33 ||
uṣovāca ||
sākha yadyeṣa me bhartā pārvatyāṃ vihitaḥ purā ||
kenopāyena te guptaḥ prāpyate vidhivanmayā || 34 ||
kasminkule sa vā jāto mama yena hṛtaṃ manaḥ ||
ityūṣāvacanaṃ śrutvā sakhī provāca tāṃ tadā || 35 ||
citralekhāvāca ||
tvayā svapne ca yo dṛṣṭaḥ puruṣo devi taṃ katham ||
ahaṃ samānayiṣyāmī na vijñātastu yo mama || 36 ||
daityakanyā tadukte tu rāgāṃdhā maraṇotsukā ||
rakṣitā ca tayā sakhyā prathame divaseṃ tataḥ || 37 ||
punaḥ provāca soṣāṃ vai citralekhā mahāmatiḥ ||
kuṃbhāṃḍasya sutā bāṇatanayāṃ munisattama || 38 ||
citralekhāvāca ||
vyasanaṃ te'pakarṣāmi trilokyāṃ yadi bhāṣyate ||
samāneṣya naraṃ yaste manohartā tamādiśa || 39 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā vastrapuṭake devāndaityāṃśca dānavān ||
gandharvasiddha nāgāṃśca yakṣādīṃśca tathālikhat || 40 ||
tathā narasteiṣu vṛṣṇīñśūramānakaduṃdubhim ||
vyalikhadrāmakṛṣṇau ca pradyumnaṃ narasattamam || 41||
aniruddhaṃ vilikhitaṃ prādyuni vīkṣya lajjitā ||
āsīdavā 1 sakhyaśiśkītivibhāvaārṣaḥ |
