||230||
śi0 pu0 ṅmukhī coṣā hṛdaye harṣapūritā || 42 ||
ūṣā provāca cauro'sau mayā prāptastu yo niśi ||
puruṣaḥ sakhi yenāśu cetoranaṃ hṛtaṃ mama || 43 ||
yasya saṃsparśanādevaṃ mohitāhaṃ tathābhavam ||
tamahaṃ jñātumicchāmi vada sarvaṃ ca bhāmini || 44 ||
kasyāyamantraye jāto nāma kiṃ cāsya vidya te ||
ityuktā sābravīnnām yoginī tasya cānvayam || 45 ||
sarvamākarṇya sā tasya kulādi munisattama ||
utsukā bāṇatanyā babhāṣe sā tu kāminī || 46 ||
ūṣovāca ||
upāyaṃ racaya prītyā tatprāptyai sakhiṃ tatkṣaṇāt ||
yenopāyena taṃ kāṃtaṃ labheya prāṇavallabham || 47 ||
yaṃ vināhaṃ kṣaṇaṃ naikaṃ sakhi jīvitumutsahe ||
tamānayeha sadyatnātsukhinoṃ kuru māṃ sakhi || 48 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā sā tayā bāṇātmajayā maṃtrikanyakā ||
vismitābhūnmuniśreṣṭha suvicāraparā'bhavat || 49 ||
tatassakhīṃ samābhāṣya citralekhā manojavā ||
buddhā taṃ kṛṣṇapautraṃ sā dvārakāṃ gaṃtumudyatā||50||
jyeṣṭha kṛṣṇa caturdaśyāṃ tṛtīye tu gate'hani ||
āprabhātānmuhūrte tu saṃprāptā dvārakāṃ purīm || 61 ||
ekena kṣaṇamātreṇa nabhasāṃ divyayo ginī ||
tataścāṃtaḥpurodyāne prādyumnirdadṛśe tayā ||52||
krīḍannārījanaissārddhaṃ prapibanmādhavīmadhu ||
sarvāṃgasundara śyāmaḥ susmito navayauvanaḥ ||53||
tataḥ |
khāṃ samārūḍhamaṃdhakāra paṭena sā ||
ācchādayitvā yogena tāmasena ca mādhavam ||54||
tatassā mūrdhni tāṃ khayaṃ gṛhītvā nimiṣāṃtarāt ||
saṃprāptā śo ṇitapuraṃ yatra sā bāṇanaṃdinī || 55 ||
kāmārtā vividhānbhāvāñcakāronmattamānasā ||
ānītamatha taṃ dṛṣṭvā tadā bhītā ca sābhavat || 56 ||
aṃtaḥpure sugupte ca nave tasminsamāgame ||
yāvatkrīḍitumārabdhaṃ tāvajjñātaṃ ca tatkṣaṇāt || 57 ||
aṃtaḥpuradvāragatairvaitrajarjarapāṇibhiḥ ||
iṃgitairanumā naiśca kanyādauḥ śīlyamācaran || 58 ||
sa cāpi dṛṣṭastaistatra naro divyavapurdharaḥ ||
taruṇo darśanīyastu sāhasī samarapriyaḥ || 59 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sarva mācakhyurbāṇāya valisūnave ||
puruṣāste mahāvīrāḥ kanyāntaḥpurarakṣakāḥ || 60 ||
dvārapālā ūcuḥ ||
deva kaścinna jānīte guptaścatiḥpure balā t ||
śakrastu tava kanyāṃ vai svayaṃgrāhādadharṣayat || 61 ||
dānavendra mahābāho paśyapaśyainamatra ca ||
yadyuktaṃ syāttatkuruṣva na duṣṭā vayamityuta || 62 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dānavendro mahābalaḥ ||
vismitobhūnmuniśreṣṭha kanyāyāḥ śrutadūṣaṇaḥ ||
63 iti śrīśivamahā purāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ paṃcame yuddhakhaṃḍe ūṣācaritravarṇanaṃ nāma dvipañcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 52 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
atha bāṇāsuraḥ kruddha statra gatvā dadarśa tam ||
divyalīlāttavapuṣaṃ prathame vayasi sthitam || 1 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā vismitaṃ vākyaṃ kiṃ kāraṇamathābravīt ||
bāṇaḥ krodhaparītā ||
