. tmā yudhiśauṃḍo hasanniva || 2 ||
aho manuṣyo rūpāḍhayassāhasī dhairyavāniti ||
koyamāgatakālaśca duṣṭabhāgyo vimūḍhadhīḥ || 3 ||
yena me kulacā ritraṃ dūṣitaṃ duhitā hitā ||
taṃ mārayadhvaṃ kupitāśśīghraṃ śastraissudāruṇaiḥ || 4 ||
durācāraṃ ca taṃ baddhā ghore kārāgṛhe tataḥ ||
rakṣadhvaṃ vikaṭe vīrā bahukā laṃ viśeṣataḥ || 5 ||
na jāne koyamabhayaḥ ko vā ghoraparākramaḥ |
vicāryeti mahābuddhissaṃdigdhobhūcchrāsuraḥ ||6||
tato daityena sainyaṃ tu daśasāhasrakaṃ śanaiḥ ||
vadhāya tasya vīrasya vyādiṣṭaṃ pāpabuddhinā || 7 ||
tadādiṣṭāstu te vīrāḥ sarvatontaḥ puraṃ drutam ||
chādayāmāsuratyugrāśchiāgha bhiṃdīti vādinaḥ ||8||
śatrusainyaṃ tato dṛṣṭvā garjamānaḥsa yādavaḥ ||
aṃtaḥpuraṃ dvāragataṃ parighaṃ gṛhya cātulam || 9 ||
niṣkrāṃto bhavanāttasmādvajrahasta ivāṃtakaḥ ||
tena tānkikarān hatvā punaścataḥ puraṃ yayau || 10 ||
evaṃ daśasahasrāṇi sainyāni munisattama ||
jaghāna roṣaraktākṣo varddhitaśśivatejasā || 11 ||
lakṣe hate'tha yodhānāṃ tato bāṇāsuro ruṣā |
kuṃbhāṃḍaṃ sa gṛhītvā tu yuddhe śauṃḍaṃ samāhvayat ||12||
aniruddhaṃ mahābuddhiṃ indrayuddhe mahāhave ||
prādyumni rakṣitaṃ śaivatejasā prajvalattanum || 13 ||
tato daśasahasrāṇi turaṃgāṇāṃ rathottamān ||
yuddhaprāptena khaṅgena daityendrasya jaghāna saḥ || 14 ||
tadvadhāya tataśśaktiṃ kālavaiśvānaropamām||
aniruddho gṛhītvā tāṃ tayā taṃ nijaghāna hi || 15 ||
rathopasthe tato bāṇastena śaktyā hato dṛḍham ||
sa. sāśvastatkṣaṇaṃ vīrastatraivāṃtaradhīyata || 16 ||
tasmiṃstvadarśanaṃ prāpte prādyumnira parājitam ||
ālokya kakubhassarvāstasthau giririvācalaḥ || 17 ||
adṛśyamānastu tadā kūṭayodhassa dānavaḥ ||
nānāśastrasahasraistaṃ jaghāna hi punaḥpunaḥ || 18 ||
chadmanā nāgapāśaistaṃ babaṃdha sa mahābalaḥ ||
baliputro mahāvīraśśivabhakta śśarāsuraḥ || 19 ||
taṃ badhvā paṃjarāṃtasthaṃ kṛtvā yuddhādupāramat ||
uvāca bāṇaḥ saṃkruddhassūtaputraṃ mahābalam || 20 ||
bāṇāsura uvāca ||
sūtaputra śira śichādhe puruṣasyāsya vai laghu ||
yena me dūṣitaṃ pūtaṃ balādduṣṭena satphalam || || 21 ||
chitvā tu sarvagātrāṇi rākṣasebhyaḥ prayaccha bhoḥ ||
athāsya rakta māṃsāni kravyādā api bhuṃjatām || 22 ||
agādhe tṛṇasaṃkīrṇe kūpe pātakinaṃ jahi ||
kiṃ bahūktyā sūtaputra māraṇīyo hi sarvathāṃ ||23||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dharmabuddhirniśācaraḥ ||
kuṃbhāṃḍastvatravīdvākyaṃ bāṇaṃ sanmaṃtrisattamam || 24 ||
kuṃbhāṃḍa uvāca ||
naitatkurtuṃ samucitaṃ karma deva vicāryatām |
asmin hate hato hyātmā bhavediti matirmama || 25 ||
ayaṃ tu dṛśyate deva tulyo viṣṇoḥ parākramaiḥ ||
vardhitaścandracūḍasya tvaddu ṣṭasya sutejasā || 26 ||
atha candralalāṭasya.. sāhasena samatsvayam ||
imāmavasthāṃ prāptosi pauruṣe saṃvyavasthitaḥ || 27 ||
ayaṃ śivaprasādādvai kṛṣṇapautro mahābalaḥ ||
asmāṃstṛṇopamān vetti daṣṭopi bhujagairvalāt || 28 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
etadvākyaṃ tu vāṇāya kathayitvā sa dānavaḥ ||
--- Page 405 [gcv] ---
śi0 pu0 ||231||
aniruddhamuvācedaṃ rājanītividuttamaḥ || 29 ||
kuṃbhāṃḍa uvāca ||
kosi kasyāsi re vīra satyaṃ vada mamāgrataḥ ||
kena vā tvamihānīto durācāra narādhama || 30 ||
daityendraṃ stuhi vīraṃ tvaṃ namaskuru kṛtāṃjaliḥ ||
jitosmīti vaco dīnaṃ kathayitvā punaḥ punaḥ || 31 ||
evaṃ kṛte tu mokṣassyādanyathā baṃdhanādi caṃ ||
tacchrutvā vacanaṃ tasya prativākyamuvāca saḥ || 32 ||
aniruddha uvāca ||
re re daityā'dhamasakhe kara piṃḍopajīvaka ||
niśācara durācāra śatrudharme na vetsi bhoḥ|| 33 ||
dainyaṃ palāyanaṃ cātha śūrasya maraṇādhikam ||
viruddhaṃ copaśalyaṃ ca bhavediti matirmama || 34 ||
kṣatriyasya raṇe śreyo maraṇaṃ sanmukhe sadā ||
na vīramānino bhūmau dīnasyeva kṛtāṃjaliḥ || 35 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityādivīra vākyāni bahūni sa jagāda tam ||
tadākarṇya sa bāṇassāṃ vismito'bhūcukopa ca || 36 ||
tadovāca nabhovāṇī bāṇasyāśvāsanāya hi ||
śṛṇvatāṃ sarvavīrāṇāmaniruddhasya maṃtriṇaḥ || 37 || ||
vyomavāṇyuvāca ||
bho bho bāṇa mahāvīra na krodhaṃ kartumarhasi ||
baliputrosiḥ sumate śivabhakta vicāryatām || 38 ||
śivassarveśvarassākṣī karmaṇāṃ parameśvaraḥ ||
tadādhīnamidaṃ sarvaṃ jagadvai sacarācaram || 39 ||
sa eva kartā bhartā ca saṃhartā jagatāṃ sadā ||
rajassattvatamodhārī vidhiviṣṇuharātmakaḥ || 40 ||
sarvasyāṃtargataḥ svāmī prerakassarvataḥ paraḥ ||
nirvikāryavyayo nityo māyādhīśopi nirguṇaḥ || 41 ||
tasyecchayā'balo jñeyo valī balivarātmaja ||
iti vijñāya manasi svastho bhava mahāmate || 42 ||
garvāpahārī bhagavānnānālī lāviśāradaḥ ||
nāśayiṣyati te garvamidānīṃ bhaktavatsalaḥ || 43 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityābhāṣya nabhovāṇī virarāma mahāmune ||
bāṇā surastadvacanādaniruddhaṃ na jaghnivān || 44 ||
kiṃtu svāntaḥpuraṃ gatvā papau pānamanuttamam ||
madvākyaṃ ca visasmāra vijahāra viruddhadhīḥ || 45 ||
tatoniruddho baddhastu nāgabhogairviṣolbaṇaiḥ ||
priyayā'tṛptacetāstu durgāṃ sasmāra tatkṣaṇāt || 46 || ||
aniruddha uvāca ||
śaraṇye devi baddhosmi dahyamānastu pannagaiḥ ||
āgaccha me kuru trāṇaṃ yaśode caṃḍaroṣiṇī || 47 ||
śivabhakte mahādevi sṛṣṭisthityaṃtakāriṇī ||
tvāṃ vinā rakṣako nānya stasmādrakṣa śive hi mām || 48 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tenetthaṃ toṣitā tatra kālī bhinnāṃjanaprabhā ||
jyeṣṭhakṛṣṇacaturdaśyāṃ saṃprāptāsīnmahāniśi || 49 ||
gurubhirmuṣṭinighatairdārayāmāsa paṃjaram ||
śarāṃstānbhasmasātkṛtvā sarparūpān bhayānakān || 50 ||
mocayitvāniruddhaṃ tu tataścāṃtaḥpuraṃ tataḥ ||
praveśayitvā durgā tu tatraivādarśanaṃ gatā || 61 ||
itthaṃ devyāḥ prasādāttu śivaśaktermunīśvara ||
kṛcchramuktoniruddho bhūtsukhī caiva ga . rudra saṃ0 2 yu0 khaṃ0 5 a0 53 ||231||
