tavyathaḥ || 52 ||
atha labdhajayo bhūtvāniruddhaśśivaśaktitaḥ ||
prādyumnirvāṇatanayāṃ priṃyoṃ prāpya sumoda ca || 53 ||
pūrvavadvijahāṃ rāsauṃ tayā svapriyayā sukhī ||
pītapānassuraktākṣassa bāṇasutayā tataḥ || 54 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhitāyāṃ pañcame yuddhakhaṃḍe ūṣācaritre aniruddhoṣāvihāravarṇanaṃ nāma tripaṃcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 53 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
aniruddhe hate pautre kṛṣṇasya munisattama ||
kuṃbhāṃḍasu tayā kṛṣṇaḥ kimakārṣīddhi tadvada || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tato gate'niruddhe tu tatstrīṇāṃ rodanasvanam ||
śrutvā ca vyathitaḥ kṛṣṇo babhūva munisattama || 2 ||
apaśyatāṃ cāniruddhaṃ tadbadhūnāṃ harestathā ||
catvāro vārṣikā māsā vyatīyuranuśocatām || 3 ||
nāradāttadupākarṇya vārtā baddhasya karma ca ||
āsanmuvyathitāssarve vṛṣṇayaḥ kṛṣṇadevatāḥ || 4 ||
kṛṣṇastadvṛttamakhilaṃ śrutvā yuddhaṃ na cādarāt ||
jagāma śoṇitapuraṃ tārkṣyamā hūya tatkṣaṇāt || 5 ||
pradyumno yuyudhānaśca gatassāṃbotha sāraṇaḥ ||
naṃdopanaṃdabhadrādyā rāmakṛṣṇānuvartinaḥ || 6 ||
akṣauhiṇībhirdvādaśabhissametā ssarvato diśam ||
rurudhurbāṇanagaraṃ samaṃtātsātvatarṣabhāḥ || 7 ||
bhajyamānapurodyāna prakārāṭṭālagopuram ||
vīkṣyamāṇo rūpāviṣṭastulyasainyo rabhiniryayau || 8 ||
bāṇārthe bhagavān rudrassasutaḥ prathamairvṛtaḥ ||
āruhya nandivṛṣabhaṃ yuddhaṃ karttu samāyayaiau || 9 ||
āsītsutumulaṃ yuddhamadbhutaṃ śomaharṣaṇam ||
kṛṣṇādikānāṃ taistatra rudrādyairbāṇarakṣakaiḥ || 10 ||
kṛṣṇaśaṃkarayorāsītpradyumnaguyorapi ||
kūṣmāṃḍakūpakarṇābhyāṃ balena saha saṃ yugaḥ || 11 ||
sāṃbasya bāṇaputreṇa bāṇena saha sātyakeḥ ||
nandinā garuḍasyāpi pareṣāṃ ca parairapi || 12 ||
brahmādayassurādhīśā munayaḥ siddhacāraṇāḥ ||
gaṃdharvāpsaraso yānairvimānairdraṣṭumāgaman || 13 ||
pramathairvividhākārai revatyaṃtaiḥ sudāruṇam ||
yuddhaṃ babhūva viprendra teṣāṃ ca yaduvaṃśi nām || 14 ||
bhratrā rāmeṇa sahitaḥ pradyumnena ca dhīmatā ||
kṛṣṇaśvakāra samaramatulaṃ pramathaissaha || 15 ||
tatrāgninā'bhavadyuddhaṃ yamena varuṇena ca ||
vimukhena tripādena jvareṇa ca guhena ca || 16 ||
pramathairvividhākāraisteṣāmatyaṃtadāruṇam ||
yuddhaṃ babhūva vikaṭaṃ vṛṣṇīnāṃ romaharṣaṇam || 17 ||
vibhīṣikābhirvahvībhiḥ koṭarībhiḥ padepade ||
nirlajjābhiśca nārībhiḥ prabalābhiradūrataḥ || 18 ||
śaṃkarānucarāñśaurirbhūtapramathaguhyakān ||
drāvayāmāsa tīkṣṇāyaiḥ śaraiḥ śārṅgadhanuścyutaiḥ ||19||
evaṃ pradyumnapramukhā vīrā yuddhamahotsavāḥ ||
cakruryuddhaṃ mahāghoraṃ śatrusainyaṃ vināśayan ||20||
viśī ryamāṇaṃ svabalaṃ dṛṣṭvā rudrotyamarṣaṇaḥ ||
krodhaṃ cakāra sumahannanāda ca maholbaṇam || 21 ||
tacchrutvā śaṃkaragaṇā vineduryuyudhuśca te ||
mardayanpratiyoddhāraṃ varddhitāśśaṃbhutejasā ||22||
pṛthagvidhāni cāyukta śāstrāṇi pinākine |
pratyakṣaiśśamayāmāsa śūlapāṇiravismitaḥ ||23||
brahmāstrasya ca brahmāstraṃ

