tvaṃ brahma paramātmā hi sarva vyāpyakhileśvaraḥ ||
brahmāṃḍatanurugreśo virāṭ sarvānvitaḥ paraḥ || 23 ||
nābhirnabho'gnirvadanamaṃbureto diśaḥ śrutiḥ ||
dyauśśīrṣa maṃtriruvīṃ te manaśvandrastava prabho || 24 ||
dṛgakoṃ jaṭharaṃ vārddharbhujeṃdro dhiṣaṇā vidhiḥ ||
prajāpatirvisargaśca dhamrmmo hi hṛdayaṃ tava || 25 ||
romāṇyauṣadhayo nātha keśā jalamucastava ||
guṇāstrayastrinetrāṇi sarvātmā puruṣo bhavān || 26 ||
brāhmaṇaṃ te mukhaṃ prāhurbāhuṃ kṣatriyameva ca ||
ūru jaṃ vaiśyamāhuste pādajaṃ śūdrameva ca || 27 ||
tvameva sarvadopāsyassarvajīvairmaheśvara ||
tvāṃ bhajanparamāṃ muktiṃ labhate puruṣo dhruvam || 28 ||
yastvāṃ visṛjate martya ātmānaṃ priyamīśvaram ||
viparyayendriyārthārtha viṣamattyamṛtaṃ tyajan || 29 ||
viṣṇurbrahmā' vibudhā munayaśvāmalāśayāḥ ||
sarvātmanā prapannāstvāṃ śaṃkaraṃ priyamīśvaram || 30 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktvā baliputrastu virarāma śarāsuraḥ ||
premapraphullitāṃgaśca praṇamya sa maheśvaram ||31||
iti śrutvā svabhaktasya bāṇasya bhagavānbhavaḥ ||
savai labhiṣyasītyuktvā tatraivāṃtaradhīyata || 32 ||
tataśśaṃbhoḥ prasādena mahākālatvamāgataḥ ||
rudrasyānucaro bāṇo mahāpramudito'bhavat || 33 ||
iti kila śaranāmnā śaṃkarasyāpi vṛttaṃ sakalaguru janānāṃ saṃ dvarośśūlapāṇeḥ ||
kathitamiha variṣṭaṃ śrotraramyairvacobhissakalabhuvanamadhye krīḍamānasya nityam || 34 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe dvitīyāyāṃ rudrasaṃhi tāyāṃ paṃ0 yuddhakhaṃḍe bāṇāsuragaṇapatvaprāptivarṇanaṃ nāma ṣaṭpaṃcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ|| 56 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu vyāsa mahāpremṇā caritaṃ śaśimau linaḥ ||
yathā'vadhītriśūlena dānavendraṃ gajāsuram || 1 ||
dānave nihate devyā samare mahiṣāsure ||
devānāṃ ca hitārthāya purā devā sukhaṃ yayuḥ || 2 ||
tasya putro mahāvīro munīśvara gajāsuraḥ ||
piturvadhaṃ hi saṃsmṛtya kṛtaṃ devyā surārthanāt || 3 ||
sa tadvairamanusmṛtyaṃ taporthaṃ gatavānvane ||
samuddiśya

--- Page 412 [gcv] ---
vidhi prītyā tatāpa paramaṃ tapaḥ || 4 ||
avadhyohaṃ bhaviṣyāmi strīpuṃsaiḥ kāmanirjitaiḥ ||
saṃvicāryaiti manasā'bhūttaporatamānasaḥ || 5 ||
sa tepe himavadroṇyāṃ tapaḥ paramadāruṇam ||
ūrddhabāhurnabhodṛṣṭiḥ pādāṃguṣṭhāśritāvaniḥ || 6 ||
jaṭābhāraissa vai reje pralayārka ivāṃśubhiḥ ||
mahiṣāsuraputro' sau gajāsura udāradhīḥ || 7 ||
tasya mūrdhnaḥ samudbhūtassadhūmonnistapomayaḥ ||
tiryagūrdhvamadholokāstāpayanviṣvagīritaḥ || 8 ||
cukṣubhurnadyudanvaṃta śvā'grermūrddhasamudbhavāt ||
nipetussagrahāstārā jajjvaluścadiśo daśa || 9 ||
tena taptāssurāssarve divaṃ tyaktvā savāsavāḥ||
brahmalokaṃ yayurvijñāpayāmā suśvacāla bhūḥ || 10 ||
devā ūcuḥ ||
vidhe gajāsuratapastaptā vayamathā''kulāḥ ||
na śaknumo divi sthātumataste śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ || 11 ||
vidhehyupa śamaṃ tasya cānyāñjīvayituṃ kṛpā ||
lokā naṃkṣyatyanyathā hi satyaṃsatyaṃ bruvāmahe || 12 ||
iti vijñāpito devairvāsavādyaissa ātmabhūḥ ||
bhṛgudakṣādibhi brahmā yayau daityavarāśramam || 13||
tapaṃtaṃ tapasā lokānyathā'bhrāpihitaṃ divi ||
vilakṣya vismitaḥ prāha vihasansṛṣṭikārakaḥ || 14||
brahmovāca ||
uttiṣṭho ttiṣṭhadaityendra tapassiddhosi māhiṣe||
prāpto'haṃ varadastāta varaṃ vṛṇu yathepsitam|| 15||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
utthāyotthāya daityendraīkṣamāṇo dṛśā vibhum ||
gi rā gadgadayā prīto'gṛṇāddevaṃ sa māhiṣiḥ|| 16 ||
gajāsura uvāca ||
namaste devadeveśa yadi dāsyasi me varam |
avadhyo'haṃ bhaveyaṃ vai strīpuṃsaiḥ kāmani rjitaiḥ || 17||
mahābalo mahāvīryo'jeyo devādibhissadā ||
sarveṣāṃ lokapālānāṃ nikhiladdhisubhugvibho || 18 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
evaṃ vṛtaśśa tadhṛtirdānavena sa tena vai ||
prādāttattapasā prīto varaṃ tasya sudurlabham ||19||
evaṃ labdhavaro daityo māhiṣiśca gajāsuraḥ |
suprasannamanāsso'tha svadhāma pratyapadyata ||20||
sa vijitya diśassavāṃ lokāṃśca trīnmahāsuraḥ ||
devāsuramanuṣyendrāngaṃdharva garuḍoragān ||21||
ityādīnnikhilāñjitvā vaśamānī ya viśvajit ||
jahāra lokapālānāṃ sthānāni saha tejasā ||22||
devodyānaśriyā juṣṭamadhyāste sma triviṣṭapam ||
mahendrabhavanaṃ sākṣānnirmitaṃ viśva karmaṇā || 23 ||
tasminmahendrasya gṛhe mahāvalo mahāmanā nirjitaloka ekarāṭ ||
reme'bhivaṃdyāṃtriyugaḥ surādibhiḥ pratāpitairūrjitacaṃḍaśāsanaḥ ||24||
sa itthaṃ nirjitakakubekarāḍ viṣayānpriyān ||
yathopajoṣaṃ bhuṃjāno nātṛpyadajitendriyaḥ || 25 ||
evamaiśvaryamattasya dṛptasyocchāstravartinaḥ ||
kāle vyatīte mahāta pāpabuddhirabhūttataḥ || 26 ||
mahiṣāsuraputro'sau saṃcikkeśa dvijānvarān ||
tāpasānnitarāṃ pṛthvyāṃ dānavassuramardanaḥ || 27 ||
surānnarāṃśca pramathānsarvāñcikkeśa durmatiḥ ||
dharmānvitānviśeṣeṇa pūrvavairamanusmaran || 28 ||
ekasminsamaye tāta dānavo'sau mahābalaḥ ||
agaccha drājadhānī vai śaṃkarasya gajāmuraḥ || 29 ||
samāgate surendre hi mahānkalakalo mune ||
trātatrāteti tatrāsīdānaṃdavanavāsinām || 30 ||
