sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti saṃprārthito devairbhaktarakṣaṇatatparaḥ ||
tatrā''jagāma soraṃ tadbadhakāmanayā haraḥ || 43 ||
āgataṃ taṃ samālokya śaṃkaṭa bhaktavatsalam ||
