yajñeṣu nāśaṃ gacchatsu hatāhārāstatassurāḥ ||
nirbalāssukhajayyāḥ syurnirjiteṣu sureṣvatha || || 12 ||
ahameva bhaviṣyāmi mānyatrijagatīpatiḥ ||
āhariṣyāmi devānāmakṣayāssarvasaṃpadaḥ || 13 ||
nirvekṣyāmi sukhānyeva rājye nihatakaṃṭake ||
iti niścitya durbuddhiḥ punaścititavānkhalaḥ || 14 ||
dvijāḥ kva saṃti bhūyāṃso brahmatejotibṛṃhitāḥ ||
śrutyadhyayanasaṃpannāstapobalasamanvitāḥ|| || 12 ||
bhūyasāṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ tu sthānaṃ vārāṇasī khalu ||
tāmādāvupasaṃhṛtya yāyāṃ tīrthātaraṃ tataḥ || 16||
yatra yatra hi tīrtheṣu yatra yatrāśrameṣu ca ||
saṃti sarve'grajanmānaste mayādyāssamaṃtataḥ ||17||
iti duṃdubhinirhrādo mārtaṃ kṛtvā kulocitām ||
prāpyāpi kāśīṃ durvṛtto māyāvī nyavadhīddijānan || 18 ||
samitkuśānsamādātuṃ yatra yāṃti dvijottamāḥ ||
araṇye tatra tānsarvānsa bhakṣayati durmatiḥ || 19 ||
yathā ko'pi na vettyevaṃ tathā''cchanno'bhava tpunaḥ ||
vane vanecaro bhūtvā yādorūpo jalāśaye || 20 ||
adṛśyarūpī māyāvī devānāmapyagocaraḥ ||
divā ghyānapara stiṣṭhenmunivanmunimadhyagaḥ || || 21 ||
praveśamurajānāṃ ca nirgamaṃ hi vilokayan ||
yāminyāṃ vyāghrarūpeṇā bhakṣayadbrāhmaṇānbahūn || 22 ||
niśśaṃkambhakṣayatyevaṃ na tyajatyapi kīkaśam ||
itthaṃ nipātitāṃstena viprā duṣṭena bhūriśaḥ || 23 ||
ekadā śivarātrau tu bhaktastveko nijoṭaje ||
saparyo deva devasya kṛtvā dhyānasthito'bhavat || 24 ||
sa ca duṃdubhinirhrādo daityendro valadarpitaḥ ||
vyāghrarūpaṃ samāsthāya tamādātuṃ matiṃ dadhe || || 25 ||
taṃ bhaktaṃ dhyānamāpannaṃ dṛḍhacittaṃ śivekṣaṇe ||
kṛtāstramantravinyāsaṃ taṃ krāṃtumaśakanna saḥ || 26 ||
atha sarvagataśśambhujña tvā tasyāśayaṃ haraḥ ||
daityasya duṣṭarūpasya vadhāya vidadhe dhiyam || 27 ||
yāvadāditsati vyāghrastāvadāvirabhūddharaḥ ||
