nataskaṃdhāḥ suvāgbhiste tuṣṭuvurbhaktavatsalam || || 42 ||
devā ūcuḥ ||
jaya śaṃkara deveśa praṇatārtihara prabho ||
etaddudubhinirhrādavadhātrātā vayaṃ surāḥ || 43 ||
sadā rakṣā prakartavyā bhaktānāṃ bhaktavatsala ||
vadhyāḥ khalāśva deveśa tvayā sarveśvara prabho || 44 ||
ityākarṇya vacasteṣāṃ surāṇāṃ parameśvaraḥ ||
tathetyuktvā prasannātmā tasmilḍiṃge layaṃ yayau || 45 ||
savismayāstato devāssvaṃsvaṃ dhāma yayursudā ||
te'pi viprā mahāharṣātpunaryātā yathāgatam || 46 ||
idaṃ caritraṃ paramaṃ vyāghreśvaraṃ samudbhavam ||
śṛṇuyācchrāvayedvāpi paṭhedvā pāṭhayettathā || 47 ||
sarvānkāmānavāpnoti narassvamanasepsitān ||
paratra labhate mokṣaṃ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitaḥ || 48 ||
idamākhyānamatulaṃ śivalīlāmṛtākṣaram ||
svargyaṃ yaśasyamāyuṣyaṃ putrapautrapravarddhanan || 49 ||
paraṃ bhaktipradaṃ dhanyaṃ śivaprītikaraṃ śivam ||
paramajñānadaṃ ramyaṃ vikāraharaṇaṃ param || 50 ||
